NK124(ngo)001:1: // snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos sde'i glegs bam brgya dang nyer gsum pa bzhugs so //
NK124(ngo)001:3: // theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK124(ngo)001:6: dmigs med mi 'byed dbyings kyi nam mkha'i klong yangs la //
NK124(ngo)001:7: 'gag med yul bral rang la 'od stong dkyil 'khor rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:8: sna tshogs lhun grub tsha zer 'gro mang pad mo'i dpal //
NK124(ngo)001:9: sku gsum dbyer med nyin mor byed la mgo bos phyag 'tshal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:10: gdod nas ma skyes rang 'byung ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:11: rang bzhin gsal mdangs ma 'gags lhun grub kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:12: thugs rje'i 'od zer phyogs med kun tu brdal //
NK124(ngo)001:13: thog ma'i kun bzang nyid la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK124(ngo)001:14: skye 'gag gnas gsum mtha' bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:15: ye shes lnga ldan bde chen rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16: sku lnga lhun grub drug pa spyi gzugs can //
NK124(ngo)001:17: gsang bdag rdo rje 'chang chen zhabs la 'dud //
NK124(ngo)001:18: skal bzang 'di la mdzad pa mthar phyin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:19: 'das dang ma byon da ltar dus gsum gyi //
NK124(ngo)001:20: gang 'dul thabs kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:21: bcom ldan thub dbang zhabs la gus pas 'dud //
NK124(ngo)001:22: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:23: skye 'chi bsgres rgud med pa rdo rje'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:24: thugs rje'i phrin las nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:25: mtsho skyes rdo rje'i zhabs la gus pas 'dud //
NK124(ngo)001:26: sangs rgyas bstan pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:27: brgyad khri bzhi stong rgyud lung man ngag bcas //
NK124(ngo)001:28: bka' dang bstan chos nyon mongs tshogs bral ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:29: bstan pa dam chos tshogs la gus pas 'dud //
NK124(ngo)001:30: ma nor lam gnas tshogs kyi zhing gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:31: 'chad brtsod rtsam pa'i bya ba mthar phyin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:32: rig grol gnyis ldan 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:33: dad cing gus pas yid kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:34: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yongs la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK124(ngo)001:35: thabs dang shes rab mdzad pa du ma yis //
NK124(ngo)001:36: sangs rgyas bstan pa mtha' ru chub bar mdzad //
NK124(ngo)001:37: drin chen bla ma rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK124(ngo)001:38: gang zhig las dang skal bar ldan rnams kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:39: tshe gcig mdo sngags bstan pa'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:40: de yang ma nor nges pa'i don mchog phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:41: bstan gnyis chu gter rgya mtsho'i klong yangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:42: zab don yid bzhin rin chen blang nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:43: thos bsam nor gyis dbul ba'i rigs rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:44: dgos 'dod re ba ci ltar tshims gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:45: slar yang nor ldan zab rgyas dbyer med kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:46: gnyis ldan bstan la tshul bzhin bshad sgrub kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:47: bya ba dus 'das 'gro mang sgral phyir bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:48: 'dir gang zag dbang po rab 'bring tha ma rnams kyis 'jug bde zhing rtogs sla ba /
NK124(ngo)001:49: theg pa spyi dang rang gis mtshan nyid ma 'dres
NK124(ngo)001:50: par ston par byed pa mdo' sngags kyis dgongs don
NK124(ngo)001:51: gsal byed nyi 'od rab gsal zhes bya ba'i don
NK124(ngo)001:53: de la spyi don bzhi'i sgo nas ston par byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:54: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:55: ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:56: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:57: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:59: rang bzhin bder gshegs gdul bya yis //
NK124(ngo)001:60: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK124(ngo)001:61: rgyud kyi dbye' ba rnam par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:62: gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo las //
NK124(ngo)001:64: de nas snang ba gzhi dag tu //
NK124(ngo)001:65: lung rig kun las gsal bar bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:68: dam pa bde gshegs kyi zhal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:69: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang sbyar te bshad /
NK124(ngo)001:70: ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba gdul bya lam gyi snang ba dang sbyar te bshad /
NK124(ngo)001:71: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba dang sbyar te bshad /
NK124(ngo)001:72: ces gsungs pa bzhin ston pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:73: dang po gnas tshul shes shing rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:74: gzhi ngos bzung ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:75: rnal ma don gyis kun gazhi'am ye ci bzhin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:79: de nyid la dbang 'byor ba'i 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:81: rig pa'i ngo bo la 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi
NK124(ngo)001:82: dri mas ma gos shing 'khrul grol gyi mtha' dang
NK124(ngo)001:83: bral te / gshis skye ba med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:85: mtshan nyid gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin rigs dang phyogs su ma lhung ba /
NK124(ngo)001:86: 'dus ma byas shing gzhan rkyen gyis sgyur du med
NK124(ngo)001:87: pa chos nyid brdal khyab chen po'i rang bzhin du
NK124(ngo)001:88: gnas pa'o // rgyud gsang snying las /
NK124(ngo)001:89: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:90: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK124(ngo)001:91: mtshan med ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK124(ngo)001:92: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:93: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK124(ngo)001:94: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:97: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid de //
NK124(ngo)001:98: yod ni gcig las med pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:99: byung ni rnam pa gnyis su byung //
NK124(ngo)001:100: khyab ni snod bcud kun la khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:102: yin ni chos kyi sku yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:103: bstan du mtshan ma'i dngos po med //
NK124(ngo)001:104: mthong du dmigs pa'i yul las 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:105: mtshon du mtshungs pa gang yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:108: 'gro drug dus nas gser bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:109: rang byung ye shes tha dad med //
NK124(ngo)001:112: thog mar bstan pa'i don nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:113: dkyil 'khor gsum po dbyer med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:114: shes bya kun gyi gzhir gnas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:115: thams cad ngo bo mnyam pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:118: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen po //
NK124(ngo)001:119: sangs rgyas pas kyang nga sngar rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:122: chos rnams kun gyi chos nyid ma bcos ma slad
NK124(ngo)001:123: snying po byang chub tu yes nas gnas pa de
NK124(ngo)001:124: la / ye ci bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas zhes su gtags so //
NK124(ngo)001:127: gzhi rang byung gi ston pa kun tu bzang po 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:128: chos sku gdod ma nas rang byung gi ye shes su sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:129: de nyid 'khrul ma myong lam sgrod kyang ma myong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:130: gnas lugs rang sa zin nas /
NK124(ngo)001:131: ye shes dang che ba'i yon tan thams cad gdod ma nas rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:132: de nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi myes po yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:133: sangs rgyas thams cad de las byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:134: lung man ngag rig pa gsum gyis sgrub pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:136: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes gting rdzogs kyi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:137: rang byung ston pa kun bzang thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:138: phyogs rigs ma na nged pa'i shar //
NK124(ngo)001:140: 'od gsal rig pa'i bstan pa sgrog /
NK124(ngo)001:143: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:144: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
NK124(ngo)001:148: nga rtogs kun tu bzang po 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:151: gang yang med pa'i gong rol du //
NK124(ngo)001:152: rang byung ngo bo kun gyi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:153: lung la ma brten man ngag chos //
NK124(ngo)001:154: rang gis rig pas rang rtog phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:155: 'khrul ma myong la rtogs ma myong //
NK124(ngo)001:159: sems can ma 'khrul sangs rgyas med pa'i gong //
NK124(ngo)001:160: ngo bo nyid kyi sku la rang byung rig /
NK124(ngo)001:161: de nyid ma 'khrul gnas lugs yin pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:162: de rtogs chos sku mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:163: kun tu bzang po ye shes rang byung thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:164: rang sems rang gis rig pa chos kyi rnyed //
NK124(ngo)001:166: sangs rgyas thog ma bcad pa'i man ngag las /
NK124(ngo)001:167: rang byung ngo bo kun gyi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:169: ye nas ye shes rnam drug gis //
NK124(ngo)001:170: gzhi gnas ma rig med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:171: rkyen gyis sngar 'khrul ma myong bas //
NK124(ngo)001:172: lung ldan gyis ni bstan mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:173: sangs rgyas kun gyi chos sku zhes //
NK124(ngo)001:175: dga' rab rdo rje'i man ngag snying sgron las //
NK124(ngo)001:176: rang byung ston pa kun bzang rgyal ba'i yab //
NK124(ngo)001:177: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:179: 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas de nyid med na /
NK124(ngo)001:180: gzhi 'khor ba'i mthar thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:181: dang po ston mkhan gyi sangs rgyas med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:182: rtogs pa'i thabs lam med pa la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:183: gzhan yang de nyid kyi sgrub byed mang du yod pas gzigs par 'tshal /
NK124(ngo)001:184: gnyis pa spyi gzhi la gsum /
NK124(ngo)001:192: zhor las klong gi 'jig rten grol lugs tshul bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:193: gong gis 'khrul ma myong gi dgongs don de nyid ma rtogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:194: rig pa 'gag nas yid du 'gyus pa'i dus su /
NK124(ngo)001:195: rig pa rang 'od kyi mdangs kha dog lngar /
NK124(ngo)001:196: dbyibs rnam par dag pa'i sgron me thugs rje'i klong du shar ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:197: rang byung gi dkyil 'khor chen po rang snang la /
NK124(ngo)001:198: yul ma sgrib pa chos kyi dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK124(ngo)001:199: chen por ma skyed gzhi la rdzogs pa'i sku snang
NK124(ngo)001:201: der mthong ba'i yul la rig pa shar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:202: de yang mkhyen pa gsum dang bcas nas sangs rgyas te /
NK124(ngo)001:205: ngo bo'i mkhyen pa ni gzhi rdzogs chos kyi sku'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK124(ngo)001:206: rang bzhin lhun grub rtogs pas sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:207: gnyis pa thugs rje'i mkhyen pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:208: sprul pa gzugs sku sna tshogs su 'char nus pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:209: gsung gi mkhyen pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK124(ngo)001:210: chos nyid don dam gyi gsung la 'gags sgrib med par mkhyen no //
NK124(ngo)001:211: thugs rje sna tshogs kyi chos ston pa mkhyen no //
NK124(ngo)001:212: de yang mkhyen pa gsum mkhyen nas sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:213: thob tu med pa'i 'bras bu thob //
NK124(ngo)001:214: rgya ru med pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:215: 'da' ru med pa'i mya ngan la 'das so //
NK124(ngo)001:216: de yang rdzogs klong gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:217: thog ma'i sangs rgyas 'od mi gyur ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:218: zhes pa la sogs rgya cher gsungs kyang 'dir mang du ma spros so //
NK124(ngo)001:219: 'di la bshad gzhi mang du 'dug pas spros pa la dgyes pa rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:220: rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung la gzigs mdzod /
NK124(ngo)001:222: theg pa rang rang gi skabs nas ston par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:223: gnyis pa 'khrul gzhi rgyas par bshad pa 'og nas 'khrul gzhi'i skabs su ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:226: gzhi'i ngo bo mtshan nyid dang //
NK124(ngo)001:227: nges tshigs nges pa'i rnam pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:228: snang tshul gnyer gyi rtogs par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:231: gnas pa'i ngo bo mtshon pa'i nges //
NK124(ngo)001:232: nges tshigs rnam grangs dgos ched dang //
NK124(ngo)001:233: rang bzhin mtshan nyid gnas pa'i dus //
NK124(ngo)001:242: ye nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:243: gzhi gtan la dbab pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:244: the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:246: chos kun ye nas sel med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:247: sems nyid rang byung ye shes rang snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:249: sems can sangs rgyas la mos pa //
NK124(ngo)001:250: thams cad ma lus lus pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:251: rang rig ma rig rtog pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:252: kun kyang rang byung ye shes yin //
NK124(ngo)001:255: rang sems ngo bo nyid kyi lhun grub ni //
NK124(ngo)001:256: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba rang rig sku //
NK124(ngo)001:257: de nyid ye shes chos skur lta ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:258: rgyal ba'i thugs nas dmyal ba yan chad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:259: kun gyi gzhi ni rang byung ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:263: ngo bo thams cad sems yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:264: gser gyi dpe' bzhin gnyis su med //
NK124(ngo)001:267: phyi nang bye rag ci rnyed pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:268: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK124(ngo)001:269: ci bzhin ngang du ye gnas pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:270: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK124(ngo)001:273: sems can bsam pa sangs rgyas dgongs pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:274: chos nyid gcig pu gzhan ni ci yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:275: ces pa la sogs rgyud lung man ngag du ma nas gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:276: des na 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis sdus pa'i chos kun /
NK124(ngo)001:277: ci ltar snang yang sel med sems nyid rang byung
NK124(ngo)001:278: gi ye shes rang snang ba de nyid kun gyi
NK124(ngo)001:279: gzhi yin no // gnyis pa mtshan nyid ni /
NK124(ngo)001:280: chos kun ci ltar snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:281: rang snang mtha' bral chen po rang byung ye shes las mi 'da' bar 'dzin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:283: mtshan nyid brjod mtha' kun bral bas //
NK124(ngo)001:284: cir yang snang la gzung du med //
NK124(ngo)001:287: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:288: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:289: rang gi mtshan nyid rang gi 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:290: thams cad rig pa rang gi stobs //
NK124(ngo)001:293: 'khor 'das thams cad 'byung zhing 'dus pas gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:295: ma bcos ye nas kun gyi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:296: rang byung ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:297: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba'i gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:298: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung //
NK124(ngo)001:302: nam mkha' rgya mtsho rin chen sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:303: nye ba'i dpe yi mtshon pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:306: cung zad mthun pa'i dpe bzung na 'di lta ste /
NK124(ngo)001:312: mngon par spro ba bzhi lta bu lags so //
NK124(ngo)001:313: gzhan yang dbus mtha' med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:316: lung pa'i dbyibs lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:317: cir yang snang las de nyid las mi g.yo bas rgya mtsho dang rlabs lta bu la sogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:318: gong gis des rnams dgrol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:321: sems de yes nas sangs rgyas la //
NK124(ngo)001:322: de min lta ba zlog pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:323: gnyis med rtogs dang sangs rgyas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:324: bdag nyid lhun grub chos dbyings dang //
NK124(ngo)001:325: byang chub chos nyid stong bsam 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:326: de bzhin nyid dang skye 'gags med //
NK124(ngo)001:327: bla dag tsam du brjod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:330: byang sems lhun grub bde chen dang //
NK124(ngo)001:331: rang snang dbu' ma mnyam pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:332: rdzogs pa chen po chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:333: gnyis med bsam 'das ma bcos grags //
NK124(ngo)001:334: ming grangs rgyal ba brjod las 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:336: chos kun rang byung ye shes las gzhan gyi sel med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:338: mnyam pa nyid la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:339: de'i mtha' gang du yang ma lhung bas sangs /
NK124(ngo)001:340: mtha' thams cad du ma 'gag par rang shar bas yes nas rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:341: chos rnams rig pa rang snang la gzhan sel med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:342: de nyid du 'dus pas bdag nyid chen po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:343: rig pa mu mtha' med pa chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK124(ngo)001:344: bcos slad med pas chos nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:346: mtshan ma med pas stong nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:347: rgyu rkyen gnyen po med pas skye 'gag med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:348: kun la khyab cing ma sgrib pas rang gsal bas rang byung ye shes dang /
NK124(ngo)001:349: rtsol ba med pa'i cir yang snang bas byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK124(ngo)001:350: rtsol med cir yang snang bas rang snang dang /
NK124(ngo)001:351: rgyu rkyen gyis ma skyed pas 'dus ma byas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:352: sems nyid la sel med pas rnam dag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:353: mtha' dang bral bas dbu' ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:354: don 'gyur ba med pas bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:355: thams cad rig par 'dus pas thig le nyag gcig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:356: thams cad rang byung ye shes su 'dus shing gong na gzhan med pas rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:357: phyogs gcig gang yang ma 'dres la phyogs med du yongs su rdzogs pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs so //
NK124(ngo)001:358: de la sogs pa ming gi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsungs la /
NK124(ngo)001:359: de rnams kyang rgyu mtshan phyogs rer brtag pas gang yang mi 'gal zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:360: de nyid rtogs pa'i thabs kyi rnam grangs su shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:362: rgyud lung man ngag du ma nas ston pas lta bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:365: ming gi rnam grangs su btags pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:368: ma nor ba de bzhin nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:372: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbyings dang /
NK124(ngo)001:377: theg pa chen po zhes su grags //
NK124(ngo)001:381: rgyu rkyen bcos slad med par chos kun rig pa rang snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:383: ma bcos rgyun gyi skad cig ma //
NK124(ngo)001:384: de yis ma byas gang yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:387: sna tshogs snang ba gzhan byung min //
NK124(ngo)001:388: rang byung rang snang ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:391: gcig po 'khor 'das kun gyi dngos gzhi ste //
NK124(ngo)001:392: ngo bo de nyid rtogs dang ma rtogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:393: byed pa med par rang nyid cir yang snang //
NK124(ngo)001:396: dus gsum thog mtha' med pa'i mnyam nyid chen por gnas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:398: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK124(ngo)001:399: sngon med phyis med gdod nas byung //
NK124(ngo)001:402: thog ma tha ma med pa ru //
NK124(ngo)001:403: byung bas snga phyi yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:406: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid la sngon gyi mtha' mi dmigs /
NK124(ngo)001:408: da lta ba yang mi dmigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:409: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:410: brgyad pa gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas pa ni gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:411: dgu pa gzhi gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:412: de ltar lung man ngag rig pa gsum gyis gtan la phab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:413: shes bya'i gting phyin pa rtogs ste /
NK124(ngo)001:416: rang grol mngon sum du rtogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:418: rang sems tshad ma'i gdeng ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:419: mi gyur don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK124(ngo)001:420: lung rig don gyi bya ra bas //
NK124(ngo)001:421: log rtog rkun bu rdul du rlog /
NK124(ngo)001:424: lung dang man ngag gnyer dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:425: blo gdings yid ches 'gyur ba bya //
NK124(ngo)001:427: bcu pa the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba la lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:428: so so skye bo'i snang ba 'di chos nyid yin nam min dang /
NK124(ngo)001:429: gshis ka dag yin nam lhun grub yin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:432: rgyud gcig gam tha dad kyi brtag pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:434: snang ba 'di chos nyid yin min la sogs pa gnad gcig tu shes par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:441: yin par 'dod pa la skyon bkal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:443: gshis stong zhing bdag med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:444: ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub cing /
NK124(ngo)001:445: shes brjod gzhal bya la 'das pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:446: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis su med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:447: dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:448: dngos po mtshan ma'i sel med par 'dod la /
NK124(ngo)001:449: 'gro drug gi snang ba 'di kun rdzob bam /
NK124(ngo)001:450: 'khrul pa'i snang ba brdzun par 'dod de chos nyid min /
NK124(ngo)001:451: bye brag tu yo ga man chad rang rang gi
NK124(ngo)001:452: 'dod zhen gyis lta ba phyogs re la dam par
NK124(ngo)001:453: lta zhing / snang ba 'di 'khrul snang rdzun pa chos nyid ma yin par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:454: rang rang gi skabs nas ston pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:455: yang gsang sngags nang pa'i drang don phyogs re la dam pa lta zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:456: dgongs pa'i don ma lon pas snang ba rdzun par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:457: gnyis pa chos nyid yin na skyon bskal ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:459: lung man ngag rig pa gsum dang 'gal te /
NK124(ngo)001:460: lung ni theg pa'i lung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:463: thams cad snang ba de gsang sngags ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:464: gal te gsang sngags yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:465: gsang sngags zhes brjod pa de nyid dang 'gal te /
NK124(ngo)001:467: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dbyer med par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:471: spyir ni log rtog bsam yas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:472: ye nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:473: so sor 'dzin rtogs bag chags kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:474: gzung 'dzin dra bas sgrib gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:475: cir yang med la cir yang snang //
NK124(ngo)001:476: don gyi snying po nyid la gol //
NK124(ngo)001:479: dngos kun log rtog tsam nyid las //
NK124(ngo)001:480: phra tsam skad tsam yin pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:481: 'khrul ba'i snang ba zhes su gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:482: zhes pa la sogs pa chos nyid min pa'i lung rnams dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:484: 'gro drug gis bden pa mthong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:485: 'khrul pa'i snang ba rgyun chad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:486: gsang sngags kyi nges tshigs med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:487: chos nyid skye 'jig can du 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:489: 'gro drug gi snang ba 'di chos nyid yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:490: 'gro drug gi bden pa sngon nas mthong bar bya rigs te /
NK124(ngo)001:491: des na lam gyi chos gtan mi dgos par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:493: 'gro drug ma 'khrul zhing 'bad rtsol med par grol zin pa la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:495: chos nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:497: snang ba chos nyid yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:498: 'khrul pa'i snang ba rgyun chad par 'gro ste /
NK124(ngo)001:500: 'khor ba dong sprugs par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:505: gsang ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:506: smrar mi rung spros bral du ma 'gyur pa la bya /
NK124(ngo)001:508: yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas su brjod pa la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:510: snang ba ni smra brjod dang /
NK124(ngo)001:511: spros bral du gyur par 'dug cing /
NK124(ngo)001:513: gsang sngags kyi nges tshig med do //
NK124(ngo)001:515: 'khrul snang gi skabs su yang rgyas par bshad pas gsal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:516: gnyis pa la phyog zhen du 'dod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:517: ma rtogs pa'i dus su chos nyid min la /
NK124(ngo)001:518: rtogs pa'i dus su yin par 'dod pa dang ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas min la /
NK124(ngo)001:519: yongs rdzogs kyi dus su yin par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:520: ngo bo'i bdag nyid gcig pa'i ngos nas yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:521: mtshon tshul tha dad pa'i ngos nas min par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:523: dang po ma rtogs pa'i dus su min pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:524: rtogs pa'i dus su yin pa gnyis gang bden /
NK124(ngo)001:525: snga ma bden na phyi ma 'gal la /
NK124(ngo)001:526: phyi ma bden na snga ma 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:527: gnyis ka bden par mi 'thad de /
NK124(ngo)001:528: gzhi gcig la yin min gnyis 'gal ba mi rigs /
NK124(ngo)001:529: yang ma rtogs pa'i dus chos nyid min na /
NK124(ngo)001:530: rtogs pa'i dus chos nyid yin par 'gal te /
NK124(ngo)001:531: de rtogs pa ma yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:533: gnyis pa ma rig pa de yongs rdzogs yin nam min /
NK124(ngo)001:534: min na yongs rdzogs kyi nges tshig med la /
NK124(ngo)001:536: yin na ma rig pa'i ngos nas min pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:537: yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas kyang yin par 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:538: yin na yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas yin pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:539: ma rig pa'i ngos nas yin par 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:541: ma rig pa nyid yongs rdzogs yin pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:543: mtshon tshul de ngo bo'i mtshon tshul yin nam min /
NK124(ngo)001:544: min na ngo bo gcig pa'i dam bca' dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:546: ngo bo'i mtshon tshul min pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:547: ngo bo gcig kyang mtshon tshul tha dad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:548: chos nyid min na ci lta te khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK124(ngo)001:549: mtshon tshul de la ngo bos khyab par 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:550: gser la bya ba'i rgyan sna tshogs la /
NK124(ngo)001:552: gser ma yin pa 'gro ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:553: gsum pa yin par 'dod pa'i lugs gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:555: de la the tshom gyi skyon spang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:557: lha rje sgro phug pa'i gsungs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:558: 'gro drug gi snang ba rang kha ma 'di /
NK124(ngo)001:559: ma spang pa'i ngos nas chos nyid min la /
NK124(ngo)001:560: mi ldan pa'i ngos nas chos nyid yin gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:561: de yang 'gro drug gi snang tshul ci ltar snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:562: chos nyid rang snang yin pas ma spang ba zhes bya ba yin /
NK124(ngo)001:563: 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di kho na ltar rang rgyud du mi gnas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:564: mi ldan pa zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:565: brda' don sprad pa'i dbang du phye ba yin gsungs skad do //
NK124(ngo)001:566: slob dpon rin po che'i zhal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:568: rang byung gi ye shes su rang snang bas /
NK124(ngo)001:569: chos nyid du ma gyur ba'i chos gcig kyang med de /
NK124(ngo)001:570: 'gro drug gi snang ba so ma nyams pa 'di rang chos nyid yin gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:571: de yang gong gi gzhi'i ngo bo dang rnam grangs la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:572: gnyis pa the tshom gyi skyon bsal ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:573: chos nyid min pa'i skyon bskal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:574: chos nyid min na slar skyon brjod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:575: yin par gtan la phab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:577: lung man ngag dang 'gal ba'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:578: min par gsungs pa ni snang ba'i mtha' la mi gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:579: ma rtogs 'khrul pa la dgongs nas gsungs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:580: des na snang ba chos nyid yin par nges pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:583: gnas brtan rab 'byor gyi bstan te 'gal ba med do //
NK124(ngo)001:584: gang mi 'gal ba'i rnam par mi 'gal ba de
NK124(ngo)001:585: gnas brtan rab 'byor gyis bstan te 'gal ba med
NK124(ngo)001:586: do // zhes pa nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar du gsungs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:588: don gyi rang rig ngo bo gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:589: bdag nyid mngon sum yin pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:590: tshad ma rnams kyis brtag bya gang //
NK124(ngo)001:591: ma mthong cha gzhan ci zhig yod //
NK124(ngo)001:594: gal te snang ba gsang sngags ma yin zhes pa'i rjes la /
NK124(ngo)001:595: de las gzhan na yang gsang sngags yod pa ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:596: gal te de las gzhan pa gcig gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK124(ngo)001:597: thams cad chos nyid du ma 'dus par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:598: thams cad kyi rang bzhin mi snang ba de yang gsang sngags ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:599: gal te mi snang ba de gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK124(ngo)001:600: gzhan mu chad pa nyid kyang yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:602: des na gsang sngags ni snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:604: log rtog nyid las nyid spyod de //
NK124(ngo)001:605: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:606: log rtog rgyu las rkyen nyid kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:607: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK124(ngo)001:608: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:612: yul dang shes par snang ba yang //
NK124(ngo)001:613: rang byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK124(ngo)001:616: rgyu rkyen las kyis ma byas pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:617: gser gong las byas rdzas rnams kun //
NK124(ngo)001:619: rig pa dang 'gal ba'i skyon yang mi 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:620: dang po la 'gro drug gis bden pa mthong ba 'gro ces pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:621: gshis kyi tshul nas mthong bar 'gro zer ram /
NK124(ngo)001:622: nges pa'i shes pa dang bcas nas mthong bar 'gro zer /
NK124(ngo)001:625: rang byung ye shes mngon sum snang dus nas //
NK124(ngo)001:626: rang byung ye shes de nyid mthong zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:629: dbang po cer mthong chos nyid gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:630: snang ba rgya yan rig pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:632: mthong na sems can thams cad grol bar 'gyur zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:633: mthong ba tsam zhig 'dug kyang nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pas grol bar mi 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:634: snang la ma nges pa'i shes pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:635: de skad byas pa la mthong ba rang gi nges shes dgos zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:636: 'o na mthong ba rang gi nges shes skye na /
NK124(ngo)001:637: log rtog 'khrul pa rgyun chad pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:640: mthong ba tsam gyi 'dug kyang nges par ma byas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:642: kun gzhi snang ba gnyis bral te //
NK124(ngo)001:643: rtag tu rang mtshan mthong gyur kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:644: gzhan la snang ba ma gyur pas //
NK124(ngo)001:645: mig gis mig bzhin ma shes pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:648: grong khyer gsum gyis sems can rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:649: thabs dang lhan cig mi gnas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:650: bden pa mthong yang nges ma byas //
NK124(ngo)001:651: mthong yang ma mthong 'dra bar gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:653: gnyis pa chos nyid yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:654: 'gro drug gis ngo shes nas 'dug pa'i bya ri zer na /
NK124(ngo)001:656: ngo ma shes pa'i bya ri ma 'khrul bar 'gro zer /
NK124(ngo)001:658: gtan tshigs ma grub te gong du bstan pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:660: ngo ma shes pa kas 'khrul pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:661: 'khrul pa rgyun chad pa'i skyon mi 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:662: 'o na snang ba 'di rang 'khrul snang yin nam /
NK124(ngo)001:664: snang ba 'di chos nyid rang snang las gzhan snang sel med pa la chos nyid yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:666: bka' bzhin rig pa yang gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:668: gsang sngags kyi nges tshigs med pa'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:669: snang ba 'di chos nyid phyogs rer yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:670: yul rtog pa phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyi smra brjod dang /
NK124(ngo)001:671: spros bral du ma gyur pas gsang zhes bya la /
NK124(ngo)001:672: de rtogs nas yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i phyir sngags zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:673: des na gsang sngags su ma gyur pa ni gcig kyang med do //
NK124(ngo)001:675: gsang sngags kyis ma khyab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:677: gsang sngags su ma gyur pa'i chos ni gang yang med do //
NK124(ngo)001:680: chos nyid skye 'jig can du thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon sel ni /
NK124(ngo)001:681: gong gi stong thun gyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:682: spyi don gnyis pa chos nyid min na /
NK124(ngo)001:683: lung man ngag rig pa gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:684: lung man ngag gong gi chos nyid yin pa'i skabs ltar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:686: snang ba chos nyid min na chos nyid chad par 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:687: mu mtha' can du 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:688: grol bar mi gyur ba la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:689: chos nyid mngon sum du rtogs pa rgyun chad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:690: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang 'khrul par 'gro ba la sogs pa'i skyon du ma 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:692: 'gro drug gi snang ba 'di chos nyid min na /
NK124(ngo)001:693: stong pa chos nyid yin nam min /
NK124(ngo)001:694: min na snang stong gnyis ka chos nyid min pas /
NK124(ngo)001:695: chos nyid ces bya ba gtan pa mi bden par 'agro'o //
NK124(ngo)001:696: yin na chos nyid de chad pa'i mthar 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:698: snang ba chos nyid min la /
NK124(ngo)001:699: stong pa chos nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:700: 'dod na mu stegs chad pa bden par 'gro ba'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:701: gnyis pa snang ba chos nyid min na /
NK124(ngo)001:702: stong pa'ang chos nyid min par 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:704: chos nyid gtan mi srid pa la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:706: snang stong gnyis ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:708: snang ba dngos po rang rgyud par 'gro ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:709: khyab pa 'di snang stong dbyer med pas grub ste /
NK124(ngo)001:710: chu nang gi zla ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:711: yang snang chos kyi min kyang stong pa chos nyid yin na ci lto ste na /
NK124(ngo)001:712: snang ba dang chos nyid tha dad par 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:714: snang ba 'di chos nyid min pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:716: chos nyid mtha' bral ma yin par 'gro ba'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:717: gsum pa 'gro drug gi snang ba chos nyid min na /
NK124(ngo)001:718: lung man ngag gis ci tsam gtan la phab kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:719: chos nyid rang mi rtogs par 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:720: 'gro drug gis lam nyams su blangs kyang grol ba rgyun chad par 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:722: lung man ngag gis gtan la phab pa don med par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:724: 'gro drug gis snang ba chos nyid min pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:725: chos nyid min kyang rtogs na ci lto zhes na /
NK124(ngo)001:726: lung man ngag dngos po skyed byed du thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:727: rtogs pa ma yin cing log shes su thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:729: chos nyid min na mngon sum rtogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:730: bden pa mthong ba rgyun chad par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:732: chos byas pa don med par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:734: snang ba chos nyid min pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:735: snang ba chos nyid min kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:736: stong pa mthong bas cos nyid mthong ngo zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:738: mthong mkhan kyang med pa'i skyon dang /
NK124(ngo)001:739: bden pa mthong ba yan chad kyis snang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:740: mdzad pa rnam par 'khrul par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon du ma 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:741: lnga pa snang ba chos nyid min cing 'khrul pa yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:742: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang 'khrul par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon du ma 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:743: des na snang ba chos nyid du mi 'dod pa rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:744: rang don phyogs re mngon par zhen cing /
NK124(ngo)001:745: chos nyid kyi don ma rtogs par phyogs 'dzin gyis rgyar chud de /
NK124(ngo)001:746: gsang sngags kyi dgongs pa'i don ma go bar /
NK124(ngo)001:747: mun pa'i klong nas spar tshod bgyis pa dang 'dra ste /
NK124(ngo)001:749: lhun grub phyogs med ma rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:750: lta ba'i 'dod gzhung du ma byung //
NK124(ngo)001:751: blo dang chos su ma 'dres pas //
NK124(ngo)001:752: mnyam nyid mtha' la phyogs su zhen //
NK124(ngo)001:753: kun rig shes pa ma skyes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:754: ris med gcig la ris su gcod //
NK124(ngo)001:755: rang byung ye shes ma shar bas //
NK124(ngo)001:756: mun pa'i klong nas tshod kyis 'jal //
NK124(ngo)001:758: spyi don gsum pa chos nyid yin par gtan la phab pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:759: lung man ngag rig pa gsum las /
NK124(ngo)001:760: lung man ngag ni gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:762: 'gro drug gis snang ba 'di chos nyid rang snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:763: gshis chos nyid las gzhan pa'i chos gcig kyang med pa'i phyir dang /
NK124(ngo)001:764: ma rtogs te 'khrul pa yin pa'i phyir ro dang /
NK124(ngo)001:765: gtan tshigs ma grub bo zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:767: 'gro drug gi snang ba ni chos nyid min na /
NK124(ngo)001:768: 'gro drug gis lam nyams su blangs kyang grol thar ba rgyun chad pa'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:770: 'khrul pa yin kyang gshis chos nyid yin na ci lto te /
NK124(ngo)001:771: khyab pa ma grub bo zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:772: 'khrul pa'i rgyu mtshan med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:773: thag pa khra bo sbrul du 'dzin pa 'khrul yang /
NK124(ngo)001:774: 'khrul gzhi thag pa khra bo ma yin pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:775: des na gshis chos nyid yin pa /
NK124(ngo)001:777: ma rtogs 'khrul pa kas gshis chos nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:778: de ltar yin pas gnyis su med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:779: gnyis med yin pa'i gnad kyis mnyam pa ris med dang /
NK124(ngo)001:780: blang dor gnyis su med pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:781: yang 'gro drug gi snang ba ni chos nyid rang snang phyogs med yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:782: snang ba gcig la snang tshul bcu la sogs pa 'char ba'i ri dang /
NK124(ngo)001:783: phyogs su 'dzin pa 'khrul pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:784: gtan tshigs log pa 'di gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:785: des na chos sam chos nyid rang snang yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:786: snang ba chos nyid du 'dod cing rdzogs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:787: gsang sngags kyi dgongs pa'i phul rdzogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:788: chos nyid la phyogs ris med pa mnyam pa nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:792: gol dus gol ba med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:794: phyogs med lhun grub stong pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:796: bya bral 'dzin med nam mkha' la //
NK124(ngo)001:797: sku gsum snying po'i nyi zla shar //
NK124(ngo)001:799: bde chen sangs rgyas zhing khams yin //
NK124(ngo)001:800: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i myu gu la //
NK124(ngo)001:801: bde chen chos sku'i 'bras bu smin //
NK124(ngo)001:803: thig le nyag gcig kun bral bas //
NK124(ngo)001:804: gnyis su bral ba'i tha snyad bral //
NK124(ngo)001:805: bya bral gcig tu kun tu kun rdzogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:806: re dogs mtha' bral btsal mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:807: dor ba bya ba'i skyon med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:808: blang ba'i yon tan ga la yod //
NK124(ngo)001:810: gnyis pa gshis ka dag yin nam lhun grub yin gyi brtag pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:811: rgyu mtshan phyogs re gang yang mi 'gal bar bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:812: phyogs rer bzung bas gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:813: rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas dbye ba bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:815: ka dag dang lhun grub la sogs pa rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas mtshon pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:816: ming du btags pas gang yang mi 'gal bar shes par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:818: khyad par ci yang mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:820: mi rtag par yang zung zhig /
NK124(ngo)001:824: tha dad pa yang zung zhig /
NK124(ngo)001:825: gcig dang tha dad kyi ngo bo las grol bar yang zung zhig /
NK124(ngo)001:828: don gyis dbyings las ma g.yos par //
NK124(ngo)001:829: rang bzhin rnam dag rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:830: lhun gyis grub pas go 'phangs gcod //
NK124(ngo)001:831: nges pa med par gtan la 'beb //
NK124(ngo)001:832: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:833: gang yang ma spang lhun gyis grub //
NK124(ngo)001:834: cir yang ma 'gag nges pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:835: gang la mi gnas rnam par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:836: rnam dag gcig gis kun byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:837: chos sku rnam par dag pa'i dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:838: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:839: cir yang ma 'gag nges pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:840: gang du mi gnas rnam par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:841: gang yang ma spang lhun gyis grub //
NK124(ngo)001:842: lhun grub gcig gis kun byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:843: chos rnams lhun gyis grub pa'i dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:844: rang bzhin nges pa med pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:845: gang yang ma spang lhun gyis grub //
NK124(ngo)001:846: gang du mi gnas rnam par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:847: cir yang 'char bas nges pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:848: nges med gcig gis kun byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:849: thams cad nges pa med pa'i dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:850: dbyings nyid gcig la der snang bas //
NK124(ngo)001:852: sangs rgyas bstan pa ma lus la //
NK124(ngo)001:853: mthar thug snying po 'di las med //
NK124(ngo)001:857: yod mtha' grol phyir med ces bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:858: med mtha' dgrol phyir yod ces bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:859: gnyis 'dzin dgrol phyir nyag gcig bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:860: nyag gcig dgrol phyir spros bral bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:861: spros bral dgrol phyir brjod med bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:862: brjod med dgrol phyir kha 'byam bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:864: ci ltar nam mkha'i mdung skor bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:865: gang ltar skor kyang dkor du btub //
NK124(ngo)001:866: ci ltar 'dam gyi phur pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:867: gang ltar sgul kyang sgul du btub //
NK124(ngo)001:868: lpags pa rlon pa'i sla bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:871: gnyis pa phyogs su 'dzin pa'i gol ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:872: gong ltar chos nyid phyogs med gang yang mi 'gal
NK124(ngo)001:873: bar ston pa'i lung rnams la phyogs re bzung nas
NK124(ngo)001:874: / dka' bas dag pa rang med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:875: stong pa log phyogs su bzung nas chos nyid kyi don ma rtogs par /
NK124(ngo)001:876: snang ba dang yod pa dang lhun grub la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:877: pa la skyon du lta zhing bkag pas gol ba
NK124(ngo)001:878: yin te / nya mo bag la nyal ba'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:879: ye shes dbyings su sus rtogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:880: de ni 'khrul pa'i rgyun pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:883: dbyings dang ye shes tha snyad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:884: rang byung rig pa'i don dang 'gal //
NK124(ngo)001:885: ye shes kun kyang 'dus byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:886: rgyud de rang byung don mi mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:887: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:888: ma grub pas grub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:890: dngos po log pa'i phyogs su bzung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:891: 'khrul grol gyi shan ma phyed par bka' log pa
NK124(ngo)001:892: skyon du ltas shing bkag pas gol ba yin te
NK124(ngo)001:894: gang yang sems yin lhun grub 'dod pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:895: phyi nang chos rnams sems su blos stub pas //
NK124(ngo)001:896: dbang po yul las phyir phyir rang sems 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:897: sems tsam ka ta red pa'i lta ba gol //
NK124(ngo)001:899: thal drag gong rgal lhun grub 'dod pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:900: chos can kha kar rdzas gcig gang rung la //
NK124(ngo)001:901: 'khor 'das dus gsum tshang bar rdzogs 'dod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:902: gcig la gcig med grangs can lta bar gol //
NK124(ngo)001:903: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:904: des na ka dag lhun grub log pa'i lung phyogs
NK124(ngo)001:905: re ba thams cad chos nyid phyogs med gtan la
NK124(ngo)001:908: kun gyis bdag nyid yin pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:909: phyogs su lta ba 'grub pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:911: gsum pa rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas phye ba la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:912: dang po ka dag pa ni chos kyi dbyings la gzhan gyis sel med pas dbyings ka dag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:913: chos kun rang byung ye shes kyi sku dang ye
NK124(ngo)001:914: shes su rang snang bas ye shes ka dag dang
NK124(ngo)001:915: / dag pa dang ma dag pa gnyis su med pa la dag pa chen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:917: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:918: rnam dag lam chen kun grol phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:921: phyi dang nang kun chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:922: rnam par dag pa'i sprul po las //
NK124(ngo)001:923: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med //
NK124(ngo)001:924: lam gyis bcos su ga la yod //
NK124(ngo)001:927: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:928: de bzhin nyid du rdo rje'i rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:931: log par rtog brtag rnam dag cing //
NK124(ngo)001:934: yul dang shes par snang ba yang //
NK124(ngo)001:935: rang 'byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK124(ngo)001:937: thams cad bdag ces bya ba yang //
NK124(ngo)001:938: dngos po gsal dag ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:939: snang spyod nyid nas rnam par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:940: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:941: sna tshogs ris su ma chad pas chos can lhun grub dang /
NK124(ngo)001:942: gnas lugs phyogs la ma zhen pas chos nyid lhun grub dang /
NK124(ngo)001:943: sgra ci bzhin pa ma yin pas thun mong ma yin pa'i lhun grub bo //
NK124(ngo)001:945: chos can gcig la snang ba lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:946: chos can gcig la 'khor 'das lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:947: chos can gcig la dus gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:948: chos can chos nyid du lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:949: de yang tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma spang pa'i dbyer med dam /
NK124(ngo)001:950: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i lhun grub yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:952: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:953: de nyid rgya chad dang snang ba gang yang ma
NK124(ngo)001:954: spangs pa'i rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa yin pas
NK124(ngo)001:955: / tha dad kyis snang ba gang yang ma 'dres te /
NK124(ngo)001:956: so sor snang la chos nyid dbyings sam rang byung
NK124(ngo)001:957: ye shes su dbyer med du yongs su rdzogs pa'o
NK124(ngo)001:959: yod med rtag dpyad bya brtsal la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:960: kun nas lhun gyis grub par ye gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:962: phyogs med lhun grub sdong po las //
NK124(ngo)001:965: mdo theg chen sgron ma las /
NK124(ngo)001:966: skra'i nyag ma gcig la yang //
NK124(ngo)001:967: sangs rgyas bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:970: chos can mtshan ma ma 'dres pa //
NK124(ngo)001:971: yongs su rdzogs pas stong bdag med //
NK124(ngo)001:972: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:973: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK124(ngo)001:976: de ltar sna tshogs ris su ma chad pa kas gnas lugs phyogs la ma zhen pa /
NK124(ngo)001:977: gnas lugs phyogs la ma zhen pa kas sna tshogs ris su ma chad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:978: des chos can mtshan mar snang ba nyid chos nyid rang snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:981: chos can mtshan mar snang ba'i rang bzhin yang //
NK124(ngo)001:982: chos nyid mtshan ma med pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:985: chos nyid pas kyang chos can gtso' //
NK124(ngo)001:986: chos can mtshan mar snang ba yis //
NK124(ngo)001:987: chos nyid skye med gtan la 'beb //
NK124(ngo)001:988: chos can chos nyid dbyer med de //
NK124(ngo)001:989: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:990: rang sar grol bas yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:992: de ltar chos nyid rgya chad phyogs lhung med cing
NK124(ngo)001:993: thun mong ma yin pa'i lhun grub chen po de
NK124(ngo)001:994: blo thun mong pa'i phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyis blo'i
NK124(ngo)001:995: spyod yul du ma 'gyur pas thun mong ma yin
NK124(ngo)001:998: lhun grub phyogs med ma rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:999: lta ba'i 'dod gzhung du ma byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1002: ma chags pad ma 'dra ba yis //
NK124(ngo)001:1003: ye shes can gyi spyod yul de //
NK124(ngo)001:1004: kun dang thun mong de ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1006: gsum pa gzhi la 'khrul gzhi yod med brtag pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:1010: rtul po ni blo rmongs shing shes rab chung ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1011: dngos su chos la 'jug pa'i blo med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1012: sbyangs nas theg pa chen po la 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1014: rmongs pa bsal phyir sems bskyed de //
NK124(ngo)001:1015: ngo mtshar tshig gis shes te bsgyur //
NK124(ngo)001:1018: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK124(ngo)001:1019: shin tu phra la sbyangs pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:1021: rnon po ni dbang po rno zhing shes rab che ba te /
NK124(ngo)001:1022: ma bsags ma sbyangs par theg chen go nus rtogs nus kyi blo dang ldan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1024: rang bzhin gyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1026: bden pa mthong ba yang 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1029: ma sbyangs grub pa gsum phyir gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:1030: mtho' brten myur rno rgya cher yang //
NK124(ngo)001:1032: gnyis pa rno rtul yod med kyi brtag pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1035: dang po ni med par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1036: yod par 'dod pa la skyon brjod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1038: shes bya'i gshis stong pa rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:1039: de la rno rtul gyi bye brag gang yang mi snang mnyam par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1041: chos kyi dbyings la dbyer med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:1042: rigs ni tha dad rung ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1045: thams cad nas thams cad du snying po byang chub nyid las ma gtogs pa gang yang med do //
NK124(ngo)001:1046: gzhan yang gzhi'i skabs kyi lung de rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:1047: yang rnon po gcig pu yin sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1048: theg pa chen po las chung ngu'i rigs med do //
NK124(ngo)001:1050: yang rtul po gcig pur 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1051: sems rgyu'i rnam pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1052: sbyangs nas sangs rgyas pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:1053: ma sbyangs bar rtogs shing grol ba med do //
NK124(ngo)001:1055: de rnams kyi lung ni rno rtul phyogs re lung rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:1056: gnyis pa gzhi la rno rtul yod na bde bar
NK124(ngo)001:1057: gshegs pa'i snying pos gzhan la ma khyab pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:1058: / gzhi bzang ngan can du thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1059: sangs rgyas te mthar thug gi dus su yang bzang ngan 'ong ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1060: rno rtul gnyis ka yod par 'dod pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:1062: the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1064: tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma 'gag pa'i mnyam pa rigs med du yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1065: de yang chos nyid kyi dbyings sam rang byung gi
NK124(ngo)001:1066: ye shes las gzhan gyis sel med par gcig pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:1067: cha nas bzang ngan rno rtul gang yang med la
NK124(ngo)001:1068: / de nyid sna tshogs su snang zhing rtogs par
NK124(ngo)001:1069: byed pa'i cha nas rno rtul gnyis ka yod do
NK124(ngo)001:1071: gzhan gyi skyon bsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1072: rno rtul med na sla skyon brjod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1073: rno rtul yod par sgrub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1075: thog mar bde bar gshegs pa'i snying pos khyab kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:1076: de nyid blo'i rigs sna tshogs su snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1078: gzhi bzang ngan can du thal ces pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:1079: bzang ngan gyi snang ba ma 'gag par thal zer ram /
NK124(ngo)001:1082: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1083: phyi ma ltar na he du ma grub ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1084: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la bzang ngan dang blangs dor med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1085: gsum pa gzhi la rno rtul yod na mthar thug
NK124(ngo)001:1086: sangs rgyas pa'i dus su yang bzang ngan yod par
NK124(ngo)001:1088: gzhi la rno rtul rang rgyud ther zug par 'dod na skyon 'ong te /
NK124(ngo)001:1089: 'dir rno rtul gyi snang ba gang yang ma spang
NK124(ngo)001:1090: ba'i mnyam pa rigs med yod par rtogs pa mthar
NK124(ngo)001:1091: phyin pa'i dus su mnyam pa rigs med du sangs
NK124(ngo)001:1092: rgyas pas bzang ngan med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1095: lung man ngag rigs pa gsum dang 'gal te /
NK124(ngo)001:1096: lung man ngag ni gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1098: gzhi la rno rtul gyi snang ba gang yang med na /
NK124(ngo)001:1099: gdod ma nyid du grol ba gtan mi 'byung ba'i thal /
NK124(ngo)001:1101: rno rtul gyis snang ba med cing mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1102: gzhi la med kyang rkyen gyi rno rtul dang bzang ngan 'byung ngo zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:1105: gzhi yin na gzhi la bzang ngan med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1106: rkyen la yang bzang ngan med de snga ma bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1107: gzhi la log pa'i rkyen yod na /
NK124(ngo)001:1108: gzhi mu mtha' can du thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1109: rkyen gzhan gyis byed pa'i phyir phya dang phyug bden par thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1110: gzhan yang blo che chung dang 'khrul grol la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:1111: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'di gzhi las ma
NK124(ngo)001:1112: byung zhing gzhi ma yin par thal ba la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:1115: gzhi las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1116: med kyang 'byung na sangs rgyas la sdug bsngal 'ong bar thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:1117: rnon po gcig pu yod na theg pa chung ngu bzang ngan gyi rigs med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1118: theg chung dang drangs don gsungs pa don med par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1119: thams cad gcig tu grol ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:1120: rtul po gcig pu yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:1121: dang po chos ston pa'i mkhan po med pas grol ba gtan mi 'byung bar thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1122: theg chen gyi rigs med pas theg chen gsungs pa
NK124(ngo)001:1123: don med du thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong
NK124(ngo)001:1124: / theg chen gyi rigs med kyang rkyen gyis sbyangs nas theg chen dang sangs rgyas 'byung zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:1125: theg chen dang sangs rgyas 'dus byas su thal ba'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:1127: lung rigs man ngag gsum gyis sgrub ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1130: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:1131: blo shin tu zab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1141: sha stag pas sngags kyi ngo bo nyid kyi gtam /
NK124(ngo)001:1144: thod rgal ba zhes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1146: lha mi sems can dbang po mi mthun te //
NK124(ngo)001:1147: la la dbang po sbyangs pa'i 'phro can yod //
NK124(ngo)001:1148: la la ye nas dbang po gcig chod yod //
NK124(ngo)001:1151: 'gro drug dbang po gcig chod dam //
NK124(ngo)001:1152: sbyangs pa'i 'phro can gang yang rung //
NK124(ngo)001:1156: de yang rang bzhin sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur la nye ring phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:1157: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:1159: gzhi la rno rtul gnyis ka yod med /
NK124(ngo)001:1160: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:1161: he du sna tshogs su snang ba nyid kyis grub bo //
NK124(ngo)001:1162: sna tshogs su snang ba rno rtul gnyis ka yod par grub bo //
NK124(ngo)001:1163: yang gzhi la rno rtul gnyis ka yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1164: 'khrul grol la sogs sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:1165: he du sna tshogs su snang ba nyid kyis 'grub la /
NK124(ngo)001:1166: sna tshogs su snang bas rno rtul gnyis ka yod pa 'grub bo //
NK124(ngo)001:1167: yang gang zag gcig gi shes pa'i rgyud la yang rno rtul gnyis ka yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1168: lung man ngag ni gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1170: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs yin pa'i phyir rno rtul gnyis ka yod pa gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1171: de la gzhan gyi skyon brjod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1172: 'gro ba sems rgyud gnyis 'changs su thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1173: gang zag gcig lam gnyis la dus gcig du grol ba thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1174: gang zag re re la rno rtul gnyis ka 'grub
NK124(ngo)001:1175: pas thams cad rno rtul khyad par med par thal
NK124(ngo)001:1177: yang skabs gcig tu 'grub bam dus rgyun chad med par 'grub /
NK124(ngo)001:1179: stong nyid gcig char du 'jug pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1180: dus rgyun du 'grub na sangs rgyas pa'i dus kyang
NK124(ngo)001:1181: theg chen mi go mi rtogs par thal ba'i skyon
NK124(ngo)001:1182: 'ong / dang po ni 'gro la sems rgyud gnyis 'chang du thal ces pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:1183: blo'i 'char lugs gnyis 'chang du thal zer ram /
NK124(ngo)001:1184: rig pa'i rgyud gnyis 'chang du thal zer /
NK124(ngo)001:1187: sems kyi rang bzhin sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:1190: shes rgyud gcig gis snang tshul yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1192: lam gnyis la bsgrod par thal ces pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1193: snod yod tshad la bcud kyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1194: rtul po theg pa chung ngu bzang ngan la zhugs tsa na /
NK124(ngo)001:1195: rtul po nus ldan du yod la /
NK124(ngo)001:1196: rno po rgyud ldan du yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1197: rno po theg pa chen po la zhug tsa na /
NK124(ngo)001:1198: rno po nus ldan du yod la /
NK124(ngo)001:1199: rtul po rgyud ldan du yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1200: gcig la zhug tsa na gcig dngos su mi 'byung bas gnyis ka'i skyon mi 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1201: yang gnyis ka 'grub kyang gtso gang che ba gcig tu 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:1202: de rang la yang gnyis ka tshang zhing lam gcig la bsgrod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1204: gnyis ka 'grub nas khyad med du thal ces pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1205: gnyis ka 'grub kyang la la rno po nus ldan du yod rtul po rgyud ldan du yod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:1206: la la rtul po rgyud ldan du yod rno po
NK124(ngo)001:1207: nus ldan du yod pas khyad med du thal ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:1209: gcig gi shes pa'i rgyud la rno rtul gnyis ka 'grub bam ma grub ces pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1210: spyir bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab cing /
NK124(ngo)001:1211: rang byung gi ye shes la gzhan gyi sel med
NK124(ngo)001:1212: pa rang chas su thams cad la gnas pas rno
NK124(ngo)001:1213: rtul bzang ngan med par mnyam la /
NK124(ngo)001:1214: de nyid sna tshogs su 'char ba'i ngos nas gcig tu ma nges te /
NK124(ngo)001:1215: blo'i rno rtul gnyis ka las grol ba'i rno po gcig pu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1217: rang bzhin gyi blo chung ba'i rtul po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1218: blo rang bzhin gyi rno ba'i rno po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1219: rno rtul gnyis ka yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1221: gzhi rang byung gi ston pa 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:1223: spyir 'khor ba thog mtha' med pas chos dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1226: theg pa chung ngu bzang ngan du rigs nges shing sbyangs nas 'jug par byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1228: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rno po rtogs grol dus mnyam pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1230: blo'i rigs ma nges shing lam nges med du bsgrod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1231: des na phyogs gcig tu gang yang mi gnas shing gang yang mi 'gal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1232: bzhi pa gzhi la 'khrul gzhi yod med 'di /
NK124(ngo)001:1237: dbu ma la sogs pa gshis chos nyid stong pa
NK124(ngo)001:1238: ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa las 'khrul ba
NK124(ngo)001:1239: dang / yang gsang sngags pa la la dag rig
NK124(ngo)001:1240: pa ye shes de rnam par dag pa las 'khrul
NK124(ngo)001:1241: pa'i gzhi med pa las 'khrul par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1243: gzhi la so so skye bo'i snang ba rang kha
NK124(ngo)001:1244: 'di kha ltar 'dod cing 'khrul gzhi yod pa la
NK124(ngo)001:1246: gsum pa gnyis med las 'khrul pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1247: yod med gnyis las gcig 'khrul par 'dod pa'i mtha' grol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1250: stog pa cir yang med pa las 'khrul na /
NK124(ngo)001:1251: gshis chad pa'i mthar thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1252: mu stegs chad pa'i bden par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1253: 'khor ba glo bur bar thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1254: rig pa ye shes rnam par dag pa las 'khrul pa byung na /
NK124(ngo)001:1255: sangs rgyas kyang 'khrul pa byung bar thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1256: yang gzhi mya ngan la 'das par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1257: rgyud dag gi sangs rgyas su thal ba la sogs pa 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1258: yang gzhi la 'khrul pa dang dngos po rang rgyud
NK124(ngo)001:1259: pa yod na grol ba gtan mi byung ba la
NK124(ngo)001:1262: gnas lugs 'khrul gzhi yod dam 'on te med las 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:1263: yod 'khrul sangs mi rgya' zhing med 'khrul 'ong don med //
NK124(ngo)001:1266: 'khrul gzhi yod med gnyis med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1267: gshis rang byung gi ye shes las gzhan gyis sel med pa'i cha nas 'khrul gzhi med la /
NK124(ngo)001:1268: de rang gis rang ma shes pa'i cha nas 'khrul gzhi yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1269: de gnyis gnyis su med pa las 'khrul pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1270: des na 'khrul gzhi yod pa dang med par bshad
NK124(ngo)001:1271: pa'i lung rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas gang yang mi
NK124(ngo)001:1273: de yang gshis rang byung gis ye shes ye nas gnas pa de dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1274: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa gnyis gnyis su med pa las khrul pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1275: 'khrul tshul gyis skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1276: de yang nam mkha' mtha' mnyam las /
NK124(ngo)001:1277: thag pa'i rang bzhin 'khrul med kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1278: 'khrul pas sbrul gyi dbang por snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1279: dngos la sbrul du mi gnas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1280: 'khrul pa'i ngo la snang gzhi yod //
NK124(ngo)001:1281: rang sems ma bcos ci bzhin la //
NK124(ngo)001:1282: rtogs dang ma rtogs mi gnas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1283: 'khrul pa gnyis su rtogs pas bzung //
NK124(ngo)001:1284: dngos la gnyis su mi gnas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1285: rang rang zhen pa'i dbang gis na //
NK124(ngo)001:1286: de ltar snang ba 'khrul gzhir gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:1289: drug gi 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK124(ngo)001:1290: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
NK124(ngo)001:1291: ci ltar ltas pas snang ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:1292: 'khrul gzhi yod med sgro skur bral //
NK124(ngo)001:1295: ma rig ye shes tha dad med //
NK124(ngo)001:1296: ma rtogs rtogs pa'i lam du gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:1297: ces pa la sogs rgyud lung man ngag du ma nas gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:1298: lnga pa rgyud gcig gam tha dad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1299: gcig na gcig grol bas thams cad grol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1300: gcig gi rnam smin thams cad la 'ong ba'i skyon 'ong la /
NK124(ngo)001:1302: mu stegs pa'i bdag grub cing gzung 'dzin rang rgyud du bden pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1304: gcig dang tha dad kyis ngo bo las grol ba'am /
NK124(ngo)001:1305: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1306: rgyas par ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs kyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1309: 'khrul pa'i rtogs sems 'gro ba so so'i sems //
NK124(ngo)001:1310: gcig na dge sdig rnam smin kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1311: ma spyad kun gyis myong bar rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:1312: las kyi rnam smin thun mong ma grub phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:1313: bag chags brtas pas 'khrul pa'i sdug bsngal yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1316: mu stegs rig byed kyi mtha' gsang bar smra ba'i sde pa'i skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1319: ngo bo nyid kyi sku la 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:1320: blo yis brtag pas gcig yul gcig min pas //
NK124(ngo)001:1321: rang sems 'khrul pa'i snang bar the tshom med //
NK124(ngo)001:1322: de phyir dbang po'i yul rnams gzhi la med //
NK124(ngo)001:1325: chos nyid gcig ste dbye ba med pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:1326: 'dzin pa'i shes pas tha dad mthong ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1327: tha dad pa ni 'dzin pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1329: dngos po thams cad 'dzin pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1332: dug gsum rtsa ba 'dzin pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1333: 'dzin pa'i shes pa ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:1334: tha dad mi 'dra rgyu mtshan ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1335: yod par sems dpas ma gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:1337: gnyis ka'i skyon med cing tha dad las grol ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1338: snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:1339: rtogs sems 'gro ba so so'i sems //
NK124(ngo)001:1340: gcig na dge sdig rnam smin yang //
NK124(ngo)001:1341: ma spyad kun gyis myong bar rig /
NK124(ngo)001:1342: de min yang dag don mi rung //
NK124(ngo)001:1343: rnam smin thun mong ma gyur phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:1344: gcig min de nyid ma skyes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:1345: tha dad don du'ang mi rung ste //
NK124(ngo)001:1346: gcig dang tha dad las grol pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1349: mnyam pa'i klong la phyogs ris med //
NK124(ngo)001:1350: klong chen gcig las ma g.yos par //
NK124(ngo)001:1351: klong phran mtha' yas kun 'byams kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1352: nges med cir gyur klong du 'byams //
NK124(ngo)001:1354: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:1355: gzhi'i gnas lugs bstan pa'i le'u ste dang po'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:1356: gnyis pa ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1357: sems can thams cad kyi sdig pa'i las spu tsam ma byas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:1358: 'khrul nas 'khor bar 'khyam tshul bstan pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:1359: rig pa sems kyi 'khrul gzhi bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1360: 'od lnga lus kyi 'khrul gzhi bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1361: chos nyid yul gyi 'khrul gzhi bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1362: dang po rig pa sems kyis 'khrul gzhi bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1363: rtsa ba gang las 'khrul na chos kyi dbyings las 'khrul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1364: gzhi ni kun gzhi las 'khrul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1365: 'khrul pa'i rgyu ni ma rig pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1366: dus ni thog ma med pa nas 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:1367: ngo bo nga bdag gis shes pa zhugs nas 'khor bar 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:1368: 'khrul tshul ni sems nyid gcig la gnyis su bzung nas phyi nang snod bcud kyi tshul du 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:1369: gang 'khrul na nyon mongs pa can gyi yid 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:1370: gang gis 'khrul na rang gi rang ma rig pa 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:1372: zo chu'i 'khyud mo bzhin gcig nas gcig tu 'khrul zhing 'khor /
NK124(ngo)001:1374: nga bdag skye 'chi dgra gnyen bde sdug 'khor 'das kyi tshul du 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:1378: srin bu'i kha chu rang las byung zhing rang 'thun pa dang 'dra'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1380: thog ma med nas sems yan btang //
NK124(ngo)001:1381: phyin ci log la 'jog nyog spyad //
NK124(ngo)001:1382: gzung 'dzin don la rab tu chags //
NK124(ngo)001:1387: bde bar bde gshegs snying po las //
NK124(ngo)001:1388: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK124(ngo)001:1389: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK124(ngo)001:1390: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:1391: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:1392: sus kyang ma bcings bcing med de //
NK124(ngo)001:1393: bcings par bya ba yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1394: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1397: dang po da lta tha ma la //
NK124(ngo)001:1398: ngo bo mtshan nyid nges tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:1399: dpe rtags gnyen po dbye ba tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:1400: rnam pa dag gis bsdus pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1403: 'od lnga lus kyi 'khrul gzhi bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1404: gzhi chos nyid dag pa'i klong nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1405: rig pa'i rang mdangs 'od kha dog rnam pa lnga /
NK124(ngo)001:1406: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le'i klong du shar bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1407: rig pa 'gag te yid du 'gyus pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1408: mthong cha phra mo mthong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1409: der 'od rnam pa lnga la rtag dpyad byas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1410: 'od pha gi las nga byung ngam /
NK124(ngo)001:1411: nga las pha gi byung snyam pa'i the tshom skyes te /
NK124(ngo)001:1412: rang snang gi 'od kha dog lngar shar ba ngo ma shes te /
NK124(ngo)001:1413: gnyis 'dzin skyes pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig par song /
NK124(ngo)001:1414: gang dang gang lhan cig skyes na /
NK124(ngo)001:1415: ma rig pa dang ye shes gnyis lhan cig tu skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1417: bcos slad med pa'i chos nyid klong du skyes so //
NK124(ngo)001:1418: gang gis gang ma rig na /
NK124(ngo)001:1419: rang bzhin gyi 'od byad lta bu des /
NK124(ngo)001:1420: rang gi rig pa'i 'od byad kyi snang ba me
NK124(ngo)001:1421: long la shar ba lta bu de ma rig pas
NK124(ngo)001:1422: / lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1423: rkyen kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1424: 'od kha dog rnam pa lngar snang ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:1425: 'dzin rtog rags su skyes pa'i dus su /
NK124(ngo)001:1426: de ma yin pa der 'dzin gyi rtog pa byung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1427: 'od lnga rang snang du ma shes pas gzhan snang du bzung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1428: de yang ma rig pa dngos su med la /
NK124(ngo)001:1429: ma rtogs pa'i blo la yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1430: skad cig ma lnga las 'khrul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1431: de la skad cig ma dang po la chos nyid dag pa me long lta bu la /
NK124(ngo)001:1432: ye shes kyi 'od kha dog rnam pa lnga nam mkha'i 'ja' ltar shar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1433: de nas skad cig ma gnyis pa la rgyu'i rkyen chos nyid ye shes lngas rgyu byas /
NK124(ngo)001:1434: de nas skad cig ma gsum pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:1435: dmigs pa yul gyis rkyen 'od kha dog lnga ru snang ba mthong /
NK124(ngo)001:1436: de nas skad cig ma bzhi pa la bdag po'i
NK124(ngo)001:1437: rkyen rig pa'i mthong chas 'od la 'dzin pa zhugs
NK124(ngo)001:1438: // de nas skad cig ma lnga pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:1439: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen zhes bya ba /
NK124(ngo)001:1440: 'od la gzhan snang du bzung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1441: mdor na rgyu'i rkyen chos nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:1445: mtshungs pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1446: 'o na 'khrul pa'i dus nam 'khrul zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:1447: ma rig pa yul la shar ba'i dus su 'khrul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1449: lhan cig byed dang nye bar len /
NK124(ngo)001:1450: ma rig rnam pa gnyis mthu' yis //
NK124(ngo)001:1451: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:1452: rgyal po'i phru gu 'khyam pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:1453: gsum gnyis bzhi yi rkyen dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:1454: bskyed dang 'phen dang stobs rgyas byed //
NK124(ngo)001:1457: sems kyi kun gzhi thog mar yang //
NK124(ngo)001:1458: gang la mi rtog pa ma zin //
NK124(ngo)001:1459: ma shes lhan cig ma rig pa //
NK124(ngo)001:1460: rtog zhugs sems kyi kun gzhi byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1462: thog mar mtha' drug rtog las 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1463: gang la mi rtog don ma zin //
NK124(ngo)001:1464: yengs pa'i tshul las rtog pa byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1465: rang snang sgrib pa bag chags brtas //
NK124(ngo)001:1466: bag chags snga phyi'i rgyu la bsten //
NK124(ngo)001:1467: 'gag pas ma rig sdug bsngal byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1469: 'khrul pa sems las byung ba'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:1470: rang snang ma rtog gnyis 'dzin skyes //
NK124(ngo)001:1471: gnyis su bzung ba bdag gis 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:1472: bag chags 'thug po brtag pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:1473: 'khor ba snod bcud gnyis su chags //
NK124(ngo)001:1474: rtog pa drug la rigs drug byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1475: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:1476: gsum pa chos nyid yul gyi 'khrul gzhi bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:1479: dang po phyi snod du 'khrul pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1480: 'od kha dog lngar snang ba brtag dpyad byas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1482: de yang gzhi dag pa me long lta bu' ye
NK124(ngo)001:1483: shes kyi rang 'od dkar po la 'dzin pa zhugs
NK124(ngo)001:1484: nas / snyigs ma'i 'byung ba chu la sogs pa dkar po'i snang bar 'khrul pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:1485: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi gazhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1486: gzhi dag pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang 'od ser po la 'dzin pa zhugs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1487: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba sa rdo ri brag rtsi shing
NK124(ngo)001:1488: nags tshal la sogs pa ser po'i snang bar 'khrul
NK124(ngo)001:1489: pa ni / mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi gazhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1490: gzhi dag pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi
NK124(ngo)001:1491: rang 'od dmar por snang ba la 'dzin pa zhugs
NK124(ngo)001:1492: nas / snyigs ma'i 'byung ba me la sogs pa dmar po'i snang bar 'khrul pa'i phyir na /
NK124(ngo)001:1493: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi gazhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1494: gzhi dag pa bya ba grub pa ye shes kyi
NK124(ngo)001:1495: rang 'od ljang gur snang ba la 'dzin pa zhugs
NK124(ngo)001:1496: nas / snyigs ma'i 'byung ba rlung la sogs pa ljang gu'i snang bar 'khrul pa'i phyir na /
NK124(ngo)001:1497: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi gazhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1498: gzhi dag pas chos nyid da byings kyi ye shes
NK124(ngo)001:1499: kyi rang 'od mthing kar snang ba la 'dzin pa
NK124(ngo)001:1500: zhug nas / snyigs ma'i 'byung ba nam mkha' la
NK124(ngo)001:1501: sogs pa mthing ka'i snang bar 'khrul pa'i phyir na
NK124(ngo)001:1502: zhug nas / / chos dbyings ye shes kyi gazhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1503: de ltar rang mdangs kyi 'od lnga la phyi'i yul lngar ltas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1505: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dang lngar don la grub pa med bzhin du chags so //
NK124(ngo)001:1506: phyi'i yul lnga la nang gi sems kyis nga dang bdag tu bzung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1507: rang bzhin gyi 'od lnga gsal ma nus te /
NK124(ngo)001:1508: dngos po sra 'khreg gdos po can du song ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1509: phyi'i 'byung ba'i bcud du shes pas srid pa'i sgo nga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1511: tsher ma can sna tshogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1516: u du 'bar ba la sogs pa 'khrungs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1519: u du 'bar ba ni dag pa ni dag pa'i rten /
NK124(ngo)001:1520: dri med ye shes bardzusa nas skyes /
NK124(ngo)001:1521: zhes pa rdzus skyes kyi rten /
NK124(ngo)001:1522: srid pa'i sgo nga ma dag rten /
NK124(ngo)001:1523: shed bu shed la rog ni de las skyes /
NK124(ngo)001:1524: de ni lus kyi skyes rten dang bcas pa 'byung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1525: shed bu shed la rog las mngal skyes byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1526: des na skye ba bzhi'i lus skyes rten dang bcas pa dngos su byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1527: des phyir snod kyi 'jig rten 'khrul tshul bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1529: ye shes rang rtsal 'byung ba lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:1530: kha dog rnam pa lnga ru shar //
NK124(ngo)001:1531: gong gi rtog byed gsum po las //
NK124(ngo)001:1532: phra rags rdul gyi cha tsam du //
NK124(ngo)001:1533: rtog dpyod rnam pa mang du shar //
NK124(ngo)001:1534: 'od khyim kha dog lnga po la //
NK124(ngo)001:1535: ma rig dngos po can du bzung //
NK124(ngo)001:1536: 'od ljang bya grub ye shes la //
NK124(ngo)001:1537: der 'dzin zhugs pas rlung gi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:1538: gyu ba'i kha rlangs tsam du 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1539: 'od dkar me long ye shes la //
NK124(ngo)001:1540: der 'dzin zhugs pas chu yi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:1541: dkar po sran 'bru tsam du byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1542: 'od ser mnyam nyid ye shes la //
NK124(ngo)001:1543: der 'dzin zhugs pas sa yi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:1544: ser po ra ril tsam du byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1545: 'od dmar sor rtogs ye shes la //
NK124(ngo)001:1546: der 'dzin zhugs pas me yi gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:1547: dmar po the bong tsam du byung //
NK124(ngo)001:1548: mthing ka chos dbyings ye shes ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1549: gdod ma nyid nas ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:1551: 'byung lnga'i gzhi ma de lnga las //
NK124(ngo)001:1552: rang 'od ye shes lnga ru gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:1554: gnyis pa nang bcud kyi sems can 'khrul lugs bstan pa la lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1560: dang po 'khrul gzhi ni ye shes rnam pa lnga yis byas /
NK124(ngo)001:1561: gnyis pa 'khrul pa'i rgyu ni ma rig pa gnyis kyis byas /
NK124(ngo)001:1562: gsum pa 'khrul pa'i rkyen ni skad cig ma lngas byas /
NK124(ngo)001:1563: bzhi pa 'khrul pa'i 'bras bu ni gong ltar 'od
NK124(ngo)001:1564: kha dog rnam pa lnga la brtag dpyad dang der
NK124(ngo)001:1566: rig pa nam mkha' stong par ma rig pa'i rlung 'gyus pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1567: yid kyi mig gis srid pa'i sgo nga mthong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1568: rig pa thugs kyi sgo nga de shin tu legs shing mdzes pa gcig tu shes nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1569: der zhal gyis sbyor ba byas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1570: sgo nga la yid chags pa rab tu skyes /
NK124(ngo)001:1572: yid kyis chags sems gnyis sgo nga'i nang du zhugs pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:1573: nyi ma rab tu snang bas drod byas /
NK124(ngo)001:1574: nor bu'i dri ma med pas rlan byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1575: drod dang dbar rlan 'dzom pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:1576: phyi ltar na lta shed bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1578: nang ltar na 'dod chags bya'i sgo nga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1579: zhe sdang sbrul gyi sgo nga zhes kyang bya /
NK124(ngo)001:1582: nor bu dri ma med ces kyang bya /
NK124(ngo)001:1583: thabs 'gag pa med par 'char ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1584: shes rab stong pa skye ba med pa gnyis byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1585: der bza' ba'i zas med pas 'dod yon lnga byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1586: de yang sa la brten nas gzugs byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1587: chu la brten nas sgra byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1588: me la brten nas dri byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1589: rlung la brten nas ro byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1590: nam mkha' la brten nas reg byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1591: der yang rig pa de kha phyir ltas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1592: 'dod yon lnga las phyi'i 'byung ba lngar song /
NK124(ngo)001:1593: shes pa nang du log pas yul lnga la brten nas nang 'dzin pa'i sems su song nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1594: nyon mongs pa dug lngar song ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1595: de yang sa las nyon mongs pa gti mug byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1596: chu la brten nas 'dod chags byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1597: me la brten nas zhe sdang byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1598: rlung la brten nas phrag dog byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1599: nam mkha' la brten nas nyon mongs nga rgyal byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1600: der nyon mongs pa dug lnga'i rtsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:1601: 'gro ba rigs drug tu smin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1602: zhe sdang las kyis srog gcog la sogs byas pas 'bras bu dmyal bar smin /
NK124(ngo)001:1603: gti mug las kyis gnyid rmug tu song bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1604: shes bya'i gnas la blang dor gyi mig ma phyed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:1605: le lo dang blun rmongs la spyad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1607: 'dod chags kyi dbang gis ser sna dang phrag dog la spyad pas 'bras bu yi dwags su smin /
NK124(ngo)001:1608: 'phrag dog gis dbang gis khong 'khro dang 'phrag dogs
NK124(ngo)001:1609: spel mar spyad pas 'bras bu lha ma yin du
NK124(ngo)001:1610: smin / nga rgyal dbang gis nga dang bdag tu bzung bas 'bras bu lha dang mir smin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1611: de ltar 'gro ba rigs drug las /
NK124(ngo)001:1612: snang srid kyi lha 'dre thams cad smin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1613: dmyal ba las las kyi gshin rje rnams byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1614: yi dwags las ma mo la sogs pa'i mo gdon rnams byung /
NK124(ngo)001:1615: pho 'dre btsan bdud la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1616: nam mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags rnams yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1617: byol song las sa bdag dang klu gnyen /
NK124(ngo)001:1620: lto phye grul 'bum dri za rnams byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1621: lha ma yin las srin po dang gaza'i tshogs rnams byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1622: lha las phya dang dbang phyug dang nyi zla gza' skar la sogs pa rnams byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1623: mi las ri rab la gnas pa'i gnod sbyin thams cad 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1624: de dag kyang gong du rigs drug tu skyes pa'i rgyu so so las byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1625: de ltar 'gro ba rigs drug tu smin pa de la /
NK124(ngo)001:1633: de dag ni nang bcud kyi sems can 'khrul lugs bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1634: rdzogs pa chen po dgongs pa zang thal gyi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:1635: de ltar 'jig rten gsum po nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:1636: phung po lnga dang dbang po lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:1637: yan lag lnga dang don snying lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:1638: yul lnga dang ni nyon mongs lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:1639: sems lnga yid lnga rtogs pa lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:1641: phung po khams dang skye mched drug /
NK124(ngo)001:1642: gzung 'dzin ngag gis gzung nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1643: 'khor ba nyid na yun ring gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:1644: khams gsum pa yi khams pa ru //
NK124(ngo)001:1645: ming dang gzugs kyi btson rar tshud //
NK124(ngo)001:1646: ma rig las kyis lcags kyis sdom //
NK124(ngo)001:1647: 'khor ba'i mun nag 'thug pos g.yog /'dod chags tsha ba'i ro la chags //
NK124(ngo)001:1648: gti mug zhags pa ske nas bcings //
NK124(ngo)001:1649: zhe sdang me yi tshad pas gdungs //
NK124(ngo)001:1650: nga rgyal dag gis mgo btum nas //
NK124(ngo)001:1652: khong khro la sogs dmag gis bskor //
NK124(ngo)001:1653: gzung 'dzin zhags pas ske la btags //
NK124(ngo)001:1654: snga phyi'i bag chags 'dam du byings //
NK124(ngo)001:1655: rnam smin nyid dang las sbrel te //
NK124(ngo)001:1656: las kyis ma bus 'tshams sbyar nas //
NK124(ngo)001:1657: gcig nas gcig tu zo chu bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:1658: bzang ngan rim pas lus blangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:1659: so so'i rigs su skye bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:1661: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho'i gting du phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:1664: chags sdang lnga la longs spyod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:1666: dmyal ba'i rang bzhin me sogs mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:1667: yi dwags mi gtsang mthong yul snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1668: byol song ngam 'grog gyen du mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:1669: mi yi mthong yul bzhi ru snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1670: lha ma yin gyis go mtshon mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:1671: lha'i rin chen sna bdun mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:1672: de dag 'gro drug sdug bsngal yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1675: ngan song lcags kyus snying nas bzung //
NK124(ngo)001:1676: rang gis rang bcings nyon mongs lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:1677: dmyal ba'i phung po me chu snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1678: yi dwags rnams la bred sdangs bsdig /
NK124(ngo)001:1679: byol song rnams la na bun ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:1680: mi rnams phung po khams dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1681: skye mched 'byung ba lnga ru snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1682: de yang bde sdug btang snyoms so //
NK124(ngo)001:1683: lha min rnams la go mtshon te //
NK124(ngo)001:1684: lha rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan no //
NK124(ngo)001:1685: dper na myur mgyogs 'khor lo bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:1686: rgyun chags 'khor bar yun ring gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:1687: de ltar snang ba sna tshogs rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:1688: thag pa la ni sbrul mthong bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:1689: de ma yin la der mthong nas //
NK124(ngo)001:1690: phyi nang snod bcud gnyis su 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:1692: lnga pa byung ba'i dngas snyigs dbye ba la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:1702: u du 'bar bar la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1703: de la chu rlan dang bcas pa ni snyigs ma'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1704: de'i dngas ma ni chu shel dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1706: me tsha shing bsregs pa ni snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1707: de'i dngas ma ni me shel dag nyi ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1708: rlung yang shing g.yo ba ni snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1709: de'i dngas ma ni byung ba'i rang sgra yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1710: nam mkha' stong zhing go skabs 'byed pa ni snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1711: de'i dngas ma 'dzon rnam lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1712: rgyun skar dang bcas pa 'di rnams yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1713: gnyis pa nang gi 'byung ba'i dngas snyigs dbye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1714: sha dang rus pa 'di snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1715: de'i dngas ma rtsa dbu' ma dar dkar gyi skud pa tsam zhig tsi ta'i nang na gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:1716: khrag dang chu ser 'di snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1717: de'i dngas ma khrag mtshal tsog la ma'i khu ba
NK124(ngo)001:1718: lta bu byi'u glen pa'i mgo bo tsam zhig snying
NK124(ngo)001:1720: lus kyi drod 'di snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1721: de'i dngas ma sos ka'i nyi ma la me long
