NK124(ngo)001:1722: bstan pa'i drod tsam zhig tsi ta'i nang na gnas
NK124(ngo)001:1723: / lus kyi dbugs 'di snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1724: de'i dngas ma gser sa 'og tu bcug pa'i dang tsam zhig snying gi nang na gnas /
NK124(ngo)001:1725: byang khog stong pa dang snying bug stong pa 'di snyigs ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1726: de'i dngas ma thig le khra'i mig tsam cig stong
NK124(ngo)001:1727: pa mi 'gyur ba snying gi nang na gnas so
NK124(ngo)001:1729: 'byung ba dngas snyigs dbye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1730: nang gi thugs ye shes rnam lnga la dngas ma zhes bstan pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:1731: phyir shar ba'i 'od kha dog rnam pa lngar shar ba 'di snyig ma yin zhes bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1732: don la sku lnga ye shes 'od kha dog lnga
NK124(ngo)001:1733: rnams dbyer med du snying gi nang na bzhugs so
NK124(ngo)001:1734: // 'o na gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:1735: 'khrul pa 'byung bar mi rigs so zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:1737: ma rig pa dang ye shes dbyer med du lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1738: ye ci bzhin pa'i ye shes zang thal gyi bkrag mdangs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1740: ye shes kyi rtsal 'gags pa med pa'i 'od kyi mdangs lhun grub kyis klong du shar ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1743: mthing ka nang du lus song pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1745: 'khrul pa thams cad ye shes kyi rtsal 'gags pa med pa las shar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1746: 'khrul kyang ye shes kyi rtsal yin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1747: 'khrul gzhi gtan la phab pa la dgos pa med dam zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:1749: 'khrul lugs gtan la phab pas 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba chod /
NK124(ngo)001:1750: de chod pas 'khor ba la yid mi 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:1751: der yid la zhugs pas gzhi snang chen po chos kyi sku'i gnas lugs gtan la phebs so //
NK124(ngo)001:1752: de pheb pas 'khrul pa rang rgyud par ma grub par nges nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1753: 'khor ba rang bzhin med pa'i ngag tu gtan la phebs so //
NK124(ngo)001:1754: de pheb pas 'khor ba spang ma dgos par /
NK124(ngo)001:1755: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams gzhi ma 'khrul par rang log /
NK124(ngo)001:1756: rnam par rtog pa thams cad mi rtog pa'i ye shes su rang log /
NK124(ngo)001:1757: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad las sher ba'i 'gyu
NK124(ngo)001:1758: ba thams cad rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye
NK124(ngo)001:1759: shes su rang log dug lnga ye shes lngar rang
NK124(ngo)001:1760: log / dug lnga las skyes pa'i rigs drug gis
NK124(ngo)001:1761: sems can thams cad bsgyur ba med par sprul pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:1763: rigs drug gis bskyed pa'i lha ma srin thams cad
NK124(ngo)001:1764: kyang gzugs sku mnyam la ma 'dres par rang log
NK124(ngo)001:1765: / yul ngam 'grog dang g.yang sar snang ba thams
NK124(ngo)001:1766: cad chos kyi dbyings mu mtha' dang bral ba'i 'od
NK124(ngo)001:1767: snang chen po'i ngang du rang log /
NK124(ngo)001:1768: snang ba thams cad ye shes kyi 'od kha dog rnam pa lngar me re rer snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1769: sa rdo ri brag thams cad 'od kyi sbubs su nub nas btsal kyang mi snyed do //
NK124(ngo)001:1770: de la ngo bo nyid kyi snang ba ma brtags ma dpyad pa'i yul can /
NK124(ngo)001:1771: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i stong mdangs /
NK124(ngo)001:1773: ye shes kyi 'od kha dog lngas bskor ba'i zhing khams kun tu bzang po'i klong zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1774: de'i klong du snying po bcud du dril ba ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i snang ba shar bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1775: rig pa kun tu bzang po sku'i klong zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1776: stong pa'i mdangs las thig le'i gsal cha 'od dkar po gsal ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:1777: ye shes kyi 'od kha dog lngas bskor ba'i zhing khams te /
NK124(ngo)001:1778: de ltar gnas pa'i klong na /
NK124(ngo)001:1781: 'od dang dbyer med du bzhugs pa ye ci bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:1782: de'i mtshan nyid yongs rdzogs chen por lhun gyis grub pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1783: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:1784: sku phyag rgya chen por rdzogs nas mkhyen dpyod kyi dgongs pa klong du gyur par rtogs pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:1785: rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:1786: rlung dang rtsa rig pa gsum bya ba grub pa'i 'od ljang ku dang lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1787: sku dang ye shes 'od thams cad snying por bzhugs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1788: 'od ljang ku phyi nas nang du thim pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1789: 'od mthing kha nang nas phyir thon te /
NK124(ngo)001:1790: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes nang na gsal bas /
NK124(ngo)001:1791: shes bya bcud du dril nas bzhugs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1792: sangs rgyas gzhon nu bum pa'i sku zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1793: de yan chad kyi 'khrul tshul gtan la phab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1794: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:1795: 'khrul tshul bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:1796: de ltar ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i sems can la /
NK124(ngo)001:1797: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje mkhyen cing gzigs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1803: thugs rje'i gzigs pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1808: spang bya sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:1809: shes bya'i gnas lugs ci lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur nas /
NK124(ngo)001:1810: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis chos nyid sgrib med du mkhyen pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1812: log par bgo brtag rnam dag cing //
NK124(ngo)001:1813: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:1814: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:1815: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1817: gnyis pa dbye ba la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:1818: ci snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:1819: ci lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1820: dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:1822: ci snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi gzigs tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1823: shes bya'i chos thams cad ma 'dren par so so mkhyen te /
NK124(ngo)001:1825: chos sku ma lus bdag gsal phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:1826: ye shes rnam grangs bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:1828: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:1829: rang snang gsal ba'i ye shes ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1830: sems dang chos dbyings nam mkha'i dbyings /
NK124(ngo)001:1831: phyogs rig bsgrangs bar ga la nus //
NK124(ngo)001:1832: tshul gyi rnam grangs de nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:1833: ci ltar 'tsham pa'i tshul du snang //
NK124(ngo)001:1834: 'od gsal rig pas thams cad mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:1835: dus gcig kun mkhyen rig pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:1836: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1839: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' thug pa thams cad du /
NK124(ngo)001:1840: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gzugs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1842: spyod pa mtha' thug pa med pa rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:1846: mi 'brel ba ni gang yang med do //
NK124(ngo)001:1848: snying po byang chub tu ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1851: de thams cad chos nyid skye ba med cing 'dus
NK124(ngo)001:1852: ma bya pas la sogs pa ci lta ba bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:1855: mkhyen ldan ye shes snying po yis /
NK124(ngo)001:1856: gang yang mi mkhyen rang gsal mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:1857: mtha' dang dbus su mi dmigs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:1858: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:1861: chos thams cad ye ci bzhin pa'i don phyin ci
NK124(ngo)001:1862: ma logs pas skye 'gags med par mkhyen pa la
NK124(ngo)001:1863: btag pas na / de nyid don gyi dbang gi
NK124(ngo)001:1864: de kho na'i tshig bla dgas su rigs par bya'o
NK124(ngo)001:1865: btag pas na / // ces gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:1866: gsum pa dbyer med mkhyen pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1867: de gnyis su med cing ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen par yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1869: mkhyen bya mkhyen byed gnyis su med pa'i ye shes yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1872: rnam rtog mi mnga' cir yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:1873: de ni dpe don gyis thams cad mkhyen pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:1874: rdo rje sems dpa' mkhyen pa'i mchog tu gsung //
NK124(ngo)001:1876: gsum pa rtsod pa'i skyon spang pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1877: mkhyen pas sems can la ci ltar phan zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:1879: bu yod pa'i rmi lam na /
NK124(ngo)001:1880: mdze byung ba la phas gnyid bslang ba dang 'dra bar /
NK124(ngo)001:1881: rgyal ba thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:1882: gdul bya med la yod 'dzin can gyi sems can 'khrul pa las zlog pa'i ched du /
NK124(ngo)001:1883: gang la gang 'dul gyi don mdzad pas phan pa yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:1884: 'o na khams gsum sems can mkhyen pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:1885: yul du byas nas mkhyen nam /
NK124(ngo)001:1888: sangs rgyas la gzung 'dzin yod pa'i skyon yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:1890: ma rig rtogs pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:1894: ci ltar 'dzin pa de ltar kun nas nyon mongs rten //
NK124(ngo)001:1895: ces pa la sogs mdo rgyud du ma nas gsungs pa dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1896: yang yul du ma byas par mkhyen na /
NK124(ngo)001:1897: sangs rgyas kyis dgongs pa las log pa'i gdul bya yod dam med /
NK124(ngo)001:1898: yod na yul med kyis dam bca' dang 'gal /
NK124(ngo)001:1899: med na gcig sangs rgyas pas thams cad sangs rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1900: de 'dod na 'khor ba dong sprugs par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:1902: sangs rgyas las logs pa'i yul du sems can med pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:1904: yul med du mkhyen pa'i dam bca' dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1905: 'o na ci ltar mkhyen na yul du byas nas kyang mkhyen te /
NK124(ngo)001:1906: yul yul can du yang ma 'gags la /
NK124(ngo)001:1907: mthar ma reg pa'i tshul du mkhyen te /
NK124(ngo)001:1908: de yang gnyis su ma 'gag la /
NK124(ngo)001:1909: gnyis kyi mthar ma lhung bas gnyis kyi skyon las grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1910: de ltar nges pa'i lung ni /
NK124(ngo)001:1911: ci snyed pa mkhyen pa'i lung gong du smos pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:1912: yul med du yang mkhyen te /
NK124(ngo)001:1913: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par sangs
NK124(ngo)001:1914: rgyas kyi dgongs pa thugs rig pa'i ye shes las
NK124(ngo)001:1915: mi gzhan par mkhyen pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1917: thams cad rang rig chos sku'i ngo bor mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:1918: mkhyen pa med pa'i mkhyen pa chen po ste //
NK124(ngo)001:1920: rdzogs pa chen po 'bras bu'i klong yangs las /
NK124(ngo)001:1921: rang gsal ye shes rnam dag bde chen des //
NK124(ngo)001:1922: rnam pa ye gsal yul min thams cad mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:1924: de'i don ni sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la mu
NK124(ngo)001:1925: mtha' med cing kun la gnyis su med par khyab
NK124(ngo)001:1926: pa'o // yang yul yul can gnyis su med par
NK124(ngo)001:1927: chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen
NK124(ngo)001:1928: pa'o // te / nam mkha' mtha' mnyam las /
NK124(ngo)001:1929: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:1930: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:1932: gong gi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi lung dang mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:1933: 'di nyid gting zab pas blos zhib tu rtog par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1934: yang rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi mkhyen pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:1935: rnam par mi rtog cir yang sa ler mkhyen ce na /
NK124(ngo)001:1936: rtog yul yod pa'i mi rtog pa yin nam /
NK124(ngo)001:1937: med pa'i mi rtog pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:1938: yod na rtog yul 'dug pa'i phyir rtog byed kyang yod dgos so //
NK124(ngo)001:1939: de 'dod na mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1942: rtog yul med pa'i mi rtog pa yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:1943: gcig grol bas kun grol ba'i skyon gong ltar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1944: yang thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:1945: dus gsum skad cig thams cad mkhyen nam mi mkhyen /
NK124(ngo)001:1947: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma yin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:1948: mkhyen par bshad pa'i lung rnams dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1949: yang mkhyen na skad cig ma gcig gis dus na /
NK124(ngo)001:1950: dus gsum rdzogs sam ma rdzogs /
NK124(ngo)001:1951: ma rdzogs na dus gsum mkhyen par mi 'gro bas 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1952: dus gsum rdzas yod du 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1953: dus gsum mkhyen par rang ma yin par 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:1955: skad cig dus gsum la snga phyi med pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:1956: de skad byas pa la 'das pa 'gags par mkhyen /
NK124(ngo)001:1957: ma 'ongs pa ma skyes par mkhyen /
NK124(ngo)001:1958: da lta ba ma skyes la ma 'gags par mkhyen /
NK124(ngo)001:1960: dus gsum gyi snang ba mngon sum du mkhyen nam /
NK124(ngo)001:1963: dus gsum mngon sum du yod par 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:1965: sangs rgyas la dus kyi sgrib pa yod par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:1968: mkhyen pa'i skad cig gcig la ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1969: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun khyab can //
NK124(ngo)001:1971: 'og nas ston par gyur ba'i lung rnams dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1973: dus gsum rnam par dpyad pa'i skad cig gis dus gsum mkhyen pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:1974: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid skye 'gags med pa'i skad cig gis /
NK124(ngo)001:1975: dus gsum ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:1976: 'o na dus gsum skad cig la yod dam med ce na /
NK124(ngo)001:1978: skye 'gags can gyis skad cig tu 'dod pa ma yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:1979: dus gsum skye 'gags med pa'i skad cig ma dus
NK124(ngo)001:1980: gsum ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par yod pa'o
NK124(ngo)001:1981: // de la dus gsum ma 'dres pa so sor mkhyen pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1982: dus gsum gcig pa'am mi mkhyen pa'i skyon las grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1984: rang byung gi ye shes su tha dad med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:1985: yongs su rdzogs pas skye 'gags can du 'dod pa las grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:1987: nam mkha' la dus gsum tha dad med cing mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:1989: rang byung gi ye shes la tha dad med cing mnyam pa nyid du gnas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:1990: dus gsum ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:1992: ma bcos ngang las gnyis med kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:1993: shes rab 'od gsal chen po yi //
NK124(ngo)001:1994: mkha' la gza' skar bkra ba'am //
NK124(ngo)001:1995: me tog mdzes pa'i phung po ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:1996: so sor gsal la gcig tu 'dus //
NK124(ngo)001:1997: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:1998: phyogs med dag snang ye shes sku //
NK124(ngo)001:1999: dus matha'i tshad las 'das par mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:2001: nya mo 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:2002: dus gsum mnyam par rang gsal yang //
NK124(ngo)001:2003: ma 'dres par ni so sor gzigs //
NK124(ngo)001:2004: ci bzhin pa dang ci snyed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:2005: gnyis po rang la rdzogs pa'i lung //
NK124(ngo)001:2008: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ma bcos la //
NK124(ngo)001:2009: thams cad mkhyen pa dus gcig gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:2010: dus gsum gcig te khyad par med //
NK124(ngo)001:2013: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid las sngon gyis mtha' mi dmigs /
NK124(ngo)001:2015: da lta ba yang mi dmigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:2017: dus gsum mi shes med pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa chen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2019: yang sems can thams cad ma gro ba gcig la sangs rgyas pa'i thabs mkhyen nam mi mkhyen /
NK124(ngo)001:2020: mkhyen na 'khor ba spyi mtshan thams cad dong nas sprugs par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:2022: sangs rgyas kyis ci lta ba dang ci snyed pa mkhyen pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2023: shes bya la sems can thams cad nang ma gro ba gcig la sangs rgyas mi srid pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2024: sangs mi rgya ba la mi rgya ba ltar du mkhyen pas skyon gnyis ka las grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:2025: gzhan yang sangs rgyas kyis sems can gyi grangs mkhyen mi mkhyen /
NK124(ngo)001:2026: mi mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:2029: sems can grangs dang log rtog grangs //
NK124(ngo)001:2030: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi mkhyen phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:2032: skabs 'dir gnad chung bas rgyas par ma spros so //
NK124(ngo)001:2033: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:2035: sangs rgyas kyis thugs rje gzigs tshul bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:2036: gnyis pa thugs rje skyes tshul la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:2037: thugs rje bskyed pa'i rgyu rkyen dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2038: thugs rje bskyed pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2041: rgyu sangs rgyas kyis mdzad pa phyogs med lhun grub
NK124(ngo)001:2042: tu snang ba'i dpe nor bu rin po che dbang
NK124(ngo)001:2043: gis rgyal po lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2044: rkyen gdul bya las dag pa klu'i rgyal po lta bu'i tshul du gzigs nas 'byung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2046: 'bras bu'i yon tan lhun grub kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:2047: yid bzhin nor ltar snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2050: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs shes bya ci snyed par mkhyen pa'i ye shes nyid yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2053: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:2054: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK124(ngo)001:2058: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs skyes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2059: yul dang 'phrad nas skyes pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2060: bskul zhing gsol btabs tshul du skyes //
NK124(ngo)001:2063: rtag par rgyun du thugs rje skyes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2066: bskul zhing gsol ba btabs pa'i tshul skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2071: rig pa byang chub kyi sems rgyun chad med par ye nas gnas pa la bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2073: spros bral thugs kyi chos thams cad kun la khyab pas rje nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:2076: sangs rgyas kyis thugs rje 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du /
NK124(ngo)001:2077: rtag par rgyun du don mdzad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2079: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:2080: chos kyang nub par mi gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:2081: le lo can la phan gdag phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:2082: sprul pa rnams ni 'das tshul ston //
NK124(ngo)001:2083: ci ltar nam mkha' zhig gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:2086: 'o na sprul sku 'da' nas da lta mi bzhugs pas mi rtag par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:2087: sku 'das pa yang thugs rje 'da' tshul ston pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2088: rtag pa'i dngos por 'dzin pa sun phyung /
NK124(ngo)001:2089: le lo can la skul mas btabs /
NK124(ngo)001:2090: brtson 'grus can la phan gdag pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2091: 'da' ba ltar snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2093: nyi ma gling bzhi la shar nub ltar snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:2094: nyi ma rang la shar nub med pa bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:2095: sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa 'di 'da' ba ltar snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:2097: khyab gdal chen po'i zhing na bzhugs la /
NK124(ngo)001:2098: byis pa rnams kyi ched du me tog bkod pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:2099: 'jig rten du mtshan nges par ma grags pa zhes
NK124(ngo)001:2101: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa mdo las gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2102: 'di nas de bzhin nyid der gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:2103: gdal khyab chen po'i zhing na bzhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:2105: de bzhin nyid du rnam par snang //
NK124(ngo)001:2106: byis pa'i ched du cho 'phrul dag /
NK124(ngo)001:2107: me tog bkod pa'i 'jig rten na //
NK124(ngo)001:2108: ma grags pa zhes bya bar snang //
NK124(ngo)001:2111: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK124(ngo)001:2112: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:2113: mi rtag smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:2114: byung nas mya ngan 'da' bar ston //
NK124(ngo)001:2116: gnyis pa rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje skye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2117: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje nyi ma'i snying po ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:2118: 'bad rtsol med par rang bzhin gyis sems can la don 'byung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2120: ye shes gsang ba'i ngang nyid nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2121: thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' ltar gdal //
NK124(ngo)001:2122: thugs rje chen po nyi 'od ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:2126: ci bzhin nyid la bzhugs pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:2127: 'di zhes tshig tu ma gsungs kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:2128: khyab pa gcig pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:2129: ci ltar 'dod pa so sor gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:2132: nam mkha' la nyi ma shar bas sa la dro ba 'byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:2133: chu'i snod tha dad pa'i nang du gzugs brnyan 'char ba ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:2134: sangs rgyas kyis dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos par /
NK124(ngo)001:2135: zhing khams gzhal du med pa rnams su rnam par
NK124(ngo)001:2136: 'phrul pa dpag tu med pa 'jig rten du 'byung
NK124(ngo)001:2137: ba rnams dang / de bzhin du chos kyis 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2138: mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul ston pa la sogs pa'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab par /
NK124(ngo)001:2139: sngon gyi smon lam gyi dbang gis rtsol med du shugs kyis 'byung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2141: ci ltar b+hee dur sngon po'i rang bzhin la //
NK124(ngo)001:2142: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan shar ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:2143: de bzhin gdul bya'i chu snod dag pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:2144: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:2146: gsum pa yul dang 'phrad nas thugs rje skye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2147: spyir sku lngas 'khor lnga la don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2148: bye brag tu sku gsum gyi thugs rjes don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2150: ye shes rgya mtsho'i 'khor rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:2151: ston pa chos kyi sku'i rig pa'i byin rlabs sam /
NK124(ngo)001:2152: skye mched don gyi gsung gis don mdzad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2153: rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:2154: chos kun nam mkha'i mtha' kun mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:2155: chos nyid 'byung ba spros med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:2156: ye shes sku la spros med gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:2157: des na byin gyi rlabs kyis bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:2159: sa la gnas pa'i byang sems la sogs pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:2160: smin pa rgya mtsho'i 'khor rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:2161: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur snang nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2162: sku mdun dang rgyab med par zhal pho 'gyur kun tu thal le bas /
NK124(ngo)001:2163: dgongs pa brda'i sgo nas don mdzad de /
NK124(ngo)001:2165: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK124(ngo)001:2166: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:2167: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:2168: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK124(ngo)001:2169: sku'i chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK124(ngo)001:2170: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:2171: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel //
NK124(ngo)001:2174: stug po bkod pa'i rgyal ba yang //
NK124(ngo)001:2175: chos sku snying por gyur pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:2177: gzugs skur bstan nas tshig ces pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2178: gdul bya smin cing dag pa rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:2179: gong ltar longs skur snang zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:2180: ma dag pa rnams la sprul skur snang nas don mdzad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2181: spyir 'jig rten gyi khams bsam gyi mi khyab par snang bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2183: longs spyod zag med rin chen gter //
NK124(ngo)001:2184: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:2185: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:2190: sprul sku mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pas dngos su gsung gis don mdzad de /
NK124(ngo)001:2192: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan dang mthu stobs pha mtha' yas //
NK124(ngo)001:2193: sems can rnams la chos rab ston cing sgrod par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:2195: ma dag pa rnams la 'gro ba rang rang gi
NK124(ngo)001:2196: snang tshul dang mthun par gang la gang 'dul du
NK124(ngo)001:2198: skye ba thams cad gzugs su snang ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2199: bya rog dang me khyer la sogs pa'i srog chags gang yin pa de dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2200: de'i gzugs su snang bar mdzad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:2201: de dag gi cha byad rnams kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:2202: gang ci ltar mos pa rnams la de bzhin du snang ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2204: de yang phyogs re tsam mtshon na /
NK124(ngo)001:2205: sngon ru tra la thugs rje bskyed de btul ba lta bu'am /
NK124(ngo)001:2206: rkang chag lag rdum la sogs pa la thugs rje skye ba lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2207: gsum pa bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa la brten nas thugs rje skye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2208: spyir bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2209: bye brag tu bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa la brten nas skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2211: 'og min du bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2212: mi yul du bstan pa 'byung bar bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2214: bde chen gdal khyab chen po'i zhing khams /
NK124(ngo)001:2215: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du /
NK124(ngo)001:2216: sku lnga lhun grub kyis sangs rgyas la sogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2217: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dgongs pa ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:2218: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par mkhyen nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2219: dgongs pa mnyam nyid du bzhugs pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:2220: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis yum pha rol du phyin
NK124(ngo)001:2221: ma la sogs pa'i 'khor rnams kyis dbyings las bskul
NK124(ngo)001:2223: chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs so //
NK124(ngo)001:2226: yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK124(ngo)001:2227: nam mkha' bzhengs nas dam tshig nye bar bshed //
NK124(ngo)001:2228: ye shes rgya mtsho'i rnam par grol ba klong //
NK124(ngo)001:2229: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK124(ngo)001:2230: zhes pa sogs kyi sgra byung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2231: chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs nas bzhugs pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:2233: mgrin gcig tu gsol ba btab pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2234: rgyud 'di go ba rtogs kyis skal dang ldan pa rnams la bshad du gsol /
NK124(ngo)001:2235: 'di nyid go ba rtogs kyis skal ba dang mi ldan pa rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:2236: lam stegs kyis theg pa bshad du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2239: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis thugs chen po //
NK124(ngo)001:2240: ye shes snying po don gyis don mchog ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:2241: rnal 'byor theg chen rdo rje theg chen lung //
NK124(ngo)001:2242: 'dus pa'i tshogs la rgya cher bshad du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2245: de tshe rdo rje sems dpas gang zhus pa //
NK124(ngo)001:2246: sangs rgyas kun gyis dgongs pa nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:2247: ma nor ma bcos rang byung chos sku de //
NK124(ngo)001:2248: sems can blo yis nges par rtogs pa'i thabs //
NK124(ngo)001:2249: kun rig ston pa thugs rje bshad du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2251: 'og min la sogs par ston pa chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2252: 'khor thun mong ma yin pa rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:2253: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te gsungs tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2254: mi 'ched 'jig rten gyis khams la sogs pa'i zhing khams dpag tu med par /
NK124(ngo)001:2255: sprul sku thub pa drug la sogs pa dpag tu med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2257: bstan pa sde snod gsum la sogs pa'i gang mtshams pa rnams gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:2259: bstan pa 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2260: rgyu'i chos 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2261: 'bras bu'i chos 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2263: bcom ldan 'das kyis dga' ldan nas byon pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2265: sangs rgyas pa'i tshul bstan te /
NK124(ngo)001:2266: grong khyer du chos 'byung bar dgongs nas gsungs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2268: rigs mnyam pa la chos nyan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2269: dpon du byed pa mi 'ong zhes nyan du ma 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:2270: des gzhan rnams nyan cing go bar ma byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2272: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK124(ngo)001:2273: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK124(ngo)001:2274: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'dug pas //
NK124(ngo)001:2275: mi smra nags 'dab nyid du gnas par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2277: sgrol rgyu'i tshal du chos ma gsungs pa bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:2278: tshong dpon ga go la dang bzang skyong gnyis kyis
NK124(ngo)001:2279: glang po ches lam du 'gro bar ma 'dod par
NK124(ngo)001:2280: / rtsa'i skyil po gcig la kha gtad nas 'dug pa la ltas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2281: bcom ldan 'das bzhugs par mthong nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2282: tshong dpon gyis yon bdag byas nas chos ston drangs /
NK124(ngo)001:2283: der thams cad kyis chos zhus pas ma gnang pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:2284: tshangs pa 'khor dang bcas pas gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa phul nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2285: ye shes chen po mchog gis dkyil 'khor bsgrub nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:2286: smra ba'i nyi ma ci slad deng 'dir btang snyoms bzhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:2287: dam pa chos kyi rnga bo che ni rdung du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2288: chos kyis mchod sdong chen po dus 'dir sbreng du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2289: ces pa la sogs pa'i gsol ba btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2290: sngon la mdo' shis pa brjod par gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:2291: de nas ba ra na se la sogs par bka'
NK124(ngo)001:2292: dang po bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo skor
NK124(ngo)001:2293: ba dang / bya rgod phung po'i ri la mtshan
NK124(ngo)001:2294: nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba dang
NK124(ngo)001:2295: ba dang / / yul yangs pa can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2296: grong khyer rtsa mchog la sogs par /
NK124(ngo)001:2297: don dam par nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2298: gnyis pa gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2299: bcom ldan 'das mya ngan la 'da' khar gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan te /
NK124(ngo)001:2301: nga ni 'di nas mi snang bar //
NK124(ngo)001:2302: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2303: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:2304: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:2305: mi las skal ldan rigs can te //
NK124(ngo)001:2306: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:2307: sngon gyi ltar snang snang bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:2308: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:2309: grogs kyis sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK124(ngo)001:2310: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:2311: lag na rdo rje ston par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:2313: de la rgyud lung man ngag gsum las /
NK124(ngo)001:2315: bcom ldan 'das mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyer brgyad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2316: rgyal po la rmi ltas rnam pa bdun byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2318: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2319: glegs bam char du babs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2320: chos kyi sgro ba byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2321: kun gyis dam par bkur ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2322: pu rtsa chen po byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2323: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2324: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan no //
NK124(ngo)001:2329: srin po lang ka mgrin bcu /
NK124(ngo)001:2330: mi li tsa byi dri med grags pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2331: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la bcom ldan 'das kyi lung bstan pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:2332: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2333: ri ma la ya gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mor lhags nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2334: phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad yid la bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2335: kye ma kye hud kye ma klong /
NK124(ngo)001:2336: ston pa sgron me 'od nub na //
NK124(ngo)001:2337: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK124(ngo)001:2338: ces pa la sogs pa'i gdung tsig nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2340: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje bskul te /
NK124(ngo)001:2341: kyee gsang ba'i bdag po khyod //
NK124(ngo)001:2342: sngon gyi go cha yal lam ci //
NK124(ngo)001:2343: 'jig rten gdung ba mi sel lam //
NK124(ngo)001:2344: snying pos sa la babs nas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:2345: 'jig rten gdung ba gsal bar rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:2347: gsang bdag gis gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes //
NK124(ngo)001:2348: thog ma tha ma med pa ru //
NK124(ngo)001:2349: bskul ba'i dus ni gang byung yang //
NK124(ngo)001:2350: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK124(ngo)001:2352: ri ma la ya'i rtser byon nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2353: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la /
NK124(ngo)001:2354: mdo dgongs 'dus la sogs pa gsungs tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:2355: de'i tshe rgyal po in dra b+ho d+hi des ri ma la ya'i sked par /
NK124(ngo)001:2356: gsang sngags phyi rgyud yo ga'i bsgrub pa mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK124(ngo)001:2357: gong bzhin rmis ltas bdun byung ba'i tha ma la /
NK124(ngo)001:2358: nangs par sgrub khang gi thog tu ltas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2359: gser gyi glegs bam la bed+aur+ya zhun mas bris pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mang po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2360: phyag rdor gyis sku gcig kyang byon 'dug go //
NK124(ngo)001:2362: gzhan gang yang shes pa ma byung /
NK124(ngo)001:2363: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i le'u shes te /
NK124(ngo)001:2364: de nyid kyis sgo nas bsgrubs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:2365: sku de nyid la gsol ba btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2366: gsang bdag dngos su byon nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2367: tan tra chen po sde bco brgyad pa sgyu 'phrul
NK124(ngo)001:2368: phyag rgya chen po'i rgyud sde rnams gsungs tshul lo
NK124(ngo)001:2369: // bka' rdzogs pa chen po rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad rdzogs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2371: ru kun dga' snying po la /
NK124(ngo)001:2372: rmi ltas rnam pa bzhi byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2373: thub pa drug gis bskor ba byas te ru la thim pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2374: bdud dang khyab 'jug gu lang gyur mig du zos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2375: phyag tu nyi zla thogs te 'jig rten khams kyis mun pa gsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2376: nam mkha' la sprin gser gyi mdog lta bu las char babs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2377: rtsi thog rgyas par smin nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2378: lha'i dbang po rgya byin la bshad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2379: lha'i dbang pos rtsol med kyi bstan pa 'byung bar shes te /
NK124(ngo)001:2380: rgyal ba rnams la rtsol med kyis bstan pa bshad du gsol /
NK124(ngo)001:2383: kye dus gsum gshegs pa rgyal ba yis //
NK124(ngo)001:2384: rtsol bcas theg pa mthar bstan te //
NK124(ngo)001:2386: rtsol med theg pa bshad du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2388: rgyal ba rnams kyis rdo rje sems dpa' bskul nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2389: rdo rje sems dpas phyag na rdo rje thugs kar sprul nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2390: chos 'chad pa'i skyes bur dbang bskur te /
NK124(ngo)001:2392: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:2394: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:2395: khyod ni smra ba'i seng+ge ste //
NK124(ngo)001:2396: rtsol med 'dus pa'i gang zag la //
NK124(ngo)001:2397: lhun grub theg pa gsung du gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:2399: gsang ba'i bdag pos rigs lnga la /
NK124(ngo)001:2400: gzhi 'bras kyi the tshom bcad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2401: lha gnas gsum du rtsol med kyis theg pa gsung tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2402: de nas gsang bdag phyag na rdo rjes /
NK124(ngo)001:2403: sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje gsang ba rdzogs pa chen po'i bdag por dbang bskur nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2404: u rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling du /
NK124(ngo)001:2405: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs pa rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:2406: rtsol med rdzogs pa chen po'i chos gsung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:2407: de dag rgyas par rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2408: gnyis pa bye brag tu skyes tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2409: bla ma yi dam dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2411: dang po bla ma mos gus kyis spyi bor b+hee la gsol ba btab na /
NK124(ngo)001:2412: dgongs pa mnyam nyid du 'gyur zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:2413: sangs rgyas bas kyang lhag par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2414: a ti bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:2415: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:2416: bla ma gnyen par shes par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:2419: des na bla ma spyi bor b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:2420: rdo rje slob dpon b+hee pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:2421: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa'i lha //
NK124(ngo)001:2422: 'bum b+hee pa yi bsod nams kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:2423: bla ma b+hee pa'i 'bum char min //
NK124(ngo)001:2425: gsum pa dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro zhing gsol ba btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2426: thugs rje dang byin rlabs 'byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:2427: skyabs 'og tu tshud pa la sogs pa'i yon tan dpag tu med par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2429: gang gis dkon mchog gsum po la //
NK124(ngo)001:2430: skyabs su 'gro bar byas nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:2431: yon tan de la gzugs mchis na //
NK124(ngo)001:2432: nam mkha' 'di yang snod du chung //
NK124(ngo)001:2434: yid kyis lha b+hee zhing gsol ba btab na /
NK124(ngo)001:2435: dus nam zhig nas zhal mthong gsung thos pa la sogs pa'i byin rlabs kyi 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2437: lha dang lha ru mchod byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2438: lha dang gnyis su med par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:2440: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2442: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed /
NK124(ngo)001:2444: thugs rje skye tshul bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:2445: lnga pa thugs skyes nas don mdzad tshul ni gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:2448: bka' dang rgyud man ngag gis khog dbub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2450: rten can gyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2451: rten med kyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2452: ngo bo nyid kyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2454: sems tsam kri yog sde gsum la sogs pa'i lugs kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:2455: sangs rgyas nyid kyi gzugs sku rang 'od sgo re ba gcig 'og min na yod la /
NK124(ngo)001:2456: de dang de'i sprul pas don mdzad par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:2457: rgyas par 'og nas theg pa rang gzhung nas ston par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:2461: dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa las spang bya blo bur gyi dri ma dag pa'i /
NK124(ngo)001:2462: dag pa gnyis kyi bdag nyid du bzhugs la /
NK124(ngo)001:2463: de la gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis byung nas don mdzad par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2464: yang chos sku stong pa la byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2465: gzugs sku gnyis gdul bya'i snang ngor tsam du 'dod pa yang yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:2466: de ni sngon gyi smon lam gyi stobs las 'byung bar 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:2467: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu las /
NK124(ngo)001:2468: longs sku sprin lta bu 'byung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2469: de las sprul sku char lta bu 'byung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2470: don mdzad zer ba yang yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:2471: rgyas pa 'og nas ston par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:2472: gsum pa ngo bo nyid kyis don mdzad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2474: gdul bya sems can gnyis dbyer med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:2475: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2477: chos kun rang byung ston pa'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:2479: nyid las mi zhen rang byung nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:2481: gong gi mkhyen pa'i lung tshig bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:2483: spyir sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2484: gang la gang 'dul ci ltar mtshams pa ltar du don mdzad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:2486: rgyu mtshan nyid pa ltar na /
NK124(ngo)001:2487: mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pas don mdzad par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2489: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2490: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2491: lhums su zhugs dang bltams pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2492: bzo'i gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2493: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis bskor ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2494: rol rtsed chen po mdzad pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2495: nges 'byung dka' ba spyad pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2496: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2497: bdud sde chen po btul ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2500: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyis kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2501: de bzhin du gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang
NK124(ngo)001:2502: phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad par
NK124(ngo)001:2503: gsungs so // mdo'i lugs kyis phyin ci log gis
NK124(ngo)001:2504: gdul bya rgyud nas dag pa'i don la 'dren pas
NK124(ngo)001:2505: gsungs so // / thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2506: grong khyer gsum gyi don du sku gsum du snang
NK124(ngo)001:2507: nas don mdzad pa ni yul dang mthun pa'i mdzad
NK124(ngo)001:2508: pa dang / sprul pa'i sku des drangs don gyi chos gsungs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2509: 'da' khar gsang sngags kyi chos phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2512: gdul thabs gsum gyis gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi las rgyun gcod pa'i mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2513: ston pa 'chad pa'i mdzad pa dang lngas don mdzad par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2514: rgyas par rang rang gi gzhung bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:2516: 'gro drug gi snang tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bstun nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2517: thabs mkhas theg pa sna tshogs kyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2519: 'gro drug gi snang ba dang bstun nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2521: 'dod yon lngar snang nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2522: phyi nang gi skal pa zung gsum ya drug gis don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2525: lha dang lha min gnas rigs su //
NK124(ngo)001:2526: che ba nga rgyal 'joms par bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:2527: shes pa mi yi gnas rigs su //
NK124(ngo)001:2528: dge sdig rgyu 'bras sde snod bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:2529: gti mug byol song gnas rigs su //
NK124(ngo)001:2530: rig pa shes pa'i chos kyang bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:2531: bkres skom yi dwags gnas rigs su //
NK124(ngo)001:2532: bkres 'phongs sel ba'i chos kyang bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:2533: sdug bsngal dmyal ba'i gnas rigs su //
NK124(ngo)001:2534: snga phyi dran pa'i zhen pa bzlog /
NK124(ngo)001:2538: 'dod yon lngar snang nas kyang rang bzhin gyis don mdzad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2540: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung //
NK124(ngo)001:2541: 'dod lnga kun du sbyor bas yang //
NK124(ngo)001:2542: sangs rgyas thugs rje rol par shar //
NK124(ngo)001:2543: thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' ltar shar //
NK124(ngo)001:2546: phyi nang gis bskal pa zung gsum ya drug tu
NK124(ngo)001:2547: snang nas las ngan gyi rgyun gcod pa yin te
NK124(ngo)001:2549: nad dang mu ge mtshon nyid dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2550: me chu rlung gis bskal pa stong //
NK124(ngo)001:2551: de dag rims par gyis bstan pa //
NK124(ngo)001:2552: thugs rje rmad 'byung rol pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:2553: gdul bya'i thabs su ston pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2555: thabs mkhas theg pas don mdzad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:2556: rtsol ba'i rim pa theg pa brgyad kyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2557: rtsol med a tis don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2559: rang rang gis skabs dang sbyar nas bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2560: gsum pa rgyud dang man ngag gis khog dbub pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:2561: bka' dang bstan bcos kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2562: rgyud lung man ngag gis khog dbub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2565: bye brag so so'i dbye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2567: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK124(ngo)001:2568: chos rnams thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis su 'dus //
NK124(ngo)001:2569: legs par bshad dang de'i dgongs 'grel dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2570: de'i dbang gis sh+aakya'i bstan pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:2571: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:2573: legs par gsung pa ni bka' yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:2574: de'i dgongs pa 'grel pa ni bstan bcos so //
NK124(ngo)001:2575: yang ston pa sangs rgyas kyi bdag rkyen las byung zhing legs par gsungs pa ni bka'/
NK124(ngo)001:2576: de la rten cing de'i dgongs pa ma nor 'grel pa ni bstan bcos so //
NK124(ngo)001:2577: gnyis pa bye brag so so'i dbye' ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2578: bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:2580: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2581: byin gyis rlabs pa'i bka' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2584: sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas gsungs pa rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2586: sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'i dus na /
NK124(ngo)001:2587: ston pa'i byin rlabs kyis sku dang gsung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2588: thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs so //
NK124(ngo)001:2590: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang po'i spyi bor /
NK124(ngo)001:2591: ston pas phyag gser gyi mdog can bzhag nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2592: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po kun tu bzang po khyod kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:2593: sangs rgyas phal po che la spobs par gyis shig gsungs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2594: byang chub sems dpa' des phal po che gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2595: gsung gis byin gyi rlabs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2596: rab 'byor la rab 'byor khyod kyis shes rab kyis
NK124(ngo)001:2597: pha rol du phyin pa spobs par bzung zhig gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:2598: pas / rab 'byor gyis 'phags pa bsdud pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2599: thugs kyis byin gyis rlabs la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:2600: thugs ting nge 'dzin gyis byin gyi rlabs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2602: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la /
NK124(ngo)001:2605: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa
NK124(ngo)001:2606: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gis shes rab kyis pha
NK124(ngo)001:2607: rol du phyin pa gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2608: thugs rjes byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2609: ston pa'i bdag rkyen gyis gnod sbyin la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2612: glang po che la sogs pa rnams kyis chos bshad pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2613: thugs rje bden stobs kyis byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2617: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2618: rtsigs pa la sogs pa rnams las /
NK124(ngo)001:2619: 'bum la sogs pa'i chos byung ba lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2620: gsum pa rjes su gnang ba'i bka' ni sangs rgyas
NK124(ngo)001:2621: kyi nga'i bka' rnams la dang po gleng gzhi'i tshig
NK124(ngo)001:2622: chug bar du mtshams sbyor gyi tshig chug /
NK124(ngo)001:2623: tha ma rjes su yi rang ba'i tshig chug /
NK124(ngo)001:2624: ces gsungs pa lung bstan pa las byung ba rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2626: ston pa mngon par sangs rgyas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2627: ci srid mya ngan ma 'das bar //
NK124(ngo)001:2628: byung ba gang yin bka' ru grags //
NK124(ngo)001:2630: tshad ma'i zhal nas byung bas na //
NK124(ngo)001:2631: bka' yi nges tshigs 'grub pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2633: bka' spyi dang bye brag gi dgongs pa 'grel pa rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2634: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi dgongs pa 'grel pa rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2635: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa ltar yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2636: rje btsun byams pa'i gsungs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2637: ci ltar sgron glog nor bu nyi zla la //
NK124(ngo)001:2638: brten nas mig dang ldan rnams lta ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:2639: thub la brten nas ngas 'di yang dag bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:2640: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:2642: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2643: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyobs byed gang yin pa //
NK124(ngo)001:2644: chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK124(ngo)001:2645: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyis lugs na med //
NK124(ngo)001:2648: sa'i dbang phyug man chad nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2649: gang zag sad pa yan chad la //
NK124(ngo)001:2650: byung ba gang yin bstan bcos te //
NK124(ngo)001:2652: gnyis pa rgyud lung man ngag gis khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2655: de yang phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshang zhing 'brel dang ma tshang ba med pa gcig rgyud /
NK124(ngo)001:2656: dpag par dka' ba'i don mngon sum ston pa lung /
NK124(ngo)001:2658: bya sla la don che bas man ngag go //
NK124(ngo)001:2660: phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshang zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:2661: 'brel dang ma tshang med pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:2662: yongs su rdzogs pas rgyud ces bya' //
NK124(ngo)001:2665: thabs che tshegs chung don dpag med //
NK124(ngo)001:2667: gnyis pa bye brag la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:2668: rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyis dbye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2671: zhus len 'dres mar gsungs shing tshang la 'brel pas rgyud /
NK124(ngo)001:2672: sangs rgyas kyi zhal ma slad cing ci bzhin gsungs pa'i cha nas lung /
NK124(ngo)001:2673: don nyid mngon du phyung ba'i cha nas man ngag go //
NK124(ngo)001:2675: gsung gis 'gyur ba de mtshon na //
NK124(ngo)001:2676: skyes bu rgyal po'i bka' lung bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:2678: skyes bu rgyal po'i bka' rgyud yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2679: de nyid nges pa kho na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2681: ma slad ci bzhin bcas pas lung //
NK124(ngo)001:2682: rtogs chen yan lag 'brel bcas rgyud //
NK124(ngo)001:2685: ngo bo gcig la rgyu mtshan phyogs res nas gsum du phye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:2687: gsum du snang ba gcig tu zad //
NK124(ngo)001:2688: dbyer med tshul gyis rang bzhin las //
NK124(ngo)001:2689: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK124(ngo)001:2692: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:2693: 'bangs dang rje dang rgyal po'i tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:2694: gcig la gcig rten gcig gis ngang //
NK124(ngo)001:2695: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK124(ngo)001:2697: gnyis pa khog dbub pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:2698: rgyud kyis khog dbub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2699: man ngag gi khog dbub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2700: rgyud dang 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2702: yongs rdzogs pa rgyud kyis don dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2703: rgyud gang la gsungs shing btad pa dang bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2704: rang rang gi skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:2705: gnyis pa man ngag la drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2713: khongs nas khongs su rgyud pa'i dgongs pa'i nyams len la bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2714: don spyi dang rang gis mtshan nyid nyams su myong ba gcig dgos gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2717: nyams su blang ba'i lag len la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2719: rje sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge'i zhal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2721: nges par myur du 'grub pas man ngag yin gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2722: yang ka dang nyams su myong ba'i don mngon du
NK124(ngo)001:2723: phyung nas ston pa gcig la man ngag ces bya'o
NK124(ngo)001:2725: lung gi dgongs pa rnams lta bar mi nus pa'i don du /
NK124(ngo)001:2726: gang zag gis lung gi bcud phyung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:2727: rtogs shing nyams su myong ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:2729: snyan rgyud zhal gyis gdams pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2730: khyad par stong nyid rang grol ba'i man ngag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2731: yi ge kun gyis man ngag go //
NK124(ngo)001:2733: kun bzang rdor 'chang man chad du yi ge ris su bris ma myong /
NK124(ngo)001:2734: bris pa dang 'gal ma myong ba'i don mtshon pa la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2738: tha mar brda' bral stong nyid rang grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:2739: gsum pa yi ge kun gyis man ngag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2740: tshig dang yi ge ris su bris pa'i man ngag la bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2741: de kho na nyid ston pa'i man ngag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2742: mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:2744: gnas skabs de kho na nyid ston pa'i theg pa
NK124(ngo)001:2745: 'og ma rnams kyi rang rang gis mthar thug gi
NK124(ngo)001:2747: mthar thug gi de kho na nyid ston pa a ti'i man ngag rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2748: gnyis pa mngon par rtog pa'i rim pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:2749: theg pa spyi dang bye brag la 'jug pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2750: rgyud spyi dang bye brag la 'jug pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2751: lam spyi dang bye brag la 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2752: de yang theg pa spyi la 'jug pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2755: snang ba bcun pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2756: theg pa bye brag ni rang rang gi skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:2758: dbu' zhabs mtshon pa'i 'brel pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2759: tri ka dang man ngag rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2760: rgyud bye brag la 'jug pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2762: rgyud kyi don phun sum tshogs pa la 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2764: sgyu 'phrul lam rim la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2765: lam rgyas par bstan pa rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:2766: lam bye brag ni cha rkyen lta ba ting 'dzin la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2767: slab pa'i mtha' bcu la sogs bye brag re re nas ston pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:2768: lnga pa rtsam pa'i tshad la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:2769: mdo sde las brten nas bstan bcos rtsam pa'i tshad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2770: rgyud sde la brten nas man ngag rtsam pa'i tshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2771: dang po ni lung la 'dres shing tshad la mkhas pa sgra dang don gnyis gtso bor gyur pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2772: rig pa'i bstan bcos brtsam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2775: mngon sum dang rjes dpag gi tshad la mkhas pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2776: rang gis don spyi dang mtshan nyid khongs su tshud pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2777: bstan bcos rtsam par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2780: rang gis nyams myong man ngag ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:2781: yongs su shes pa'i dngos po rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:2782: tshad du shes pa gdams pas bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:2783: ces pa lung gis tshig dang don gyis dgongs pa khrol ba /
NK124(ngo)001:2784: rang gis rtogs shing nyams su myong ba /
NK124(ngo)001:2785: khong nas khongs su rgyud pa'i gdams ngag dang ldan pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2786: shes pa'i dngos po bcu la mkhas pas rtsam par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2788: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab /
NK124(ngo)001:2789: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yis //
NK124(ngo)001:2790: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2791: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK124(ngo)001:2792: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2794: rab chos nyid kyis bden pa mthong ba /
NK124(ngo)001:2795: 'bring yi dam lha'i zhal mthong lung bstan thob pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2796: tha ma shan 'byed cing la zlas pa'i bka' lung gis tshig la mkhas pas rtsam par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2799: thos chung par bu yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2800: man ngag spyi don rtsis sgo lnga yis gzhoms sam /
NK124(ngo)001:2802: yid ches shing khungs tsun pa'i phyir slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2803: bka' dang mig gsal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2804: rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gang du gtogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2805: bstan pa la mtshan nges shing don gyis mdo tsam rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2806: mtshan ci la btags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2807: dgos byed dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2808: gang gis don du mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2809: dbu' zhabs kyi don khongs su chud par bya ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2810: dbu' zhabs kyi don du bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2811: de rnams rang rang gis skabs dang sbyar la bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2812: bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis rgyud man ngag 'chad kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:2813: spyi don lnga dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:2815: dang po yid ches khungs ni bstan pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2816: lo rgyus don gyis bshad lugs bstan par bya /
NK124(ngo)001:2817: chos kun rtsa ba sems su 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2818: de nas rtsa ba'i don de bstan par bya /
NK124(ngo)001:2819: theg pa'i khyad par so so phye ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2820: yo ga don gyi rtsa ba bstan par bya /
NK124(ngo)001:2821: rtsol sgrub bya mi dgos par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:2822: dgos byed don gyis dgongs pa de ru bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:2823: ma rtogs don de rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:2824: tshig gis don de sgra ru brjod par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:2827: man ngag khung phyung ldugs pos dang //
NK124(ngo)001:2828: 'jug sgo theg pa yo ga'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:2829: rten gyis gang zag dgos pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:2830: dril nas mtshan gsol rtsa ba'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:2831: dbu' zhabs dkyus bshad tshig gis don //
NK124(ngo)001:2832: spyi don lnga yis bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2834: de la dang po don gyis rgyud pa can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2835: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon pa //
NK124(ngo)001:2836: man ngag tshad mas rang mtshan ston //
NK124(ngo)001:2837: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag rgyud //
NK124(ngo)001:2839: rgyal ba dgongs pas rgyud pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2841: gang zag snyan khung rgyud pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2842: dang po lo rgyus bstan pa ni la bcu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2843: ston pa sangs rgyas kyi che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2844: bstan pa dam chos kyi che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2849: sgrub po grub thob kyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2850: gtan la phebs pa gzhi'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2852: mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i che ba bcu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2854: ston pa yongs rdzogs kyis che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2855: gzhi rang bzhin gyis ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK124(ngo)001:2856: 'khrul ma myong pas ston pa sangs rgyas kyi che
NK124(ngo)001:2858: sde snod gsum la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2859: sprul pa'i sku re res gsung pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:2860: bka' rdzogs pa chen po ni sku lnga yongs rdzogs kyis sangs rgyas kyi gsungs pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:2862: rang byung gis ston pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2863: ye ci bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas las 'khrul ma myong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2866: theg pa so so'i sangs rgyas las /
NK124(ngo)001:2867: phyogs 'dzin dang lam bsgrod ma myong bas khyad par du 'phags pas /
NK124(ngo)001:2868: 'bras bu rtogs pa mngon gyur gyis sangs rgyas las
NK124(ngo)001:2869: lam gyis rtogs ma myong bas khyad par du 'phags
NK124(ngo)001:2870: so // de dag gis lung ni 'khrul ma myong gis skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:2871: gnyis pa bstan pa dam chos kyi che ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:2872: bstan pa yongs su rdzogs ma rdzogs kyis khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2873: che ba rgyu mtshan lnga'i khyad par du 'phags pa bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2874: dang po ni theg pa rim pa dgu las mtshan nyid kyis theg pa gsum ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2877: yang sde snod rnam pa gsum las /
NK124(ngo)001:2878: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong du gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2879: gsang sngags phyi rgyud gsum ni 'bras bu spyi'i rnam pa tsam lam du byed pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:2880: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i bstan pa gtso che bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2881: de la yang rgyud sde dpag tu med pa yod par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2882: nang pa dbang gyur thabs kyi theg pa gsum ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2883: sku lnga lhun grub kyis bstan pa yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:2884: khyad par du ngo bo nyid kyis sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2886: de la ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2887: 'bras bu rang gi mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lam
NK124(ngo)001:2888: du byed cing 'khor 'das gnyis su med par ston
NK124(ngo)001:2889: pa yin / ma h+aa ni sgyu 'phrul sde bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2890: tan tra chen po sde bac+wo brgyad la sogs pa
NK124(ngo)001:2891: dpag tu med cing brjod las 'das par yod par
NK124(ngo)001:2892: gsungs / a nu ni lung gis bam mdo chen po lnga la sogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2895: chos kun rang byung ye shes la las rgyud gnyis su med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:2896: 'khor 'das gnyis med rgya chad phyogs lhungs med par gtan la 'bebs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2897: de yang a nu man chad kyi theg pa yongs su rdzogs par ston la /
NK124(ngo)001:2898: khyad par a ti'i bstan pa nam mkha' dang 'dra ste mtha' med par stan /
NK124(ngo)001:2899: de yang phyogs tsam gcig mtshon na /
NK124(ngo)001:2905: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa gdams ngag gi skor dang drug go //
NK124(ngo)001:2906: sems sde ma bu bco brgyad de /
NK124(ngo)001:2907: rmad byung dang rig pa mchog gi rgyud la sogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2908: rgyud sde chen po bco brgyad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2910: phyi 'gyur bcu gsum la sogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:2911: gdams ngag bco brgyad la sogs pa dpag tu med pa yod par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2912: klong sde'i skor la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:2914: glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud la sogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2915: zer bu brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK124(ngo)001:2917: rig pa rtsal gyi rgyud la sogs pa'i man ngag brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK124(ngo)001:2918: gsang ba rgyud bu chung gis skor la /
NK124(ngo)001:2919: rin chen bkod pa'i rgyud la sogs pa bsam gtan brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK124(ngo)001:2920: dgongs pa gtad rgya'i skor la /
NK124(ngo)001:2921: klong chen rab byams kyi rgyud la sogs pa brgya dang brgyad cu gsungs par gsal /
NK124(ngo)001:2922: rgyud sde'i skor la nam mkha' mtha' mnyam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2923: nya mo 'khor lo'i rgyud la sogs pa rgyud bzhi
NK124(ngo)001:2924: bcu zhe gnyis man ngag dang bcas pa yod par
NK124(ngo)001:2926: bram ze rtsa ba'i rgyud drug /
NK124(ngo)001:2927: yan lag gi rgyud sum cu rtsa drug gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2928: de la nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2929: ye shes gting rdzogs kyi rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2930: kun tu bzang po ye shes klong gi rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2931: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2932: nges don 'dus pa gter gyi rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2933: 'khor ba rtsad gcod kyi rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2934: spyi rgyud ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2935: la zla rgyal po'i skor ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2936: bkris dus tshod 'dzin pa khu byug rol pa'i rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2937: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2938: sgron ma gsang ba bkod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2939: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2940: rig pa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud la sogs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK124(ngo)001:2941: man ngag gi rgyud sde brgya tham pa /
NK124(ngo)001:2942: man ngag dang bcas pa yod par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2944: gab pa mngon du phyung ba'i skor dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2945: rig pa gtan la phebs sgeg pa'i skor dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2946: chos nyid ma bu ngo sprad pa'i rdzong 'phrang gi skor dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2947: rang grol mngon du stan pa rgyud tha ma'i skor dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2948: de re re la yang rgyud sde man ngag dang bcas pa yod par gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:2949: de rnams kyi khongs nas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:2950: mu stegs pa'i log rtog bsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2951: theg pa brgyad kyis shan 'byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2952: rdzogs pa chen po la zla ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2953: rang grol mngon sum du ngo sprod pa la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:2954: pa theg pa thams cad kyi 'dod lugs yod par
NK124(ngo)001:2955: gsungs so // rke tshang gi skor la /
NK124(ngo)001:2959: yang gsang bla na med pa'i skor la sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2962: spros bral don gsal gyi skor /
NK124(ngo)001:2965: kun grol gyi skor la sogs pa brjod las 'das pa yod par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:2966: gnyis pa che ba bdun nam lnga'i khyad par du 'phags pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:2967: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin pa'i che ba ri rgyal lhun po lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2968: lung thams cad kyi rgyal po yin pa'i che ba nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2969: bka' thams cad kyi 'grel pa yin pa'i che ba
NK124(ngo)001:2970: nam mkha' dwangs nas snod bcud thams cad gsal ba
NK124(ngo)001:2971: lta bu dang / bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung
NK124(ngo)001:2972: gnas yin pa'i che ba nam mkha' las 'byung ba
NK124(ngo)001:2973: lnga snang ba lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2974: man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin pa'i che
NK124(ngo)001:2975: ba rgyal po'i bka' lung thog pa'i mi lta bu
NK124(ngo)001:2976: dang / don thams cad kyi 'jug sdud yin pa'i che ba /
NK124(ngo)001:2977: mgron po don 'grub nas rang khyim du 'ong ba lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:2978: chos thams cad kyi me long yin pa'i che ba me long g.ya' dag pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:2980: gling dang ri bo mu 'khyud bcas //
NK124(ngo)001:2981: lhun po'i rtse mo nyid nas gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:2982: ci snyed theg pa'i rnam grangs kun //
NK124(ngo)001:2983: bdag nyid chen po nyid mthong gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:2986: gza' ldan rgyal po nyi ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:2987: chos kun yongs rdzogs gsal ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:2988: kun snang chen po de nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:2990: go skabs chen po nam mkha' ni //
NK124(ngo)001:2991: chen po nyid ni go 'byed ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:2992: gsungs shing 'dus pa de nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:2993: brjod pa'i tshig kun gsal bar 'grol //
NK124(ngo)001:2995: gang gis bka'i gsang thos nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2996: mi gang gzhan la rags ma las //
NK124(ngo)001:2997: gsang ba'i snying por kun chub nas //
NK124(ngo)001:2998: smra brjod gang la yang rtsal mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:3000: rgyud dang bcas pa'i 'byung ba rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:3001: nam mkha'i ngang nas 'byung zhing snang //
NK124(ngo)001:3002: de ni smra brjod 'byung ba rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:3003: de nyid zab mo'i dbyings nas 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:3005: don du bya ba'i rnam grangs kun //
NK124(ngo)001:3007: rnam grangs rgya che brjod mod kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:3008: de kun de bzhin nyid du 'dus //
NK124(ngo)001:3010: me long gsal ba'i snying po ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3011: gzhan gyi gzugs brnyan ston pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:3012: de bzhin chos kyi me long gis //
NK124(ngo)001:3013: kun gyi rang bzhin gsal bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:3015: gsum pa mkhas pa pan+di ta'i che ba ni rig 'dzin rnam pa gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3016: rdzogs pa chen po 'khor 'das dbyer med chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3017: rig pa mchog la mnga' brnyes pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3018: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3020: bi ma la mi tra la sogs te mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3022: dam pa'i rigs can lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3023: slob dpon chen po h'u ka ra dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3024: 'gu ru pad ma 'byung gnas la sogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3025: de rnams kyis chos nyid rgyun chad med par mngon sum du rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3026: lha ma srin bran du 'khol zhing snang srid dbang du bsdud pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3027: sgra sgyur sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa la mnga' brnyes zing /
NK124(ngo)001:3028: rigs drug gis skad la thogs pa med par chos ston nus pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3029: bzhi pa sgra sgyur lo ts+aa'i che ba /
NK124(ngo)001:3032: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3033: bee ro tsa na la sogs pa'i lo pan brgya
NK124(ngo)001:3034: rtsa brgyad rnams rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas shing
NK124(ngo)001:3035: / sgra sgyur sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa mkhyen pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3036: rigs drug gi skad la thogs pa med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:3037: snyan gyis dus gcig la chos nyan nus pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3038: bstan pa thams cad thugs la rdzogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3039: rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3040: sprul pa sku'i lo ts+aa ba yin gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:3041: lnga pa yon bdag zhing gis che ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3042: rgyal po mes dbon rnam gsum sprul pa'i sku yin par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3043: lha tho tho ri'i snyan shal ni phyag na rdo rje'i sprul pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3044: srong btsan b+hee po ni spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3045: khri srong sde btsan ni 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi sprul pa yin par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3046: de gsum gyi sku ring la dang po chos kyis dbu brnyes /
NK124(ngo)001:3048: tha ma khri srong sde btsan gyis ring la dar zhing rgyas par mdzad do //
NK124(ngo)001:3050: bod du rten bzhengs su ma btub pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:3054: me rtsa bzhi la sogs pa byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:3055: lha sa bsam yas la sogs pa gtsug lag khang brgya rtsa brgyad bzhengs /
NK124(ngo)001:3056: de rnams su rang byung gis lha tshogs mang po dngos su bzhugs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3057: bzhengs pa'i lha tshogs rnams la srong btsan b+hee po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3058: slob dpon pad ma 'byung gnas la sogs pa rnams kyis rab gnas mdzad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3059: ye shes kyi lha dngos su spyan drangs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3060: gnyis su med par bstims pa'i tshe rten thams cad chos kyi sgro ba mdzad par gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:3061: bdun pa grub thob byin gyis rlabs che ba bod
NK124(ngo)001:3062: du gnubs nam mkha'i snying po la sogs pa dge
NK124(ngo)001:3064: a tsa ra dpal dbyangs la sogs pa dpal yang
NK124(ngo)001:3065: dag gi sgo nas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin
NK124(ngo)001:3066: dang / phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sogs pa thob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3067: lus bor ma dgos pa sangs rgyas /
NK124(ngo)001:3068: brgyud pa'i lugs re re la'ang mang du 'byung bar gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:3069: brgyad pa gtan la phebs pa gzhi'i che ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3070: gzhi 'khor 'das dbyer med rang byung ye shes su gtan la phebs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3071: gong du gzhi'i skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3072: dgu pa sgrod pa lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3073: bcu pa mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i che ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3074: gsang sngags kyi gzhi lam 'bras bu'i skabs nas bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3075: spyi don gnyis pa yo ga'i don ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3076: yo ga'i bye brag phye la a ti yo gar la zla'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3078: spyir theg pa rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3079: khyad par du rtsol sgrub can tshe chad pa'i nad dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:3081: ma nor bar la bzlas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3082: rang grol mngon sum du bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3083: bzhi pa dril nas mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3084: chos kun rtsa ba rang byung ye shes su 'dus shing rdzogs la /
NK124(ngo)001:3085: de nyid kyis gong na gzhan med pas rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3086: de la yang bye brag tu phye na /
NK124(ngo)001:3087: mdo sa lu ljang pa la sogs pa dpe' la mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3088: lang kar gshegs pa la sogs pa yul la mtshan btags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3089: rims gsum dang brgya bcu pa la sogs pa grangs la mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3090: lam rim dang gsang snying la sogs pa brjod bya la mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3091: la shan la sogs pa rjod byed la mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3094: klong chen la sogs pa don la mtshan du btags pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3095: de la sogs pa mtshan gyis 'dod lugs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3096: rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:3097: lnga pa dbu zhabs kyis kyus bshad pa tshig gi don /
NK124(ngo)001:3098: rang rang gis skabs bzhin shes par bya /
NK124(ngo)001:3099: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed /
NK124(ngo)001:3101: thugs rje skyes nas don mdzad tshul bstan pa'i le'u ste lnga pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:3102: gsum pa gdul bya lam gyi snang ba la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:3103: nyams su len pa'i rten gang zag ngos bzung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3104: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3105: theg pa'i rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3107: dal 'byor don yod pa bya ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:3108: rnyed dka' zhing don che bar bsam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3109: tshe 'di la mi zhen par bya ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:3110: de nyid mi rtag par shes par bya ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3111: 'khor ba bde sdug dge sdig la rag las phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:3113: nges 'byung gi blo skyed pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:3114: zag pa dang bcas thams cad sdug bsngal du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3117: dal 'byor 'di ni rnyed pa shin tu dka' //
NK124(ngo)001:3118: skyes bus don 'grub thob par 'gyur pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:3119: gal te 'di la phan pa ma bsgrub na //
NK124(ngo)001:3120: phyis nas yang dag 'byor pa ga la 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3123: mi khom pa brgyad dang bral bas dal ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3125: dmyal ba yi dwags dud 'gro dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3126: kla klo tshe ring lha dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3127: log lta sangs rgyas kyis stong pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3128: lkugs pa 'di dag mi khom brgyad //
NK124(ngo)001:3135: mi nyid dbus skyes dbang po tshang //
NK124(ngo)001:3136: las mtha' ma log gnas la dad //
NK124(ngo)001:3140: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la dad pas gnas la dad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3141: log lta ma skyes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3142: las kyi mtha' ma log pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3144: sangs rgyas byon dang des chos gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:3145: bstan pa gnas dang de rjes 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:3146: mkhan po slob dpon sbyin bdag bcas //
NK124(ngo)001:3147: gzhan phyir snying brtse yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3149: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3150: des bstan pa dam chos gsungs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3151: bstan pa yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3152: rang nyid de'i bstan pa la 'jug pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3153: gzhan gyi phyir snying brtse yod pa rnams rang 'byor
NK124(ngo)001:3154: lnga dang mi khom pa brgyad spang pa ngo bo
NK124(ngo)001:3155: gcig ste / mi lus thob pa dang mi ma
NK124(ngo)001:3156: yin gyis 'gro ba bzhi spang ba ngo bo gcig
NK124(ngo)001:3157: gcig ste / / gnas la dad pa dang zhing stong par ma skyes pa ngo bo gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:3158: yul dbus su skyes pa dang kla klo ma skyes pa gcig la /
NK124(ngo)001:3159: dbang po tshang ba dang lkugs par ma skyes pa gnyis gcig cing /
NK124(ngo)001:3160: las kyi mtha' ma log pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3161: log par lta ba spang pa gcig pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3162: dal 'byor ngo bo gcig pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3163: 'on kyang dal ba ni bral ba'i cha yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3164: 'byor pa ni ldan pa'i cha yin pas ldog pa tha dad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3165: de lta bu'i dal 'byor rnyed pa dka' ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3166: gang la rnyed par dka' na mi khom pa'i gnas las rnyed par dka' ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3168: ngan song las ni mi nyid thob par dka' gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:3170: rgyu gang gis rnyed dka' na /
NK124(ngo)001:3171: dge ba phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu las byung ba yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3173: dge ba byed pa'i skabs med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3174: 'bras bu dal 'byor rnyed par dka' ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3176: rgya mtsho gcig na gnya' shing bu ga dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3177: rus sbal phrad pa bas kyang ngan song las //
NK124(ngo)001:3178: mi nyid ches thob dka' bas mi dbang gis //
NK124(ngo)001:3179: dam chos spyad pas de 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK124(ngo)001:3182: sangs rgyas 'byung ba rgya lam rnyed par dka' //
NK124(ngo)001:3183: mi rnyed pa yang shin tu dka' ba ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3184: grogs po gang dag dang pa'i chos nyan pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3185: 'di 'dra skal pa brgyar yang rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3188: mngon par mtho' ba lha mi'i dpal phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3189: nges par legs pa byang chub rnam pa gsum yang /
NK124(ngo)001:3190: dal 'byor la brten nas 'byung ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:3191: gzhan gyis ma yin pas don che ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3193: gang zag zhig thob nas 'gro ba'i rgya mtsho'i mthar phyin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:3194: byang chub mchog gis sa thob dge bas krun gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3195: yid bzhin nor bu bas kyang yon tan lhag pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:3196: mi rnyed de ni su zhig 'bras bu med par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:3198: gnyis pa mi rtag pa'i tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3199: thob pa'i dal 'byor yun ring mi rtag ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3200: 'chi ba'i rkyen ni mang bas nam 'chi cha med la //
NK124(ngo)001:3201: gson pa'i rkyen ni ches nyung bas //
NK124(ngo)001:3202: de nyid kyang 'chi rkyen du 'gyur srid de /
NK124(ngo)001:3204: 'chi ba'i rkyen ni mang ba ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3205: gson pa'i rkyen ni cung zad tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:3206: de dag nyid kyang 'chi ba'i rkyen //
NK124(ngo)001:3207: de bas rtag tu chos mdzod cig /
NK124(ngo)001:3209: de yang nyin zhag la sogs par ltos pa med par myur du mdzad pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3211: nyin mtshan sdod par yongs med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:3213: bsnan pa rgud na yong med na //
NK124(ngo)001:3217: mi'i dbang po gang gis nub mo nas //
NK124(ngo)001:3218: mngal du zhugs te rab tu 'jug gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3219: de nas bzung ste de ni nyin re bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:3220: 'gro shul med par 'chi bdag gzhan du 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:3222: skad cig ma re re 'gag cing 'chi ba la nye bas /
NK124(ngo)001:3223: dper na gsod sar khrid pa'i mi bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3224: de ltar tshe thung la myur du mdzad pa de yang /
NK124(ngo)001:3225: tshe la mthar phyin pa nyung ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3226: blo bur du 'chi ba'i rkyen bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3227: lo phyi ma dang zla ba phyi ma'am /
NK124(ngo)001:3228: mtha' ma nyin zhag gnyis sdod pa'i nges pa med de /
NK124(ngo)001:3230: 'di ni sang bya 'di ni thang gcig 'og tu bya //
NK124(ngo)001:3231: 'di ni de'i ring bya zhes skye bos bsam pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:3232: gshin rje bo con zhags thogs zur gyis lta ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:3233: mig rtsa dmar 'khros ma rangs gad mo re snyams 'debs //
NK124(ngo)001:3236: yid rten mi rung 'chi bdag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3237: byas dang ma byas mi sdod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3238: na dang mi na kun gyis kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:3239: blo bur tshe la yid mi rten //
NK124(ngo)001:3242: sang tsam shi'am sus shes kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:3243: de ring nyid nas btud de bya //
NK124(ngo)001:3244: 'chi bdag dregs can de dag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3245: bdag dang bshes pa ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3247: bdag gis dge sgom ma byas na //
NK124(ngo)001:3248: 'di las slu ba gzhan med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3249: 'di las rmongs pa gzhan med do //
NK124(ngo)001:3252: ci srid du ni 'tsho bsags bya //
NK124(ngo)001:3253: de tshe le lo spangs kyang 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:3254: dus ma yin pa ci zhig bya //
NK124(ngo)001:3256: de yang rang nyid 'chi ba'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:3257: gnyen bshes la sogs gang gis mi phan la /
NK124(ngo)001:3258: bdag nyid mya ngan gyis gdung zhing 'chi ba 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:3260: bdag nyid mal na 'dug bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:3261: gnyen bshes kun gyis mtha' bskor yang //
NK124(ngo)001:3262: srog chad pa yi tshor ba dag /
NK124(ngo)001:3263: bdag nyid gcig pos myong bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3264: gshin rje'i pho nyas zin pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:3265: gnyen pas cis phan gshes cis phan //
NK124(ngo)001:3266: de tshe bsod nams gcig skyabs na //
NK124(ngo)001:3267: de yang bdag gis ma bstan no //
NK124(ngo)001:3269: mi rtag pa b+hee tshe 'di la ma zhen par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3270: gsum pa las 'bras la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:3275: 'dres ma'i las gsum gyis go rims bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:3278: bde sdug 'dres mar myong bar gsungs la /
NK124(ngo)001:3279: yang sbyor ba dkar la bsam pa nag pa'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal 'ba' zhig tu myongs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:3280: sbyor ba nag la bsam pa dkar ba'i 'bras bu bde ba myong bar gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:3281: yang byas la bsags pa'i las ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3283: dad pa log pas mi dge ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3284: dge ba la sbyor ba yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3285: byas la ma bsags pa'i las ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3286: kun slong dge ba'i bsam pa med pa'i bzlas brjod la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3287: bsod nams sems med pa'i bya ba pha rol shi ba la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3288: ma byas la bsags pa'i las ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3289: gzhan gyis dge ba dang mi dge ba la rjes su yi rang bya ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3292: mthong ba'i chos la myong ba 'gyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3293: skyes nas myong ba 'gyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3294: lan grangs gzhan du myong bar 'gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3296: zhing sam phul byung la bsam pa phul byung gis /
NK124(ngo)001:3297: dngos po phul byung gcig spyad nas 'bras bu de nyid la 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3299: zhing dang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i khyad par gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3300: mthong chos 'bras bu can gyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:3303: gang dag 'gog lam nyon mongs med //
NK124(ngo)001:3304: mthong dang dgra bcom 'bras lang ba //
NK124(ngo)001:3305: de la phan gnod byas pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:3308: skyes nas myong ba 'gyur pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3310: tshul khrims 'chal pa la sogs pa'i las sdig /
NK124(ngo)001:3311: tshe phyi ma nges par smin 'gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:3313: sdig pa'i las rnams bgyis pa gang yang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3314: de'i mod la mtshon bzhin mi gcod de //
NK124(ngo)001:3315: 'chi ba'i dus la bab pa gyur pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:3316: las kyi 'bras bu gang lags mngon du 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3318: mtshams med pa mang po byas pa dag kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:3320: sdug bsngal tshor ba mi zad pa mang du myong bar gsungs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3322: skyes nas myong ba'i chos rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3323: thog mar brtsams pa yin gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3325: dmyal ba la yang nas yang du tshe 'phos zhing
NK124(ngo)001:3326: skyes bas rnam par smin pa myong bar gsungs so
NK124(ngo)001:3327: // gzhan ma de dag gi tshe thal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3328: myong ba thams cad lan grangs gzhan las myong ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3330: lus can dag gis las rnams ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3331: skal pa brgyar yang chud mi za' //
NK124(ngo)001:3332: tshogs shing dus la bab pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:3337: mngon par zhen nas 'jug pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3338: gnyen po dang ma 'brel ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3339: zhing yon tan dang ldan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3340: lus nar son te kun slong rtag pos kyang stobs dang ldan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3342: rtag tu mngon par zhen dang gnyen po med //
NK124(ngo)001:3343: yon tan rtsol ldan gzhi las 'byung de ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3344: dge dang mi dge rnam lnga chen po ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3345: de bas dge ba spyad la brtson par gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:3348: las 'bras bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:3355: mtshams med pa la sogs sdig lci ba gzhan gyis rnam bzhag go //
NK124(ngo)001:3360: mi dge ba las kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3361: nyon mongs dug lnga dug gsum gyis bsdus pa'i bya ba sdug bsngal gyis nyer len du 'gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3363: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:3364: de skyed la ni mi dge ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3367: mi dge ba la sdug bsngal byung //
NK124(ngo)001:3370: 'di phyi mi shes pas mi dge ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3371: sgo gsum gyi bya ba yin pas las dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3372: ngan 'gro'i rgyu yin pas lam zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3375: lci yang gis bye brag go //
NK124(ngo)001:3376: dang po srog gcod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3377: yan lag bzhis rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:3379: der shes shing bsam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3381: rjes su mthun pa'i tshor ba myong ba dang des shi ba ste bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3383: gzhan gyis yin zhing de bdag tu bzung ba dang /
