NK124(ngo)001:3384: der shes shing blang par bsam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3387: 'dod pa log par g.yems pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3391: bsgrod bya ma yin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3392: reg la reg tu shes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3394: rjes su mthun pa'i tshor bas myong ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3395: de la gnas ma yin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3399: dkon mchog bzhugs pa'i gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:3401: bsnyen gnas la gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3405: zla mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3406: mi mos shing yid mi bde ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3407: yan lag ma yin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3408: kha dang gshangs lam la sogs pa bud med kyi dbang po las bzhan pa thams cad do //
NK124(ngo)001:3409: bsgrod bya ma yin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3411: chos kyi rgyal mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3412: gzhan gyis bdag gir bzung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3413: rang gi bdun brgyud las mi ring ba'i nye du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3414: bud med dang khyo phyogs kyis nye dus srungs ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3415: rigs dang yon tan gyis srung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:3417: gzhan don che bas spyad mi bzod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3419: don ma nor ba khong du chud pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3420: 'du shes gzhan du bsgyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3424: gzhi sems can yin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3435: smra ba la chags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3439: gzhan gyis yin zhing der shes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3440: bdag gis byas bar nges pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3442: gzhi sems can yin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3443: de la gnod pa bya bar nges pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3445: don phyin ci ma log par gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3446: bsam pa phyin ci log tu nges pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3447: yan lag ma rdzogs na sdig pa byas par 'gyur gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3451: gnod sems la khyad par yod par ma mthong la /
NK124(ngo)001:3452: med na yang nyon mongs pa dang las sam /
NK124(ngo)001:3453: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i khyad par med par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:3456: chags sdang bsam kyang yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3457: 'di nyid bsam sbyor 'tshogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:3458: de ltar chags pas kun nas slangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3459: gzhan gyi yo byad bdag gir bya bar sems na brnab sems yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3460: zhe sdang gis kun nas slangs nas gzhan la gnod pa bya bar sems na gnod sems yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3461: lta ba lnga'i log lta dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3462: las sam log lta'i khyad par yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3463: snga ma ni bsam rkyang yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3464: 'di ni bsam sbyor 'tshogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3465: gti mug gis kun nas slangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3466: skye ba snga phyi la sogs med nges bsnyam pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3467: gnyis pa lci yang gis bye brag gnyis te las /
NK124(ngo)001:3468: ngo bo'i sgo nas lci yang ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3469: yid lus ngag gsum go rim nas lci la /
NK124(ngo)001:3470: yid kyi log lta nas rim gyis lci zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:3471: lus kyis spog gcad na lci la /
NK124(ngo)001:3473: gnyis pa yid kyis sgo nas lci yang ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3474: yul mchog tu gyur pa la mi dge ba gang byas kyang lci la /
NK124(ngo)001:3475: 'bring dang dman pa rnams la rim gyis yang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:3476: gsum pa kun slong gis sgo nas lci yang ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3477: nyon mongs pa rags pob kun nas slangs nas lci zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:3478: chung ngus kun nas slang ba rnams yang la /
NK124(ngo)001:3479: nyon mongs pa'am zhe sdang gis kun nas slangs pa rnams lci la /
NK124(ngo)001:3480: 'dod chags dang gti mug gis slangs pa rnams rim gyis yang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:3481: bzhi pa lan grangs kyi sgo nas lci yang ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3482: mi dge ba gang yang rung ba grangs mang du spyad pa rnams lci la /
NK124(ngo)001:3483: nyung ngu spyad pa rnams yang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:3484: gsum pa gang na yod bsam pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3485: dmyal ba na tshig rtsub ngag 'khyal gnod sems gsum yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3486: dmyal srung la tshig ngan brjod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3488: gcig la gcig zhe sdang yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:3490: las ma zad par bsdad bas mi 'chi ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3491: yid du 'ong ba'i dngos po gang yang med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3492: lus rgud cing sdug bsngal gyis bzir ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3493: 'dod pa'i don thob rgyu med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3494: mdza' bo su yang med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3495: chags gnas ci yang med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3496: las kyi me long la las 'bras mthong ba dran pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:3497: sgra mi snyan pa ngag 'khyal yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3498: chags pas glu len par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:3499: dgu pa mngon gyur med de /
NK124(ngo)001:3500: rim pa ltar tshe nges pas bsad pas mi 'chi ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3501: rdzas dang bud med la bdag bzung med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3502: rdzun dang phra ma tshig rtsub gsum smras pa la dgos pa med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3503: longs spyod la bdag 'dzin med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3504: sems kun nas nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3505: yang dag pa'i lta ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:3506: gzhan nam gling gsum pa'i mi rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3508: yi dwags dang dud 'gro la bcu ka yod pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3513: sdig to mi dge ba'i chos dbyen zhes pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:3514: gnyis pa mtshams med pa lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3515: pha dang ma dang dgra bcom pa bsad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3516: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems kyis khrag 'byin pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3518: de dang nye ba lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3519: pha bsad pa dang nye ba byang chub sems dpa' bsad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3521: nye ba dge slong ma dbang med du khrims dang 'phral ba /
NK124(ngo)001:3522: dgra bcom pa bsad pa dang nye ba 'phags slob pa bsad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3523: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems kyis khrag 'byin pa dang nye ba /
NK124(ngo)001:3525: dbyen byed pa dang nye ba dge 'dun gyis sgo 'phrog pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3526: 'di dag yan lag tshang na der 'gyur gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3527: ma tshang na mtshams med du mi 'gyur ba bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:3529: dge slong rang gis pha rgan la //
NK124(ngo)001:3530: myur 'dong zhes ni skul gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:3531: phul bas de ni shi gyur kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:3532: mtshams med 'gyur ba yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:3534: de las gzhan nam sdig pa lci ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3535: dam pa'i chos spang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3536: byang chub sems dpa'i dge ba'i bar chad byas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3537: byang chub sems la brnyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3540: pha ma la ma gus pa rnams kyang sdig lci bar gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:3541: gzhan log pa'i 'tsho ba rnams kyang lci bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3543: kha bsags gzhogs slong thob phyir 'jal //
NK124(ngo)001:3544: snyed pas snyed pa tshol ba lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:3545: ma dag pa yin 'tsho ba ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3548: tshul chos snyed dang bkur sti'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:3549: dbang po bsdams par byed pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3550: kha bsags snyed bkur sti'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:3552: gzhogs slongs de ni thob bya'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:3553: gzhan gyis rdzas la sngags byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3554: thob phyir 'jal ba snyed pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:3555: mngon sum gzhan la smod byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3556: snyed pas snyed pa slab 'dod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3557: snga ma thob la sngags byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3559: gnyis pa 'bras bu la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:3560: rnam smin dang rgyu mthun dbang gis 'bras bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3562: kun gyis dang po ngan song ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:3564: mi dge ba cher spyad pas dmyal ba /
NK124(ngo)001:3570: mnar med po' yang de tsam mo //
NK124(ngo)001:3571: de'i steng na dmyal ba bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:3572: brgyad po kun la lhag bcu drug /
NK124(ngo)001:3573: de dag gis ni ngos bzhi la //
NK124(ngo)001:3574: me mar mur dang ro myags 'dam //
NK124(ngo)001:3575: yi dwags lam sogs thal tshan chu //
NK124(ngo)001:3576: chu bur can sogs bgrang brgyad bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:3578: 'dzam gling 'di'i mtsho ma dros pa'i 'og na /
NK124(ngo)001:3579: tsha ba'i dmyal ba brgyad rim pa bzhin du yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3581: me dang dmyal srung gis sdug bsngal med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3582: phan tshun rngon pa ri dwags mthong ba lta bur
NK124(ngo)001:3583: gsod pa'i sems su 'gyur zhing lag tu blang ba
NK124(ngo)001:3584: thams cad mtshon cha sna tshogs par 'gyur nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3585: gcig gis gcig la rgyab ste gsod par byed /
NK124(ngo)001:3586: yang sos par gyur cig gis byung nas snga ma bzhin du 'tsho /
NK124(ngo)001:3587: yang 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal mi'i nyin zhag gcig la lan brgya'i bar du 'tsho //
NK124(ngo)001:3588: rta dbyangs nyer bzhag chung ngu las /
NK124(ngo)001:3589: phan tshun 'khon zhing zhe gnod la //
NK124(ngo)001:3590: mi gang mi ni gsod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3591: gzhan nam skyes nas gsod byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3592: de dag nges par ngan song 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:3593: gang gis phyir ni lo stong phrag /
NK124(ngo)001:3594: yang sos yang sos de dag tu //
NK124(ngo)001:3595: bsad cing bsad cing yang 'tsho bas //
NK124(ngo)001:3596: de phyir yang sos zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3599: dmyal ba'i lus la dmyal bsrung gis thig nag po
NK124(ngo)001:3600: btab nas spyi bo dang rkang mthil bar du sog
NK124(ngo)001:3601: les dra zhing stod pa'i tshe smad 'byar la /
NK124(ngo)001:3602: smad dra ba'i tshe stod 'byar la /
NK124(ngo)001:3603: de ltar yang yang byas pa'i sdug bsngal myong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3605: bya men byed du 'jug pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3606: mi rnams 'dza' bo byed byed pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:3607: phra ma rdzun smra ru byed pas //
NK124(ngo)001:3611: ri rab lug gis gdong pa lta bu gnyis kyi bar du ltems nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3615: de ltar yang yang bsdus shing 'joms pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3616: yang lcags kyis gshongs chen por dmyal ba rnams bsdus shing /
NK124(ngo)001:3617: tho ba me 'bar bas 'joms pa'i sdug bsngal dmyong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3619: ri dwags phag dang bya nag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3620: gzhan nam skyes gnas gsod byas rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:3624: lcags kyis khang pa dra mig lta bu me 'bar ba'i nang du bsregs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3625: dra mig nas las la grub pa'i bya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3626: khyi dang sbrul la sogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3627: srog chags mang pos gnod pa byas nas nyams 'thag pa'i sgra 'byin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3629: gzhan bslu g.yo' dang rgyu byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:3630: skye bo dag ni yid phyung pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3635: lcags kyi khang pa'i nang du bsregs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3636: snga ma ltar srog chags rnams kyis gnod pa byed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:3637: sdug bsngal dmyong nas sgra chen po 'byin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3639: gang gis lha dang bram ze dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3640: bla ma'i rdzas la 'phrog sdul byas //
NK124(ngo)001:3641: gang dag snyems pas 'phrogs byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3645: lcags kyi khang pa me 'bar ba'i nang du bsregs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3646: gshin rje'i las mkhan rnams kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3647: lcags zangs dpag med du ma yod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3648: tsha zhing 'bar ba'i nang du bcug nas skol te /
NK124(ngo)001:3649: lcags kyi gsal shing me 'bar rtse gcig pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3650: lus kyi bshang lam nas gtsugs nas spyi bor 'byin pa'i sdug bsngal dmyong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3652: dge sbyong bram ze dge ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3653: de ni gang zag gis pha ma la //
NK124(ngo)001:3654: gnod pa drag pos gnod byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3655: de ni tsha ba rab tu bsregs //
NK124(ngo)001:3658: lcags kyi khang pa me 'bar ba gnyis rim gyis nang du bsregs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3659: lcags kyi gsal shing rtse gsum pas lus kyi bshang lam nas gtsugs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3660: spyi bo dang phrag pa gnyis su 'byin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3661: lcags leb mo tsha zhing 'bar bas lus thams cad dkris pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3662: lcags zangs chen mo'i nang du 'gyur med kyis bskol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3663: kun du 'bar ba'i nang du spyi bo nas 'jug go //
NK124(ngo)001:3664: sha dang lpags pa zhig nas keng rus 'bigs lus po de tshe phyir 'byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:3665: lcags kyis sa gzhi la 'grams nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3666: sha dang khrag lpags pa skyes nas /
NK124(ngo)001:3668: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal myong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3670: med par lta ba gang dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:3671: chos dang chos min log ston cing //
NK124(ngo)001:3672: skye bo dam pa dag la sdang //
NK124(ngo)001:3673: de ni rab tu tsha bar bsreg /
NK124(ngo)001:3676: lcags kyi khang pa ngos re la dpag tshad nyis stong yod pa'i grub bzhi'i nang du bsregs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3682: mnar med me'i phung po bcu gcig tu 'bar zhing bsregs la /
NK124(ngo)001:3683: mdor na khang pa de'i nang du me dang sems can dbyer mi phyed pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3684: skad 'byin pa sems can du ma mngon par zad do //
NK124(ngo)001:3685: sdug bsngal ba tshad med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:3686: dmyal ba gong ma'i sdug bsngal thams cad tshang bar yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3688: yon tan dag gis che ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:3689: gnod pa drag po byas pa'am //
NK124(ngo)001:3690: pha ma bla ma bsad byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:3691: nges par skal pa mnar med 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:3692: gang phyir bde ba'i skabs med phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:3693: de phyir mnar med yin par bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:3695: dus matha'i me bas dmyal ba'i me bdun 'gyur gyis tsha zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:3696: de yang rim gyis 'og ma rnams bzhi 'gyur gyis tsha bar bshad la /
NK124(ngo)001:3697: sdug bsngal de dag kyang mtshon pa tsam te /
NK124(ngo)001:3698: shin tu mang ba dran pa nyer bzhag nas bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:3699: tsha dmyal brgyad po de dag re re bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:3700: 'khor lhag ma bcu drug yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3702: de ltar de dag dmyal ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3703: brgyad ces bya ba rgal ba dka' //
NK124(ngo)001:3704: drag po'i las kyis kun tu gang //
NK124(ngo)001:3705: re re la'ang lhag bcu drug /
NK124(ngo)001:3707: mnar med de'i ngos bzhi'i sdug bsngal gyis las zad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3708: shar sgo lta bu nas mthon te phyin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3711: pus mo nub tsam phyogs bzhir bar mtshams med par
NK124(ngo)001:3712: skor nas yod pa 'bod cing rgam nas 'gro ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:3713: tshe / rkang pa'i sha bsregs te dmar ngar gyis 'gro /
NK124(ngo)001:3714: rkang pa btegs pa dang sha slar skye ba /
NK124(ngo)001:3715: de lta bu la 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3717: gang zag gi brdugs bzang mnos nas //
NK124(ngo)001:3718: legs par bsrung ba mi byed na //
NK124(ngo)001:3719: de ni nges par sha dang rus //
NK124(ngo)001:3720: 'jig pa'i me ma mur du bsregs //
NK124(ngo)001:3722: de'i phyi rol na ro myag gis 'dam zhes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3723: mi gtsang ba shin tu dri mi zhim pas gang
NK124(ngo)001:3724: ba'i 'dams rdzab rked pa nub pa tsam la 'gro
NK124(ngo)001:3725: bas na / srin bu mchu rnon zhes pa lcags
NK124(ngo)001:3726: kyis mchu can dag gis lus sang sing 'bigs par
NK124(ngo)001:3727: bas na / byed do // de nyid las /
NK124(ngo)001:3728: gang du 'tsho ba log pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:3729: cung zad tsam zhig 'tsho byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3731: srin bu rnams kyis za bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3733: mtshon cha'i skor ma gsum la /
NK124(ngo)001:3734: spu gri gtams pa'i lam zhes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3735: spu gri rnon po kha gyen la bltas pa'i thang la 'gro ba'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:3736: rkang pa'i sha rus gcod par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:3738: gang zhig chos kyis rtags 'dzin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:3739: yang dag ma yin lam smra ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:3740: mi dge bas ni spu gri'i so //
NK124(ngo)001:3743: ral gri lo ma'i nags tshul zhes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3744: nags kyis lo ma ral gri 'bar bar 'gyur pa rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:3745: lhung nas lus dum bur phye mar byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3746: des ma bzod nas phyin na /
NK124(ngo)001:3747: khyi sre bo lcags kyi mche ba can gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3748: rbad cing za' ba'i sdug bsngal myong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3750: bag phebs pa la gnod byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:3751: nags tshal ral gri'i 'dab can gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:3752: btubs te ngu zhing bya rog khyi //
NK124(ngo)001:3755: der ma bzod par phyin pas shal ma ri'i sdong
NK124(ngo)001:3756: po lcags kyi tsher ma sor bcu drug tsam la
NK124(ngo)001:3757: 'dzeg ste / yar 'gro ba'i tshe tsher ma kha thur du bltas te /
NK124(ngo)001:3758: sha dum bur dum bur gcod do //
NK124(ngo)001:3759: rtse mor phyin pa na bya kha da 'dabs 'jig ces pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3760: mgo ltoms te glad pa za' bar byed /
NK124(ngo)001:3761: yang thur la 'bab pa na tsher ma gyen la ltas te 'bigs par byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:3763: byi bo byas nas shal ma rir //
NK124(ngo)001:3764: lcags kyis tsher ma rtse mo 'bar //
NK124(ngo)001:3765: so ni bcu drug yod pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:3768: de gsum mtshon char gcig pas gcig tu rtsi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3769: de'i phyi rol na thal tshan gyis chu bo rab med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3770: thal skyol khol mas gang ba rab med pa la lus ril nub pas /
NK124(ngo)001:3771: sha rnams tshos shing rus pa skya zang gis 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3772: phyogs kun skor ba la rgal dgos pa'i sdug bsngal yod /
NK124(ngo)001:3774: chu skyar nya mo bsad pa na //
NK124(ngo)001:3775: chu bo rab med 'bar ba yis //
NK124(ngo)001:3776: zangs kyi khu ba chur 'gyur zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:3777: mi de mes kyang bsregs par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3779: de lta bzhi las med kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:3780: khang pa'i sgo phyogs kyis bcu drug tu rtsi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3781: lhag ma de dag tu dmyal bsrungs lag na mtshon cha sna tshogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3782: skra dngas shing 'bar ba a ba glang mgo dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3785: rngam pa dom mgo la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:3786: dbang med du zlog par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:3787: gzhan yang sor mos shig la sogs pa bsad na /
NK124(ngo)001:3789: de dag lus ni cher 'gyur la //
NK124(ngo)001:3790: stong brgyar yang dang yang du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3794: srog chags mthong nas 'joms pa gang //
NK124(ngo)001:3795: de ni lcags kyis gtun shing gis //
NK124(ngo)001:3796: yang nas yang du brdung bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3798: grang dmyal brgyad kyis gnas ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3799: tsha dmyal nas dpag tshad khri gzhal ba'i byang phyogs na yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3800: grang ches bas lus chu bur byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3801: shin tu grang che bas chu bur rdol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3802: smre ngag la a chu zer ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3804: skad 'byin mi nus pas so tham tham pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3805: lpags pa'i mdog sngon por 'gyur zhing lus lnga'am drug tsam du gas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3807: lpags pa'i mdog dmar por song zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:3808: kha bcu'am de las lhag par gas pas pad ma ltar gas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3809: lus ser ka gting ring po sha dum bu mar chad la khang du mar gas pa /
NK124(ngo)001:3810: pad ma ltar cher gas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3811: de dag tu skyes pa'i rgyu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3812: chos 'chad pa'i 'du khang bshig pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3814: chos kyis na bza' bshus pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3815: 'phags pa la bskur pa btab pa la sogs yin gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:3816: nye tshe ba'i dmyal ba rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3817: rang gis lus la rang gis las kyi sdug bsngal myong ba mdo sde dag las /
NK124(ngo)001:3819: gro zhun skyes pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa las bshad pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3820: de rnams kyi tshe tshad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3826: stong drug brgya ni go rim bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:3832: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyis bar gyis nyin zhag re re yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3833: de rtsis pa'i rang lo brgya /
NK124(ngo)001:3840: rgyal chen bzhi nas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyis bar gyis rang rang gis tshe tshad yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3842: mi rnams lo ni lnga bcu yin //
NK124(ngo)001:3843: 'dod pa dag gis nyin zhag gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:3844: lha rnams 'og ma de dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:3845: des na tshe lo lnga bargya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3847: de rnams kyang go rim bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:3855: rang rang gis nyin zhag re re yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:3856: de rtsis pa'i rang lo brgya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3858: de rnams go rim bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:3864: yang sos nas tsha ba'i bar gyis rang rang gis tshe tshad yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3865: de la dmyal ba yang sos kyi zhag gcig ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3866: mi lo sa ya phrag dgu yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:3868: yang sos la sogs drug rim bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:3869: 'dod lha'i tshe dang nyin zhag mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:3870: des ni de dag rnams kyis tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:3871: 'dod pa'i lha dang mnyam pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:3873: nye tshe nye 'khor pa'i dmyal ba ni nges pa med par gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:3874: grang dmyal rnams kyi tshe tshad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3875: ma ga d+ha'i bres bcal ba'i khal brgyad cu la /
NK124(ngo)001:3876: lo brgya re la til re phyung bas zad pa chu bur can gyi tshe'i tshad yin /
NK124(ngo)001:3877: 'og ma de la nyi shu 'gyur du gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:3879: til sbyangs nang nas lo brgya zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:3880: til gcig phyung pas zad gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3881: chu bor can gyi tshe tshad yin //
NK124(ngo)001:3884: yi dwags la gnas la gnas pa dang mkha' la rgyu ba gnyis yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3886: grong khyer yangs pa can gyi 'og /
NK124(ngo)001:3887: dpag tshad lnga brgya la gnas te //
NK124(ngo)001:3888: de la phyi'i sgrib pa can dag /
NK124(ngo)001:3889: bkres shing skom pa lus sdong dum tshig pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:3890: gdong pa skras kheb cing bzhin mi sdug pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:3891: kun tu zas skom tshol ba la rgyugs kyang mi snyed la /
NK124(ngo)001:3892: cung zad mthong yang gshin rje lag na mtshon cha
NK124(ngo)001:3893: thogs pa rnams kyis bsrungs nas longs spyod dbang med
NK124(ngo)001:3894: pa dang / chu dag kyang rnag khrag tu mthong nas btung du mi rung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:3895: nang gis sgrib pa can dag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3896: kha khab kyi mig tsam du zas mi tshud mgrin pa gzhu rgyud tsam du mi thar /
NK124(ngo)001:3897: lto ba lung pa tsam mi khengs pa la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:3898: zas skom gyi sgrib pa can ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3900: lcags kyi tho lum me 'bar bar 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:3901: lto ba bsreg par 'gyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3902: ljan ljin za ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3903: mi gtsang ba rnams za zhing btung bar byed par skye bar bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:3905: gang gis byis pa rnams la 'tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:3906: srid pa 'grib par byed pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:3907: khong pa'i dri ma za byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3908: lus srul por ni skye bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3909: mi gang spyod pa dman pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3910: shin tu zhums dang ser sna can //
NK124(ngo)001:3911: rtag tu 'dod byed de shi nas //
NK124(ngo)001:3912: yi dwags sna ba can du skye //
NK124(ngo)001:3913: gang gi ci yang mi ster dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3914: sbyin pa zlog par byed pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:3915: yi dwags bkres pas btung ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:3916: bsus che kha ni khab tsam 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3917: gang gi spyod dang byin mi byed //
NK124(ngo)001:3918: rigs kyis don du nor srung na //
NK124(ngo)001:3919: de ni yi dwags tshun ltor spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:3920: shi dus bsngo za der skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3922: byin nas 'gyod pa byed pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:3923: shi nas phyi ma'i skyug pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:3924: za bar byed pa'i yi dwags skye //
NK124(ngo)001:3925: gang zhig khros nas mi snyan smra //
NK124(ngo)001:3927: las de shin tu yun ring bas //
NK124(ngo)001:3929: gang zhig 'thab mo byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3930: ma chags pas na khro byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3931: srin dang sdig sbrul phye leb za //
NK124(ngo)001:3934: zas kyi ched du rtse med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3935: srog chags gsod nas sbyin byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3936: de ni shi nas nges par ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3937: srin bu'i zla dang bcas par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3939: ma rung khro zhing sbyin byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3940: chang zhim bdag la dga' ba'i mi //
NK124(ngo)001:3941: shi nas gnod sbyin ma rungs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3942: chang la dga' ba rnams su skye //
NK124(ngo)001:3943: sred dang ser sna can gyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3944: shi nas yi dwags de rnams 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3945: nyon mongs can dge'i gnod sbyin no //
NK124(ngo)001:3946: de ni de phyir spangs par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:3950: zhag gcig byas pa'i rang lo lnga bargya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3951: mi lo khri lnga stong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:3953: lnga stong dag dang khri yang 'chir mi btub //
NK124(ngo)001:3955: dud 'gro la byings la gnas pa dang kha 'thor ba gnyis la /
NK124(ngo)001:3957: phyi'i rgya mtsho'i nang na chang dang ma'i sbang ma tsam yod /
NK124(ngo)001:3958: de rnams kyang gcig la gcig za ba'i sdug bsngal dpag tu med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:3959: rgya mtsho'i klu rnams la nyin re la bye tshan
NK124(ngo)001:3960: gyis char lan bdun bdun babs pa'i sdug bsngal yod
NK124(ngo)001:3962: lha mi'i yul dag na gnas pa rnams te /
NK124(ngo)001:3963: de dag la gcig za ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:3964: gzhan gyis bkol zhing spyod pa'i sdug bsngal te /
NK124(ngo)001:3966: de phyir dge ba spangs pa rnams la ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3967: gcig la gcig za shin tu mi bzod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3968: kha cig mu tig bal dang rus pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3969: sha dang lpags pa'i ched du 'chi bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:3970: gzhan dag dbang med lag pas brdeg pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3971: lcags dang lcags kyus btab pas btab ste bkol //
NK124(ngo)001:3973: de mi dge ba'i las mtha' dag gis /
NK124(ngo)001:3974: dud 'gro gang du skyes tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:3976: 'dod chags kyis ni rmongs pa na //
NK124(ngo)001:3977: ngang pa phu ron la sogs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:3978: bong bu 'dod chags can rnams kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:3979: skyes gnas srin po'i skyes gnas skyes //
NK124(ngo)001:3981: nga rgyal khengs pa seng ge ru //
NK124(ngo)001:3982: che ba yi ni nga rgyal gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:3983: khyi dang bong bu'i skyes gnas skyes //
NK124(ngo)001:3984: ser sna phrag dog la sogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:3985: skyon gyis lus can shi nas sprel //
NK124(ngo)001:3986: mu cor smra dang spyi rnal che //
NK124(ngo)001:3987: rang bzhin mi brtan khar skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:3988: gsod dang bcing dang ser sna yis //
NK124(ngo)001:3989: lus can ba glang khyi la sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:3990: 'gyur ro mi srun las kyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3991: sdom dang sdig pa mi sdug skye //
NK124(ngo)001:3992: khro dang ser sna can gyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:3993: shi nas sha ni za byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:3994: stag dang sprel dang wa dang dom //
NK124(ngo)001:3995: bya rgod spyang ki la sogs te //
NK124(ngo)001:3996: mi srun khro zhing sbyin byed mi //
NK124(ngo)001:3998: gtong zhing khro dang dregs pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:3999: nam mkha' lding gis dbang phyug skyes //
NK124(ngo)001:4000: rang gis lus dang ngag yid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:4001: sdig pa'i las ni gang byas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:4002: de ni dud 'gror skye bas na //
NK124(ngo)001:4003: de ni chung yang ma byed cig /
NK124(ngo)001:4006: tshe ni dud 'gro mchog ring skal pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4008: klu kha cig skal pa'i bar gnas la /
NK124(ngo)001:4009: gzhan rnams la nges pa med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4010: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:4013: de dag nyid la goms shing dga' ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4014: gnyis pa myong ba rgyu mthun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4015: mi dge ba bcu rim pa ltar smin te /
NK124(ngo)001:4017: bsad pa yin ni tshe thung 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4018: ma byin len pas dbul ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:4019: byi bo byas pas dgra dang bcas //
NK124(ngo)001:4020: rdzun du smra bas lkugs pa mang //
NK124(ngo)001:4021: phra ma yis ni bshed dang 'byed //
NK124(ngo)001:4022: rtsub mo nyid kyis mi snyan thos //
NK124(ngo)001:4023: ngag 'khyal pas ni tshig mi btsun //
NK124(ngo)001:4024: brnab sems yid la re ba 'joms //
NK124(ngo)001:4025: gnod sems kun du 'tshe ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:4026: log par lta ba lta ngan nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:4028: log par 'tshe bas bslus pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:4029: khengs pa yis ni rigs ngan nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:4030: phrag dog gis ni gzi 'chung zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:4031: khro bas kha dog ngan pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4032: mkhas la mi dri blun pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:4033: mi nyid la ni 'bras bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4034: kun gyis dang po ngan song ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4036: gsum pa dbang gis 'bras bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4037: phyi'i dngos po mthu chung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4038: 'bras bu dus su mi dman pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4040: nas la sran ma ltar 'gyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4043: lo nyes sha stag 'ong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4045: kha zas lus la gnod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4046: lo thog ser ba'am dgra kun gyis khyer nas yer med par 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:4048: phyi rol mthu chung gnod pa mang //
NK124(ngo)001:4049: rdul 'khrig dring na mtho' dman dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4050: tsha sgo can sogs dus la sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:4051: 'bras bu phra kha chu dang me //
NK124(ngo)001:4052: phyi rol dngos po 'gyur ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4055: gnyis pa dge ba'i rgyu la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:4056: rgyu ni dge ba bcu yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4062: sems 'byung dge bas kun nas slangs pa'i sgo gsum
NK124(ngo)001:4063: gyi bya ba 'bras bu dge ba bskyed byed du
NK124(ngo)001:4064: 'gyur ba ste / rin chen 'phreng ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:4065: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug med //
NK124(ngo)001:4066: des bskyed la ni dge ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:4069: de phyir shes pas dge ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4070: sgo gsum gyi bya ba yin pa'i las dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4071: bde 'gro'i rgyu yin pa'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4072: gsum pa sgo gsum gyi mi dge bcu spang ba ni dge ba bcu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4074: mi gsod pa dang rku spongs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4075: gzhan gyi chung ma spangs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4076: log dang phra ma rtsub nyid dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4077: mi 'bral smra ba yan lag gdoms //
NK124(ngo)001:4078: 'phyes dang gnod sems med pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4079: nyid kyi lta ba yongs spang ba //
NK124(ngo)001:4080: 'di dag las lam dkar bcu ste //
NK124(ngo)001:4081: log pa dag ni nag po yin //
NK124(ngo)001:4082: chang mi btung dang 'tsho ba bzang //
NK124(ngo)001:4083: rnam smin me dang gus sbyin dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4084: mchod 'os mchod dang byams pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:4085: mdor na chos ni de yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4087: gnyis pa 'bras bu la gsum las /
NK124(ngo)001:4089: bsod nams cha mthun gyis dge ba chung 'bring che gsum spyad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4090: mi dang lha ma yin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4092: dge bcu'i steng du mi g.yo' ba'i las kyi khams gong ma gnyis kyis lhar skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4093: gnyis pa rgyu mthun la'ang gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:4095: dge ba bcu ngang gis spyod par 'gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4096: gnyis pa myong ba rgyu mthun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4097: dge ba bcu go rim bzhin du tshe ring ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4106: yang dag pa'i lta ba 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4107: gsum pa dbang gis 'bras bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4109: phyi'i dngos po lo thog mthu che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4114: gtan du lo legs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4117: rang gis longs spyod par 'gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4119: de la gong du smon pa'i mtho' ris kyi rnam par dag pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:4120: mi dang lhar skye ba'i tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4121: snod kyi rnam par dag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4122: bcud kyi rnam par dag pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4124: mi'i rnam par dag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4125: lha'i rnam par dag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4126: bde 'gro ngan 'gro'i lus dang tshe tshad bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4128: las sna tshogs kyis mi phal pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4129: las khyad par can gyis mtho' ris yon tan bdun ldan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4130: las mchog gis 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po ji ltar 'byung ba'i tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:4132: mi ni gling bzhi gling phran brgyad la gnas pa rnams yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4133: de dag kyang rgyu dge ba stobs che chung gis /
NK124(ngo)001:4134: mi dge ba dang 'dres pa'i stobs kyis 'bras bu
NK124(ngo)001:4135: bzang ngan bsod nams che chung la sogs tha dad
NK124(ngo)001:4139: lha mi rnams su tshe ring 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4141: de phyir 'tshe ba rnam par spangs //
NK124(ngo)001:4142: mdze dang rmang bu zad byed rims //
NK124(ngo)001:4143: mi nad gzhan nam gang dag rims //
NK124(ngo)001:4144: 'byung po rnams la bsad bcad cing //
NK124(ngo)001:4145: brdeg par bya ba rnams kyis 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4146: gnyis pa mi dge ba dang ma 'dres pa'i bsod nams kyis 'bras bu 'di lta ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4148: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' chos bcu dang ldan na /
NK124(ngo)001:4149: mngal gyi dri mas ma gos par skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4150: bcu gang zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4151: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gzugs byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4152: mchod rten zhig pa bcos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4153: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten la spos kyis byug pa phul ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4154: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gzugs sku dag la khrus kyis spos chu phul ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4155: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten dag la phyag dar dang rkyang 'bul byas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4156: pha ma la bkur sti dang rim 'gro byas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4157: mkhan po dang slob dpon dag la lus kyi rim 'gro byas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4158: mtshungs par spyod pa rnams la rim 'gro byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4159: de yang zang zing med pa'i sems te /
NK124(ngo)001:4160: zang zing dang bcas pa ma yin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4161: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di yang 'di ltar dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis /
NK124(ngo)001:4162: sems can thams cad la mngal gyis dri mas ma gos par skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4163: zhes yongs su bsngo zhing bsam pa 'thad pa nas sems pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4164: rigs kyi bu bcu po 'di dag go //
NK124(ngo)001:4166: mtho ris yon tan bdun ldan ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4167: dam pa'i chos bsgrub pa'i rten zhun tshogs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4169: tshe ring de bzhin nad med dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4170: gzugs dang skal ba de bzhin rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:4171: nor mang shes rab dag dang ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:4172: yon tan mdo sde dag las gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:4173: zhes pas bdun po de dag tshang dgos shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4174: re re ma tshang yang nyes pa skyed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4175: drug po yod na tshe ring ba med na ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4176: bsad par khrid pa'i mi bzhin du 'gyur /
NK124(ngo)001:4178: nad med pa dang ma ldan na ma ning la
NK124(ngo)001:4179: bud med chags pa yod pa dang 'dra bar yon
NK124(ngo)001:4180: tan gzhan longs spyod du med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4181: gzugs bzang ba dang ma ldan na /
NK124(ngo)001:4182: gzugs ngan rgyal po'i bu mos mthong ba dang 'dra bar /
NK124(ngo)001:4183: don du mi gnyer ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4184: skal pa bzang po dang ma ldan na /
NK124(ngo)001:4185: drang srong gi bran bzhin du shin tu mnar zhing bsam pa mi grub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4186: rigs bzang po dang ma ldan na drang srong gi
NK124(ngo)001:4187: bu mo yon tan can rigs ngan gyi lag na
NK124(ngo)001:4188: gnas pa ltar / longs spyod bar med na dur
NK124(ngo)001:4189: khrod na gnas pa'i mi shin tu rang nyid zhums
NK124(ngo)001:4190: shing gzhan gyis brnyes par 'gyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4191: de bzhin du gzhan drug po yod kyang shes rab med na /
NK124(ngo)001:4192: chu shing gi 'bras bu dang 'dra bas /
NK124(ngo)001:4193: blun po bdag nyid kyi yon tan thams cad 'joms par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4195: de ltar ci skad bshad yon tan //
NK124(ngo)001:4196: yan lag re re ma tshang nyams //
NK124(ngo)001:4197: yi ge gcig gis ma tshang bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:4199: yon tan yongs rdzogs mdzes pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4200: yi ge tshangs pa'i rig pa 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:4201: de dag la sngon du song ba la 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4203: 'di dag rgyu ni gang yin pa //
NK124(ngo)001:4204: mdo bshad pa la rtogs par gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:4205: gsod par tshud pa legs btang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4206: de bzhin srog gis phan gdags phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:4207: srog chags 'tshe ba las ldog pa //
NK124(ngo)001:4208: tshe ring pas ni thob par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4209: nad pa'i bsnyen bkur byas sman pa //
NK124(ngo)001:4210: sman ni rab tu byin pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4211: srog chags bung ba dbyig sogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:4212: mi 'tshe bas ni nad med nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:4213: khro ba med la brten pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:4214: brgya byin pas ni gzugs bzang 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4215: phrag dog med pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4216: skal pa bzang por yongs su bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:4217: dam pa mchod cing brnyen bkur bya' //
NK124(ngo)001:4218: nga rgyal spangs pas rigs mthor 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4219: sbyin byed rku pa las log pas //
NK124(ngo)001:4220: longs spyod phun tshogs thob par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4221: dge dang sdig pa gang yin zhes //
NK124(ngo)001:4222: yang dag 'di la brtson pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4223: chos kyi bstan chos byin pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:4224: blo gros rgya cher thob par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4226: gsum pa bsod nams mchog gi 'bras bu ni gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:4227: 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4228: stobs kyi rgyal po gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:4229: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4230: stong phrag brgyad cu la mi bye zhes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4233: 'dul ba'i skye bo la sogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4234: brgyad khri man du mi tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:4235: tshe lo dpag tu med pa nas /
NK124(ngo)001:4237: 'di ni mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'khor los bsgyur ba'i dbang du byas pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4238: gnyis pa stobs kyis 'khor lo bsgyur ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4239: tshe lo brgya pa phan chad du'ang 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4244: lcags kyi 'khor los can dang bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4245: gling la dbang byed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4249: gser 'khor can gling bzhi kar dbang byed /
NK124(ngo)001:4250: de dag gzhan la 'dra zla med pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:4251: gling gcig tu 'khor lo bsgyur ba gnyis nam yang mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:4252: stong gsum gcig tu sangs rgyas gnyis mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4253: g.yul las rgyal bar byed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4254: gser 'khor can la gling gsum gyis rgyal phran rnams kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:4255: gser gyis gzhongs pa dngul sil mas bkang ba thogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:4256: lha tshur byon pa legs so //
NK124(ngo)001:4257: bdag gis yul 'khor 'byor ba rgyas par bde ba
NK124(ngo)001:4258: la sogs legs pa mis gang ba 'di lha nyid
NK124(ngo)001:4260: bdag cag rnams kyis ni lha'i zhabs 'bring 'gyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:4263: khyed rnams nga'i ngag ma bcag par mi dge bcu rgyun chod cig /
NK124(ngo)001:4266: de'i dus kyis mi phal cher lhar skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4267: sgra mi snyan du lo du ma bsdad pa tsam la dbang byed kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:4269: de lta bu'i 'dud pa med de /
NK124(ngo)001:4270: rje 'bangs dang dge sdig med pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4271: dngul gyis 'khor lo can gyis gling gnyis la rang
NK124(ngo)001:4272: nyid rgyal ldan gyis rtsar 'gro zhing bsnyen bkur sngar
NK124(ngo)001:4274: gling gnyis su g.yul bshams te /
NK124(ngo)001:4276: de nas bka' bsgo ba nyan no //
NK124(ngo)001:4281: rgyal zhing bka' bsgo ba nyan no //
NK124(ngo)001:4282: de ltar mod kyis gsod pa la sogs pa'i gnod pa med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4283: de dag kyang dge ba bcu la gnas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4286: ngan 'gro 'grib cing bde 'gro 'phel ba yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4288: sangs rgyas kyi mtshan 'khor lo la sogs pa phyag zhabs dbus na gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4289: 'od gsal zhing ri mo dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4290: rtsibs la sogs pa ma tshang ba med pas rdzogs pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4291: rgyal po la yang yod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4292: 'od med la ri mo ma dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4293: rtsibs ma tshang pas ma rdzogs la /
NK124(ngo)001:4294: gsang ba'i gnas su nub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4295: spyi gtsug mthong ba yang med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4296: gzhan la med pa'i lus dang longs spyod dang ldan te /
NK124(ngo)001:4297: lus ni mtshan dpe yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4298: longs spyod ni rin po che nyi shu rtsa gcig yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:4299: rin po che sna bdun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4301: mu sa la ka b+he d+aur+ya //
NK124(ngo)001:4302: dngul dang shel dang gser dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4303: mu tig mar gad rdo rnying dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4304: kun la phan pa'i rin chen bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:4306: mchog gi rin chen sna bdun la /
NK124(ngo)001:4307: 'khor lo rin po che gser la sogs pa la byas pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4310: nam mkha' la dpag tshad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4311: 'bum du nyi ma gcig gis bgrod par nus shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4312: gling bzhi dang lha ris gnyis su yang de'i mthus /
NK124(ngo)001:4313: glang po che la sogs pa thams cad nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4314: rgyal pos ma thos pa des thos par byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4315: bsngo ba su yang med par byed pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:4318: b+he d+aur+ya sngon po mi chen po'i bla tsam la zur brgyad pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4319: mtshan mo dpag tshad tsam du 'od 'byung la /
NK124(ngo)001:4320: nyi ma tsha na 'od bsil ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4321: lam du skom na chu yan lag brgyad ldan 'byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4322: rgyal po ci 'dod pa'i dngos po dang 'od sna tshogs 'byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4323: dpag tshad brgyar nad med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4324: mi 'dod pa'i byas pa'i las thams cad ci ltar 'dod pa ltar 'bras bu 'byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4325: klu ngan pas ser ba la sogs phab par mi nus pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4326: mya ngan g.yang sa'i yul dang bral ba rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:4327: ljon pa dang 'tsho ba la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa 'byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4328: mi rnams kyang dus ma yin pa mi 'chi zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4329: dud 'gro mi mthun pa rnams phan tshun mi gnod pa zhig rgyan gyis ster /
NK124(ngo)001:4332: kha n+aa ud pa la'i dri 'byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4333: reg na nyon mongs par mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4334: gling gis bkroms mya ngan dang bral bar byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4335: mi rnams kyis ma dang sring mo ltar mthong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4336: bud med gzhan la sems phrag dog med pa zhig blon pos ster /
NK124(ngo)001:4338: bya ba rnams la bsgros kyang shes nas byed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4339: mi dge ba spangs nas nyon mongs pa med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4340: sems can thams cad la pha ma ltar phan pa zhig 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4342: cang shes shing bka' nyan la /
NK124(ngo)001:4343: pha rol las rgyal bar byed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4344: glang po che gzhan stong gis stobs yod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4345: chu skam sa bar snang gsum la g.yul 'gyed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4346: nyin gcig gcig la gling bzhi lan gsum bskor ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4347: skud pas kyang bkrir rung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4349: gang du 'jug par bskul mi dgos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4350: dal gyis 'gro ba zhig brgya byin gyis ster ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4352: rma bya'i mgrin pa ltar sngo ba /
NK124(ngo)001:4353: sngar gyis glang po che dang yon tan mtshungs pa zhig brgya byin gyis ster ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4355: rdzogs byed dge ba rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4357: sa 'og gi gter mthong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4358: gser dngul la sogs pas mdzod gang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4360: skye bo thams cad la mi gnod pa zhig 'byung /
NK124(ngo)001:4361: de rnams kyis phyag mtshan dang yo byad rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4362: rgyu dge ba bcu cher spyad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4363: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten bzhengs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4365: gnod sems spangs pa las 'byung bar bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4366: gnyis pa lha'i rnam pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:4367: lha ma yin lhar bsdu' ba'i 'dod khams kyis lha dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4371: lha ma yin gyis gnas ni ri rab kyis tshu 'tshams man chad stong pa'i nang nas rim bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:4376: gser gyi sa gzhi'i steng na thag bzang ris gnas pas 'og ma bzang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4377: longs spyod lha la 'gran pa ltar yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:4378: rgyal chen bzhi'i lha rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4379: ri rab kyis bang rim bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4381: nam mkha' la nyi zla gza' skar rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4382: 'khor yug la gos sngon can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4386: brgya byin dang nye dbang sum cu rtsa gnyis yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4387: ri rab kyi steng gi ngos re re la dpag tshad brgyad khri /
NK124(ngo)001:4388: mtha' skor la gsum 'bum nyi khri'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4389: ri rab kyi zur gyi lcogs bzhi la /
NK124(ngo)001:4390: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje /
NK124(ngo)001:4392: dbus na spyi bo'i grong khyer yid du 'ong zhing lta na sdug ces pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4393: dpag tshad nyis stong lnga brgya la mtha' skor du khri yod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4394: gyen la dpag tshad gnyis 'phags pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:4395: ngo bo gser dang rka ba gdung la sogs pa b+hee d+aur+ya'i rang bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:4396: sa gzhi mtshon sna brgya rtsa brgyad kyis mdzes pa rkang pa bzhag na sor bzhi mnems pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4397: bteg na sor bzhir 'phar ba mnyam yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:4398: phyi skyabs rin po che sna bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4399: sgo stong du gcig gis ma tshang ba /
NK124(ngo)001:4400: sgo re re la srung ma lnga brgya dang ka ba drug khri dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4402: rdzing bu la sogs pa du ma yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:4404: brgya byin gyi pho brang gzhan thams cad zil gyis mnon pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4405: rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4406: ngos re la dpag tshad nyis brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4407: mtha' skor du dpag tshad stong yod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4408: lta na sdug las dpag tshad phyed dang lngas gyen la 'phags pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4409: rin po che sna bzhi la byas pa'i ba sgam /
NK124(ngo)001:4410: re re la mig khang bdun bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:4411: de re re la mdzod mig bdun bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:4412: de re re la lha'i bu bdun bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:4413: de re re la lha'i bu mo bdun bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:4414: de re re la g.yog mo bdun bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:4415: de re re la'ang sil snyan bdun bdun yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:4416: lta na sdug gi phyi rol dpag tshad nyi shu shar na /
NK124(ngo)001:4417: shing rta sna tshogs can gyis tshal /
NK124(ngo)001:4424: bza' btung sna tshogs yod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4425: de'i nang du lha dang lha ma yin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4428: nub na lha'i bu dang bu mo 'dres par spyod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4430: byang na yid rab tu zhi zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4431: dga' bar 'gyur pas dga' ba'i tshal te /
NK124(ngo)001:4433: lha de dag gi ngos bzhi na /
NK124(ngo)001:4434: dpag tshad nyi shu gzhal ba'i shar na /
NK124(ngo)001:4435: sa gzhi bzang po shing rta can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4438: byang na dga' ba zhes bya ba rnams yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:4439: tshal dang sa gzhi thams cad kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:4440: gser rnams rgyal dang mnyam zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4442: dpag tshad re res skor ba la bar na lam bzang po dang ldan pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:4443: lta na sdug gi byang shar mtshams na /
NK124(ngo)001:4444: shing yongs su sa 'dul zhes bya ba /
NK124(ngo)001:4445: dpag tshad lnga bcu thur la zugs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4447: yan lag dpag tshad lnga bcur khyab cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4448: phyogs su dpag tshad brgyar dris khyab cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4449: rdzing phyogs ma yin par lnga bcu ldang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4450: lta na sdug nas dpag tshad lnga bcu'i lho phyogs na /
NK124(ngo)001:4451: brgyad dang 'grims pa chos bzang zhes pa zlum por thad khar sum brgya la /
NK124(ngo)001:4452: mtha' skor du dgu brgya ba /
NK124(ngo)001:4453: gser gyi ra bas skor ba yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:4454: a ma li ga zhes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4455: zla ba dkar po lta bu'i rdo leb ngos re la lnga bcu pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4456: mtshon sna brgya rtsa gcig can rngams su lhag /
NK124(ngo)001:4457: de'i dbus nas brgya byin gyi gdan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4458: khor yug la nye dbang gi gdan yod /
NK124(ngo)001:4459: brgya byin la dge slong gnyis yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:4463: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas la /
NK124(ngo)001:4464: rab brtan 'dzam bu gling mtsho' ma dros par gnas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4466: me tog ku mud ta ltar dkar ba /
NK124(ngo)001:4467: yan lag bdun legs par gnas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4469: mche ba drug dang ldan zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4470: srid du dpag tshad phyed gsum yod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4471: zheng du gcig gis tshad dang ldan pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4473: re re la 'khor glang po che brgya dang ldan no //
NK124(ngo)001:4474: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gong du /
NK124(ngo)001:4475: nam mkha' la rten pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4476: lha ma yin dang 'thab dang bral bas /
NK124(ngo)001:4478: skye ba gcig gis thogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK124(ngo)001:4479: rnams bzhugs shing theg chen gyi chos kyi dga' ba
NK124(ngo)001:4481: rang gis sprul pa la longs spyod pas na 'phrul dga' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4483: thun mong du longs spyod pas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4484: 'dod khams kyi lha ris drug po'i tshe tshad ni gong du bshad zin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4487: bsam gtan dang po tshangs ris dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4489: tshangs chen gyis lha dang gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:4493: 'od gsal gyi lha dang gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:4497: dge rgyas kyis lha dang gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:4501: 'bras bu che ba dang gsum ni so so'i skye bo'i gnas yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4503: gtsang ma ris kyis lha lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4509: lha tshe ring po zhes bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4510: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i 'bras bu che ba'i bye brag /
NK124(ngo)001:4511: grong dang dgon pa'i tshul du yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:4512: dgra bcom pa thob snyam pa mngon pa'i nga rgyal gyis gnas la /
NK124(ngo)001:4513: bar do'i snang ba shar bas na /
NK124(ngo)001:4514: dgra bcom pa mi bden par snyam na /
NK124(ngo)001:4516: dmyal bar skye bar bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4517: las dang tshe'i tshad ni 'bras bu che ba'i lha dang mtshungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:4518: gsum pa gzugs med khams la bzhi las /
NK124(ngo)001:4519: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4521: ci yang med pa'i skye mched dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4522: yod min med min srid rtse'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4523: 'dod khams kyis lha ris drug po rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:4524: lha'i bu dang bu mo'i pang du rdzus te skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4525: rigs bzhi nas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyis bar go rim bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:4533: ngo tsha dang khrel med pas gcer bu 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4534: bskyed drag pas lus myur du rdzogs la /
NK124(ngo)001:4536: lus rdzogs shing snga phyi barje ba yang mi tshor bar bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4537: lha rnams la rgas shing 'khogs pa med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4538: gzugs khams kyi lha rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4540: ngo tsha dang khrel yod pas brgyan dang gos dang bcas pa bskyed la /
NK124(ngo)001:4542: pho mo'i dbang po med kyang skyes pa'i cha byad bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4543: gsum pa lus dang tshe'i tshad bstan pa la drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4546: ma nges pa'i dbye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4548: skye gnas kyis dbye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4551: 'dir bde 'gro dang ngan 'gro lus kyi tshad ci ltar yin zhes /
NK124(ngo)001:4552: 'dzam bu gling gi mi rnams tshe lo brgya'i dus su khru bzhi dang phyed bzhi yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4553: skal pa dang po'i mi rnams lus shin tu che ba /
NK124(ngo)001:4554: tshe lo bcu pa na da ltar gyi mtho gang chag gang tsam du 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4556: ba glang spyod khru bcu drug /
NK124(ngo)001:4557: sgra mi snyan sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:4560: rgyang grags gcig gis bzhi cha dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4561: sum cu rtsa gsum phyed dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4563: dga' ldan rgyang grags gcig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4564: 'phrul dga' gcig dang bzhi cha dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4565: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed rgyang grags gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:4566: lha ma yin rnams ni sum cu rtsa gsum dang mnyam par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4567: gnyis pa gzugs khams lha'i lus tshad la /
NK124(ngo)001:4568: bsam gtan dang po tshangs ris kyis lus tshad la dpag tshad phyed /
NK124(ngo)001:4570: tshangs che phyed dang gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:4571: bsam gtan gnyis pa 'od chung la gnyis la /
NK124(ngo)001:4574: bsam gtan gsum pa'i 'od chung bcu drug /
NK124(ngo)001:4575: tshad med dge sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:4576: dge rgyas la drug cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4577: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i sprin med 'od la brgya nyi
NK124(ngo)001:4578: shu rtsa brgyad las gsum dor bas brgya nyi shu
NK124(ngo)001:4579: rtsa lnga'o // bsod nams skyes nyis brgya lnga bcu /
NK124(ngo)001:4581: gtsang ma rigs kyi lha lnga la /
NK124(ngo)001:4583: gya nom snang ba bzhi stong /
NK124(ngo)001:4584: shin tu mthong ba brgyad stong /
NK124(ngo)001:4585: 'og min gyis lus la dpag tshad khri drug stong /
NK124(ngo)001:4586: gzugs med kyi lha la lus med pas tshe tshad med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4587: ngan song gsum la ni lus tshad med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4588: mtshams med pa gcig byas pas lus dpag tshad gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:4589: lnga byas pas lnga'i bar du bshad pa dran pa nyer bzhag las so //
NK124(ngo)001:4590: yang mtshams med pa byas pa'i lus la /
NK124(ngo)001:4591: dpag tshad brgya bzhi yod kyang gcig la gcig mi thogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4592: chos la skur pa 'debs pa'i lus tshad bshad mi rung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4593: theg chen la bskur pa 'debs pa'i lce dpag tshad 'bum yod par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4594: yi dwags chung ba la mtho' gang dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4595: che ba la dpag tshad stong du yang bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4596: dud 'gro chung ba la skra rtse cha lnga bcu tsam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4597: che ba la chu srin dpag tshad nyis stong bdun brgya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4598: klu dga' bo dang nyer dga' gnyis kyis lus kyi ri rab lan gsum 'khor bar bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4599: 'o na rgyang grags dang dpag tshad ci ltar yin zhes na /
NK124(ngo)001:4601: phra rab rdul dang rdul phran dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4602: lcags chu ri bong lug dang glang //
NK124(ngo)001:4603: nyi zer ba dul dang sro ma dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4604: shig dang nas 'bras de bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4605: sor gcig zhes bya gong bdun 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:4606: sor mo nyi shu bzhi la khru //
NK124(ngo)001:4607: khru bzhi la ni gzhu 'doms gang //
NK124(ngo)001:4608: gzhu 'doms lnga brgya rgyang grags gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:4609: rgyang grags de la dgon par 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:4610: de brgyad dpag tshad zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4613: ngan song gsum dang 'dod khams kyi lha'i rnams kyi tshe'i tshad ni gong du brjod zin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4614: mi rnams kyi tshe tshad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4615: 'dzam bu gling na nges pa med de /
NK124(ngo)001:4616: skal pa dang po'i mi rnams tshe lo dpag tu med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4617: tha ma tshe lo bcu la ring shos byed pa yang 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4618: lus 'phags po lo phyed dang sum brgya /
NK124(ngo)001:4620: sgra mi snyan lo stong thub bo //
NK124(ngo)001:4621: gzugs khams kyi lha rnams la ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4622: nyin mtshan gyis rnam zhag med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4623: zhag dang lo'i grangs mi rtsis te /
NK124(ngo)001:4624: rang lus las gzhal ba'i dpag tshad kyi grangs mthun pa'i skal pa'i grangs kyis 'jig ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4625: tshangs ris kyi tshe skal pa phyed dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4632: tshad med dge sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:4633: dge rgyas drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK124(ngo)001:4634: sprin mdo 'od lus la dpag tshad gsum dor ba ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:4635: tshe la yang skal pa gsum dor bas brgya nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4636: bsod nams skyes nyis brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4637: 'bras bu che ba lnga brgya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4639: mi gdung ba nyis stong dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4640: gya noms snang ba bzhi stong dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4641: shin tu mthong ba brgyad stong dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4642: 'og min gyi tshe skal pa khri drug stong thub bo //
NK124(ngo)001:4644: skal pa chen po nyis khri dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4650: sems can thams cad kyi tshe de ltar nges pa snyams na ma yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:4651: sgra mi snyan ni tshe nges pa can yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4652: gzhan ni bar mar dor 'chi ba yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:4653: gzhan nam gang zag brgyad bar ma dor mi 'chi bar bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:4654: skye ba gcig gis thogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:4655: dga' ldan na bzhugs pa de gzhan rgyal tshab tu dbang ma bskur bar du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4656: srid pa tha ma dgra bcom pa dang sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4657: rgyal bas lung bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4658: rgyal bas basngagasa pa'i pho nya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4659: dad pa dang chos kyi rjes su 'brang ba gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:4660: mthong lam ma rdzogs bar du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4661: byang chub sems dpa' srid pa tha ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4662: 'khor lo bsgyur ba de lhums na yod pa de ma bltams bar du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4665: byams pa la sogs pa'i snyoms par zhugs pa de las ma langs bar du mi 'achi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4671: bar do grub pa'i tshul rnams ni mdo sngags spyi gzhung ltar las gal chung bas ma spros so //
NK124(ngo)001:4672: ngag gi dbang po'i 'chi slu las /
NK124(ngo)001:4673: tshe dang yid rnam par shes /
NK124(ngo)001:4675: thabs kyis yun rings 'tsho ba mi 'chi ba bslu ba zhes bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4676: gnyis pa zhor la sems can rnams kyi snod kyi
NK124(ngo)001:4677: 'jig rten gyi rnam par bzhag pa la lnga ste
NK124(ngo)001:4682: bskal pa'i rnam dbye bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4685: rngams su yang drug dang 'bum phra gcig kha dog sngo skya dbyibs zlum po leb mo'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4686: mtha' skor dang chu zheng du /
NK124(ngo)001:4687: grangs med pa khyams yugs stong gsum gyi brten byed la /
NK124(ngo)001:4688: de'i steng du chu dang gser gnyis la /
NK124(ngo)001:4689: chu'i dkyil 'khor rngams su dpag tshad 'bum dang nyi shu yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4690: gnas pa'i tshe rngams su 'bum phrag brgyad yod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4691: lhag ma gsum 'bum nyi khri ni gser du 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4693: chu dang gser gyi dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:4694: thad kar 'bum phrag bcu gnyis dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4695: stong phrag gsum dang brgya phrag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4696: phyed dang lnga rnams kho na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4701: dbyibs ni zlum po leb mo'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4702: 'di ni gling bzhi gcig gi dbang du byas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4703: spangs la ni chu dang gser gnyis rlung dang mnyam par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4708: de la lhun po gnya' shing 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:4709: shol mda' 'dzin dang seng ldeng can //
NK124(ngo)001:4710: de bzhin lta na sdug ri dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4711: stag sna dang ni rnams 'dud dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4715: phyi rol na ni 'khor yug go //
NK124(ngo)001:4716: bdun ni gser yin de lcags so //
NK124(ngo)001:4717: lhun po rin chen bzhi rang bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:4721: nub pad ma ra ga dmar po /
NK124(ngo)001:4722: byang e kra' ni la ser po /
NK124(ngo)001:4723: gling bzhi'i nam mkha'i mdog kyang de bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4724: dbyibs ni ri rab gru bzhi la ri bdun gru bzhis bskor zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4725: lcags ri zlum po bskor ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4727: ri' chu'i nang du brgyad khri nub cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4728: ri gzhan dang gling rnams kyang de bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4729: chu'i steng du ri rab brgyad khri 'phags pas 'bum phrag drug khri'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4732: gnya' shing 'dzin dang lcags ri'i bar gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4738: stong gnyis dang lnga bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4739: sum brgya phyed dang bcu 'phags so //
NK124(ngo)001:4741: chu 'tshams yan chad kyis rang rang gis 'phangs dang mnyam te /
NK124(ngo)001:4742: brgyad bzhi nas sum brgya phyed dang bcu gsum gyi bar du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4743: ri bdun gyis bar rol mtsho dang mu 'khyud nas lcags ri'i bar phyi'i rgya mtsho' ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4745: de dag bar bdun rol mtsho yin //
NK124(ngo)001:4746: dang po stong phrag brgya pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4747: de'i nang gis mtsho' chen yin //
NK124(ngo)001:4749: rol mtsho' gzhan gyis phyed phyed do //
NK124(ngo)001:4750: lhag ma phyi'i mtsho' chen yin /
NK124(ngo)001:4751: 'bum phrag gsum dang stong phrag ni nyi shu gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:4753: bdun ni yan lag brgya dang ldan te /
NK124(ngo)001:4755: chu ni sil dang dri zhim dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4756: 'jam pa dang dar dri ma med //
NK124(ngo)001:4757: 'thungs na mgrin par mi gnod cing //
NK124(ngo)001:4758: lto la byams shing rab tu gang //
NK124(ngo)001:4760: gcig ni tsha sgo can te /
NK124(ngo)001:4761: mi rnams kyi longs spyod du mi rung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4763: gling rnams kyi rgyu ni sa yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4764: kha dog ni gro bo la /
NK124(ngo)001:4765: rdo rje gdan ni ser du bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4771: gling de dag gi mi'i byad kyis dbyibs kyang de dang 'dra'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4772: tshad ni 'dzam bu gling gi ngos che ba gsum la /
NK124(ngo)001:4773: dpag tshad gnyis stong nyis stong dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4774: chung ba la phyed dang bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4775: lus 'phags po'i che ba gsum snga ma gnyis po dang 'dra la /
NK124(ngo)001:4776: chung ba la sum brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4777: nub ba glang spyod la mtha' skor du /
NK124(ngo)001:4778: stong phrag phyed dang brgyad la /
NK124(ngo)001:4779: chu zheng la stong phrag phyed dang gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:4780: sgra mi snyan gyi ngos re la /
NK124(ngo)001:4781: dpag tshad nyis stong nyis stong la /
NK124(ngo)001:4782: mtha' skor du brgyad stong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4783: gling de dag ni 'bru'i phung po ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:4784: 'og bzhi rgya che zhing 'og gi tshad bshad pa ni med la /
NK124(ngo)001:4785: gling phran brgyad ni lus dang lus 'phags /
NK124(ngo)001:4786: sgra mi snyan dang sgra mi snyan gyi zla /
NK124(ngo)001:4787: rnga yab dang ni rnga yab bzhan //
NK124(ngo)001:4788: g.yo' ldan dang ni lam mchog 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:4790: dang po gnyis shar dang nub tu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4791: gnyis pa gnyis byang gi shar dang nub tu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4792: gsum pa gnyis lho'i nub dang shar du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4793: bzhi pa gnyis nub kyi nub dang shar du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4797: gling nas lcags ri dang gser gyi ri'i bar gyi tshad ni bshad pa med do //
NK124(ngo)001:4798: ri rab dang gling de dag la /
NK124(ngo)001:4799: lha dang mi'i 'gro ba rnams ci ltar gnas pa ni brjod zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:4800: gnyis pa 'jig pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:4801: bcud 'jig pa dang snod 'jigs pa gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:4803: mnar med nas sems can gcig kyang ma lus pa nas dmyal ba rnams 'phos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4806: gling bzhi pa la sogs pa'i mi rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4807: rigs bzhi nas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi bar dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4808: tshangs chen gyi bar du rim gyis 'jig cing 'apho'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4809: de la bar skal bcu dagu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4810: gnyis pa snod 'jig pa ni bar skal gcig yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:4812: da lta'i nyi ma 'di las bzhi 'gyur gyis tsha ba'i nyi ma gnyis nas drug gi bar dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4813: de bas bdun 'gyur gyis tsha ba'i rim pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:4814: rtsi shing nags tshal dang lteng ka che chung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4817: phyi'i rgya mtsho'i lhag ma dang bcas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4821: bsam gtan dang po man chad lhag ma med par /
NK124(ngo)001:4822: me nyid kyang snod dang lhan cig tu med par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4823: de ltar skal pa chen po re re bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:4825: tshangs chen gyi tshe bar skal pa bcu drug go //
NK124(ngo)001:4826: me'i 'jigs pa bdun phrag gcig song nas bsam gtan gnyis pa nas chu byung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:4827: bsam gtan gnyis man chad snga ma bzhin bsal /
NK124(ngo)001:4828: de ltar chus lan gcig 'jigs pa'i skal chen po brgyad /
NK124(ngo)001:4829: 'od gsal gyis tshe skal pa chen po brgyad do //
NK124(ngo)001:4831: chus lan re 'jigs pas chu bdun song nas /
NK124(ngo)001:4833: de nas bsam gtan gsum pa nas rlung byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4834: gsum pa man chad rlag par byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:4835: me bdun bcu rtsa drug chus lan bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:4838: me bdun dang ni chu yis gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:4839: de lta chu bdun thal nas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:4840: me yis bdun po de nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4844: skal pa chen po drug cu rtsa bzhi yod pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:4845: 'jigs skrag 'khor lo chen po gcig ces bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4846: des nas dge rgyas kyi tshe skal pa chen po drug cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4847: de nas yang me 'jigs pa la sogs thogs mtha' med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4848: da lta'i 'jig rten 'di ni rlung gis 'jigs pa'i rjes yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4850: bsam gtan gnyis pa la rtog dpyod me lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4851: gsum pa la dga' bde chu lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4852: bzhi pa la dbugs 'byung rngub rlung lta bu'i skyon yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4856: rlung gis rim pa bzhin 'jig go //
NK124(ngo)001:4857: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i sa na rtog dpyod gnyis dbugs 'byung rngub gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:4858: sems dga' mi dga' gnyis med de /
NK124(ngo)001:4859: bsam gtan gyi skyon brgyad dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:4860: de dag mi 'jig mod kyi mi rtag de'i gzhal med khang //
NK124(ngo)001:4864: gzhal med khang dang bcas pa 'byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4865: 'chi ba'i dus kyang mnyam du 'jig pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4866: de ltar snod 'jig pa la bar skal nyi shu yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:4867: 'jig pa re re'i 'og tu nam mkha' las med
NK124(ngo)001:4868: pa'i stong pa bar skal nyi shu 'byung ba yin
NK124(ngo)001:4869: no // bzhi pa 'jig rten chags pa'i tshul ni gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:4873: mes 'jig pa sngon du song nas /
NK124(ngo)001:4874: bsam gtan gnyis pa nas sprin sa la babs pa bzhin du tshangs pa'i 'jig rten chags la /
NK124(ngo)001:4875: de bzhin du 'thab bral rim gyi chags so //
NK124(ngo)001:4876: chu dang rlung gis 'jig 'jig pa nam mkha' gnyis pa dang gsum pa yang de bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4877: de'i 'og nas gzhi la brten pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4878: spyi mthun gyi las kyi rlung lang ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4880: sprin gser gyi snying po can las char babs pas chu dang rlung gis dkrug pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4882: de nas yang khams sgo can ces pas /
NK124(ngo)001:4883: rin po che du ma'i sa bon yod pa'i sprin las char babs /
NK124(ngo)001:4885: de rlung gis dkrugs pa las bcud dang po ri rab bye ba phrag brgya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4886: bcud gnyis pa gser gyi ri bdun bye ba phrag brgya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4887: bcud gsum pa gling bzhi gling phran 'khor yug lcags
NK124(ngo)001:4888: ri dang bcas pa bye ba phrag brgya chags so
NK124(ngo)001:4889: // de la bar skal gcig go //
NK124(ngo)001:4890: de nas sems can chags pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4891: 'od chung gis lha tshe dang las zad pa gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:4892: tshangs chen gyi gzhal med khang du skyes pa nas /
NK124(ngo)001:4893: lha shed bu zhes bya ba yid skyo nas grogs gcig yod na rung snyam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4896: kho'i bsam pa'i dbang gis byung snyams shing /
NK124(ngo)001:4897: phyis 'jig rten sems can gyis gang ba'am /
NK124(ngo)001:4899: log lta la snga ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4900: 'jig rten gyi myes por grags so //
NK124(ngo)001:4901: de nas 'dun na 'don nas rgyal chen bzhi'i bar dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4902: de nas sgra mi snyan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4905: 'jug tu 'dzam bu'i gling gi sems can 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:4909: mnar med du sems can gcig skyes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4912: tshe lo brgyad khri pa bzhi dus mnyam /
NK124(ngo)001:4913: de la 'jig rten gyi khams gcig ni stong gsum gyi stong chen po zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4915: gling bzhi dang ni nyi zla dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4916: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4917: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:4918: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4919: de stong la ni stong gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:4922: stong spyi phud de lcags ri gcig gis skor la /
NK124(ngo)001:4923: gnyis pa yang lcags ri gcig gis skor zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4924: stong gsum ni tshangs pa'i 'jig rten dang mnyam pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:4925: 'khor yug chen po gcig gis skor nas yod de
NK124(ngo)001:4926: / 'di ru 'jig rten chags gnas stong dus mnyam du bya ba yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4927: gong 'og dang phyogs kyis tshad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:4928: 'dzam bu gling nas rgyal chen bzhi'i bar du dpag tshad bzhi khri yod la /
NK124(ngo)001:4929: de nas shin tu mthong ba'i bar la dpag tshad bzhi khri bzhi khri yod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:4930: shin tu mthong ba nas 'og min gyi bar dpag
NK124(ngo)001:4931: tshad drug 'bum dang brgyad khri yod par bshad de
NK124(ngo)001:4933: kha cig 'thab bral la sogs bya //
NK124(ngo)001:4934: ri rab rtse dang mnyam zhes zer //
NK124(ngo)001:4938: bsam gtan dang po la sogs bzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:4939: gling bzhi ri rab bcas pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4940: stong chen chung ngu dag dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4941: stong gnyis stong gsum rim bzhin mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:4942: kha cig bsam gtan dang po dag /
NK124(ngo)001:4943: go rim bzhin du stong gsum dang //
NK124(ngo)001:4944: mnyam zhing bsam gtan bzhi pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:4945: mu mtha' yas pa yin zhes zer //
NK124(ngo)001:4946: 'jig rten ni ji lta ba bzhin du phyogs bcu kun nas mtha' thug pa med pa yod la /
NK124(ngo)001:4947: de dag dbyibs dang tshad ni nges pa med de /
NK124(ngo)001:4949: zhing ni la la spyi gtsug la la gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:4950: la la zlum po la la zur gsum te //
NK124(ngo)001:4951: de dag la la phyogs na gru bzhir gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:4952: nor bu bar ma 'khor lo yan lag brgyad //
NK124(ngo)001:4953: kun kyang las rnams rgya mtsho' rnam par bris //
NK124(ngo)001:4954: rnam par 'khrul pa gzhan dang gzhan dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:4955: zhing rnams rgya mtsho' sangs rgyas ston par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:4957: zhing gi rgya mtsho' la la ni //
NK124(ngo)001:4958: rdo rje bzhin du mi shigs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:4959: la la 'od zer rang bzhin te //
NK124(ngo)001:4962: gnyis pa skal pa'i rang bzhin la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:4963: skal pa bar ma gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4967: tshe lo sum cu pa la mu ge dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4969: bcu pa la mtshon gyis bskal pa bar ma 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4973: nang zla ba bdun dang zhag bdun 'byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4974: mtshon zhag bdun gyis bar du 'byung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:4978: de yang bar skal re re bar du 'byung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:4979: skal pa bar ma zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:4980: dge 'dun la chos ston bsod snyoms phul ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4981: nang pa la sman byin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4982: dge 'dun la a ru ra tsam phul ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4983: srog gcod pa spongs shing spangs su bcug na /
NK124(ngo)001:4985: skal pa bar ma gsum las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:4987: tshe lo dpag tu med pa nas /
NK124(ngo)001:4988: bcu bar song bas ya thog ring mo yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4989: bcu pa nas brgyad khrir song ba ya thog ring mo yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4990: bcu pa nas brgyad khrir song zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:4991: de nas bcu par song bas khug pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:4992: de lta bu bco brgyad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:4993: yang bcu pa nas brgyad khrir 'phebs pa ma thog ring mo ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4995: skal phran nyi shu zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:4997: de'i bar la 'jig rten gnas pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:4998: de la dang po la lo brgya re zhig bri la /
NK124(ngo)001:4999: khug pa rnams lnga bcu zhig 'phel ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5001: tha ma la yang brgya re zhig 'phel ba yin zer ro //
NK124(ngo)001:5002: da lta ni ya thog ring mo yin /
NK124(ngo)001:5003: skal pa bzang po sangs rgyas stong la bzhi las ma byon pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:5005: bskal pa chen po gcig yin /
NK124(ngo)001:5006: de yang mi mched 'jig rten gyi dbang du byas pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:5007: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan du ni nges pa med de /
NK124(ngo)001:5008: mi mched kyi skal pa ni bde ba can du
NK124(ngo)001:5009: zhag gcig gis sangs rgyas zhing gi yon tan bkod
NK124(ngo)001:5010: las bshad pa'o // yang bskal pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5011: sangs rgyas mi 'byung ba mun pa'i skal pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5012: sangs rgyas 'byung ba sgron ma'i bskal pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5013: de yang bskal pa bzang po de'i 'og tu /
NK124(ngo)001:5014: bskal pa chen po drug cu rtsa lngar sangs rgyas mi 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5015: de'i 'og bskal pa drag pa chen po zhes bya ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:5017: de'i 'og tu bskal pa brgyad cu la sangs rgyas mi 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5018: de'i 'og tu bskal pa skar ma lta bu la sangs rgyas brgyad khri 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5019: de'i 'og bskal pa sum brgya la sangs rgyas mi 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5020: de nas bskal pa chen po yon tan bkod pa zhes bya ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:5021: sangs rgyas brgyad khri bzhi stong 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5023: bskal pa chen po gcig la yang gnas pa kho na'i bar gyis bskal pa nyi shu la /
NK124(ngo)001:5025: brgyad khri bar du mi byon te /
NK124(ngo)001:5026: sems can rnams skyo shas chung bas gdul bya mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:5027: brgyad khri nas brgya'i bar du 'byung la /
NK124(ngo)001:5028: de man chad du yang mi 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5029: sems can rnams snyigs ma lnga shas ches bas /
NK124(ngo)001:5032: tshe'i snyigs ma srog rgud pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5033: dus kyi snyigs ma la longs spyod rgud pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5034: nyon mongs pa dang lta ba'i snyigs ma la dge ba'i rtsa ba rgud pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5035: sems can gyi snyigs ma la gzugs dang nad la sogs pas lus rgud par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:5036: yang gdul bya'i dbang gis 'jig rten du the 'ong can zhes bya ba /
NK124(ngo)001:5037: the bong gi tshad tsam mi rnams kyi nang du /
NK124(ngo)001:5038: tshe lo bcu pa'i dus su sangs rgyas skar ma dga' ba zhes bya ba /
NK124(ngo)001:5039: 'byon par gsung pa yang yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:5040: dad pa ni shin tu 'byung dka' ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5041: tshogs bsags pa yang dka' zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:5042: gdul bya snod du gyur ba nyung ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:5043: sems can la phan par byed pa'i 'khor los bsgyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5044: rang sangs rgyas ni yar 'phel ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5045: sangs rgyas mi 'byon pa'i dus kyang 'byung bar gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:5046: spyi don bzhi pa nges 'byung gi blo skyed pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:5047: zag pa dang bcas pa sdug bsngal du shes par bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5048: brjod ma dag pa'i ma gi sdug bsngal ba thams cad skad cig ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5049: rgyun gyi mthar mi rtag pas 'du shes kyis sdug bsngal yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5051: 'du byas thams cad skad cig ma //
NK124(ngo)001:5052: mi gnas bya ba ga la yod //
NK124(ngo)001:5055: sa dang lhun po rgya mtsho' nyi ma bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:5056: 'bar bas sreg pa'i lus can kha cig la //
NK124(ngo)001:5057: lhag ma tsam yang lus par mi 'gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:5058: shin tu nyams chung mi lta smos ci dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:5060: 'gro ba lnga'i sems can gang ci snyed pa de dag /
NK124(ngo)001:5061: zag pa dang bcas pa'i las kyi /
NK124(ngo)001:5062: 'khor ba ru 'khor lo bzhin du 'khor te /
NK124(ngo)001:5064: ji srid ma rig dbang gis 'gro ba rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:5065: lha dang mi dang ngan song gnas gsum po /
NK124(ngo)001:5066: 'gro ba lnga'i gnas su mi bas 'khor /
NK124(ngo)001:5067: dpe' na rdza mkhan 'phang lo 'khor ba bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:5069: rta dbyangs kyis mya ngan bsal ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:5070: gtsang ma'i gnas rnams ma rtog par //
NK124(ngo)001:5071: bros pas gang du'ang mi gtong ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:5072: sems can gang du'ang yod pa min //
NK124(ngo)001:5073: yang nas yang du dmyal ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:5074: zangs zhun bskol ba gang 'thung ba //
NK124(ngo)001:5075: rgya mtsho' nang gis chu bas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:5076: de'i tshad kyang yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5077: khyi dang phag tu 'gyur pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:5078: mi gtsang ba ni gang zos pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5079: ri'i rgyal po lhun po yi //
NK124(ngo)001:5080: tshad las shin tu lhag par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:5081: mdza' bshes rab kyis bral ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:5082: 'gro ba de dag gang rung pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5083: mig gi mchil ma'i thig pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5084: snod du rgya mtsho' rung ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5085: phan tshun dag tu rtsod pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:5086: mgo bo gcad pa gang yin pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5087: spangs nas de ltar mthong ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5088: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten las kyang thal //
NK124(ngo)001:5090: 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas sdug bsngal dpag tu med pa myong zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:5091: da rung 'khor ba'i bde 'bras la chags shing /
NK124(ngo)001:5092: nges 'byung gi blo ma skyes na /
NK124(ngo)001:5093: da lta sdug bsngal mtha' med dmyong bar 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:5095: re res rgya mtsho' bzhi las lhag pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5096: nu zho 'thungs kyang da rung so so yi //
NK124(ngo)001:5097: skye bos rjes su 'breng zhing 'khor ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:5098: de bas che mang lhag cig ltung 'tshal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:5100: mtho' ris kyi lha dang mi rnams kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:5101: bsod nams kyis 'phel ba zad pa na /
NK124(ngo)001:5102: slar ngan song du 'gro bas ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5105: lha'i 'jig rten dag nas 'phos pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5106: gal te dge ba'i lhag ma 'ga' med na //
NK124(ngo)001:5107: de nas dbang med yi dwags du 'gro dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5108: dmyal bar gnas pa gang yang rung bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:5110: 'dod khams kyi lha dang mi dag gis ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5111: sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal bzod par dka' ba yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5112: mi rnams skyes rgas na 'chi bzhi dang brgyad la
NK124(ngo)001:5113: sogs pas sdug bsngal ba ni mngon sum du 'gyur
NK124(ngo)001:5114: la / 'dod khams kyi lha rnams 'chi bar 'gyur pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:5115: 'chi ltas rnam pa lnga lha'i zhag bdun gyi bar du 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5116: klu nam mkha' lding gis khyer ba'am /
NK124(ngo)001:5117: rgya mtsho'i dbus su gru zhig pa lta bu'i sdug bsngal yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5119: lus kyi kha dog mi sdug 'gyur ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5120: gdan la mi dga' me tog phreng rnying dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5121: gos la dri ma chags dang lus la ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5122: sngon med pa'i sdug bsngal 'byung zhes bgyi //
NK124(ngo)001:5123: mtho ris 'chi 'pho sbron gyi snga ltas lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:5124: lha yul gnas pa'i lha rnams la byung ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5125: sa steng mi rnams 'chi bar 'gyur pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:5126: sbren par 'gyur pa'i 'chi ltas rnams dang 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:5128: gzugs khams dang gzugs med pa'i lha rnams kyang 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5129: bsam gtan nags mes yang nas yang du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5130: nyon mongs tshang tshing bsregs par 'gyur kyang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5131: bdag lta'i tsha ba brtan po ma spangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:5132: char gyis rlan bzhin mos pa rab tu skyed //
NK124(ngo)001:5135: khyod kyis bstan la phyir phyogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:5136: skye bo ma rig gis mdongs rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:5137: srid rtse'i bar du song nas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:5138: sdug bsngal ma byung yang srid bsgrub //
NK124(ngo)001:5140: ngan song gsum gyi sems can rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:5141: sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal bzod mi nus pa'i lugs ni gong du bshad zin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5142: des na 'khor ba'i gnas gang du skyes kyang bde ba'i go skabs med de /
NK124(ngo)001:5144: mi gtsang ba la dri zhim med //
NK124(ngo)001:5145: 'gro lnga dag la bde ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:5146: ces pa'i tshul gyis 'khor ba mtha' dag las yid 'byung bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5148: spyi don gnyis pa 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rnam par bzhag pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:5149: 'jig rten 'jig rten las 'das pa'i khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5150: grub mtha' blo bsgyur ma sgyur gyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5151: drang don nges don gyi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:5155: theg pa'i rim pa gnyis bstan te //
NK124(ngo)001:5159: lta ba'i khyad par bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:5166: ngo bo'i sgo nas bzhag pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5168: lta ba'i rgyu'i sgo nas bzhag na lta ba gang
NK124(ngo)001:5169: zag gi bdag med rtogs pa yan chad 'das pa
NK124(ngo)001:5170: / de las log pa gcig 'jig rten pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5171: de yang mu stegs man chad 'jig rten pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5174: nyon mongs lan gcig gis phyir 'ong ba'i gang zag man chad 'jig rten pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5175: dgra bcom thob pa ni 'das pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5176: de yang b+hee lam lan gcig phyir 'ong ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5177: 'dod khams kyi sa bon dang bral bas 'dod khams mi 'ong la /
NK124(ngo)001:5178: khams gong ma gnyis las 'das pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5181: 'dun pa snod yang chags bral na //
NK124(ngo)001:5182: dgra bcom 'grub par gsung pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5183: mi mnyam byas pa rtogs pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:5189: de dag zag bcas bsam gtan te //
NK124(ngo)001:5190: gnyis med yul bral de mthong min //
NK124(ngo)001:5192: rang gis mtshan nyid mngon sum du gsal ba mthong ba dbugs phyin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5197: mi 'jig pa la mi 'jig pa rten pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5198: 'jig pa la mi 'jig pa bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5199: de dag la mi rtag skye 'jig gis sdug bsngal dang bcas pa 'jig rten pa /
