NK124(ngo)001:5202: ma rig log rtog gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:5203: yul drug chos la nges rtags pas //
NK124(ngo)001:5204: 'jig pa drug dang rten pa drug /'jig rten zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5206: yul drug chos la mi rtog pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5207: skye drug gnas su mi skye ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5208: sdug bsngal drug las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:5209: mya ngan 'das pa de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:5212: rgyu mtshan dang ngo bo'i sgo nas bzhag na /
NK124(ngo)001:5213: nyon mongs 'chings ba dang bcas pa 'jig rten pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5215: yang zag pa dang bcas pa 'jig rten pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5216: zag pa gsum dang bral ba 'das pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5218: zag kun zad pa'i rigs can gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:5219: ci ltar spyad kyang rtog pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:5222: khams gsum 'jig sogs zag bral dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5223: mi rtog mi gnas phyir mi 'ong //
NK124(ngo)001:5225: gnyis pa grub mtha' blo bsgyur mi sgyur gyis khyad par la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5229: rang rang gi gzhung la brten te /
NK124(ngo)001:5230: rgyu lam tshul 'bras bu mtho ris dang thar pa 'dod pa'i blo dang ldan pas blo sgyur ba /
NK124(ngo)001:5231: de las log par ma sgyur bar 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5232: de ltar na mu stegs chad lta blo ma sgyur bar thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5233: 'o na ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:5234: rang rang gi gzhung lugs la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5235: rang mos pa shes bya'i don la sems pa'i blo dang ldan pas blo sgyur ba /
NK124(ngo)001:5236: de las log pa blo ma bsgyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5238: yang 'khor ba las grol 'dod kyi blos rang mos
NK124(ngo)001:5239: pa shes bya'i don la 'jug cing rtog par byed
NK124(ngo)001:5241: de las log pa gcig la ma sgyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5242: theg pa chen po mdo sde las /
NK124(ngo)001:5243: rmongs pa gsal phyir sems bskyed do //
NK124(ngo)001:5247: 'gro drug mun pa'i shes pa blo ma sgyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5248: mu stegs pa dang nyan thos yan chad blo bsgyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5249: gsum pa drang don nges don gyis dbye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5250: brjod bya kun rdzob kyi bden pa gtso bor ston pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5251: gdul bya' 'jig rten pa rnams la gtso cher dgongs nas gsungs pa rnams ni drang don yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:5252: gdul bya 'jig rten las 'das pa rnams la gtso
NK124(ngo)001:5253: bor dgongs nas gsungs pa rnams ni nges don yin
NK124(ngo)001:5255: mdo gang bshad pa de nyid drang don te //
NK124(ngo)001:5256: stong nyid don bshad nges don shes par gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:5258: gzhan nam byang chub sems dpa' sde snod las /
NK124(ngo)001:5259: drang nges dbye ba brgyad gsungs te //
NK124(ngo)001:5260: lam la 'jug pa drang don te //
NK124(ngo)001:5261: 'bras bu la 'jug pa nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:5262: kun rdzob sgrub byed drang don dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5263: don dam sgrub byed nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:5264: las kyi bya la 'jug pa drang //
NK124(ngo)001:5265: las dang nyon mongs zad rten las //
NK124(ngo)001:5266: kun nas nyon mongs bstan pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5267: rnam byang ston pa nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:5268: 'khor bar skyo skye drang don la //
NK124(ngo)001:5270: tshig 'bru sna tshogs ston pa drang //
NK124(ngo)001:5271: zab cing rtogs dka' nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:5272: tshig mang sems can mgu' byed drang //
NK124(ngo)001:5273: tshig nyung bzung bde nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:5274: bdag sogs gtsor bshad drang don la //
NK124(ngo)001:5275: bdag med ston pa nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:5277: spyi don gsum pa theg pa'i rnam par bzhag pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:5278: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5279: cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5280: don dam nges pa'i theg pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5286: khams gsum la gnas pa'i sems can rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5288: 'dod khams la gtso cher zhen pa'i 'dod pa dang ma bral ba /
NK124(ngo)001:5289: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5291: 'khor lo rgyun gyi gdul bya ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5292: khams gsum gnas pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:5293: zhen gsum 'dod pa ma bral bas //
NK124(ngo)001:5294: 'dod la zhen pa'i gdul byar brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:5297: 'byung ba rnam pa lnga ye nas che ba lnga'i
NK124(ngo)001:5298: sangs rgyas su gsang sngags rgyud sde rnams nas grags
NK124(ngo)001:5299: pas / 'byung ba lngar snang ba 'di dag kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:5300: sems can la bar 'tshams med pa'i don byed pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:5301: thugs rje rtag pa'i sangs rgyas yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5302: rdzogs chen nam mkha' che las /
NK124(ngo)001:5304: chub par gnas pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:5305: 'gro ba kun la rnam par snang //
NK124(ngo)001:5307: dam pa bde bar gshegs pa'i zhal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5309: ma bcos rtog bral ye nas dag /
NK124(ngo)001:5311: gsum pa 'dul thabs la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:5315: 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi skyed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5316: 'tsho ba'i longs spyod kyi rkyen dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5318: mthun pa'i grogs dang bcas pa rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:5319: rtog pa med pa ngang gis lhun grub tu 'byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5320: rang bzhin ngang ngam bar 'tshams med par 'khor lo'i rtsibs ltar gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:5322: 'gro drug sems can thams cad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:5323: bskye dang 'tsho dang brten pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:5324: rgyu dang rkyen dang gnas pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5325: mi rtog ngang gis kun 'byung ba //
NK124(ngo)001:5326: ngang gis rgyun gyi 'khor lor gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:5327: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5331: de ltar 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa la don mdzad tshul yang /
NK124(ngo)001:5332: rtsol bsgrub med par rang bzhin shugs kyis gdul bya snod du rung bar byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:5333: skyes 'tsho' rten sogs bya ba mdzad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5334: nges pa don gyi gdul byar gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5336: de ltar rgyun gyi theg pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5337: rang bzhin shugs kyi gdul bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5341: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i yul du gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:5342: kun kyang zag pa med pa'i dbyings su bkod do //
NK124(ngo)001:5344: dam pa'i 'khor lo rab skor nas //
NK124(ngo)001:5345: kun kyang zag med dbyings su bkod //
NK124(ngo)001:5347: gsang snying le'u gnyis pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:5348: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki //
NK124(ngo)001:5349: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma te //
NK124(ngo)001:5350: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK124(ngo)001:5351: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:5352: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK124(ngo)001:5353: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5354: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:5355: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi rnyed do //
NK124(ngo)001:5357: gnyis pa cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:5365: gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya ngo bo nyid kyis skus 'dul ba'i gdul bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5366: nges pa'i theg pa'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5367: nyon mongs drag pos gdungs shing 'dul dka' ba'i sems can la /
NK124(ngo)001:5368: cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pas don mdzad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5371: dam pa'i spyod yul ma 'gyur pas //
NK124(ngo)001:5372: shin tu dug gsum bsngo ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:5373: 'dul bar dka' ba'i sems can la //
NK124(ngo)001:5376: phyi nang gis bskal pa'i 'khor lo drug gis gdul bya yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5379: gti mug gis mi dge ba bcu po rgyun bcad de /
NK124(ngo)001:5381: skal pa 'khor lo'i gdul bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5382: zhen dang rmongs dang 'khrul pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5383: las ngan 'du shes ngan pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:5386: gsum pa 'dul thabs spyir bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5387: rgyal ba rnams kyis 'khor lo rgyun dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5388: don dam nges pa'i 'khor lo bskor ba yang /
NK124(ngo)001:5389: gdul byar ma gyur pa de dag la /
NK124(ngo)001:5391: bskal pa'i 'khor los las rgyun bcad de /
NK124(ngo)001:5394: 'dul bar ma gyur de dag la //
NK124(ngo)001:5395: bskal pa'i 'khor los las rgyun bcod //
NK124(ngo)001:5397: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5405: yul dngos po zhen pa'i gdul bya la /
NK124(ngo)001:5411: za ma bdun la sogs pas 'dod yon la zhen pa'i chags pa'i rgyun bcod /
NK124(ngo)001:5413: srid zhi tshogs bral bskal pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5414: sems dang yid kyi las rgyun bcod //
NK124(ngo)001:5416: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i mdzad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5417: gdul bya 'dod yon can rnams kyi don /
NK124(ngo)001:5418: mu ge'i bskal pa'i tshul du snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5419: gnyis pa nad kyi bskal pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5420: sdug bsngal mi bzod pa'i nad rlung 'khris bad kan
NK124(ngo)001:5421: la sogs pas dran pa nyams par byed pas na
NK124(ngo)001:5422: / rmongs pa'i ba skal pas lus kyi zhen pa bcod par byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:5423: zla ba bdun zhag bdun gyis gti mug gis lus la chags pa'i las rgyun bcod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5425: bzod ldan rmongs pa'i bskal pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5426: zhen pa chags pa'i las rgyun bcod //
NK124(ngo)001:5428: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i mdzad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5429: gdul bya gti mug can rnams kyi snang ngor //
NK124(ngo)001:5430: nad kyi bskal pa'i tshul du snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:5431: gsum pa mtshon gyi skal pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5432: gdul bya gnyen 'dun la sogs pa rnams la zhen cing chags pa'i sems can rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:5433: zhe sdang gis kun nas slang nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5435: zhe gcod pa'i mtshon cha'i bskal pa shar nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5436: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i dngos po thams cad kyi las rgyun bcad de /
NK124(ngo)001:5439: dngos po dngos po thams cad bcod //
NK124(ngo)001:5441: zhe sdang can la mtshon cha'i bskal pa zhag bdun za ma bdun gyi bar la rgyun bcad de /
NK124(ngo)001:5442: de yang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i mdzad pa gdul bya zhe sdang can rnams kyi snang ngor /
NK124(ngo)001:5443: gnyis pa phyi'i bskal pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5450: lhag mthong me'i bskal pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5451: dngos po'i dra ba ma lus bsreg /
NK124(ngo)001:5453: yul dngos po rang rgyud du 'dzin pa'i snod kyi 'jig rten rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:5456: sangs rgyas rnams kyis thugs rje'i mdzad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5457: gdul bya nga rgyal can rnams kyi snang ngor /
NK124(ngo)001:5461: nga rgyal tshul gyis nga rgyal 'joms mdzad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5462: nga rgyal 'joms mdzad rat+na he ru ka /
NK124(ngo)001:5465: zhi gnas chu'i bskal pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5466: 'dzin pa'i bag chags thams cad dkru //
NK124(ngo)001:5468: rang bzhin gyi rtog 'dzin zhi bar byed pas chu'i bskal pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5469: sems kyi rtog pa thams cad 'jig par byed pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5472: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i mdzad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5473: gdul bya 'dod chags can rnams kyi snang ngor /
NK124(ngo)001:5474: chu'i bskal pas 'jig pa'i tshul du snang ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5476: 'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'dul mdzad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5477: 'dod chags 'dul mdzad pad ma he ru ka /
NK124(ngo)001:5481: thogs med rlung gi bskal pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5482: shes bya thogs med kun tu skor //
NK124(ngo)001:5484: mtshan nyid gang du'ang mi 'dzin pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:5485: skad cig mar thogs pa med par rlung gis bskal pa'i tshul gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:5486: dngos po phra rags thams cad gtor te /
NK124(ngo)001:5489: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs rje'i mdzad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5490: gdul bya phrag dog can rnams kyi snang ngor /
NK124(ngo)001:5491: rlung gi ba skal par shar ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5492: de'i dus nyid kyang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i las ma g.yos te /
NK124(ngo)001:5494: phrag dog tshul gyis 'phrag dog 'dul mdzad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5495: 'phrag dog 'dul mdzad karma he ru ka /
NK124(ngo)001:5497: sangs rgyas thod pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:5498: dug lnga ma spangs ye shes lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:5499: dug gsum ma spangs sku gsung thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:5500: zhes pa'i dgongs pa dang yang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5503: shes rab nam mkha'i bskal pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5504: mtshan ma'i rgas rgud thams cad stong //
NK124(ngo)001:5506: bskal phran nyi shus snod dang thams cad stong par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:5507: de yang sangs rgyas kyi gdul byar gyur pa rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:5508: snang tshul de ltar ston pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5509: gdul byar nges 'byung skyo shas skyes te /
NK124(ngo)001:5510: don dam nges pa'i gdul byar gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5511: tshul de dag ni sangs rgyas rnams thugs rje'i mdzad
NK124(ngo)001:5512: pa gdul bya rnams kyi snang ngor stong pa'i snang
NK124(ngo)001:5513: bar shar ba'o // dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:5514: 'khor ba ci snyed yod bar du //
NK124(ngo)001:5515: bstan pa'i snying po nyi ma shar //
NK124(ngo)001:5517: mi nub rgyun mi chad par bskor //
NK124(ngo)001:5519: don bsdu' ba la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:5522: theg pa gang gis gdul bya gang las /
NK124(ngo)001:5523: 'dul thabs ci ltar snang ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5524: dus snyigs mar gyur pa'i bar skabs rnams su 'khor lo rgyun dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5525: don dam nges pa'i theg pa mdo' sngags rnam pa gnyis nub pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:5526: ngo bo nyid kyis don mi mdzad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5527: cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5528: gdul bya las ngan can rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:5529: 'dul thabs las rgyun gcod pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:5530: sdug bsngal rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i tshul du snang nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5533: snyigs mar gyur pa'i skabs rnams su //
NK124(ngo)001:5534: 'dul ba rnams ni nub pa na //
NK124(ngo)001:5535: bskal sogs thugs rje'i bstan pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:5536: las ngan las rgyun gcod pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:5537: sdug bsngal rnams ni rnam par snang //
NK124(ngo)001:5540: lang ka'i bdag po de ltar na //
NK124(ngo)001:5541: 'di kun gsang ba dam pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5542: dbyings las gar yang ma g.yos te //
NK124(ngo)001:5543: snying po kho na'i dbyings nyid las //
NK124(ngo)001:5544: stong pa'i chos rnams 'byung bar zad //
NK124(ngo)001:5545: stong nyid gsang ba'i de kho na //
NK124(ngo)001:5551: de ltar 'khor lo rgyun dang cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pas don mdzad na /
NK124(ngo)001:5552: ston pa sangs rgyas mi bzhugs shing bstan pa dam chos nub nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5553: 'gro ba 'dul thabs med zhes smra ba na /
NK124(ngo)001:5556: 'das dang nub bo zhes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5557: ston pa sangs rgyas la 'das grong mi mnga' //
NK124(ngo)001:5558: bstan pa dam chos la 'char nub mi mdzad //
NK124(ngo)001:5559: gsang sngags kyi thugs rjes shar thabs med pa ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:5560: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa gsang ba gnyis med kyis
NK124(ngo)001:5561: thugs rje'i mdzad pas shugs kyis 'dul ba yin te
NK124(ngo)001:5563: theg chen gsang ba de nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:5566: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK124(ngo)001:5567: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:5568: thabs dang theg pa gang rtags las //
NK124(ngo)001:5569: tha ma'i tha mar bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5571: gsum pa don dam nges pa'i theg pa la yang /
NK124(ngo)001:5575: nges pa'i theg pa'i dngos po gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:5583: rgyu dge ba la 'bras bu mtho' ris kyis bde ba yang mi shes shing /
NK124(ngo)001:5584: rgyu mi dge ba la 'bras bu ngan song gi
NK124(ngo)001:5585: sdug bsngal myong ba'i tshul yang dag par ma rig
NK124(ngo)001:5586: ste / dus skye ba snga phyi yang ma shes
NK124(ngo)001:5587: pas tshe 'di'i rten 'tsho ba'i bya ba don gnyer
NK124(ngo)001:5588: ste / ba yin te / spyi chings las /
NK124(ngo)001:5589: khams gsum sems can 'di dag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:5590: dge dang mi dge chos rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:5591: 'bras bu bde dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK124(ngo)001:5592: yod med gang du'ang mi rtogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:5593: dus kyis skye ba snga phyi dag /
NK124(ngo)001:5594: yod med mi rtog tshe 'di la //
NK124(ngo)001:5595: skyes tshe rten pa'i bya ba de //
NK124(ngo)001:5596: lta ba med pa'i phyal pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5598: gnyis pa bye brag tu phye ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5602: 'khor ba spyi gtsan gyi sems can rnams yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5603: gnas skabs mthar thug gang du yang sangs rgyas bstan
NK124(ngo)001:5604: pa'i sgor 'jug pa'i skal ba dang mi ldan pas
NK124(ngo)001:5605: / sems rig kun du rmongs shing 'thib pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5608: dman rigs 'jug pa'i skal med de //
NK124(ngo)001:5609: shes rig med pas dud 'gro mtshungs //
NK124(ngo)001:5612: yang gang zag sgos btsan kha cig /
NK124(ngo)001:5613: rigs sad ma'i skal pa dang ldan na yang /
NK124(ngo)001:5614: gzhan rkyen gyis dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang ma mjal
NK124(ngo)001:5615: gyi bar du dus skabs kyis bstan pa'i sgor 'jug
NK124(ngo)001:5616: mi nus pas dal 'byor gyi chos dang mi ldan
NK124(ngo)001:5619: ma nges skal yod rkyen ma 'joms //
NK124(ngo)001:5620: dal bcas 'byor ba med dang mtshungs //
NK124(ngo)001:5622: gnyis pa rgyang 'phen pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5627: bye brag rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs sad pa'i skal pa dang mi ldan pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:5628: rigs chad pa zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5630: rigs chad rgyu rkyen skal med yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5638: rigs bye brag gis khams rang dngas cha yod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:5639: gnas skabs kyi gzhan rkyen sdig to can dang ma bral bas /
NK124(ngo)001:5640: sdig pa'i rnam smin drag po bsags pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:5642: ya nga can gyi ya mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5643: rnam smin drag po'i las byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:5644: sdug bsngal drag po 'phen byed pas //
NK124(ngo)001:5645: shes ldan ltas na skyi g.ya' ba //
NK124(ngo)001:5646: ya nga can zhes grags pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5648: gnyis pa rnam g.yengs can ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5649: tshe 'di bya ba ched du gnyer zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:5650: khe dang grags pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5651: lus ngag yid gsum rnam g.yengs kyis bya ba 'ba' zhig la spyod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5653: g.yengs can tshe 'di yi ched phyir du //
NK124(ngo)001:5654: khe dang grags pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:5655: g.yengs pa'i bya ba sna tshogs byed //
NK124(ngo)001:5657: gsum pa zhan pa can ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5658: tshe 'di'i zas nor rigs rgyud don du gnyer nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5660: mo dang pra la sogs pa mig 'phrul sna tshogs kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:5661: gzhan gyi 'du shes bsgyur bar byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:5663: zhan pa'i 'du shes can nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5664: zas nor rigs rgyud ched phyir du //
NK124(ngo)001:5665: brtson pas 'jig rten lha la brten //
NK124(ngo)001:5666: mig 'khrul nor dang zas bsgrub ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5667: gzhan gyi 'du shes sgyur bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:5669: bzhi pa mos pa can ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5670: tshe 'di yi rnam g.yengs kyis dbang du byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:5671: thar lam don du gnyer ba med na yang /
NK124(ngo)001:5672: sngon sbyangs pa'i stobs kyis sdig pa'i rnam smin gyi las mi bsag cing /
NK124(ngo)001:5673: bye brag rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs sad pa'i skal ba dang ldan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5674: yul dkon mchog gsum la yang skur ba mi 'debs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:5675: lus ngag yid gsum ngang ngam shugs kyis nges 'byung skyo shas dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5676: rnam par dkar ba'i spyod pa la gzhol ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5678: mos pa can gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5679: lta ba phyal par gyur pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5680: dkon mchog sum la skur mi byed //
NK124(ngo)001:5681: sdig pa'i las la ya nga zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:5682: cung zad dkar ba'i sa bon ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:5683: rgyud las sbyangs pa'i las yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5685: gnyis pa log par lta ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5689: rang bzhin gyis log pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5691: rang bzhin gyis log pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5692: gzhan rkyen med kyang sngon sbyangs stobs la sogs pa'i stobs kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:5693: tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras la sogs pa med par lta zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:5694: 'di ltar du snang ba'i chos thams cad /
NK124(ngo)001:5695: spang la sha mongs rdol ba ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:5696: blo bur pa yin par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5698: dang po mi dge ba'i rkyen med kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:5699: las kyis sbyangs pa'i log par 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:5700: dge sdig rgyu 'bras tshe snga phyi //
NK124(ngo)001:5701: de dag thams cad med par lta //
NK124(ngo)001:5702: da lta'i snang ba blo bur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5703: rgyu rkyen med par shugs kyis snang //
NK124(ngo)001:5704: snod bcud kun la de ltar rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:5706: gnyis pa rkyen gyis log pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5707: 'od bsrungs rdzogs byed la sogs pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5708: log par rtog pa'i lta ba 'dzin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:5709: dkar nag gi rgyu 'bras rnam par lta zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:5711: dus snga phyi thams cad med par smra ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5714: gnyis pa rkyen gyis log pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5715: 'od bsrungs rdzogs byed la sogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:5716: lta ba yongs su 'dzin byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:5717: dkar nag rnam smin med smra zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:5718: skye ba snga phyi med par smra //
NK124(ngo)001:5719: de nyid rang gis grub mthar 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:5720: phyi ma med phyir dmu rtug ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5723: gnyis pa mu stegs pa ni gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5726: dang po ni 'khor ba las thar 'dod kyi blo brod pa dang bcas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5727: lam gyis dka' ba sna tshogs dang du blangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5728: log pa'i brtul zhugs la spyod cing 'bras bu thob pa ra 'dod nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5729: dge sdig log par spyod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5732: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las //
NK124(ngo)001:5734: lta log lta spyod ya char 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:5736: kun tu tshol ba'i lam du zhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:5738: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5739: 'phra men spyod pa'i mu stegs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5742: lung gis phyogs tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5743: dang po 'phra men spyod pa'i mu stegs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5744: mtho' ris bde ba 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:5745: grub mthas blo bsgyur ba bdag tu 'dzin pa'i rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:5746: pa la zhugs te spyod pa mi dge ba sna
NK124(ngo)001:5747: tshogs spyad nas / lus mi gtsang ba gtsang bar 'dzin pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5748: tshor ba sdug bsngal ba bde bar 'dzin pa /
NK124(ngo)001:5749: 'dus byas mi rtag pa rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5750: chos thams cad bdag med pa la bdag tu 'dzin pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5751: phyin ci log gis lta ba bzhi las /
NK124(ngo)001:5752: yang dag pa'i lta bar 'dzin pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5754: 'phra men spyod pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5755: thar pa 'dod pas bdag tu lta //
NK124(ngo)001:5756: mtho' ris bzhed phyin mi dge bsgrub //
NK124(ngo)001:5757: phyin ci log pa bzhi la gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:5758: 'di dag kun la dngos por smra //
NK124(ngo)001:5759: 'dod dang lta spyod mi mtshungs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:5760: 'phra men spyod ces de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:5762: gnyis pa rten log 'chal pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5764: dbang phyug la sogs pa'i lha chen rnams la rten bcas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5765: de dag gi go 'phangs thob par 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:5766: nang pa'i sangs rgyas la sogs dkon mchog rnams la log par ltas te /
NK124(ngo)001:5767: phyin ci log pa'i lam la zhugs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5769: rten log 'chal pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5770: tshangs pa la sogs lha chen dag /
NK124(ngo)001:5771: bsod nams sbyangs pa'i stobs las 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:5772: sbyangs stobs ches bas mnga' dbang brnyes //
NK124(ngo)001:5773: byang chub sems dpa' mthu' chen de //
NK124(ngo)001:5775: log lta can gyis mi shes te //
NK124(ngo)001:5776: phya dang dbang phyug ming btags nas //
NK124(ngo)001:5777: de dag rang rgyud ye grub smra //
NK124(ngo)001:5779: de dag rgyas par phye na bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5780: 'bras bu re ba log par spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5781: gol ba'i ngo bo la rgyu 'bras log par lta ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5785: 'bras bu lha chen dbang phyug la sogs pa'i go 'phangs thob par 'dod pa dag gis /
NK124(ngo)001:5787: dbyug gu zhes bya ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5788: kha tam rtse gsum la sogs pa'i btul zhugs /
NK124(ngo)001:5789: khyi'i cha byad la gnas pa'i dka' thub dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5790: ba glang ma he la sogs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5791: glang po che'i seng ge'i lci ba la sogs pa'i btul zhugs ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5792: logs pa'i btul zhugs sna tshogs spyod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5795: me lnga brten dang dbyug gu dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5796: khyi'i dka' thub la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5797: log pa'i btul zhugs sna tshogs spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:5799: gnyis pa gol ba'i ngo bo rgyu 'bras la log par lta ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5800: kha cig de dang de'i 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:5801: rdul dang mun pa snying po stobs gsum la gzhi bcas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5802: gsum po cha mnyam du gyur na rdul la brten nas 'bras bu sku gsum thob par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5804: dug gsum rdul dang mun pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:5805: snying stobs dag gis bye brag las //
NK124(ngo)001:5806: cha mnyam mi mnyam khyad par gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:5807: rgyu dang 'bras bu yin par smra //
NK124(ngo)001:5809: yang kha cig nang pa'i dkon mchog gsum la log par lta ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5810: 'jig rten pa'i lha chen rnams la dngos po rang rgyud du brten bcas te /
NK124(ngo)001:5811: dug gsum rang rgyud kyi spyod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5814: rin chen gsum la rten log nas //
NK124(ngo)001:5816: 'chal pa'i spyod pa sna tshogs spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:5818: bzhi pa de dag spyi'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5820: thob bya mtho' ris thar pa mi thob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5821: phal cher ngan song gi sdug bsngal myong bar 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:5822: skyabs gnas dang bral bas mtho ris thar pa'i gegs su gyur pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5824: thob bya'i 'bras bu mi thob ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5825: sdug bsngal can du phal cher gzhol //
NK124(ngo)001:5826: rten log 'chal pa'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK124(ngo)001:5828: gsum pa rtags tsam 'dzin pa la spyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5831: lus kyi cha lugs sangs rgyas sprul sku'i tshul rtags 'dzin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:5832: sems phyin ci log tu zhugs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5834: rtag tsam 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5836: gnyis pa bye brag la drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5838: don rtag chad gnyis su 'dus tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5839: bka'i dgongs don mi khrol lta log sna tshogs byung tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5840: de nyid la sgra don dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5841: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa nang pa'i nang nas yod par bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5843: sangs rgyas sprul sku mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5844: bstan pa snyigs mar gyur pa'i dus /
NK124(ngo)001:5845: gzugs brnyen gyis bstan pa'i 'dzin pa'i dus su 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5847: sprul pa snga ma 'das pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5848: bstan pa snyigs mar 'gyur pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:5849: bstan pa de'i gzugs brnyan las //
NK124(ngo)001:5852: bstan pa la 'jug 'dod kyis gang zag kha cig /
NK124(ngo)001:5853: tshul rtags bstan pa'i sgor zhugs kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:5854: thos bsam b+hee gsum gyis shes rab gsum la ma sbyangs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5855: bstan pa'i don la rtogs dpyod byas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:5856: drang nges bden gnyis la sogs pa'i dgongs don ni ma rtogs /
NK124(ngo)001:5857: rgyal ba'i gsung pa'i bka' la rag chod byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5859: sgyu rtsal gyi bu ring phur la sogs pa'i log par smra ba du ma byung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5862: shes rab gsum la ma sbyangs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:5863: bden gnyis zab mo'i don ma phig /
NK124(ngo)001:5864: zab mo'i bka' la zhen phyogs drengs //
NK124(ngo)001:5865: rigs byed lhag spyod la sogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:5866: log par smra ba du ma byung //
NK124(ngo)001:5868: gsum pa rtag chad gnyis su 'dus tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5869: yang kha cig stong pa'i don la nyi tsher ltas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5872: dngos po 'di dag blos brtags nas //
NK124(ngo)001:5873: dngos po mtshan mar brtags par 'dod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5875: nyi tshe'i stong pa kho na lta //
NK124(ngo)001:5876: la las rnam par rtags pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:5877: bdag rtags dngos po mtshan mar smra //
NK124(ngo)001:5879: bzhi pa bka'i dgongs don mi khrol ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5880: la la dag shes rab zab mo'i don dang mi ldan pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5881: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' zab mo'i dgongs don ma khrol bas /
NK124(ngo)001:5882: grub mtha' log pa'i lta ba sna tshogs 'byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5884: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:5885: zab cing rgya che dpag dka' bas //
NK124(ngo)001:5886: yin snyam dpyod pas ma phig ste //
NK124(ngo)001:5887: log pa'i lta ba sna tshogs 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:5891: sems phyin ci log gi lta ba la zhugs kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:5892: lus nang pa'i tshul rtags 'dzin pa dag yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5895: ngur smig gis ni gos gyon pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:5896: 'bras bu yod dang med smra ba //
NK124(ngo)001:5897: ma 'ongs phyi ma'i dus su ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5898: 'bras bu med ces smra ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5899: skye bo mang po brlag par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:5902: sems can log pa'i lam du zhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:5903: lus kyi sangs rgyas rtags 'dzin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:5904: rtags tsam 'dzin ces de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:5907: tshul rtags 'dzin pa nang pa'i nang nas kyang yod par bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5908: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa sde snod gsum la sogs pa rnams nub tu nye bas /
NK124(ngo)001:5909: snyigs ma'i dus la babs pa'i dus su /
NK124(ngo)001:5911: ding sang nang par khas ches ba rnams kyi nang na'ang mang bar bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:5913: sh+aakya seng ge'i bstan pa brgas //
NK124(ngo)001:5914: snyigs ma'i dus la deng sang babs //
NK124(ngo)001:5916: ding sang nang pa'i nang na mang //
NK124(ngo)001:5918: bzhi pa lung phyogs 'dzin pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5922: rgyal ba'i bka' lung las byung ba'i /
NK124(ngo)001:5924: grangs dang lta ba nor ba'i phyogs su song ba'i mu stegs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5925: rang gis 'dod phyogs su zhen nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5927: gtan tshigs rang gis grub mtha' la zhen nas /
NK124(ngo)001:5928: mkhas rtogs tshad ma rnams kyis bkag kyang ldog par dka' ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5930: lung gis phyogs tsam 'dzin pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:5931: rgyal ba'i bka'i zhor byung bas //
NK124(ngo)001:5932: phyogs mthun tsam las lta bar log /
NK124(ngo)001:5933: grang mthun tsam las nor bar song //
NK124(ngo)001:5934: zhen phyogs 'khrul pa'i lam du zhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:5935: nga rgyal snyam pas zlog par dka' //
NK124(ngo)001:5937: bye brag tu phye na gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:5938: lta ba las log pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5943: dang po spyi la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5948: dang po phyi rol pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5949: theg pa chung ngu las gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5951: dbu ma chen po las gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5952: gsang sngags pa ni phyi rgyud sde gsum las gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5953: gsang chen pa ni bla med rnam gsum las gol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5954: phyi rol pa la yang gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:5958: dang po bye brag pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5959: nyan thos bye brag tu smra ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:5960: cha mthun tsam du gol te /
NK124(ngo)001:5962: kun rdzob kyi snang ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5964: ni'u sing gis bar bskor ba dang bcas pa rdzas can du 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5965: nang gi sems can skad cig cha med de /
NK124(ngo)001:5966: gtso bo dbang phyug can du 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:5967: phyi nang gnyis ka 'dus ma byas pa'i don dam par 'dod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:5968: gnyis pa tha snyad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5969: nyan thos mdo sde pa la cha mthun tsam du gol te /
NK124(ngo)001:5972: bye ma'i phung po ltar 'dod pa de la /
NK124(ngo)001:5974: sems skad cig cha med 'di nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:5975: gtso bor rtag pa'i rang bzhin can du 'dod /
NK124(ngo)001:5976: phyi nang gnyis ka 'jig rten pa'i lha chen gyis byas par 'dod /
NK124(ngo)001:5977: gsum pa rang snang phyogs gcig pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:5978: rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba la cha mthun tsam du gol te /
NK124(ngo)001:5981: rdul phran phra rags gang du yang ma grub par 'dod pa yin pa de la /
NK124(ngo)001:5982: mu stegs pas de ltar ma rtog ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5983: yul gyi snang ba 'di kun rdzob tu yang med par rtogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:5984: nang gi sems skad cig cha med de la bdag tu ltas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:5985: rang snang phyogs gcig pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:5987: nyan thos bye brag mdo sde pa //
NK124(ngo)001:5988: rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:5989: cha mthun zhen pas log par song //
NK124(ngo)001:5991: yang dag pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:5992: gang zag gsum gol tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5993: spyod pa mthun pas gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5994: bdag nyid ma spangs pa'i skyon dang /
NK124(ngo)001:5995: log lta'i rnam grangs byung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:5999: rgya cher yangs pa gsum po 'di dag /
NK124(ngo)001:6000: sems tsam rnams bden pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6001: phyi rol gyi snang ba 'di dag sems 'khrul pa'i snang ngor bden la /
NK124(ngo)001:6002: don dam par mi bden par 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:6003: de las gol ba'i mu stegs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6004: nang bdag rtags pa gcig pu ba ni bden la /
NK124(ngo)001:6005: yul rdzun par 'dod pas phra ba pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6006: gnyis pa sems tsam rnams rdzun pas yul gyi snang ba 'di rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:6007: 'khrul ngos la rdzun par 'dod pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:6008: de las gol ba'i mu stegs pa ni yul snang
NK124(ngo)001:6009: 'di rnams gtan nas med par 'dod pas zab pa
NK124(ngo)001:6010: zhes bya'o // gsum pa dbu' ma chen po bas /
NK124(ngo)001:6011: kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad sgyu ma rmi lam lta bu la /
NK124(ngo)001:6012: don dam par stong zhing bdag med du 'dod pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:6013: de las gol ba'i mu stegs pa tshangs pa 'dra ba'i rjes su 'brang ba'i /
NK124(ngo)001:6014: gsang ba'i grub mtha' smra ba dag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6015: 'gro ba'i shes rig bdag gcig pu rang dbang can yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6016: rnam par rtog pa'i 'khrul pa zad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6017: bum pa chag pas nam mkha' chen por 'dus pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:6018: srog kyang de bzhin du 'dus par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:6020: yang dag pa la rnam gsum te //
NK124(ngo)001:6021: phra ba zab pa rgya cher yang //
NK124(ngo)001:6022: 'di dag sems tsam rnams bden rdzun //
NK124(ngo)001:6023: dbu' ma chen po'i lta ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:6024: cha mthun tsam gyis log par song //
NK124(ngo)001:6026: gnyis pa spyod pa mthun pas gol tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6027: gong gi gang zag gsum pos /
NK124(ngo)001:6028: nang gi sems tsam dbu' ma pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6029: gsum po'i spyod pa dkar phyogs rtsis spyod pa las mthun te /
NK124(ngo)001:6030: bdag med rnam pa gnyis ma rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6031: lta ba ci ltar zab pa'i tshig smras kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6032: don la gol ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6034: spyod pa phyogs mthun tsam du zhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:6035: ci tsam zab pa'i tshig brjod kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:6037: gsum pa bdag nyid ma spangs pa'i skyon ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6038: gong gis spyod pa nang pa dang cha mthun kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6039: lta ba gzung 'dzin gyi bdag nyid ma spangs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6040: b+hee pa ting 'dzin kyang nor ba'i rjes su 'brang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6042: bdag 'dzin gnyis po ma spangs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6043: bsam gtan nor ba'i lam du zhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:6045: bzhi pa log lta'i rnam grangs 'byung tshul ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6048: rtsa ba drug po 'di las gyes pa'i rgyu'i theg
NK124(ngo)001:6049: pa log pa'i lta ba mang du byung ba yin
NK124(ngo)001:6051: rtsa ba 'di las gyes pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:6052: log pa'i lta ba mang du byung //
NK124(ngo)001:6054: gsang sngags pa la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:6055: gang zag gsum rgyud las gol tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6056: lta spyod log pa'i skyon dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6057: de las log rtog gis grangs su ma byung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:6063: bya rgyud pa 'di ltar du snang ba'i dngos po
NK124(ngo)001:6064: thams cad rigs gsum gyis dkyil 'khor du 'dod cing
NK124(ngo)001:6065: / don dam pa dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma
NK124(ngo)001:6066: dang bral bar 'dod pa de las log pa'i mu
NK124(ngo)001:6068: khrus dang gtsang sbra la gtso bor byed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:6069: don ma rtogs yid smon shor bas rigs byed pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6072: kun rdzob thams cad rigs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6073: don dam par stong zhing bdag med kyi rang bzhin du 'dod pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:6074: de las gol ba'i mu stegs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6075: kun rdzob kyi snang ba la dngos po lta zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:6076: don dam par bdag tu lta bas /
NK124(ngo)001:6079: yo ga pas yul dbyings dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6080: sems ye shes gnyis dbyer med du 'dod pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:6081: de las gol ba'i mu stegs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6083: tshe ba skye mched mu bzhi'i snyoms 'jug dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6084: kun rdzob smra ba rang rgyud par ltas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6087: gsang sngags pa la rnam gsum te //
NK124(ngo)001:6088: rigs byed rigs spyod rigs sbyor ba //
NK124(ngo)001:6089: bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor las //
NK124(ngo)001:6090: lta ba spyod pa bsam gtan dag /
NK124(ngo)001:6091: cha mthun rtsams te don la gol //
NK124(ngo)001:6093: gnyis pa lta spyod log pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6094: gong gi de rnams bdag tu 'dzin pa'i 'khrul pa la zhen nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6097: rigs gsum mgon po'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK124(ngo)001:6099: gang du gol na thams cad kyis bdag nyid thob bya'i 'bras bu smra ba las gol te /
NK124(ngo)001:6100: 'jig rten pa'i phya dang dbang phyug gi go 'phangs thob par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6101: rigs byed kyi smra 'don la sogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6102: lus ngag gi dka' ba ci spyad kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6103: 'khrul snang gi zhen pa ma spangs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6104: 'khor ba'i 'thags las thar bar ma gsung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6107: bder gshegs sprul sku'i snang ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:6108: phya dang dbang phyug dag tu 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:6109: rigs byed smra 'dun la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:6110: dka' thub dka' spyad ci bsgrubs kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:6111: zhen pa'i mun pa ma dang pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6112: 'khor ba nyid du skye mang rgyud //
NK124(ngo)001:6114: gsum pa log lta'i rnam grangs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6115: gsang sngags phyi rgyud las gol ba'i log lta mang du 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:6117: lta ba 'di las gyes pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:6118: log pa'i lta ba du ma byung //
NK124(ngo)001:6124: gang zag gsum gol tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6125: longs sku dang spyod pa las gol tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6128: rtul zhugs cher spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6131: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6132: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6133: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga gsum las /
NK124(ngo)001:6136: ting nge 'dzin gsum la ltos te 'khrul pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6138: gsang chen pa la rnam gsum te //
NK124(ngo)001:6139: brtul zhugs cher spyod pa dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6140: rgyal dpog pa dang rgyal 'thabs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:6141: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen las //
NK124(ngo)001:6142: lta ba spyod pa'i ting 'dzin las //
NK124(ngo)001:6143: 'dra' mthun tsam gyis ltos te 'khrul pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6145: gnyis pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku las gol tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6146: nang pa'i bde bar gshegs pa'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku gzugs la ltos nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6147: khyab 'jug la seng ge'i mgo' yod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6148: tshangs pa 'jig rten thams cad skyed par byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6149: 'dra mthun tsam gyis sbyor sgrol la sogs pa'i spyod pa rang rgyud du spyad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6150: 'jig rten pa'i lha la longs skur zhen nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6151: mtho' ris thar pa dang bral nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6152: rtogs dpyod phyin log gis dka' thub spyad de /
NK124(ngo)001:6153: rang gis bsam yul du 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6154: spyod pa rnam smin drag po las /
NK124(ngo)001:6155: bsags pas ya mtshan zhes grags pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6157: bder gshegs longs sku'i gzugs brnyan las //
NK124(ngo)001:6158: seng ge dang ni 'phrog byed dang //
NK124(ngo)001:6159: dbyig gis snying po dag tu 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:6160: 'dra mthun spyod pa ci spyod kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:6161: sgro 'dogs zhen pa ma spangs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6162: thar pa'i 'bras bu mi myong ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6163: rtogs spyod log pa'i dka' thub can //
NK124(ngo)001:6164: bsam pa'i 'bras bu dag par bzhed //
NK124(ngo)001:6165: spyod pa yang yang sna tshogs byed //
NK124(ngo)001:6166: 'di dag ya mtshan can zhes grags //
NK124(ngo)001:6168: bye brag tu phye ba la gsum te /
NK124(ngo)001:6169: brtul zhugs cher spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6174: gol ba'i ngo bo lta spyod gzhan la gnod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6175: log zhen phra mo la bden par zhen pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6176: dang po mu stegs brtul zhugs cher spyod kyi gol gzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6177: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i ngang nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6178: thugs rjes gzhan don rlabs po che /
NK124(ngo)001:6179: thun mong ma yin pa yan lag gi dam tshig gis /
NK124(ngo)001:6180: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don bsgrub pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:6181: ltos pa'i cha mthun tsam las gol zhing 'khrul pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6183: rtul zhugs pa ni gsang sngags kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:6184: thabs kyis mdzad pa'i spyod pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:6185: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don bsgrubs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6188: gnyis pa gol ba'i ngo bo lta spyod gzhan la med pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6189: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi don ni ma rtogs /
NK124(ngo)001:6190: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa rtul zhugs kyi spyod pa cha mthun tsam du spyad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6191: bdag gzhan gnyis kas bde 'gro la sogs pa'i 'bras bu mi thob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6193: mnyam pa'i lta ba ma rtogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:6194: brtul zhugs spyod pa cha mthun spyad //
NK124(ngo)001:6195: bdag gzhan gnyis ka chud bsan te //
NK124(ngo)001:6196: phal cher mtho ris mi myong ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6197: thar pa'i 'bras bu ga la srid //
NK124(ngo)001:6199: gsum pa log zhen phra mo la bden par 'dzin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6200: 'jig rten pa'i lha chen la zhen nas de nyid kyis mthu' rtas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6201: gzhan skabs su thun mong gi dngos grub snang ngos /
NK124(ngo)001:6202: nor 'phel chu la mi bying ba la sogs pa 'byung bas ya mtshan du lta'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6204: log ltas zhen pa'i mtha' brtas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6205: 'jig rten dngos grub phra mo dag /'byung bar 'gyur zhing ya mtshan skye //
NK124(ngo)001:6207: gnyis pa rgyal dpog pa la lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6209: gol ba'i ngo bo dbyings ye shes gnyis las gol tshul /
NK124(ngo)001:6211: gol tshul gyi rnam grangs sngon nas byung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:6212: da lta nang pa'i b+hee chen po la yang yod par bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6213: dang po mu stegs rgyal dpog pa'i gol gzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6214: rjes su rnal 'byor lung a nu yo ga'i lta b+hee spyod gsum la cha mthun gyis 'khrul te /
NK124(ngo)001:6216: rgyal dpog rjes su rnal 'byor las //
NK124(ngo)001:6217: cha mthun tsam gyis 'khrul pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6219: gnyis pa dbyings ye shes las gol tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6220: lung gis dgongs pa chos dbyings skye ba med cing zad mi shes pa de las /
NK124(ngo)001:6221: gtso bo bems po chos sku nyid du gzung nas 'khrul zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:6222: skye 'gags thams cad bral ba'i ye shes de la ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6223: nang gi bdag rtag pa shes rig gi skyes bu zhes bya bar gzung nas 'khrul pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6225: chos nyid nam mkha' mu med las //
NK124(ngo)001:6226: gtso' bo bems po nyid du 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:6227: med la mi zad ye shes las //
NK124(ngo)001:6228: nang gi skyes bu byed par 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:6230: gsum pa gol ba'i skyon ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6231: rgyal dpog pa de nyid kyis lta ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:6232: gtso' bo skyes bu de nyid dbyer med do //
NK124(ngo)001:6234: dbyings ye shes dbyer med du 'dod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6235: yang dag pa'i lta ba dbyings ye shes kyi dgongs don ma rtogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:6236: ngan 'gro sdug bsngal gyi gnas su yang yang 'khyams te /
NK124(ngo)001:6238: zab pa'i tshul du smra byas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:6239: yang dag don chen ma rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6242: gol ba'i rnam grangs sngon nas byung tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6243: lung a nu yo ga'i lta ba la gol ba'i lta ba 'di bye brag las /
NK124(ngo)001:6244: zab mor bcos pa'i log lta'i grangs kyang mang du 'byung bar bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:6246: lta ba 'di yi bye brag las //
NK124(ngo)001:6247: zab bcos lta ba grangs mang byung //
NK124(ngo)001:6249: lnga pa da ltar ba'i b+hee chen pa'i nang du mang bar bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6250: rgyal dpog pa'i lta ba 'dzin pa'i rnal 'byor pa la la ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6251: da ltar nang pa'i b+hee chen pa'i nang na yod par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:6253: phal cher da lta ba'i b+hee chen pa //
NK124(ngo)001:6254: b+hee chen rnams kyi nang du mang //
NK124(ngo)001:6256: gsum pa rgyal 'thabs pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6264: shin tu rnal 'byor rdzogs pa chen po las gol ba'i mu stegs rgyal 'thab pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6265: gong ma'i lta b+hee spyod pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:6269: mthun pa'i phyogs gcig 'khrul pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6271: gnyis pa gol ba'i ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6272: lta ba las gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6275: bden pa gnyis las log par rtogs shing gsang ba smra ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6276: khams gsum pa yang de dang mtshungs par rtogs pa
NK124(ngo)001:6277: dang las kyi rnam par smin pa'i 'dod tshul lo
NK124(ngo)001:6279: rgyal 'thab pa de dag gi lta ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6280: kun rdzob sgyu ma rmi lam lta bu las /
NK124(ngo)001:6282: don dam par brten med stong pa nyid dang kun
NK124(ngo)001:6283: rdzob kyi bden pa gnyis po 'brel pa med par
NK124(ngo)001:6284: smra ste / gang zag so so skye bo sems kyi rang bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:6285: bdag rtag pa'i skyes bu zhes bya ba yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6286: spyod yul du ma gyur ba zhes brjod pa nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:6288: de dag kun gyis lta ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6289: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i rten 'brel dang //
NK124(ngo)001:6290: don dam de med brten pa'ang med //
NK124(ngo)001:6291: gang zag sems kyi rang bzhin las //
NK124(ngo)001:6292: bdag gcig yod de dngos ma gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:6293: 'di zhes bya ba'i khas len med //
NK124(ngo)001:6295: gnyis pa khams gsum po de dang mtshungs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6296: khams gsum gyi sems can 'di dag kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6297: kun rdzob kyi rten 'brel gong bzhin du lta zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:6298: thams cad sems kyi rang bzhin bdag rtag pa shes rig gi skyes bu zhes bya bar de nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:6299: rang gi snying gi dkyil du kha dog dkar la
NK124(ngo)001:6300: mtsher ba bsnums la 'dril ba nyid sems can rang
NK124(ngo)001:6301: gi ngos yid dang mtshams par 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:6302: de dus gsum du rtag par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6304: khams gsum sems can 'di dag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:6305: kun rdzob don dam gong ma bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:6306: kun gyi sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK124(ngo)001:6307: bdag re yod de dngos ma gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:6309: las kyi rnam par smin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6310: gong gi log lta de rnams kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:6312: sdig pa'i 'bras kyi rnam smin rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:6313: rang gi blo yul du 'dod na yod cing mi 'dod na med do //
NK124(ngo)001:6315: dkar nag las kyis rnam smin dag /'dod na yod de mi 'dod med //
NK124(ngo)001:6317: gnyis pa 'bras bu la gol tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6318: chos sku las gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6321: a ti yo ga'i dgongs pa chos sku ka dag gi ngo bo /
NK124(ngo)001:6322: gzung 'dzin rnams kyi mtshan ma dang bral ba'i ngo bo de la blo brtags kyis snang ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:6323: rang phyogs kyi 'bras bu thob pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:6324: rig pa ye shes med cing dngos po dang mtshan
NK124(ngo)001:6325: ma med pa'i nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba lta
NK124(ngo)001:6326: bu de la / chos sku thob pa zhes brjod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6328: 'bras bu mngon sum thob pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:6329: rig pa med pas ye shes med //
NK124(ngo)001:6330: dngos po med pas dngas pa min //
NK124(ngo)001:6331: sprin med nam mkha' dngas pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:6332: gyur nas chos sku yin zhes brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:6334: gnyis pa gzugs sku las gol bar song ba rnams
NK124(ngo)001:6335: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyis thugs rjes 'dul bar
NK124(ngo)001:6337: ye shes dang thugs rjes med par 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:6338: gdul bya dang 'dul byed rnams kyang sgyu ma'i skyes bu dang mtshungs par /
NK124(ngo)001:6339: rang rang gi blos rtogs par byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:6341: bder gshegs thugs rje'i mdzad pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:6342: rig pa med cing ye shes med //
NK124(ngo)001:6343: snang nyid sgyu ma'i skyes bu mtshungs //
NK124(ngo)001:6344: phal cher rang gis rtogs par smra //
NK124(ngo)001:6347: gong gi rgyal 'thab pa'i log par rtogs pa'i rnam grangs mang du 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6349: de 'dra lta ba bye brag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:6350: cha mthun log pa mang po 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:6352: gnyis pa gol ba'i rnam grangs la lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6353: chad par lta ba'i rnam grangs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6354: rtag par lta ba'i rnam grangs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6355: log par lta ba bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6356: nang pa la yang lta ba ngan pa yod par bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6357: log par rtogs pa'i skyon no //
NK124(ngo)001:6358: dang po ni mu stegs chad lta ba dag gis /
NK124(ngo)001:6360: da lta ba ni blo bur ba /
NK124(ngo)001:6361: sangs rgyas thob pa'i rgyu med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6363: tshe phyi ma med par 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:6364: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye shes yang med par 'dod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6365: 'bras bu chad par lta ba de /
NK124(ngo)001:6366: des na snga ma'i rgyu yod pa phyi ma med par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6367: rags pa yod la phra ba med par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6368: sangs rgyas thob pa med cing stong pa phyogs chad du 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6370: rgyu nyid chad par rtogs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:6371: rgyu'i cha gcig chad par rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:6372: 'bras bu chad par rtogs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:6373: rgyu 'bras kun tu chad par rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:6374: chad par lta ba'i rnam grangs yin //
NK124(ngo)001:6376: gnyis pa rtag par lta ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6377: yang mu stegs rtag par lta ba'i 'dod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6378: gtso' bo dang skyes bu rtag la /
NK124(ngo)001:6379: de las byung ba'i rtags pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6380: sangs rgyas thob nas kyang las nag po'i 'bras bu 'byung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:6382: rgyu rtags par 'dod pa rtags par rtogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6383: 'bras bu'i phyogs gcig rtag par rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:6384: rgyu 'bras kun tu rtag par rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:6385: rtags par lta ba'i rnam grangs yin //
NK124(ngo)001:6387: gsum pa log par rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6388: gong gis rgyu 'bras chad par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6389: rtags par 'dod pa'i bye brag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6390: log lta spyi'i rnam grangs yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6391: gang las log na 'bras bu bla na med pa'i theg pa las log pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6393: rtag dang chad pa'i bye brag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:6394: log lta can gyi rnam grangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:6395: bla med theg pa las log yin //
NK124(ngo)001:6397: nang pa la yang log lta 'dzin pa yod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6398: gong gi rtag chad kyi lta ba yod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6399: snyigs ma tha ma'i dus su /
NK124(ngo)001:6400: rdo rje theg pa khas blangs pa'i rnal 'byor pa kha cig /
NK124(ngo)001:6401: thos bsam gnyis kyi shes rab la ma sbyangs pa'i /
NK124(ngo)001:6402: rnal 'byor dam par khas blang ba yang mang ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6404: lta ba'i bye brag gong ma ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6405: da lta snyigs ma'i ding sang la //
NK124(ngo)001:6406: gsang sngags theg par khas 'che ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:6407: shes rab gnyis la ma sbyangs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:6408: de dag kun gyi nang na mang //
NK124(ngo)001:6410: lnga pa log pa'i skyon ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6411: gong gi lta log de rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:6412: lta ba zab mo yin pa'i tshul smras kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6413: bdag tu zhen pa'i rtogs pa ma spangs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6414: srid pa'i 'khor ba'i gnas su 'khor ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6416: log pa'i lta ba zab mo dag /
NK124(ngo)001:6417: shin tu zab pa'i tshul smras kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:6418: zhen pa'i mtha' gnyis ma spangs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6419: srid pa'i gnas su yang yang 'khor //
NK124(ngo)001:6421: gnyis pa b+hee pas gol ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6425: gong gi gsang sngags bla med kyi lta ba las gol ba'i /
NK124(ngo)001:6426: b+hee pa ting nge 'dzin kha cig ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6427: zhi gnas las gol ba'i snyoms 'jug kun gzhi rig
NK124(ngo)001:6428: rtogs kyi rtogs pa de la brtan pa thob kyang
NK124(ngo)001:6430: skye mched mu bzhi la sogs pa'i gnas su skyes shing /
NK124(ngo)001:6431: gzhan yang yid kyi dbang po gsal rtogs kyi rtog med dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6432: sgo lnga snang thog gis rtog med la sogs pa la brten bcas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6433: bla ma mtshan ldan gyis gdams pas ma zin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:6434: gnas lugs rtogs pa'i drod dang rtags dang mi ldan pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6435: rtogs med gsum la 'bras bu barloma pa dag yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6437: bsam gtan bye brag kha cig gis //
NK124(ngo)001:6439: skye mched bzhi sogs skye gnas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6440: sngon gyis mkhas pa ma brten pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6441: 'bras bu nyid du yang dag barlomasa //
NK124(ngo)001:6443: gnyis pa gol ba'i skyon ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6444: bsam gtan nor ba'i sgor zhugs rtog med la brtan pa thob kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6445: las kyi mtha' ma zad pas 'chi 'phos pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:6446: bag chags 'khrul pas mtshams sbyar nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6447: bar dor sdug bsngal shar ba'i dus /
NK124(ngo)001:6449: bstan pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang bcas pa rnams la skur pa btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6450: mnar med rdo rje dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal myong bar 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:6452: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6453: ye shes rgyas pa'i mdo' las gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:6454: bzhi pa mu stegs pa de rnams lam 'tshol ba'i gtan tshigs la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6456: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa la brten nas lam 'tshol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6457: kha cig ni gzugs brnyan gyi chos la brtag dpyad byas nas lam 'tshol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6458: kha cig ni byang chub sems dpa' thabs mkhas pas
NK124(ngo)001:6459: skal dman lam du zhugs nas lam tshol ba dang
NK124(ngo)001:6460: / zhor byung du bstan pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:6462: nang pa la dga' ba'i phyi rol pa kha cig /
NK124(ngo)001:6463: skye mtsho' brten sogs la gnas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6464: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa'i gdul bya yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6466: lam tshol ba'i sems rtogs kyi 'du shes yod pa'i phyir na /
NK124(ngo)001:6467: 'bras bu tshol ba'i gzhan phyogs can zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6469: phyi rol lta ba 'di dag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:6470: 'khor lo rgyud kyi gdul bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6471: sems la rtogs pa thob pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:6472: 'bras bu tshol ba'i gzhan phyogs can //
NK124(ngo)001:6476: sprul sku mya ngan la 'das nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6477: bstan pa nub tu nye ba'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:6478: bstan pa de nyid la brtag dpyad byas pa'i sgo nas 'gyur zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:6481: sprul pa snga ma 'das pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:6482: bstan pa rgas par gyur pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:6483: rtog dpyod log pa'i 'khrul pa can //
NK124(ngo)001:6486: yang log par zhugs pa kha cig ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6487: thabs mkhas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:6488: skal dman thabs kyi lam du zhugs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6489: lam tshol ba dag kyang yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6491: log par gyur pa 'ga' zhig ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6492: sangs rgyas ston pa thabs mkhas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6493: skal dman thabs kyi zhugs pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:6494: lam tshol ba yi thabs su bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:6497: theg pa dgu'i zhor las byung ba'i mu stegs de dag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6498: nang pa'i theg pa'i zhor las byung ba'i zhar 'byung /
NK124(ngo)001:6500: sangs rgyas snga ma'i bstan pa la zhugs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6501: phyi ma gzhan rkyen log pa'i dbang du 'khrul pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6502: sangs rgyas nye gnas zhes kyang bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6503: rnam grangs mngon byang gi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:6504: mu stegs can la smad mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:6505: rnam par snang mdzad ring ba'i rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:6507: mdo' sngags theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:6508: ma rtogs log rtog gi rnam par dag pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:6509: gsum pa don dam nges pa'i theg pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6513: theg pa dang gdul bya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6515: de dag so sor sdeb tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:6518: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6519: nang pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6522: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6525: gdul bya'i skabs kyang gsum nyid de /
NK124(ngo)001:6526: blo'i bskal pa che chung las //
NK124(ngo)001:6532: gnyen pos spongs dang thabs kyis bsgyur //
NK124(ngo)001:6533: ye shes chen po'i gnas su dag /
NK124(ngo)001:6537: gdul bya 'dul thabs theg pa gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:6538: so sor sprad de sdeb par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:6540: gnyis pa rgyas par bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6541: theg dgu'i lung rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6542: de dag gi yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6544: theg pa dgur dbye' ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6546: de dag so sor sdeb tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:6548: gong gi theg pa gsum po re re las gsum gsum du 'byed par byed pa nyid de /
NK124(ngo)001:6549: de gsum re re la'ang gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6550: tha ma 'bring dang mchog gi tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:6551: des na theg pa dgu' zhes grags //
NK124(ngo)001:6553: gnyis pa de dag 'dul ba'i thabs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6555: nyon mongs pa'i gnyen po thabs kyi sbyang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6556: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pas nyon mongs pa
NK124(ngo)001:6557: nyid dag pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du sgyur ba dang
NK124(ngo)001:6558: / dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pas nyon mongs pa
NK124(ngo)001:6559: ma spang par ye shes chen po'i ngang du dag
NK124(ngo)001:6562: thabs kyang de bzhin bye brag dgu //
NK124(ngo)001:6565: de dag gi grangs so sor sprad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6566: dgu gsum nyi shu rtsa bdun sdeb pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6568: dgu' gsum nyi shu rtsa bdun sdeb //
NK124(ngo)001:6570: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6575: gdul bya'i stabs kyis gsum du dbye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6579: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6580: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6581: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6582: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6583: dang po nyan thos kyi theg pa la yang gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6588: dbang po tha ma'i tha ma nyan thos kyis theg pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6590: tha ma'i tha ma 'di lta ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6592: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:6600: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6603: chos spyi'i mtshan nyid bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6604: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6605: srid par 'khor ba thams cad sdug bsngal ba /
NK124(ngo)001:6606: khams gsum thams cad stong pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6607: chos thams cad bdag med pa dang bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6608: phyi rol pas ni phung po la /
NK124(ngo)001:6610: mi gtsang ba'i lus la gtsang bar 'dzin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6611: sdug bsngal la bde bar 'dzin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6612: 'dus byas rtag par 'dzin pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6615: sangs rgyas theg pa'i bkar rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6618: mi rtag sdug bsngal stong bdag med //
NK124(ngo)001:6619: bdag tsam spyi rtag las zlog pa //
NK124(ngo)001:6620: sangs rgyas theg pa spyi'i sgo //
NK124(ngo)001:6623: nyan thos gang gi sgor 'jug na /
NK124(ngo)001:6624: 'khor ba'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal du shes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6625: 'khor ba'i rgyu kun 'byung spang byar shes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6626: mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'bras bu 'gog pa thob byar shes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6627: de nyid mngon du byed pa'i lam b+hee par bya ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6628: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i 'jug sgo yin par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6632: de yang kun 'byung spangs par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:6634: lam rgyud la rten par bya /
NK124(ngo)001:6641: rdzogs pa chen po sa lam klong las /
NK124(ngo)001:6642: de rgyu las nyon mongs phung po'i sa bon ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:6643: de las rgyu drug khams gsum 'byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6644: bag chags brtas shing mngon par smin byed rkyen //
NK124(ngo)001:6645: rgyu rkyen 'brel pas khams gsum rab tu skye //
NK124(ngo)001:6647: ma rig nyon mongs las kyis khams gsum rgyur gyur pas rgyu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6648: de las rgyu drug kun 'byung bas kun 'byung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6649: bag chags kyis zhen pa brtas shing 'bras bu smin pas rkyen dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6650: rgyu rkyen 'brel bas khams gsum du skye zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:6653: sdug bsngal ba la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6659: rkyen gyis skye zhing rang dbang med mi rtag /
NK124(ngo)001:6660: gsum mam brgyad kyis gnod pas sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6661: bdag gi lta ba mi mthun phyogs stong pa //
NK124(ngo)001:6662: lnga phung bdag tu ltar med stong pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:6664: dus skad cig mar mi sdod pas mi rtag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6665: gsum mam brgyad kyis sdug bsngal bas sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6666: gang zag gi dngos po stong par stong pas stong pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6667: gang zag bdag med pas bdag med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6674: rgyu rkyen bral bas phung khams 'jig phyir 'gogs //
NK124(ngo)001:6675: sdug bsngal med pas bsam mi 'byung zhing gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:6676: phyis kyang khams gsum sdug bsngal bral rgyal lam //
NK124(ngo)001:6677: don dam bde ba phyin te skyon las nges pa 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:6679: khams gsum sdug bsngal che 'bring 'joms shing de'i 'bras bu 'gog pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6680: nang du nyon mongs pa'i me ro zhi bas zhi ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6681: gnas skabs kyi yon tan thob pas gya nom dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6682: mthong ba b+hee pa la sogs rang rang gis don rtogs shing thob pas nges par 'byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6683: lam gyi bden pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6688: 'phags pa'i sa zhugs myang 'das grol lam las //
NK124(ngo)001:6689: 'khrul ba'i gnyen por chos nyid ma gyur rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:6690: phyin ci log spangs yang dag thob phyir sgrub //
NK124(ngo)001:6691: 'khor bar mi skye 'das pa nges par 'byin //
NK124(ngo)001:6693: so so skye bo las blo 'phags shing /
NK124(ngo)001:6694: mya ngan las 'das pa'i sar 'gro bas lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6695: skad cig rang gsal gyi don rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6696: 'dzin pa'i 'khrul pa bcoms nas rig pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6697: blo rab 'bring rnams nyams su len pas sgrub pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6698: 'khor ba las grol zhing mya ngan las 'das pa thob pas nges par 'byin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6700: sprul pa sku'i nyan thos dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6701: tshul rtags 'dzin pa'i nyan thos dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6702: grub pa mthar phyin gyi nyan thos dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6705: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:6706: theg dman gyi gdul bya'i ched du /
NK124(ngo)001:6707: nyan thos su sprul pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6708: kun dga' bo phyag na rdo rje'i sprul pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6710: sha ri'i bu 'jam dpal dbyangs su sprul pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6711: gnyis pa tshul rtags 'dzin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6713: nyan thos kyi tshul rtags 'dzin cing nyan thos dang mthun par smra ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6714: gsum pa grub pa mthar 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6715: nyan thos kyi ris ma nges pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6718: da lta nyan thos kyi lam la gnas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6719: lam bor nas theg chen du gyur ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6720: 'di la'ang so so skye bo dang 'phags pa gnyis yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6722: nyan thos drod rtse la gnas pa theg chen du gyur nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6723: bzod 'bring du gnas pas rang sangs rgyas su 'gyur srid pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6725: gnyis pa slob rigs log nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6726: sangs rgyas su 'gyur gzhan gsum las //
NK124(ngo)001:6728: de yang phyis nas sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba dpal 'phreng gis zhus pa'i mdo' las /
NK124(ngo)001:6729: nyan thos su 'gyur nas rang sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:6730: phyis nas sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:6733: 'dod chags dang ma bral ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6736: nyan thos 'phags pa'i gang zag /'dod chags ma bral ba te /
NK124(ngo)001:6738: lan cig phyir 'ong ba gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6739: de gnyis smon lam gyi stobs kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:6740: 'dod khams su skye ba mtshan nyid pa lon /
NK124(ngo)001:6741: gnyis pa 'dod chags dang bral ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6744: 'dod khams kyi nyon mongs pa dgu spangs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6745: der skye ba mtshan nyid pa mi len kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:6746: sprul pa'i lus kyis sems can gyi don byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:6747: de gnyis 'phags pa'i lam thob kyis 'dod khams su skye ba len pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:6748: zab pas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6749: de yang las dang po ba theg chen du zhugs pa bas /
NK124(ngo)001:6750: skal pa bzhi bcus sangs rgyas bul ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6752: rang bzhin zhi ba 'dod pa yang yang goms pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:6754: nyan thos ma nges rnam gnyis te //
NK124(ngo)001:6755: theg don mthong dang ma mthong ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6756: don mthong 'dod chags bral ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:6758: de nyid 'phags pa'i lam thob pa //
NK124(ngo)001:6759: srid pa dag tu bsgyur ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:6760: bsam gyis mi khyab 'gyur ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:6761: skye ba dag ni yang dag ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:6762: gcig ni smon lam dag gis na //
NK124(ngo)001:6763: skye ba rab tu sgyur bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:6764: gcig shos phyir mi 'ong ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:6765: ldan phyir sprul pa rab tu bsgrub //
NK124(ngo)001:6766: de ni yang dang yang du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6767: rang sems kun tu 'byung ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:6768: mya ngan 'das pa mngon dga' phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:6769: rtogs pas bul ba yin par 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:6771: gsum pa rigs ma nges pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6772: bye brag tu smra ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6775: chos dang smra ba'i nyan thos la //
NK124(ngo)001:6776: bye brag pa dang mdo' sde pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6777: phyi rol yul la brtsod byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:6778: shes pa skad cig snang ba mthun //
NK124(ngo)001:6781: phyi rdul phran du 'dod pa mthun la /
NK124(ngo)001:6782: kun rdzob rags pa mi mthun te /
NK124(ngo)001:6784: rdul phran ma 'dres ne sing lta bur 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:6786: gzhi lnga rdzas grub tu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6788: dang po rdul phran sil bu pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6789: g.yag rnga dang ne sing gis tshul du 'dod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6790: klu sgrub kyis g.yu' thang las /
NK124(ngo)001:6791: kun rdzob bye brag 'dod zhugs nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:6792: snod kyi rdzas rnams dngos po 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:6793: rdul phran sil bu phan tshun bar //
NK124(ngo)001:6794: ma 'dres ne sing lta bu ste //
NK124(ngo)001:6798: gzung 'dzin tha dad dus mnyam gcer 'phrad 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6800: bzhi lnga rdzas grub tu 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6805: rtags pa 'dus ma byas kyi bzhi dang lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6807: snang ba gzugs kyi chos bco lnga pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6810: 'byung ba lnga thun mong du gyur pa'i yid dang bco lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6811: gzugs kyi mtshan nyid ni gzhig cing gzhoms du rung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6812: de yang rags pa gzugs su 'dod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6813: yul phan tshun reg tu yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6814: bcad pa gzugs su 'dod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6815: sgo lngas yul so sor bcad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6816: gdag pa gzugs su 'dod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6817: yid gzugs log gzugs su snang ba rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:6818: gtso bo sems kyi gzhi ni rnam shes tshogs drug go //
NK124(ngo)001:6819: 'khor sems las byung ba'i gzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6820: sems 'byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig go //
NK124(ngo)001:6821: drug rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:6827: nyi shu nye ba'i nyon mongs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6857: yul so sor nges pa lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6871: gtong bsam rnam par mi 'tshe ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6872: 'du byas kyi gzhi ni nyer gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6882: ming tshig yi ge so so skye bo ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6883: mi mthun pa'i 'du shes bcu gnyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6894: brtan pa ma yin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6898: rtag pa 'dus ma byas pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6903: dus gsum rtag par rdzas yod du 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6905: rgyu 'bras rdzas gcig ni ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:6906: gnyis pa mdo sde pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:6907: phyi rdul phra rags 'dus pa'i gong bur 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6908: da ltar gyi gzung yul rags pa 'di /
NK124(ngo)001:6909: don dam dgos po ma yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:6910: 'di rnam pa skye byed kyi gzhi /
NK124(ngo)001:6911: lkog gyur mun rdzas lta bur 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6913: mdo' sde kun rdzob phra rags rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:6917: snod bcud rdul phran sil bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6918: skad cig cha med nang gi sems //
NK124(ngo)001:6919: de la sogs pa'i bye brag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:6920: nyan thos theg pa'i lta ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:6922: bye brag pas skad cig cha med don dam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6923: rdul phran cha med kun rdzob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6924: skad cig cha shas med pa rgyun du gnas par 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6926: nya dang lcags kyu bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:6927: blo rno med kyis gcer 'thong du 'dzin par smra'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6929: gzung 'dzin gnyis gzhal bya gzhal byed kyi 'brel pa yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:6930: rnam pa gzhal yul yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:6932: rnam bcas kyis yul 'dzin par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6933: bzhi pa gzhung 'dzin pa'i nyan thos la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6938: de las gyes pa sde pa bco brgyad de /
NK124(ngo)001:6939: phal chen pa la'ang lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6940: shar gyis ri bo'i sde dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6941: nub kyis ri bo'i sde dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6944: yod par smra ba'i sde la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:6945: gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i sde dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6951: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6952: gnas brtan pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6955: gtsug lag lam chen gyi sde'o //
NK124(ngo)001:6956: mang pos bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:6957: sa sgron rig byed kyi sde dang /
NK124(ngo)001:6961: bye brag pa dang mdo' sde pa bshad pa yang yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:6962: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6967: nges 'byung gis bsam pa la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6968: nyan thos kyi sde snod la thos bsam gyis bden bzhi /
NK124(ngo)001:6969: mi rtag lam bcu drug tsam rtogs par byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6970: tshogs lam bzhi gsum bcu gnyis b+heer byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:6972: tshul gnas thos dang ting 'dzin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6973: b+hee pa la ni rab tu sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:6981: dang po gsum la che 'bring gsum gsum yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6982: bzod chung man chad chos bcu drug po dmigs nas mtshungs par b+hee /
NK124(ngo)001:6983: bzod 'bring du lam 'gogs kun 'byung gis bzhi bzhi rim gyis dor nas /
NK124(ngo)001:6985: skad cig re re las med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:6988: ci ltar bzod chen skad cig la //
NK124(ngo)001:6989: gcig yin de ni chos kyi mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:6991: gnyis pa zag med la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:6999: rgyun zhugs 'bras bu la zhugs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7000: mthong lam skad cig bco lnga mngon du gyur pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7002: de la skad cig bco lnga ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7003: ma mthong mthong phyir mthong ba'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:7006: rgyun zhugs 'bras bu la gnas pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7007: mthong lam skad cig bcu drug la gnas pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:7009: bcu drug pa la de 'bras gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:7011: 'dir ni mthong spangs ma lus pa spangs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7017: 'dod khams kyi b+hee spangs che 'bring dgu yod pa'i /
NK124(ngo)001:7018: che rims nas lnga man chad spangs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7020: rnam par lnga'i bar bcom nas //
NK124(ngo)001:7021: gnyis pa la ni zhugs pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7023: gnyis pa 'bras bu la gnas pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7024: b+hee spangs drug spangs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7026: rnam par drug po zad gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7027: de ni lan cig phyir 'ong pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7029: 'di la bye brag 'bras gnas khyad par /
NK124(ngo)001:7030: che ba bdun nas brgyad zad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7031: tshe gcig bar chad gcig zad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7033: lha mi tshe gcig la dgra bcom thob par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:7034: 'dod khams kyi lha mi'i nang nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7035: skye ba rigs 'dra man chad las mi lan pas lan gcig phyir 'ong ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7036: sra ba phyir mi 'ong ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7037: zhugs pa dang zhugs 'bras gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:7039: phyir mi 'ong 'bras bu la zhugs te /
NK124(ngo)001:7041: dgu pa spangs pa'i sbyor ba la brtson pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7043: 'dod khams kyi spangs cha dgu po thams cad spangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7044: 'dod khams su mi skye ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7046: rnam dgu zad pa phyir mi 'ong //
NK124(ngo)001:7048: gzugs kyi spang bya ma lus pa spangs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7049: phyir mi 'ong ba'i khyad par gyis chos yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:7050: gzugs med kyi srid rtse'i brgyad spangs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7051: dgra bcom 'bras bu la zhugs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7053: srid rtse'i bar pa brgyad zad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7055: gsum pa mthar phyin gyi lam la gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7058: bshad ma thag pa'i dgra bcom 'bras bu la zhugs pa thal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7059: gnyis pa dgra bcom 'bras bu la gnas pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7060: khams gsum gyi spang bya ma lus pa spangs nas mya ngan las 'das pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7062: bden pa bzhi dang dbugs 'grang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7063: zad pa brgyad dang keng rus so //
NK124(ngo)001:7064: de dag bsam gtan bye brag yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7066: gong gi b+hee spangs pa bden pa bzhi b+hee pa'i tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7067: nyan thos rab kyis 'gogs pa la zhugs /
NK124(ngo)001:7069: tha ma keng rus la brten te /
NK124(ngo)001:7070: bar skabs rnams su zad par b+hee pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7079: de dag ni nam mkha' rnam par shes pa'i mdo' las bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:7080: bzhi pa spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7084: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med lnga /
NK124(ngo)001:7085: de dang nye ba lnga la sogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:7086: mdor na mi dge ba phra zhing phra ba nas spangs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7087: kha na ma thob pa mtha' dag bsdoms nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7088: dge ba bcu la sogs pa'i legs spyod thams cad phun sum tshogs par spyod do //
NK124(ngo)001:7090: shin tu ya nga'i las spangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:7091: zhan pa'i dge ba phun sum tshogs //
NK124(ngo)001:7093: sbyangs yon bcu gnyis yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:7094: dang po gnas 'thab pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7106: spyod lam mthab pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7110: gzhan rnams khrus dang gtsang sbra lta spyod zhi du len pa /
NK124(ngo)001:7112: rang don du tshul ltar skyon mtha' dag spangs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7113: yon tan mtha' dag blangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7114: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa yis /
NK124(ngo)001:7115: spangs blangs dgag sgrub tshul bzhin spyod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7117: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7118: gang yang kun rdzob mtshan ma'i tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:7119: thams cad spang blang dgag sgrub pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7120: nyan thos pa yi spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7123: so sor thar pa rigs bdun yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7127: bar slob ma dang bdun yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7129: so so thar pa rigs bdun te //
NK124(ngo)001:7131: de rnams kyis slab pa srung tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7136: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang gsum /
NK124(ngo)001:7137: ngag gis rdzun rtsa ba bzhi /
NK124(ngo)001:7138: yan lag chang dang lnga rdzogs par bsrung pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7140: slab pa bzhi lnga rdzogs pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7143: slob dpon la chos bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7144: mkhan po las thob pa gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7147: sdom pa'i rtsa ba bcu gsum dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7150: gang zhig srog gcod gzhan gyis nor 'phrogs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7151: mi tshangs spyod rdzun bcos pa'i chang la sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:7152: gar sogs 'phreng sogs mal stan mthon po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7153: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul len pa spangs //
NK124(ngo)001:7155: mkhan por gsol btab mkhan po las thob pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7156: khyim pa'i rtags spangs rab byung tshul rtags 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:7157: chos gsum dang po dang ni ldan par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:7159: dge slong pho ni rtsa ba bzhi /
NK124(ngo)001:7160: lhag ma bcu gsum ma nges pa'i chos gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7162: ltung ba 'ba' zhig pa dgu bcu /
NK124(ngo)001:7163: bslab pa'i chos brgya bcu bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7164: dril bas nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa gsum bsrung bar byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:7168: nyis brgya lnga bcu lnga brgya gang //
NK124(ngo)001:7171: nyi shu rtsa gnyis bsrung ba yang bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:7173: nyan thos bsrungs pa'i tshul khrims yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7176: dang po nges byung bslab pa'i sgor zhugs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7177: khams gsum gyi spang bya phra rags ma zad kyi bar du /
NK124(ngo)001:7178: 'jig chags stong gnas re re la skal phran nyi shu nyi shu byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:7179: skal phran brgyad cu tham pa la bskal pa chen
NK124(ngo)001:7180: po gcig tu rtsis pa'i bskal pa chen po gcig
NK124(ngo)001:7181: gam / de las sbyangs yun ring na /
NK124(ngo)001:7182: skal pa brgya la sogs pa yang sbyang bar bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:7184: 'jug nas srid pa zad kyi bar //
NK124(ngo)001:7185: bskal pa chen po brgya sogs yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7188: de ltar khams gsum gyi sa bon dang bral nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7189: dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7194: bsdug bden gyi brten phung po tsam zhig lhag lus te /
NK124(ngo)001:7195: dper na sdong po bcad pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7197: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK124(ngo)001:7198: ma 'gags pa yi lus kyi su //
NK124(ngo)001:7199: tshor ba dang du len pa na //
NK124(ngo)001:7200: de'i sems ni rnam par grol //
NK124(ngo)001:7201: mi shi bar ni gyur ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:7203: de la yang rgyan can dang rgyan med gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:7205: nyan thos kyi skabs kyi ston pa sh+aakya thub pa lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:7206: sprul pa'i sku'i mtshan dpe' dang ldan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7207: gzhan ni rgyan sna tshogs dang ldan pa /
NK124(ngo)001:7209: rdzogs pa chen po 'bras bu'i klong las /
NK124(ngo)001:7210: sangs rgyas dgra bcom rdul phran ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7211: thub pa dbang po'i sku 'chang ba //
NK124(ngo)001:7215: ya brgyad kyi skad cig la mngon du byas /
NK124(ngo)001:7216: nyon mongs pa'i 'chi ba mtha' dag dang bral te /
NK124(ngo)001:7217: dgongs pa mtsho la 'khyag zhu ba'am /
NK124(ngo)001:7218: nam mkha' la sprin 'khrig pa ltar 'byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7220: zung bzhi ya brgyad lus rgyan bral //
NK124(ngo)001:7222: phyogs 'das mngon las nyon mongs zhi //
NK124(ngo)001:7223: shing zad me shi ci ltar bar //
NK124(ngo)001:7224: dge slong mya ngan 'das pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:7225: lus med gzung 'dzin phra ba tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:7227: de nyid kyang ngo bo gcig ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7228: rnam pa'i cha nas rgyan can la //
NK124(ngo)001:7229: dgongs pa'i cha nas rgyan med do //
NK124(ngo)001:7231: rten phung po yang med par nye bar zhi ba ni lhag med do //
NK124(ngo)001:7233: dper na sdong po bsregs pa lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7234: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK124(ngo)001:7235: gang na lus zhig tshor ba 'gags //
NK124(ngo)001:7237: 'du shes nye bar zhi ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7238: rnam par shes pa nub gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7239: de dag la ci'i phyir nyan thos zhes bya zer na /
NK124(ngo)001:7241: sgra bcas kyi chos nyan zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:7242: thos pa gzhan la sgra bcas su sgrogs par byed pas na nyan thos te /
NK124(ngo)001:7243: kho rang kho na'i phyir byed bcos yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:7244: yang theg chen gyi chos rang gis thos pa gzhan la sgrog par byed na thos sgrogs zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7246: mgon po de ring bdag cag nyan thos 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:7247: byang chub dam pa yang dag sgrag par dmigs //
NK124(ngo)001:7248: byang chub sems dpa' sgra yang rab tu rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:7249: de bas bdag cag nyan thos mi zad 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:7251: de ltar nyan thos kyis dbye ba bcu de bstan nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7252: sa'i rnam gzhag ci ltar yin zhe na ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7254: dkar po rnam par mthong ba'i sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7259: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i sa dang /
