NK124(ngo)001:7260: byas pa rtogs pa'i sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7262: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7266: thar pa cha mthun gyi lam yin pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:7269: de nas rigs nges par bshad pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:7270: gsum pa rgyun zhugs 'bras bu la zhugs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7271: yas mar bgrangs pas brgyad yin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7272: bzhi pa rgyun zhugs 'bras gnas yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7273: mthong lam rnam grol gyi lam yin pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:7274: lnga pa ni phyir 'ongs 'bras gnas yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7275: 'dod khams kyi b+hee spangs ma lus pa spangs pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:7278: 'dod khams kyi b+hee spangs ma lus spangs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7282: bya ba byas pa rtogs pa yin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7283: brgyad pa nyan thos kyi sa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7284: sngar ma bshad pa'i 'bras bu gnyis pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7286: bzhi pa'i zhugs pa gsum yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7287: spyi ming bye brag la btags pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:7288: rang sangs rgyas kyi sa ni 'og nas 'byung ba'i rang sangs rgyas kyi sa kho na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7289: kha cig tu dkar po rnam par mthong ba'i sa mi bgrang na brgyad do //
NK124(ngo)001:7290: gsum pa lung gis zhabs bsdud pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7292: shin tu ya nga'i las spangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:7294: rang gis rtsa ba bden bkrun pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7295: so sor thar pa'i lam du snang //
NK124(ngo)001:7297: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:7298: nyan thos kyis rnam par bzhag pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:7299: gnyis pa dbang po tha ma'i 'bring rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7304: dbang po tha ma'i 'bring rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7306: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:7316: rten 'brel bcu gnyis 'jug pa'i sgo zhes pa tshul ci ltar na /
NK124(ngo)001:7317: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos kyi rten 'brel bcu gnyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7318: lugs zlog mya ngan las 'das pa'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7323: g.yung drung gi shugs 'bras la brten nas rtogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7324: rgyu dang 'brel pa drug /'bras bu dang 'brel pa drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7340: lugs nas ldog pas rgyu 'bras ma grub par rtogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7342: dur khrod kyi keng rus la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7343: ma grub par rtogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7355: nang rten 'brel lugs nas ldog pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7357: 'dzin pa rag pa rang bzhin med par rtogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7358: nang skad cig rang gsal nyan thos dang mthun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7360: nyan thos rang rgyal don dam 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:7361: kun rdzob snang ba'i khyad par ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7362: gzugs kyi bsdus pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK124(ngo)001:7363: rten 'brel rgyu rkyen dbang gyur pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7367: lta ba phyi rol rdul phran las //
NK124(ngo)001:7368: gzugs kyi phung po bdag med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7370: gong gi rten 'brel lugs ldog pas gzugs kyi phung
NK124(ngo)001:7371: po bcu bzhi la sogs bdag med par rtogs kyang
NK124(ngo)001:7372: / rnam par rig byed ma yin par bdag med par ma shes shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7373: gang zag skad cig cha med stong par ma rtogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:7374: slob dpon ti ra ma tis gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:7375: gzugs don rtogs pa spangs phyir dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7376: 'dzin pa mi spang phyir na yang //
NK124(ngo)001:7377: brten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:7380: bse ru ltar gcig pur gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7381: ne tso ltar tshogs la gnas pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:7384: lam 'grod tshul dang 'bras bu rang don la gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7385: gzhan don rgyu ba dang lngar shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7386: dang po bse ru lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7387: theg pa gsum gyi dbang po rnon po skyo shas che zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:7389: gcig pur gnas pa la dga' ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7390: gnyis pa tshogs bsag tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7392: nges 'byung gis tshul khrims rnam dag la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7393: thar pa cha mthun gyi dge bas bsdus pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7394: skal pa brgya yi bar du bsags pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7396: bse' ru skal pa brgya'i rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:7398: tshogs bsags pa tshogs chen por phyin pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:7399: skye ba len par mngon shes kyis gzigs nas smon lam 'grub par bya ba'i don du /
NK124(ngo)001:7400: ye shes kyi tshogs nyan thos kyi sde snod la rten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7407: mkhas pa'i don drug la mkhas par byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7408: sangs rgyas dang nyan thos med pa'i zhing stong par skye bar gyur cig /
NK124(ngo)001:7409: de yang gzhan la mi ston pa /
NK124(ngo)001:7410: rang gi rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis lam 'grod par gyur cig /
NK124(ngo)001:7411: byang chub thob pa nas gdul bya la lus kyi snying brtse bar byed kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7412: ngag gi snying brtse bar gyur cig /
NK124(ngo)001:7413: ces smon lam gyis tshogs bsogs par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:7417: shi 'phos nas smon lam gyi stobs kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7420: rus pa ni ci las byung bsam pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:7421: rten 'brel lugs 'byung lugs ldog tu rtogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:7422: bsam gtan la brten nas lam lnga mngon du byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:7424: sangs rgyas rnams ni mi bzhugs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:7425: nyan thos rnams kyang zad gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7426: rang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7427: brtan pa med par rab tu skyed //
NK124(ngo)001:7430: ston dang byang chub bse ru bar //
NK124(ngo)001:7431: bsam gtan mtha' brten gcig la kun //
NK124(ngo)001:7434: snum zad pa'i mar me lta bu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7435: ma rig pa'i gnyen po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7436: shes pa rang gsal go ma 'gags par b+hee pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7437: spangs bya ma rig pa zad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7438: gnyen po b+hee byed kyi 'du shes zad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:7439: rga shi'i bar du zad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7441: gnyen po ting nge 'dzin stobs su gyur pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7442: las dang nyon mongs pa'i zhen pa gnyis 'gags /
NK124(ngo)001:7443: lta bas shes bya bden pa bzhi zad par byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7445: lam lnga sa brgyad man chad non pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7447: mar me bzad pa lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7448: ma rig zad nas 'du shes zad //
NK124(ngo)001:7449: de nas rga shi'i bar du ste //
NK124(ngo)001:7450: de ltar zhen pa gnyis 'gags pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7451: bsam gtan yin par rgyal bas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:7456: smad la chu 'brub pa la sogs rdzu 'phrul ya
NK124(ngo)001:7457: ma zung gi sgo nas don mdzad par gsungs so
NK124(ngo)001:7459: nyan thos kyi skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:7461: spyod pa tshul khrims nyan thos dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7462: mthun par 'jug la khyad par du //
NK124(ngo)001:7463: gcig bur gnas pa bsgyur par byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7465: bse ru lta bu'i rang rgyal gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7467: kha na ma mtho ba spangs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7468: dge bcu so thar gyi sdom pa tshul bzhin du bsrungs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7469: khrus dang gtsang sbra la 'bad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:7470: yid bzhin mchog thob kyi 'bras bu bsgrub par byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7472: gcig pur gnas pas sgrub byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7475: bskal pa chen po brgya'i bar du sangs rgyas dang
NK124(ngo)001:7476: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mnyes par byed cing
NK124(ngo)001:7477: / rgyal ba'i bka' las 'byung ba ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:7478: mkhas pa'i longs spyod la sbyangs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7479: tshogs spyod kyi chos rnams tshogs lam chen pos /
NK124(ngo)001:7480: skal pa chen po brgya'i gsum gnyis tsam gcig nas sbyor lam non /
NK124(ngo)001:7481: tshogs chung gsum cha non par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:7482: chos rnams la rim gyis ldog par gyur kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:7483: sems can gyi don byed pa'i smon lam rgya cher ma btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7484: smon lam tsam la brten par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:7486: skal pa chen po brgya'i bar //
NK124(ngo)001:7487: rgyal ba'i bka' la rab sbyangs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7488: chos rnams rim gyis rtogs gyur kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:7489: smon lam rgya cher ma btabs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7491: bdun pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7498: lamabadena bzhi dang rten 'brel gyis don rtogs pa la rgyun du gnas so //
NK124(ngo)001:7500: 'bras bu thob ka'i skye ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:7501: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sten pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7502: chu zla la sogs rkyen rnams sam //
NK124(ngo)001:7503: rtog tshig nyams su blangs pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:7504: bden pa mthong zhing srid pa zad //
NK124(ngo)001:7505: yid bzhin bde mchog sa la gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:7508: 'dod khams kyi brten can yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7510: gcig pur rgyu zhing lus kyi rdzu'aphrula gyis gzhan don byed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:7513: gang gang don ni gang gang la //
NK124(ngo)001:7514: ci ltar ci ltar nyan 'dod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7515: de de la don de dang de //
NK124(ngo)001:7516: sgra med kyang ni de ltar snang //
NK124(ngo)001:7519: slad kyi 'gro don mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:7520: rigs kyi sprul pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:7521: sangs rgyas byang chub mi bzhugs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:7522: bar skabs dag tu don mdzad pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:7523: gsung gis chos 'chad mi mdzad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7524: rang sangs rgyas su nges par grags //
NK124(ngo)001:7526: gsum pa lung gis zhabs bsdu ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7529: bdag med chos gcig med mthong bas //
NK124(ngo)001:7530: brjod med sprul pa'i chos rnams ston //
NK124(ngo)001:7532: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:7533: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa rnam par bzhag pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:7534: gsum pa dbang po tha ma'i rab byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7539: rang gzhan don gnyis spyod pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7540: srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7541: sku gsum gyi 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7543: shes pa srid la mi gnas shing //
NK124(ngo)001:7544: snying rjes zhi la mi gnas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7551: 'bras bu sku gnyis su'ang bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:7553: gter dang ljon pa'i shing bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:7554: rigs ni rnam gnyis zhes bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:7555: thog med rang bzhin gnas pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:7556: yang dag blang ba mchog yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:7558: gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:7559: gang zag dang 'jug sgo thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7569: kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang don dam pa'i bden pa'i sgo nas 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7571: bden pa gnyis po 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK124(ngo)001:7573: gnyis pa lta ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7575: bye brag rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7576: lta ba bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7578: 'og nas 'byung ba'i dbu ma dag gi lta ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7579: lang kar gshegs pa 'i mdo' las /
NK124(ngo)001:7580: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyis don rab tu 'byed pa'i ris kyi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7581: bdag med gnyis kyi rnam par mi rtog pa la gnas pa bco brgyad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7583: don rab 'byed pa'i bsam gtan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7584: de bzhin mi dmigs bsam gtan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7586: skabs su 'dir theg pa che chung gi rnam par bzhag pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7587: theg pa che chung gi khyad par bzhag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7588: theg chen gyi mtshan nyid bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7590: nyan thos kyi theg pa de las gzhan don gyi thabs mkhas pa la tshang pa'i phyir dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7591: rang nyid gcig pu zhi bar gyur pa'i lam gyis
NK124(ngo)001:7592: 'bras bu thabs mkhas pa'i sangs rgyas 'byung ba las
NK124(ngo)001:7594: nyan thos kyi theg pa de sangs rgyas kyi thabs ma yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:7595: gang thabs ma yin pa la 'bad kyang 'dod pa'i 'bras bu mi 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7596: nyan thos kyi sde snod las byang chub sems dpa' slab par byas pa ma bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7597: nyan thos kyi theg pa gang yin pa de theg chen du mi gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:7599: ma tshang ba dang 'gal ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7600: thabs med de ltar ma bstan te //
NK124(ngo)001:7601: nyan thos kyi ni theg pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7602: theg chen chos zhes bya ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:7605: 'gal ba rnam pa lnga gsung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7611: de dag kyang rim pa bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:7612: nyan thos kyis theg pa rang gcig pu mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7613: mdo sde las kyang de kho na ston pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7614: sbyor bas kyang de kho na la 'jug pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7615: tshul khrims la sogs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7616: gang gi bdag med tsam rtogs pa ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:7617: tshogs gnyis kyi bstan pa rgya chung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7618: myur pa srid pa gsum du grol shes pa'i tshul gyis dus kyang thung pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:7619: theg pa chen po las ni thams cad de las zlog pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7620: sems can la tshad med pa bsam pa'i snying rje dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7621: byang chub sems dpa' sde snod rgya chen po bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7622: sbyor bas kyang gzhan la 'jug pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7623: thabs la mkhas pa dang ma bral ba'i pha rol du phyin pas bsdu ba'i bsod nams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7624: ye shes kyi tshogs rgya che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7625: dus kyang bskal pa grangs med gsum la sogs par rjod par bshad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7627: theg pa dman pa nyid ni dman pa kho na yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7628: theg pa chen po ma yin pa kho na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7629: de yang mdo' sde rgyan las /
NK124(ngo)001:7630: bsam pa dang ni bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7631: sbyor ba dang ni ston pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7632: dus 'gal phyir na dman pa gang //
NK124(ngo)001:7633: de ni dman pa kho na yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7635: gnyis pa theg pa chen po'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7637: dmigs pa chen po nyid dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7638: de bzhin bsgrub pa tha dag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7639: ye shes brtson 'grus rtsam pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7640: thabs la mkhas par gyur pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7641: yang dag bsgrubs pa chen po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7642: sangs rgyas 'phrin las chen po ste //
NK124(ngo)001:7643: chen po bdun dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:7644: theg chen zhes ni nges par brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:7646: sde snod rgya chen po la dmigs pa rgya che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7647: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa la 'jug pas sgrub pa chen po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7648: sa dang po la sogs pa nas bdag nyid kyis
NK124(ngo)001:7649: stong pa mngon sum du rtogs pas ye shes che
NK124(ngo)001:7650: ba dang / grangs med gsum du tshogs gnyis la rtag tu sbyor bas brtsoms pa che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7652: de'i nyes pa ma gos pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7653: thabs mkhas pas che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7655: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa yang dag pa sgrub pa che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7656: 'khor bar gnas kyi bar du mdzad pa rgyun mi chad du ston pas 'phrin las chen po ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7657: chen po bdun dang ldan pa'i phyir na theg pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7658: de la dang po lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7659: 'dis 'gro ba lam gyi theg chen yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:7660: phyi ma gnyis ni 'dir 'gro bas 'bras bu theg pa chen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7661: gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7669: gang yang bden pa gnyis smra ba //
NK124(ngo)001:7670: rnam rig gnas kyi lta ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7676: run shan ti ba'i sems tsam rgyan las /
NK124(ngo)001:7677: kun brtags dang ni gzhan gyi dbang //
NK124(ngo)001:7678: yongs su grub pa 'di rnams ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7679: rtags dang rgyud ma skyes pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:7680: mi 'gyur phyir na go rim bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:7682: dang po kun brtags la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7683: mtshan nyid chad pa'i kun brtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7684: rnam grangs kyis kun brtags so //
NK124(ngo)001:7686: mtshan nyid chad pa'i kun brtags te /
NK124(ngo)001:7688: ri bong gi ra la sogs pa med pa'i chos bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7689: mu stegs pa'i bdag tu 'dzin pa'i rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:7691: snang la zhen bcas kyis rtog pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7693: rigs drug gi mthong snang drug tu mthong ba la sogs pa'i snang tshul rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:7694: de yang sems tsam gsum pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:7695: rnal 'byor pa dag gang gang gis //
NK124(ngo)001:7696: dngos po gang gang rnams rtags pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7697: de nyid kun tu rtags pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7698: ngo bo nyid de de med do //
NK124(ngo)001:7701: rdzas sna rnam pa gcig la yang //
NK124(ngo)001:7702: log mthong brgyad dang yang dag dgu //
NK124(ngo)001:7703: cir yang snang ba'i ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:7705: gnyis pa gzhan dbang la yang gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7710: skad cig ma snga ma las phyi ma 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7711: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang zhing ma dag pas /
NK124(ngo)001:7712: 'khor ba'i rkyen du snang ba rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:7715: skad cig snga ma las phyi ma skyes pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7716: gzung 'dzin bdag gzhan gnyis su 'dzin pa dag cing /
NK124(ngo)001:7717: lam gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i rim pa rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:7719: gzhan dbang don gyis mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7720: gzhan gyi dbang gis ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:7721: rnam rtog yid bzhin rten las 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:7723: gsum pa yongs grub la'ang gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7727: gshis myong yang gnyis med kyis rang rig rang gsal ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7728: sems can rnams kyi rgyud la rang bzhin gyi rtog bral med par gnas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:7729: rgyun chad med par gnas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7731: skad cig rang gsal la spangs bya blo bur gyi dri ma dang bral ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7734: yongs su grub pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7735: grub na de la snga ma'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7736: rtag tu med par 'gyur ba gang //
NK124(ngo)001:7737: de ni dus rnams kun la yod //
NK124(ngo)001:7739: drug po de dag bden pa gnyis su bstan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7740: bden pa gnyis kyis bzhag tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7743: kun brtags kun rdzob kyi bden pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:7744: gzhan dbang dang yongs grub gnyis don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7745: de la'ang gzhan dbang ni chos can don dam pa'i bden pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7746: yongs grub ni chos nyid don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7747: bden pa gnyis kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7748: yang dag rig pa brtags cing spyad na mi bden pa kun rdzob /
NK124(ngo)001:7749: brtags cing spyad na bden pa don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7750: de gnyis ni spyir rang du'ang bden pa gnyis kyi mtshan nyid du'ang 'agro'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7751: gnyis pa mtha' dang bral tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7752: kun brtags dngos por mi bden pas sgro 'dogs kyi mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:7753: yongs grub chos nyid rgyun chad med pas bskur 'debs kyi mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:7754: gzhan dbang la rtag pa'i skye ba med la rten
NK124(ngo)001:7755: 'brel gyis skye ba yod pas gnyis ka'i mtha' sel
NK124(ngo)001:7756: / yang yongs grub la bdag gnyis kyis stong pas sgro 'dogs kyi mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:7757: gzhan dbang ni chos nyid yin cing rgyun chad med pas bskur ba'i mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:7758: kun brtags rten 'brel tsam du 'byung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:7762: gnyis pa bye brag so so'i 'dod pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7763: rnam bden pa dang rnam rdzun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7766: nang shes pa'i ngo bor bden pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7768: don yod ma yin sems yod de //
NK124(ngo)001:7769: phyi rol don mthong log pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7772: yul ltar snang ba 'di dag kun //
NK124(ngo)001:7773: rab rib sku gzugs rmi mthong ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:7774: shes pa 'khrul pa'i gzugs brnyan phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:7778: rnam rig skad cig ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:7779: dngos po gnyis snang phyir tsam ste //
NK124(ngo)001:7780: rmi lam la sogs ci lta bar //
NK124(ngo)001:7781: dngos po thams cad skad cig ma'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7784: snang ba dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:7785: bden shes pa gcig gi ngo bor bden pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7786: rnam pa'i grangs ji snyed yod par shes pa'i grangs kyang de snyed du yod par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7787: rnam pa dang shes pa sgo nga bkas pa ltar tha dad du 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7789: yul snang dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:7790: nang shes pa gcig gis ngo bo yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7791: dper na rmi lam snang tshul bsam gyis mi khyab kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:7792: shes pa gcig gi ngo bor bden pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:7794: rnam pa'i grangs ji snyed par bden la /
NK124(ngo)001:7795: shes pa'i grangs yang de snyed bden pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7796: rnam grangs ma 'dres par gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:7798: kun rdzob phyi yul dang nang shes pa phan tshun du bden la /
NK124(ngo)001:7800: de gsum yang ngo bo skad cig gi rang gsal dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7801: phyi rol gyi snang ba yin par mthun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7802: de yang mdo sde nas don mthun par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:7803: snang tshad sems su gcig pa'i cha nas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:7805: de nyid ma 'dres pa sna tshogs su snang ba'i cha nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7806: rnam pa dang shes pa'i grangs ltar yang bden /
NK124(ngo)001:7807: de nyid yul shes gnyis su snang ba'i cha nas /
NK124(ngo)001:7808: rnam pa dang shes pa ltar yang bden gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:7809: gnyis pa rnam rdzun pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7811: nang shes pa yang mi bden te /
NK124(ngo)001:7812: nam mkha' la skra shad 'dzag pa ltar bzung ba tsam rdzun par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7814: ci ltar rab rib can dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:7815: skra shad la sogs 'dzin pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:7816: med pa dag kyang snang ba 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:7817: byis pa'i 'dzin pa rnams blod ces pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7818: 'di dag rnam par rang rig tsam ste //
NK124(ngo)001:7819: yod pa ma yin don snang phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:7820: dper na rab rib can dag la //
NK124(ngo)001:7821: skra shad la sogs med mthong bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:7823: de la bye brag tu gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7827: sems dang snang ba 'di gcig pa yang ma yin tha dad pa yang ma yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7831: snang ba rdzun pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:7832: rang rig rang gsal shel ltar dag cing /
NK124(ngo)001:7834: yang bden pa stong ba'i snang ba gcig sangs rgyas kyi sa na yod par 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:7836: dri bcas med par 'dod pa'i dri med de /
NK124(ngo)001:7838: rang rig gnyis med shel ltar dag /
NK124(ngo)001:7839: de nyid dam pas yod par smra //
NK124(ngo)001:7841: de yang kha phyir lta ba'i yul du snang ba thams cad kun brtags yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:7842: nang sems las byung ba'i rgyu rkyen las bskyed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7844: don myong ba gnyis med kyis rang rig rang gsal
NK124(ngo)001:7845: ni shin tu brtags par dka' bas yongs su grub
NK124(ngo)001:7847: gcig shes cha shas rnam pas stong //
NK124(ngo)001:7848: nyi shel chu zla me long sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:7849: brtag par dka' ba'i ye shes nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:7850: de ltar rgyud du rang gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7853: phyi rol gang dang gnas 'di kun //
NK124(ngo)001:7854: yul rnams sems kyis 'khrul smra zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:7855: sems nyid dus matha'i skad cig ma //
NK124(ngo)001:7856: skad cig mi rtag rgyun gyi gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:7858: gnyis pa dbu ma la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7859: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7860: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7863: kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7864: don dam pa dngos smra dag nas stong nyid du bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7865: bden pa gnyis kyi 'dod tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:7866: kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7868: sems so so'i rkyen gyis snang bas kun rdzob ces bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7870: mdo sde kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:7871: yul sems log nas snang ba ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:7874: yul tshogs drug la sogs rnam par snang ba phra rags rdul cha drug tu phye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7875: phra rdul kun rdzob phyogs cha drug tu gzhal bas /
NK124(ngo)001:7876: nyan thos bye brag pa ltar gzhigs na dngos po med de /
NK124(ngo)001:7877: stong nyid spros bral don dam du 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:7878: sems nyid thog matha'i skad cig ma de la /
NK124(ngo)001:7879: dus gsum gzhig nas dngos med de /
NK124(ngo)001:7880: de la rkyen gyis skyes pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:7884: de ma thag pa'i rkyen thams cad mtshogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7886: lhan cig skyes pa'i rkyen las dang nyon mongs pa dag gis /
NK124(ngo)001:7887: snod bcud phyi snod nang bcud gnyis su snang ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:7888: tshe rten 'brel gyis med bzhin du snang bas na
NK124(ngo)001:7889: / kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam du snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7891: mdo sde dbu ma kun rdzob tu //
NK124(ngo)001:7892: yul sems rdzun pa sgyu ma tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:7893: snang ba yul sems so sor 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:7894: don dam pa'i don du gnyis su med //
NK124(ngo)001:7897: yul rnams phra reg rdul cha de //
NK124(ngo)001:7898: phyogs char gzhig na dngos po med //
NK124(ngo)001:7899: sems nyid thog matha'i skad cig ma //
NK124(ngo)001:7900: dus gsum gzhig nas rang bzhin med //
NK124(ngo)001:7901: rkyen ni gnyis dang bzhi dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:7902: snod bcud gnyis su snang ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:7903: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:7905: gsum pa bden pa gnyis kyi 'dod tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7906: de ltar kun rdzob dang don dam bden pa gnyis snang ba yang /
NK124(ngo)001:7907: de nyid gzhan du brjod du med pa'i tshul du 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:7908: de rnams kyi mdo sde spyod pa'i lta ba'i bye brag gtan la phab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7909: gnyis pa rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu' ma la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7913: don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:7914: de gnyis ngo bo gcig la bzlog pa tha dad du bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7916: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu' ma kha cig /
NK124(ngo)001:7917: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad bden pa gnyis su snang ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:7919: shes pas btags pa'i 'khrul pa tsam du snang ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7920: sems rang bzhin skad cig ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7921: dus gsum gyi cha shas dang bral ba'i stong nyid
NK124(ngo)001:7922: spros bral du 'dod pa de nyid don dam pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:7925: nang pa rnal 'byor dbu ma ni //
NK124(ngo)001:7926: kun rdzob rdzun pa tsam du yang //
NK124(ngo)001:7927: yul sems gnyis med yul snang sems //
NK124(ngo)001:7928: kun rdzob rnam rig ci lta bu //
NK124(ngo)001:7929: don dam ma skyes stong pa lta //
NK124(ngo)001:7932: kha cig phyi nang snod bcud dag /
NK124(ngo)001:7933: bden pa gnyis su gnas pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:7934: snod ni sems kyis 'khrul pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:7935: sems ni skad cig dus gsum bral //
NK124(ngo)001:7936: de nyid don dam bden pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7938: dbu' ma de nyid don dam cir yang ma grub cing /
NK124(ngo)001:7939: mtha' dang bral ba mthun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7941: don dam pa de nyid ma rtogs pa'i snang ngor /
NK124(ngo)001:7942: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du yang ma 'gags te /
NK124(ngo)001:7943: sems tsam rnam bden pa dang yang mtshungs /
NK124(ngo)001:7944: yul du snang dus nyid nas yang /
NK124(ngo)001:7945: ngo bo nyid kyis bden pa ma grub ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7946: sems nyid rang gi mtshan nyid dus gsum skye 'gags med pa'i skad cig ma /
NK124(ngo)001:7947: de nyid kun rdzob ltar snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:7949: kun rdzob sgyu mar ma 'gags te //
NK124(ngo)001:7951: sems nyid dus gsum skad cig ma //
NK124(ngo)001:7952: 'gags pa med pa kun rdzob yin //
NK124(ngo)001:7954: gsum pa ngo bo gcig la bzlog pa tha dad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:7955: de ltar bden pa gnyis kyi bye brag so sor gtan la phab kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:7956: ngo bo gcig la zlog phyogs tsam gyis tha dad pa yin la don la dbyer med do //
NK124(ngo)001:7958: bden pa gnyis kyi bye brag kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:7959: ldog phyogs kyis ni tha dad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7960: gsum pa rab tu mi gnas pa la yang gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7963: dang po la yang gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:7964: kun rdzob tu 'khrul pa ma zad bar snang ba mi khegs pa dpe' dang bcas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:7965: don dam par 'khrul pa dag nas yul bems thabs /
NK124(ngo)001:7966: stong nyid spros bral du gtan la phab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:7968: sems nyid don dam pa mtha' bral de nyid ma
NK124(ngo)001:7969: rig 'khrul pa'i rgyu rkyen gyis nyis snang bag chags
NK124(ngo)001:7971: dper na mig nad can gyi snang ngor rab rib
NK124(ngo)001:7972: mthong ba ltar du yul phyi rol gyi snang ngor
NK124(ngo)001:7974: dpang po dang bcas pa 'di rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:7975: don dam par bden par ma grub kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:7976: 'khrul pa spyi mthun gyi blo ngos la bden pa ltar du snang ste /
NK124(ngo)001:7977: nang du 'khrul pa'i bag chags ma zad kyi bar du /
NK124(ngo)001:7978: phyi rol gyi snang ba rnams su yang khegs pa mi gyur ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:7980: rab rib mthu'i skra shad la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7981: ngo bo log pas gzhan dbang rnam dag pa //
NK124(ngo)001:7982: de nyid gang zhig bdag nyid ming dag pas //
NK124(ngo)001:7983: mthong ba de bzhin de nyid 'dir shes gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:7986: ma rig 'khrul pa'i bag chags kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:7987: mig la rab rib snang ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:7988: phyi rol nang dang gnas 'di rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:7989: mi bden bden ltar kun du snang //
NK124(ngo)001:7990: 'khrul pa'i bag chags ma zad tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:7991: nam yang khegs par 'gyur ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:7994: don dam pa 'khrul pa dag nas yul sems thams
NK124(ngo)001:7995: cad stong nyid spros bral du gtan la phab pa
NK124(ngo)001:7996: ste / dbu' ma rab tu mi gnas pa de
NK124(ngo)001:7997: nyid lam rim par 'grod nas 'bras bu thob tshul
NK124(ngo)001:7999: mig nad sangs dus phyi rol du skra shad la
NK124(ngo)001:8000: sogs rab rib kyi snang ba dngas pa bzhin du
NK124(ngo)001:8001: / don dam nang du 'khrul pa brtags pa'i bag chags thams cad zad pa'i tshe na /
NK124(ngo)001:8002: phyi rol gyi yul thim pa med pa rang grol /
NK124(ngo)001:8003: 'khrul reg gzhan du song ba med par mngon sum dngas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8005: nad zad rab rib dngas pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:8006: 'khrul pa'i bag chags thams cad zad //
NK124(ngo)001:8007: mthun par med par yul dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:8008: gzhan gsum med par mngon 'khrul dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8011: de ltar ma rig 'khrul pa zad pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:8012: rig pa ye shes nyid kyang zad cing med par smra ba yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:8013: de la sa bcu rgyun mthar ma rig pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:8014: gnyen po mnyam du zad pas dag pa gnyis ldan
NK124(ngo)001:8016: rang rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i ye shes kyang med par 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:8017: 'o na 'gro don ci ltar 'byung zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:8018: bsod nams kyi tshogs la 'byung ba'i gzugs sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8019: gzhan snang gi ye shes ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8020: sngon gyi smon lam gyi stobs kyis gdul bya rang rgyud dag pa rnams la /
NK124(ngo)001:8021: 'bad rtsol med par gang la gang 'dul du 'byung ba rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:8022: spyod 'jug dang dbu' ma la sogs pa las bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8024: 'khrul rig mnyam du zad smra ba //
NK124(ngo)001:8025: dbu' ma'i lta ba kha cig bzhed //
NK124(ngo)001:8027: gzhan yang thal rkya ba kha cig sangs rgyas la
NK124(ngo)001:8028: rang rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i ye shes med par 'dod
NK124(ngo)001:8029: de / slob dpon zla ba grags pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8030: shes bya'i bud shing skam po sreg pa'i me //
NK124(ngo)001:8031: zhi bde'i tshul gyis rgyal rnams chos sku ste //
NK124(ngo)001:8032: de tshe skye ba med cing 'gag pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:8033: sems 'gags pa ste sku'i mngon sum mdzad //
NK124(ngo)001:8035: ma rig pa dang bcas pa'i rig pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:8036: rig pa phyi ma skyed pas thob kyang rig pa tsam las rig pa phyi ma skyed pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8038: ma rig pa la sogs pas rig pa la sogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:8039: sems dang sems 'byung gi 'jug pa thams cad rgyun zad pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:8040: dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa la blo
NK124(ngo)001:8041: bur gyi dri mas kyang dag pa mngon sum du
NK124(ngo)001:8042: byas pa la chos sku zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8043: 'o na gzhan don gang las 'byung zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:8044: sngon byang chub sems dpa'i gnas skabs na /
NK124(ngo)001:8045: yun ring por smon lam btab pa'i mthu' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8046: gdul bya rang rgyud pa'i snang ngo la /
NK124(ngo)001:8047: gzhan snang gis ye shes gzugs sku 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8049: ci ltar nam mkha' lding gis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8050: mchod stong bsgrub nas 'das gyur pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8051: de 'das yun ring lon kyang de //
NK124(ngo)001:8052: dug la sogs pa zhi byed bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:8054: de na rang snang gi ye shes med ces zer ro //
NK124(ngo)001:8056: ye shes med par dgag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8058: de la mi 'thad pa spangs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8059: de dag dgag pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8060: dri ma sems kyi rang bzhin du thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8061: dbyings rkyang las don gnyis 'byung bar thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8062: ye shes med na 'phrin las mi 'byung ba mi 'thad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8064: ma rig pa las log nas rig pa log na /
NK124(ngo)001:8065: dri ma sems kyi rang bzhin du thal /
NK124(ngo)001:8066: sems dang dri ma gcig par zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:8067: rtags khas blangs khyab pa yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:8068: dri ma zad pas rig pa zad na /
NK124(ngo)001:8070: nag po dang sol ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8072: rgyang 'phen pa de dgags mi nus par 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:8073: nyes pa blo bur dag ldan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8074: yon tan rang bzhin nyid ldan phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:8077: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:8078: 'on kyang bla bur dri mas sgribs //
NK124(ngo)001:8079: dri ma de bsal sangs rgyas nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:8080: ces sogs mdo' rgyud thams cad dang 'gal ba spangs daka'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8082: chos nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8083: rgyu rkyen rig pa'i bden gnyis 'gal lam mi 'gal /
NK124(ngo)001:8084: dang po ltar na mthong lam chos nyid mngon sum
NK124(ngo)001:8085: du mthong ba nas 'phags pa'i lam thams cad du
NK124(ngo)001:8086: / kun rdzob rtogs pa'i blo je phra la 'gro bar thal /
NK124(ngo)001:8087: gnyen po shes rab stobs je cher 'gro ba'i phyir rtags lung gis grub /
NK124(ngo)001:8089: gcig shos je chung je zad la 'gro bas khyab /
NK124(ngo)001:8091: 'dod na snang bcas bsod nams kyi tshogs je chung je zad la 'gro bar thal /
NK124(ngo)001:8092: de'i rgyu snang bcas rtogs pa'i blo je chung je zad la 'gro ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8095: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK124(ngo)001:8096: spyod pas bsod nams dag par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:8099: bsod nams ye shes rang bzhin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:8100: dge ba'i phal ba de phan no //
NK124(ngo)001:8102: tshogs gnyis mi 'gal zhing 'phel ba gsungs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8103: gzhan yang yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:8104: snang bcas kyi ye shes gong nas gong du rgya
NK124(ngo)001:8107: khyod 'dod pa'i sangs rgyas la don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa med par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:8108: mkhyen brtse ye shes med pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8109: rtags khas blangs khyab pa yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:8110: de dag ye shes yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:8113: dngos po'i sku ni stobs la sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:8114: bral ba'i yon tan rnams dang ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:8117: sangs rgyas kyi 'phrin las thams cad ye shes kyi bdag rkyen la mi ltos par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:8118: ye shes med pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:8119: rtags dang khyab pa khas blangs /
NK124(ngo)001:8122: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:8123: chos kyi sku zhes brjod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8125: ye shes nyid chos skur brjod la /
NK124(ngo)001:8127: rnam pa nyi shu bdun du brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:8128: ces pa ye shes las 'phrin las 'byung bar gsungs pa dang 'gal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8129: de dag ni rgyang 'phen pa dag 'chi bas tshe ring pa rgyun chad par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8130: nyan rang dag lhag med kyi mya ngan las 'das
NK124(ngo)001:8131: pa na rig pa rgyun chad par 'dod pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:8132: / thal rkyang pa dag pa bcu' rgyun mtha' na
NK124(ngo)001:8133: rig pa rgyun chad par 'dod pa'i log rtog rnams
NK124(ngo)001:8134: / dgag zin no // gnyis pa ye shes yod par bsgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8137: byed las gsum gyi sgo nas bsgrub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8138: dang po ni rgyu'i sgo nas bsgrub pa skal pa
NK124(ngo)001:8139: grangs med gsum la sogs par tshogs gnyis mthar phyin
NK124(ngo)001:8140: te / thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes skyed par nges so //
NK124(ngo)001:8142: skad cig gcig dang ldan pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:8143: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa mngon sum du byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:8145: gnyis pa ngo bo'i sgo nas sgrub pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8147: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:8149: bdag gis dngos po'i sku ni ma nyes pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8150: sher phyin gyi pha rol du phyin pa dang thabs mkhas pa'i rgyu las byung ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8151: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi rten du 'gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8153: gsum pa byed las kyi sgo nas bsgrub pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8154: dngos po phyogs mthar thug med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8156: shin tu lkog gyur don shin tu phra ba rten
NK124(ngo)001:8157: 'brel zab cing rtogs dka' ba 'di dag sangs rgyas
NK124(ngo)001:8158: kyi ye shes kyis ma lus mkhyen pa yin te
NK124(ngo)001:8159: / shin tu lkog gyur la lung tshad ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8161: don 'di las ni rgyal ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:8162: lhag pa'i tshad ma gzhan su yod //
NK124(ngo)001:8165: gang zhig rgyal las che mkhas pa yang 'jig rten 'di na yod min zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:8166: ma lus mchog ni tshul bzhin kun mkhyen ci bzhin gzhan min pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8169: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis 'di mi mkhyen pa'am mi gzigs pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:8170: thugs su mi chud pa gang yang mi gada'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8172: gsum pa tha mi dad pa spangs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8173: sangs rgyas gzugs sku tha dad la ye shes yod dam med /
NK124(ngo)001:8174: yod na rgyud du mar 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:8175: sku tha dad pa ltar ye shes kyang tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8176: ye shes med na yod pa'i dam 'aca'a nyams so //
NK124(ngo)001:8178: gcig char ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8183: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba mthun par snang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8184: don dam rang bzhin med pa mtshan nyid gsum ldan du ldan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8186: gcig char du 'jug pa'i dbu' ma ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8188: nang gi bcud kun gang du kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du snod kyi tshul du snang ba'am /
NK124(ngo)001:8189: don gyi rang bzhin gang du yang grub pa med pas sgyu ma'i rta dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8190: glang po lta bu thams cad kyi rang rang gi
NK124(ngo)001:8191: dge sdig la sogs las dang bag chags mthun par
NK124(ngo)001:8192: snang ba ni / bde' sdug la sogs so sor tha dad du snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:8195: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8196: mtha' gnyis su mi 'gyur ba'i pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8198: kun rdzob chos can ci snyed pa /
NK124(ngo)001:8199: chos nyid don la g.yos pa gang yang med de /
NK124(ngo)001:8200: kun rdzob rten 'byung ci ltar yang snang bas med pa'i mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:8201: de nyid dngos por ma grub rtag pa'i mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:8202: don dam rang bzhin ngo bo nyid kyis stong pas yod pa'i mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:8203: rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang ldan pas med pa'i mtha' sel lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8204: des na chos dbyings 'od gsal 'phel 'grib med par gnas pas med pa'i mtha' sel /
NK124(ngo)001:8205: don dam dngos po mtshan ma gang gis kyang stong pas yod pa'i mtha' dang bral /
NK124(ngo)001:8206: kun rdzob dang don dam ngo bo gcig la ldog
NK124(ngo)001:8207: pa tha dad pas gnyis mtha' dang gcig mtha' sel
NK124(ngo)001:8209: don dam tha dad med tshul gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:8210: chos can med cing chos nyid med //
NK124(ngo)001:8211: stong pa nyid las tha dad ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8212: cung zad yod pa ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8217: zhes gzugs rnams bkrun par mi bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8220: kun dga' ra ba na dge 'dun mi bzhugs pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:8221: kun dga' ra ba stong pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8222: kun dga' ra ba ni med pa ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8224: chos nyid la bdag dang bdag gis stong pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:8225: chos nyid stong pa zhes bya'i /
NK124(ngo)001:8226: chos nyid med par 'gyur ba ni ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8229: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8230: mtha' gnyis su mi gyur ba'i pha rol du phyin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8232: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8233: yod med brtag par gnyis ka'i mtha' las 'das pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8235: yod ces bya ba'i mtha' yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:8236: de bzhin med bya ba yang mtha' //
NK124(ngo)001:8237: gtsang dang mi gtsang gnyis ka'i mtha' yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:8238: de phyir gnyis kyi mtha' ni rnams spangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:8239: mkhas pas dbus la gnas pa yongs mi byed //
NK124(ngo)001:8241: de nyid gtan la 'bebs par byed pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:8242: yod med rtag chad kyi mthar lhung na gol ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8246: yang dag can ni yongs shes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:8247: gnyis la mi rten thar bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:8250: stong pa nyid la lta nyes na //
NK124(ngo)001:8251: shes rab chung rnams phung bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:8252: zhes pa la sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:8253: gnyis pa bsam gtan la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8258: skye 'gags gnas gsum smra brjod las 'das pa'i don /
NK124(ngo)001:8259: mtshan nyid gsum ldan gyi don dam pa de nyid nyams su len pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:8260: dus gsum gyi rtogs pa'i rjes phyir mi 'brang cing /
NK124(ngo)001:8261: ci bzhin pa nyid kyi ngang du mnyam par gzhag pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8262: dper na sprin dang bral ba'i nam mkha' lta bu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8264: bsgrub tshe mnyam par gzhag pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8265: nam mkha' lta bu spros dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:8268: rjes shes sgyu ma lta bu'i ngang nas spyod yul
NK124(ngo)001:8269: thams cad dang bral ba'i stong nyid snying rje'i snying
NK124(ngo)001:8271: ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams la pha rol phyin
NK124(ngo)001:8272: drug la sogs gang la gang 'dul gyis spyod pa
NK124(ngo)001:8275: rjes la sgyu ma lta bu yi //
NK124(ngo)001:8276: zhen chags bral ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8277: kun rdzob snying rjes gnas pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8279: gsum pa nyams su len tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8280: dus ci srid bar du smon pa dang 'jug pa sems bskyed nas bzung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8281: tshogs sbyor mthong b+hee mthar phyin dang lnga rim pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:8282: chos nyid don dam gzhal bya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8283: gzhal med gtan tshigs gtan la phab nas /
NK124(ngo)001:8284: gcig char ba'i rnal 'byor pa des /
NK124(ngo)001:8285: lta ba chos nyid bden pa'i don rtogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:8286: b+hee pa de don nyams su blangs nas tshe gcig
NK124(ngo)001:8287: lus gcig la don dam pa'i bden pa gcig char
NK124(ngo)001:8288: du rtogs nas / yang dag pa ci lta ba'i don la mnyam par 'jog cing /
NK124(ngo)001:8289: 'bras bu mngon du byed pa yang yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:8291: sems bskyed nas bzung mthar thug par //
NK124(ngo)001:8292: gzhal dang b+hee pa nyams su blangs //
NK124(ngo)001:8293: tshe gcig don dam bden pa mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:8294: dbu' ma'i lta ba kha cig bzhed //
NK124(ngo)001:8296: de ltar rtogs pas grol ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8297: de'i don la b+hee pa'i gnas tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8298: rtogs pa'i don mngon du gyur nas sangs rgyas pa'i tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8300: de ltar rtogs nas grol ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8301: gzugs nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bar du /
NK124(ngo)001:8302: gnyis su med cing grol ba med pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8304: gzugs nyid rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:8305: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid gzugs so //
NK124(ngo)001:8306: gzugs las rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid gzhan ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8307: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid las gzugs gzhan ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8308: zhes thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar du gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:8310: gzugs dang 'du shes tshor ba dang ni sems dpa' dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8311: rnam par shes pa ma bcings ma grol yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8312: de ltar byang chub la grub zhums pa'i sems med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8313: 'di ni gang zag dam pa rnams kyi go cha'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:8316: de ltar gnyis su med cing bcings grol med pa'i don rtogs /
NK124(ngo)001:8317: b+hee pa yang cir snang b+hee bya b+hee byed med par chos nyid kyi b+hee pa yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:8318: mi b+hee pa'i b+hee pa zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8320: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni shin tu zab ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8321: de ni sus kyang b+hee par mi bgyid /
NK124(ngo)001:8322: cir yang b+hee par mi bgyi'/
NK124(ngo)001:8323: gang du yang b+hee par mi bagyi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8325: chos nyid dmigs su ma mchis pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8326: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i b+hee pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8328: chos nyid thams cad b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8329: yongs su 'dzin pa ma mchis pa b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8331: kun nas b+hee pa'i mdo las /
NK124(ngo)001:8332: 'jam dpal gzugs ting nge 'dzin du b+hee par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8334: sgra dang dri dang reg bya dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8335: chos dang nyon mongs pa thams cad rang bzhin du rtogs par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8337: gsang ba mtha' yas pa'i mdo' las /
NK124(ngo)001:8338: sems ngo shes pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8339: ci ltar byas kyang b+hee pa'i ngang //
NK124(ngo)001:8340: gnyug ma'i don la gnas pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8341: ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams su bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:8344: de ltar rtogs shing dgongs pas nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i 'ching ba mtha' dag las grol nas /
NK124(ngo)001:8345: lam gyi rim pa med par sangs rgya' bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:8347: mdo dang pha rol du phyin pa'i gzhung rnams nas
NK124(ngo)001:8348: shin tu yang rgyas par gsungs nas de rnams su
NK124(ngo)001:8350: gsum pa lta ba bsdus te bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8351: bden gnyis tha dad du 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8354: dbu' ma de dag gi lta ba bden gnyis su dbye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8355: kha cig kun rdzob spyad mi bzod pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:8356: don dam las zlog pa ste snang ba dang stong
NK124(ngo)001:8357: pa dbyer med kyis chos thams cad kun rdzob spyad
NK124(ngo)001:8358: mi bzod pas snang ba med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8359: dbyer med kyis chos thams cad spyad bzod yin la de phyir bden pa gnyis dngos 'gal yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8360: chos can dang chos nyid kun rdzob dang don dam yin zhes smra'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8362: de dag la sogs bden pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8363: rigs su dbye ba byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8366: de dag kun gyi kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bur 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid tsam las /
NK124(ngo)001:8367: sbyin pa la sogs pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK124(ngo)001:8369: chos spyod rnam pa bcu la sogs pa'i spyod pa
NK124(ngo)001:8370: byang chub sems dpa' thabs kyis zin pa'i lta ba
NK124(ngo)001:8372: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:8373: sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:8374: spyod pa byang chub lta ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8376: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:8379: dang po ni bsam gtan ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par gzhag pa'i tshe na /
NK124(ngo)001:8380: rnam par rtog pa'i sprin tshogs dngas nas chos nyid
NK124(ngo)001:8381: nam mkha' kha cig pa lta bu spros pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:8384: bsam gtan mnyam par gzhag pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:8385: nam mkha' lta bu spros dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:8387: gnyis pa ni kha cig dngos po rnams la rig pa bden pa'i dngos po khegs kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:8388: snang ba sgyu ma tsam mi khegs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8389: snang la rang bzhin med pa tsam ni don dam pa'i bden pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:8390: de la med par sgros btags pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8391: sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam du dngos po la zhen
NK124(ngo)001:8392: pa med pa'i tshul du 'di ltar du snang ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:8393: chos thams cad sems nyid rang gsal bar 'dod de
NK124(ngo)001:8394: / de'i ngang la sems can thams cad bde ba dang 'phrad 'dod pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:8395: sdug bsngal dang bral 'dod pa'i byams dang snying rje
NK124(ngo)001:8396: rnams sbyong bar byed pa ni theg pa chen po'i
NK124(ngo)001:8399: rjes la sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:8400: zhan med tshul gyis gsal bar smra //
NK124(ngo)001:8401: byams dang snying rje rnams sbyong ba //
NK124(ngo)001:8402: byang chub sems dpa'i bsam gtan yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8404: gong gi gcig char ba'i b+hee pa de las rgal ba'i gang zag kha cig /
NK124(ngo)001:8405: gang snang ba la ngo sprad nas khrid par byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:8406: nad gdon la sogs sems la gang gzan pa skye med stong par ngo sprad cing rtsal sbyangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:8407: lam nges med du grol ba yang mdo' dang pha rol phyin pa las gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:8409: rgyal ba'i dngos po shes rab pha rol phyin pa 'di rigs sngags che //
NK124(ngo)001:8410: sems can khams mang mya ngan sdug bsngal chos zhi byed //
NK124(ngo)001:8411: ces pa la sogs gsung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8412: rigs kyi drangs don nyams su len cing sa dang lam gyi rim pa la sbyor ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8413: sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi rim par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8415: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing smon 'jug gnyis
NK124(ngo)001:8416: kyi ci byed sems can gyi don du 'jug pa'o
NK124(ngo)001:8418: tshogs gnyis sam mnyams rjes gnyis kyi lan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8420: bsdu' ba'i dngos po bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8421: sbyin pa tshul khrims bzod pa la sogs pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8422: bsam gtan shes rab gnyis ye shes kyi tshogs so //
NK124(ngo)001:8423: brtson 'grus ni gnyis ka'i grogs byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:8424: mnyam rjes gnyis ni mnyam gzhag rnam par mi rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8425: rjes byang chub kyi spyod pa dge ba'i las la 'bad pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8426: mjug dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad sems can gyi
NK124(ngo)001:8427: don du bla na med pa'i byang chub du bsngo'a
NK124(ngo)001:8428: ba'o // bzhi pa spyod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8429: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8430: tshad med bzhi sogs rnam dkar gyi spyod pa rnams la zhen 'dzin med pa'i tshul gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:8431: rang 'dod med pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8432: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i spyod pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8433: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8435: sbyin sogs rnam par dkar ba'i las //
NK124(ngo)001:8436: zhen med tshul gyis spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8437: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8439: lnga pa tshul khrims la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:8440: rang gzhung gi sdom pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8441: so thar spyi'i bsrung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8443: theg pa che chung spyi'i rtsa ba bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8444: nyes byas bzhi bcu zhe drug la sogs pa mdo' du ma nas bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8445: gzhan yang rgyal po'i rtsa ltung lnga /
NK124(ngo)001:8447: las dang po'i rtsa ltung brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK124(ngo)001:8448: spyi'i rtsa ltung bzhi las bdag stod gzhan smad ma gtogs pa gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8450: yang na de'i steng nas byang chub kyi sems dor ba /
NK124(ngo)001:8451: sems can blos dor ba ste rtsa ba gsum las rgyal po dang blon po'i rtsa ltung bcu /
NK124(ngo)001:8453: blon po'i gro 'joms pa thun mong ma yin pa gcig dang drug ste bcu dgu /
NK124(ngo)001:8454: rang 'dod smon pa rtsa ba nyi shu bzhi ltar rtsi ba dang bzhi bcu zhe drug gzhan yang /
NK124(ngo)001:8455: bsdom pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8456: spang blang gis slab pa rnams ni bsrung ba'i tshul khrims yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8457: theg pa chen po dbu' ma'i rang gzhung gis tshul khrims so //
NK124(ngo)001:8459: rtsa ba bzhi dang nyi shu dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8460: sdom pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8461: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims yin par stan //
NK124(ngo)001:8462: byang chub sems dpa' rang gzhung gi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8465: thun mong gi bsdom pa bye brag tu dbye na /
NK124(ngo)001:8466: rang don gzhan don gnyis kyi bsrung tshul mtha' yas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:8467: brten gang zag gi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8468: snod dbang po'i tshul gyis byang chub sems dpa'i yan lag so sor thar pa'i sdom pa yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8469: mi nyams pa bsrung dgos tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8471: so so thar pa'i sdom pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8472: bye brag rnam pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:8473: brten nas snod kyi tshul gyis phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:8474: byang sems yan lag sdom pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8477: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa chen po'i lam yun
NK124(ngo)001:8478: chos mngon pa'i grangs kyis gnas gzhan drug cu rtsa
NK124(ngo)001:8480: tshogs sbyor gnyis la grangs med gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:8481: ma dag pa bdun la grangs med gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:8482: dag pa sa gsum la grangs med gcig dang grangs med gsum gyi sa lam 'grod pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:8483: smon 'jug sems skyed nas bzung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8484: mthar sangs rgyas kyi bar sgrib gnyis rim gyis sbyangs shing bsod nams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8485: ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'i tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8486: sa lam rim gyis bgrod nas bcu gcig kun du 'od kyi 'bras bu thob par 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:8488: grangs med skal pa gsum dag gi //
NK124(ngo)001:8489: sems skyed nas bzung sangs rgyas bar //
NK124(ngo)001:8490: sgrib sbyangs ye shes rdzogs tshul gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:8491: bcu gcig kun du 'od kyi sa //
NK124(ngo)001:8493: theg pa chen po'i lam la lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8494: lam gyi gzhi' byang chub mchog tu sems skyed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8495: thun mong gi lam phyogs mthun sum cu so bdun dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8496: khyad par gyi lam yar phar phyin drug dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8497: lam gyi sa mtshams lam lnga sa bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8498: theg chen gyi lam gyi nges par 'byung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8501: sems skyed kyi rang bzhin bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8502: de ci ltar nyams su len pa'i tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:8510: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen no //
NK124(ngo)001:8511: dang po la gnyis las lus kyi brten ni lha mi'i lus phun sum tshogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8513: gang tshe rkang gnyis gtso bo yis //
NK124(ngo)001:8514: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8515: de tshe lha mi stong phrag brgya' //
NK124(ngo)001:8516: byang chub mchog tu sems skyed do //
NK124(ngo)001:8518: gnyis pa sems skyed kyi brten ni skyabs 'gro khyad par can yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8520: theg pa mchog phyir dkon mchog skyabs rab song ba gang //
NK124(ngo)001:8522: gnyis pa nyer len gyi rgyud la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8523: che chung bya ba sems can gyi ngang tshul shes pa'i snying rje yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8525: de la thog med rig nus pas //
NK124(ngo)001:8526: snying rje'i sa bon rab sad cing //
NK124(ngo)001:8527: sbyor dang bsam pa phun tshogs las //
NK124(ngo)001:8528: byang chub sems 'di yongs su bzungs //
NK124(ngo)001:8530: gnyis pa rgyal ba sras bcas la /
NK124(ngo)001:8531: dang ba'i dad pa khyad par can la skye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8533: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i chos la dad gyur cing //
NK124(ngo)001:8534: rgyal sras rnams kyi spyod la dad byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:8535: byang chub bla na med la dad gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:8536: skyes bu rnams ni sems ni skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8538: gsum pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa la skye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8540: byang chub smon pa'i sems ni sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8542: gsum pa lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8543: yang dag pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:8544: cho ga phun sum tshogs pa la skye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8545: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:8546: bla ma bsdoms la gnas shing mkhas //
NK124(ngo)001:8547: nus dang ldan la blang bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8548: gnyis pa ngo bo la don dam dang kun rdzob tu sems skyed pa la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:8550: sangs rgyas brgya' las mi nyung ba'i zhal mthong bas /
NK124(ngo)001:8551: lung gi chos thos 'dzin pa dam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8552: skal pa brgya' las mi nyung bar bsod nams dang
NK124(ngo)001:8553: ye shes kyi tshogs gsogs pas sgrub pa'i chos 'dzin
NK124(ngo)001:8554: pa bsgrub pa dam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8555: mnyam gzhag na rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK124(ngo)001:8556: bskye' zhing rtogs pa'i chos 'dzin pas rtogs pa dam
NK124(ngo)001:8557: pa ste / mdo sde rgyan las /
NK124(ngo)001:8558: rdzogs chen sangs rgyas rab mnyes byas //
NK124(ngo)001:8559: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rab bsags //
NK124(ngo)001:8560: chos la mi rtogs ye shes ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8561: skye phyir de ni dam par 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:8563: de ni mthong lam gyi ye shes skye bas don dam sems skyed yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8564: 'dir theg chen byang chub tu sems skyed pa'i ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8569: rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par 'dod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8570: smon pa sems skyed yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:8571: rgyu las 'jug par 'dod pa ni 'jug pa sems skyed yin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:8572: de la mi mthun pa'i phyogs spangs pa ni byang
NK124(ngo)001:8573: chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims kyi bsdom pa yin te
NK124(ngo)001:8575: spong ba'i sems 'di thob pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:8576: tshul khrims pha rol phyin gsungs te //
NK124(ngo)001:8579: sems can gyi don du byang chub thob par 'dod pa ni sems bskyed dam /
NK124(ngo)001:8580: mya ngan 'das kyi bsil ba thob par byed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8581: tshul khrims mi dge ba bsdom zhing dge ba bsag pa'i bsdom pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8582: gsum pa rang bzhin la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:8586: yid kyi rnam par shes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:8589: byang chub la dmigs pa ni sems skyed kyi ngo bo yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8590: gnyis pa dbye' ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8591: ngo bo'i sgo nas dbye na smon 'jug gnyis yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8593: byang chub sems de mdor bsdus na //
NK124(ngo)001:8594: rnam pa gnyis su shes bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:8595: byang chub smon pa'i sems dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8596: byang chub 'jug pa nyid yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8598: gnyis pa sa mtshams sgo nas dbye' ba la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8599: tshogs sbyor na yod pa mos pa spyod pa'i sems skyed /
NK124(ngo)001:8600: sa dang po nas bdun pa'i bar la yod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:8601: lhag bsam dag pa'i sems skyed de /
NK124(ngo)001:8603: sems skyed de ni sa rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:8604: mos dang lhag bsam dag pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8605: rnam par smin pa bzhin du 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:8606: de ni sgrib pa spangs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8608: gsum pa grogs kyi sgo nas dbye' na nyi shu yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:8610: de yang sa gser zla ba me //
NK124(ngo)001:8612: rdo rje ri sman bshes gnyen dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8613: yid bzhin nor bu nyi ma klu //
NK124(ngo)001:8614: rgyal po mdzod dang lam po che //
NK124(ngo)001:8615: gzhon pa rkod ma'i chu dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8616: sgra snyan chu bo sprin rnams kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:8617: rnam pa nyi shu rtsa gnyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:8619: dpe nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyi grogs nyi shu rtsa gnyis bstan la /
NK124(ngo)001:8620: grogs kyi mtshan nas grogs can nyi shu rtsa gnyis ston pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8621: de dag gi don rgyas par bshad na mdo' gzhung nas gsal /
NK124(ngo)001:8623: gzhan don byang chub thob 'dod kyi 'dun pa dang ldan pa sa lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8624: phar phyin drug la bslab pa ni gser lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8625: byang chub kyi so bdun la slab par 'dod pa'i bsam pa ni zla ba lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8626: mkhyen gsum gyi sbyor ba dang ldan pa ni me lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8627: sbyin pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa ni gter chen po lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8628: tshul khrims dang ldan pa ni rin po che'i gter khung rnyed pa lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8629: bzod pa dang ldan pa ni gting mi g.yo' ba rgya' mtsho lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8630: brtson 'grus dang ldan pa ni rdo rje pha lam lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8631: bsam gtan dang ldan pa ni ri bo chen po lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8632: shes rab dang ldan pa ni sman bzang po lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8633: thabs mkhas pa dang ldan pa ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8634: smon lam dang ldan pa nor bu lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8635: stobs dang ldan pa nyi ma lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8636: ye shes kyi phar phyin dang ldan pa ni dri
NK124(ngo)001:8637: za'i rgyal po rab dbyags kyis glu dbyangs snyan pa
NK124(ngo)001:8638: lta bu / mngon shes khyad par can drug dang ldan pa ni rgyal po lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8639: bdag gzhan gyi don 'bad med 'byung bas mdzod lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8640: byang chub phyogs kyi chos dang ldan pa ni lam po che lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8641: zhi gnas lhag mthong dang ldan pa ni rta cang shes lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8642: gzung spobs pa dang ldan pa ni rkod ma'i chu lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8643: chos kyi dga' ston dang ldan pa ni rnga bo che'i sgra lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8644: 'grod pa gcig pu'i lam dang ldan pa chu bo lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:8645: chos kyi sku dang ldan pa ni sems bskyed pa ni sprin lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8646: gsum pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:8651: nyams bcas dman dang bsrungs dang de bzhin ston pas smad //
NK124(ngo)001:8654: gal te de ltar dam bcas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:8655: las kyi bsgrub par ma byas na //
NK124(ngo)001:8656: sems can de dag kun bslus pas //
NK124(ngo)001:8660: byang chub sems dpa' sun 'byin rigs par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8661: byang chub sems dpa' sri dar du rigs par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8664: sems skyed de ni phas 'pham bas kyang shin tu lci //
NK124(ngo)001:8667: cung zad bsam nas ma byin na yi dwags su skyes /
NK124(ngo)001:8668: dam bcas nas ma byin na dmyal bar 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:8670: gnyis pa phan yon gyi 'bras bu la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8671: skyes thob kyi 'bras bu ngo mtshar ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8672: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu don che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8673: mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'tshang rgya' ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8676: sems bskyed thob phyin chad byang chub sems dpa' dang rgyal ba'i sras zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8678: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK124(ngo)001:8679: blo ldan nyid dang gsal ba'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:8680: rgyal sras rgyal bu'i bzhi dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8681: rgyal byed rgyal ba'i myu gu dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8684: sems bskyed phyin chad 'jig rten gyi lha chen rnams
NK124(ngo)001:8685: kyi tshur la phyag 'tshal ba'i 'os su 'gyur te
NK124(ngo)001:8687: byang chub sems par gyur na skad cig gis //
NK124(ngo)001:8688: srid pa'i rtson rar bsdom pa'i nyams thag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:8689: rgyal ba rnams kyi sras zhes rab brjod cing //
NK124(ngo)001:8690: 'jig rten lha mir bcas pa'i phyag byar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:8692: gnyis pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8695: don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8696: sngar gyi sdig pa zad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:8697: phyin chad bsdom par 'gyur ba yin /
NK124(ngo)001:8699: de ni dus matha'i me bzhin sdig can rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:8700: skad cig gcig gis nges par bsreg par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:8703: blo ldan sems mchog bskyed ma thag tu yang //
NK124(ngo)001:8704: mtha' yas nyes pa skyed la sems rab bsdom //
NK124(ngo)001:8707: dge ba gzhan rnams chu shing bzhin du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8708: 'bras bu byung nas zad par 'gyur ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:8709: byang chub sems ni ljon shing rtag par yang //
NK124(ngo)001:8715: bdud rtsi mchog kyang 'di bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8716: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:8717: mi zad gter dang 'di yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8718: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs gdung sel ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:8719: sems kyi zla ba shar ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8720: 'gro ba'i mi shes rab rib dag /
NK124(ngo)001:8721: mi zad gter yang 'di yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8722: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs gdung sel ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:8723: sems kyi zla ba shar ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8724: 'gro ba'i mi shes rab rib dag /
NK124(ngo)001:8725: dpyid 'byin nyi ma chen po yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8727: gsum pa rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8729: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa dmyes mdzad yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8730: sems can smin par byed pa yang 'di nyid yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8731: rang don yang dag bsgrub pa yang ni de nyid yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8734: skye bo rmongs pa rang gi bde don brtson //
NK124(ngo)001:8735: de ma thob par rtag tu sdug bsngal 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:8736: bstan pa gzhan gyi don la brtson pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8737: gnyis ka'i don byas mya ngan 'da' bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:8739: gsum pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'tshang brgya' ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8740: sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par bya ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8742: gser 'gyur rtsi'i rnam pa mchog lta bu //
NK124(ngo)001:8743: mi gtsang lus 'di blangs nas rgyal ba'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:8744: rin chen rin thang med par 'gyur pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:8745: byang chub sems zhes bya ba rab brtan bzung //
NK124(ngo)001:8747: gsum pa nyams su len tshul sbyor dngos rjes gsum
NK124(ngo)001:8748: la sogs rang rang gi gzhung nas 'byung ba bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:8750: gnyis pa las phyogs mthun la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8755: dang po ni bdun yod pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:8756: thog mar dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:8760: chos dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8761: byang chub sems dpa' lus tshogs bzhi mi gtsang ba la sogs sgyu ma lta bu b+hee la /
NK124(ngo)001:8763: mtshan nyid mi dmigs pa b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8764: chos spyi dang rang gis mtshan nyid shes par byed pa shes rab yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8765: 'di dag gi don rtogs pas dran pa la gnas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8767: sa mtshams tshogs lam chung ngu nas yod do //
NK124(ngo)001:8768: gnyis pa yang dag pa'i spongs pa bzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8769: sdig pa ma skyes pa mi skyed /
NK124(ngo)001:8771: dge ba ma skyes pa skyed /
NK124(ngo)001:8772: skyes pa mi nyams shing 'phel bar byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8773: de yang sbyor ba'i dus su 'dun pa skyed /
NK124(ngo)001:8776: bying ba'i gnyen por lhag mthong gis sems rab tu 'dzin /
NK124(ngo)001:8777: rgod pa'i gnyen por gzhi gnas la yang dag par 'jog /
NK124(ngo)001:8778: mnyam pa thob nas btang snyoms su 'jog pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8780: mi dge' skye ba spangs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8783: yang dag pa rab tu 'jog go //
NK124(ngo)001:8785: 'og ma gsum la yang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8786: de ltar spang bya spang zhing gnyen po skyed pa brtson 'grus yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8787: yang dag spong ba brtson 'grus yin /
NK124(ngo)001:8789: sa mtshams tshogs lam 'bring por nas so //
NK124(ngo)001:8790: gsum pa rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8791: yang dag pa spong ba'i brtson 'grus sems las su rung ba la skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8792: de yang lam snga ma'i rjes kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:8793: de tsam gyis chog par 'dzin pa'i gnyen po 'dun pa bskyed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8794: phyis nas mi sbyor ba rnam par g.yeng ba'i gnyen por zhi gnas kyi rgyu rkyen la 'bad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:8795: lam la spros pas brtson 'grus rtsams pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8796: dngos gzhi dus su rgod na sems pas sems rab tu zhib /
NK124(ngo)001:8797: bying na so sor spyod pas yang dag par g.yeng 'dod pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8798: de gzhi dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la 'dun pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8802: ting nge 'dzin gyis spong ba'i yan lag dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8803: rdzu 'phrul ni yod pa bsgyur ba /
NK124(ngo)001:8804: med pa sprul pa sogs yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:8805: rkang pa ni de thob pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:8806: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8808: sa mtshams tshogs lam chen po nas /
NK124(ngo)001:8809: bzhi pa dbang po lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8810: rdzogs pa'i byang chub yon tan can du shes nas /
NK124(ngo)001:8812: phar phyin drug spyod pa la spro bas /
NK124(ngo)001:8813: nan tan du byed pa brtson 'grus kyi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8814: thos pa'i chos ma rjed pa dran pa yid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8815: sems rtse gcig pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8816: shes rab tu 'byed pa shes rab kyi dbang po dang lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8817: snga mas phyi ma la dbang byed kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:8818: shes rab kyis chos thams cad la dbang byed pas shes rab kyi dbang po zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8820: thar pa'i cha dang mthun skyes nas //
NK124(ngo)001:8821: mdun dang sbyor ba gang byed de //
NK124(ngo)001:8822: dmigs pas brjod par mi 'gyur tam //
NK124(ngo)001:8823: mi 'phro rloms par mi byed kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:8825: sa mtshams drod rtse mo nas so //
NK124(ngo)001:8827: dbang po lnga'i gnyen po 'phrul ldan du gyur ba mi mthun phyogs 'joms par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:8832: 'chal ba'i shes rab stobs chung bar byed pa stobs zhes byed /
NK124(ngo)001:8834: mi mthun phyogs nyid nyams chung bas //
NK124(ngo)001:8835: de dag nyid la stobs zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:8837: sa mtshams bzod pa chos mchog gnyis nas so //
NK124(ngo)001:8838: drug pa byang chub kyi yan lag bdun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8839: bdag med mngon sum du rtogs pa mthong ngam /
NK124(ngo)001:8840: byang chub kyi grogs su gyur bas byang chub kyi yan lag zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8841: dran pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8847: gtang snyoms byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK124(ngo)001:8848: de yang shes bya'i chos rab tu 'byed pa /
NK124(ngo)001:8849: yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8850: rang bzhin gyi yan lag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8851: mthong lam gyi ngo bo yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8852: mthong spang 'joms pa'i phyir glang po che bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8853: mthong lam gyi rtogs pa ma rdzogs pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8855: shes bya'i g.yul rgyal bar byed pa 'khor lo lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8856: brtson 'grus yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8858: lam myur du 'grod par byed pa rta mchog lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8859: dga' ba byang chub kyi yan lag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8860: phan yon gyi yan lag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8861: mthong lam yon tan gyi dga' bas lus sems la phan thog par byed pas nor bu lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8862: nyon mongs pa med pa'i yang dag la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8863: lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8864: nyon mongs med pa gzhi'i yan lag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8865: nyon mongs pa'i rgyu gnas ngan len pa 'joms pa'i phyir btsun mo lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8866: ting nge 'dzin byang chub kyi yan lag /
NK124(ngo)001:8867: nyon mongs pa med pa'i gnas kyi yan lag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8868: ting nge 'dzin las 'dod pa'i don 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8870: gtang snyoms byang chub kyi yan lag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8871: nyon mongs med pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi yan lag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8872: nyon mongs pa gtang ba ye shes kyi ngo bo yin pa blon po lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8873: de yang mdo' sde rgyan las /
NK124(ngo)001:8874: rang bzhin yan lag gnas yan lag /
NK124(ngo)001:8875: gsum pa nges 'byung yan lag ste //
NK124(ngo)001:8876: bzhi pa phan yon yan lag yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8877: rnam gsum nyon mongs med yan lag /'di la'am bzhi dang gnas dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8878: ngo bo nyid du bstan pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:8880: de ltar mthong lam dang po'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK124(ngo)001:8881: 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang 'dra bar gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:8883: yon tan de lta'i sems dpa' ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8885: rtag tu rin chen bdun lta bu'i //
NK124(ngo)001:8886: byang chub yan lag rnams kyis bskor //
NK124(ngo)001:8888: bdun pa 'phags lam yan lag brgyad ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8889: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i b+hee lam gyi mtshungs ldan grogs su 'brel ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8890: yang dag pa'i lta ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8897: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK124(ngo)001:8898: de dag kyang rang bzhin gyis dgongs pa la ltos na yan lag bzhir 'dus te /
NK124(ngo)001:8899: rang gis rtogs pa myong pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8900: gzhan gyis go bar byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8901: gzhan yid ches par byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8903: dang po ni yang dag pa'i lta ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8904: mthong lam mnyam gzhag gi rtogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:8909: 'phags pas brda' sbyor ba'i rgyu yang dag pa'i rtogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8911: rtogs pa brjod par 'dod pa las ngag gis brjod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8912: brjod bya gzhan gyis go bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:8915: dge' sdig chung ngu la yang blang dor byed na /
NK124(ngo)001:8916: yang dag pa'i las kyi mtha' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8917: log 'tsho' lnga spang bas yang dag pa'i 'tsho' ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8918: gsum pa go rim bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:8921: chung ba gsum gyi 'bras bu yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8922: gzhan yid ches par byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:8924: yang dag pa'i rtsol bas rgyun chad med par lam b+hee pas /
NK124(ngo)001:8925: b+hee spangs rtsa ba'i nyon mongs spangs /
NK124(ngo)001:8926: yang dag pa'i dran pas gzhi gnas lhag mthong gis
NK124(ngo)001:8927: rgyu mtshan b+hee pas b+hee spangs nye ba'i nyon mongs
NK124(ngo)001:8929: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:8930: mngon par shes khyad par can thob /
NK124(ngo)001:8931: yon tan gong ma las dbang byed pa'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyang gnyen po byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:8933: yongs su spyod dang go 'byed dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8934: rnam gsum gzhan yid ches par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:8935: mi mthun phyogs kyi gnyen po ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8936: lam gyi yan lag 'di brgyad do //
NK124(ngo)001:8937: rta dang tshul khrims kyi yod byad skang //
NK124(ngo)001:8938: gzhan la rnam par rig byed 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:8939: nyon mongs nye ba'i nyon mongs dbang //
NK124(ngo)001:8940: mi mthun phyogs kyi gnyen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8942: gnyis pa rigs bsdu' ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8943: tshogs sbyor mthong b+hee kyi phyogs chos so bdun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8944: bcur 'dus pa yang dag gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:8946: dran pa nyer bzhag shes rab dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8947: yang dag spong ba brtson 'grus te //
NK124(ngo)001:8949: ming gi sgo nas rdzas bcu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8950: dad dang brtson 'grus dran pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8951: shes rab ting 'dzin gtang snyoms dga' //
NK124(ngo)001:8952: rtogs dang tshul khrims shin tu sbyangs //
NK124(ngo)001:8953: dran pa nyer bzhag shes rab ste //
NK124(ngo)001:8954: brtson 'grus yang dag spong zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:8957: gsum pa theg chen gyi khyad par 'phags tshul la /
NK124(ngo)001:8958: nyan rang chos phyogs mthun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:8959: dmigs pa rang gi lus la sogs pa nye 'tshe ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8960: rnam pa mi rtag la sogs gang gis bden pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8961: 'bras bu bdag gcig pu sdug bsngal spangs pa'i ched du /
NK124(ngo)001:8962: dran pa nyer bzhag la sogs b+hee pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:8964: bdag dang gzhan gyi ni lus srogs la dmigs pa rgya che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8965: mi rtag la sogs mi dmigs pa'i tshul gyis yid la byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8966: shes rab dang snying rje 'khor 'das gnyis la mi
NK124(ngo)001:8967: gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa thob par bya
NK124(ngo)001:8968: ba'i phyir du b+hee pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:8970: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8971: dmigs dang yid la byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8972: mi gnas mya ngan 'das pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8973: thob pa de ni khyad par 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:8976: rang rang gis zad pa dang mi skye ba shes pa'i ye shes ni byang chub yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:8977: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos yin pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:8978: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa zhes byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:8980: zad dang mi skye shes pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:8981: byang chub de dang mthun byed phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:8982: sum cu rtsa bdun de phyogs mthun //
NK124(ngo)001:8984: gsum pa thun mong ma yin pa'i phar phyin la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:8985: thun mong gis bsgrub pa'i tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:8986: sher phyin bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:8992: srid zhi pha rol du phyin pa'i thabs khyad par can te /
NK124(ngo)001:8994: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson bsam gtan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:8995: de bzhin shes rab gzhal med pha rol phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:8996: 'di dag rgyas mdzad srid pa'i rgya mtsho yi //
NK124(ngo)001:8997: pha rol phyin pa rgyal ba'i dbang po mdzod //
NK124(ngo)001:9000: dbul ba dor bas sbyin pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9001: gdung ba sel ba tshul khrims /
NK124(ngo)001:9003: yon tan la sbyor bas brtson 'grus /
NK124(ngo)001:9005: don dam shes pas shes rab bo //
NK124(ngo)001:9007: dbul ba dor ba byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9008: bsil ba thob dang 'khro bzod dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9009: mchog sbyor ba dang yid 'dzin dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9010: don dam shes pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:9014: sems can don byed tshul khrims so //
NK124(ngo)001:9016: bya dka' khyad du bsad pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9017: sdug bsngal la ci mi snyam pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9018: chos la nges par rtogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9021: sbyor chog par mi 'dzin pa'i brtson 'grus so //
NK124(ngo)001:9022: bsam gtan la chos la bden par byas pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9023: yon tan khyad par can mngon par bsgrub pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9024: sems can don la dmigs pa'i bsam gtan no //
NK124(ngo)001:9027: b+hee pa las 'byung ba'i shes rab ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9029: g.yeng ba med pa'i sbyin pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9030: sa srid mi 'dod tshul khrims dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9031: thams cad la ni bzod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9033: bsam gtan gzugs dang gzugs med yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9034: shes rab thabs dang bcas pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9035: pha rol phyin pa drug po la //
NK124(ngo)001:9036: brten pa rnams kyis yang dag sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:9039: bye brag tu bshad pa la yang gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9040: thos byung dang bsam byung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9043: lung dang rigs pa phyin ci ma log par smra ba'i gang zag la /
NK124(ngo)001:9044: shes bya'i gnas lugs gtan la 'bebs par byed pa
NK124(ngo)001:9045: bka' bstan bcos legs par nyan nas don khong du
NK124(ngo)001:9046: chud par bya'o // bsam 'byung gis shes bya'i sgro 'dogs bcad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9047: b+hee 'byung gis shes rab kyis nyon mongs pa rtsad nas gcod cing drung nas phyin pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9049: tshul gnas thos dang ting 'dzin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:9050: b+hee pa la ni rab tu sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:9053: thos bsam b+hee pas lta mthar phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:9056: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis phyi nang chos la sgro 'dog gcod /
NK124(ngo)001:9057: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9058: de don rgyud la b+hee par bya' //
NK124(ngo)001:9059: tha mar b+hee ba'i shes rab kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:9060: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i nyon mongs zhi //
NK124(ngo)001:9062: bzhi pa thun mong ma yin pa khyad par can gyi lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9064: skyes 'phags thun mong lam lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9065: thun mong ma yin pa'i sa bcu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9066: dang po tshogs sbyor mthong b+hee mi slob pa'i lam lnga las /
NK124(ngo)001:9071: dang po brten ni lus sems gnyis yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9073: thar pa cha mthun mi nang du //
NK124(ngo)001:9076: bsam gtan ma thob mngon par zhen //
NK124(ngo)001:9079: thar pa cha mthun gyi dge ba la brten nas so //
NK124(ngo)001:9080: gnyis pa tshogs lam rang gi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9085: theg pa thun mong gi lam nges 'byung gis tshul khrims kyis thob par b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:9086: bye brag theg chen tshogs lam bdag nyid rtogs pa'i thabs mkhas pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9088: tshogs gnyis yang nas yang du bsog pa tshogs /
NK124(ngo)001:9089: byang chub thob pa'i thog ma yin pa lam /
NK124(ngo)001:9091: gsum pa dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9098: chen po rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ste gong du bshad zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:9099: gsum pa 'bras bu tshogs lam chos rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9107: rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam /
NK124(ngo)001:9108: rtog pa yang med la dpyod pa yang med /
NK124(ngo)001:9115: yid la byed pa ste 'dod khams kyi sems pa rtse gcig pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9116: yid la byed pa bcu gcig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9124: mnyam par 'jog par byed pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9126: lus sems shin tu sbyangs ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:9127: byung ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'dod khams las /
NK124(ngo)001:9131: mngon par shes pa lnga la sogs pa 'byung /
NK124(ngo)001:9132: sangs rgyas mchod cing sems can smin par byas /
NK124(ngo)001:9133: shes rgyud tshogs gnyis gang bas /
