NK124(ngo)001:9134: chos rgyun ting nge 'dzin skyes pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9136: bsam gtan la thob mngon par zhen //
NK124(ngo)001:9137: shes sngon bsgrub pa'i sgo nas te //
NK124(ngo)001:9138: sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:9139: mchod pa'i phyir dang mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:9141: 'dis ni sangs rgyas dpag med la //
NK124(ngo)001:9142: skal pa grangs med bsnyen bkur byas //
NK124(ngo)001:9143: de la mnyes byas skur bya ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:9144: sems ni las rung mchog tu gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9145: gnyis pa tshogs gnyis phul phyung las /
NK124(ngo)001:9146: chos thams cad skye med du rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9147: tshig don rgya cher 'dzin nus dang ldan te /
NK124(ngo)001:9149: gang gis thos pas tshig dang don 'dzin par 'gyur
NK124(ngo)001:9150: ba'i chos kyi rgyun zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK124(ngo)001:9152: gtsug na rin chen gyis zhus pa'i mdo' las /
NK124(ngo)001:9153: rdzu 'phrul gyis rkang pa bzhi la gnas pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9154: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyang mthong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:9155: de dag la chos kyang nyan to //
NK124(ngo)001:9159: mi ma yin pa thams cad kyang gtam zer /
NK124(ngo)001:9161: sems yongs su sbyangs pa byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9163: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku la thob ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9164: de tshe chos kyi rgyun las ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9165: sangs rgyas rnams la gzhi gnas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9166: ye shes yang ba thob bya'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:9167: gdams ngag rgya chen thob par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9169: gnyis pa sbyor lam la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9174: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9175: lus kyi brten ni tshogs lam dang 'dra /
NK124(ngo)001:9176: sems kyi brten bsam gtan bzhin yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9178: bsam gtan bzhi pa shin tu dag thob pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9179: mi rtog ting 'dzin yongs su bzungs nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9180: ci ltar rnams gnas yid la byed pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9181: mthu' grub pa yi dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9183: gnyis pa nyer bstan gyi rgyu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9184: tshogs lam chen po mthar phyin pa'i chos rgyun ting nge 'dzin la b+hee pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9186: 'di ni sangs rgyas dpag med la //
NK124(ngo)001:9187: rtag pa med par bsnyen bkur byed //
NK124(ngo)001:9188: de la bsnyen bkur byed pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9189: sems kyis las rung mchog tu 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9191: gnyis pa ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9196: 'jig rten pa'i b+hee byung rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:9197: shes rab mthong lam gyi nyer len du 'gyur ba'o
NK124(ngo)001:9199: chos nyid kyi bden pa mngon sum du rtogs pa mthong lam la sbyor bas sbyor lam /
NK124(ngo)001:9200: lhag par mos pas mos pa bskyed pa'i sa /
NK124(ngo)001:9201: mthong spang rnam par 'byed pa mthong lam gyi rgyur gyur pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9204: bye brag tu mthong lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:9205: ye shes kyi che ba'i snga ltas yin pas drod
NK124(ngo)001:9206: / dge ba'i rtsa ba g.yo' ba rnams kyi rtse mo yin pas rtse mo /
NK124(ngo)001:9207: chos zab mo la mi skrag pas bzod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9208: 'jig rten pa'i chos kyi mchog yin pas de nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:9209: gsum pa dbye' ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9210: dbye' ba'i khyad par dang rtogs pa'i khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9212: nges 'byed yan lag bzhir byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:9213: spang rtogs thog mar bskyes pas drod /
NK124(ngo)001:9216: brten pa mthar phyin pas chos chog go //
NK124(ngo)001:9217: de dag gi dmigs yul bden bzhi sgyu ma lta bu /
NK124(ngo)001:9218: ngo bo rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9219: sgro 'dogs chod pa'i shes rab ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9220: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong zung du 'jug go //
NK124(ngo)001:9221: de yang drod rtse gnyis la dbang po lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9222: bzod pa chos mchog gnyis la stobs lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9223: de ci ltar ldan tshul gong du brjod zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:9224: cha mthun bzhi po re re la yang che 'bring chung gsum yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:9226: de ltar nges 'byed cha mthun ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9227: chung dang 'bring dang chen po yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9229: gnyis pa rtogs pa'i khyad par la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:9231: blo rigs kyi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9232: dang po cha mthun gzhi'i mnyam rjes la khyad par yod dam med na /
NK124(ngo)001:9233: mnyam gzhag chos thams cad kyi rnam pa tsam rtogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9234: rjes thob dmigs yul tsam la khyad par med la /
NK124(ngo)001:9235: chos can ngo bo dang 'brel pa'i chos thams cad
NK124(ngo)001:9236: rgya che chung rtogs pa'i khyad par yod pas mi
NK124(ngo)001:9238: cha mthun gzhi'i mnyam gzhag de blo rig gang du 'du zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:9239: rnal 'byor dngos su rjes mthun pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9240: bcad shes log par 'dod pa yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:9241: de dag mi 'thad pa'i tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9242: mkhas pa dag gis dgag yang zin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9244: de ltar tshogs sbyor gnyis po 'di rtogs pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:9245: bcas pas 'jig rten pa'i lam rnam par byang ba
NK124(ngo)001:9246: dang bral bas so so skye bo'i sa /
NK124(ngo)001:9247: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos rnams dang ldan pas byis pa'i sa zhes byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:9248: lam rjes mthun pa dang mos pa spyod pa'i sa btags pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9250: byis pa so so skye bo rnams la lam yang med la /
NK124(ngo)001:9252: lam b+hee pa yang med na 'bras bu rnam par 'god pa lta ga la yod /
NK124(ngo)001:9255: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i mthong lam nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:9256: gsum pa dang bzhi pa mthong b+hee gyis lam la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:9257: spang bya sgrib pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9258: gnyen po lam gyi rang bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9259: dang po la yang gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9261: ci ltar spong ba'i tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:9262: dang po la yang mthong spang gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:9263: mthong spang la yang shes bya'i sgrib pa ni shugs las shes par bya la /
NK124(ngo)001:9264: 'dir mthong spang nyon sgrib la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9269: rgyu'i rkyen nyan thos sngar b+hee spangs snga mas bzhag
NK124(ngo)001:9270: pa'i bag chags bdag rkyen tshul bzhin ma yin pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:9271: rnam rtog dmigs rkyen gnyis su snang bas /
NK124(ngo)001:9272: de ma thag rkyen rig pa snga ma snga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9274: phra rgyas spang pa myur bsam gtan //
NK124(ngo)001:9275: yul ni nye bar gyur pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9276: tshul bzhin ma yin yid byed las //
NK124(ngo)001:9277: nyon mongs rnams ni skye bar gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9280: snga ma thug med yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9282: rnam shes snga mas bzhag pa'i nus pa bag chags bzhag par 'dod /
NK124(ngo)001:9284: gnyis pa ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9285: mthong byed nye rgyud kyi mtshan nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:9289: nye rgyud gang zhig mthong lam gyi gzhoms byar gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9291: chos nyid mngon sum du gsar du mthong bas spang ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9294: ci ltar myug sogs rim skyes nas //
NK124(ngo)001:9295: sa bon shug pa bcod pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:9296: de bzhin de nyid mthong ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9297: mthong spang rnams ni ldog par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9299: gsum pa dbye' ba la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:9301: 'dod khams la bden pa bzhi la /
NK124(ngo)001:9304: 'jig tshogs mthar 'dzin tshul khrims rtul zhugs mchog 'dzin gsum ma gtogs bdun bdun /
NK124(ngo)001:9305: lam bden pa lta ba tshogs gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9309: de dang bcu' dang bdun bdun brgyad //
NK124(ngo)001:9310: lta ba gsum gnyis ma rtogs so //
NK124(ngo)001:9312: khams gong ma gnyis la khong khro med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9313: de dag dgu dang drug bdun du 'gyur bas nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9314: bsdom na nyi shu rtsa brgyad do //
NK124(ngo)001:9315: gnyis pa theg chen pa ltar na /
NK124(ngo)001:9319: dang po phung po lnga la gang zag gi bdag tu 'dzin pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9320: 'jig tshogs lta ba phung po lnga la /
NK124(ngo)001:9321: rtag pa'am chad pa'i mtha' gcig tu zhen pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9323: kun rdzob don dam dang mthun par 'dzin pa log par lta ba /
NK124(ngo)001:9324: lta ba ngan pa la bzod par 'dzin pa lta ba la phyogs 'dzin /
NK124(ngo)001:9325: lta ngan dang 'brel ba'i spyod pa ngan pa la
NK124(ngo)001:9326: spyod pa bzod par 'dzin pa tshul khrims dang brtul
NK124(ngo)001:9328: lta ba lnga dang yang dag pa ma yin pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:9329: yul la mngon par dga' ba'i 'dod chags 'ga' zhig
NK124(ngo)001:9330: pa kun nas mnar sems pa'i zhe sdang /
NK124(ngo)001:9331: blo gang zag gis kun rdzob gnas lugs ma shes pas ma rig pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9332: bdag lta la brten pas khengs pas nga rgyal /
NK124(ngo)001:9333: kun rdzob bden pa la som nyi za bas the tshom dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9336: 'dod khams la bden pa bzhi la dge bcu' ste bzhi bcu /
NK124(ngo)001:9337: khams gong ma gnyis la khong 'khro med pas so drug bcu gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9338: yan lag gis dbye' ba brgyad dang bcu gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9339: khong khro med pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:9340: rgyu gzhi gnas dang ldan pa'i phyir dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9343: phyis byed par 'gyur ba gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9344: bdag gis gnyen rnams la gnod pa byas sogs su dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9345: bdag gis dgra rnams la phan gtags so //
NK124(ngo)001:9348: mnar sems pa'i dngos po dgu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9350: mthong spang nyan thos kyi sa bon las /
NK124(ngo)001:9351: ma rig pa mngon 'gyur skye ba /
NK124(ngo)001:9352: zag bcas rten 'brel lugs 'byung bar ma chad par /
NK124(ngo)001:9353: mthar rga shi dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9355: sems can tha ma 'bring dang mchog 'gyur ci snyed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9356: de kun ma rig las byung bde bar gshegs pas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:9358: gnyis pa b+hee spang sgrib pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9362: rgyu ni mthong spang dang mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:9364: b+hee spang nyon sgrib kyi mtshan nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:9368: nyon mongs gang zhig b+hee lam gyis gzhom byar gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9370: chos nyid mthong ba tsam gyis spang mi nus pas
NK124(ngo)001:9371: mngon sum gyis mthong zin goms pas spang bas na
NK124(ngo)001:9373: de nas bden pa mthong bas spang ba mthong spong yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9374: 'di la bden pa'i sgo nas dbye' ba ma byed pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9382: gnyis pa khams kyi sgo nas dbye' na bcu drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9384: khams gong ma gnyis la zhe sdang med pas lnga lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9385: gsum pa sa tsam dbye' na /
NK124(ngo)001:9387: gzugs khams bsam gtan sa bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9394: mthar 'dzin lta ba rnams re re la dgu dgu' yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9395: dgu' po re re la'ang chen po'i chen po la sogs dgu yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9396: lnga po re re zhing dgu dgu brgyad cu rtsa gcig pa lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9397: 'dod khams kyi zhe sdang dgu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9399: gsum pa b+hee spang 'bras bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9401: rigs mi 'dra ba sa dang lam gyi gegs byed pa dang skye ba len pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9402: gnyis pa gnyen po spang bya spong tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9403: yul chos dbyings spros bral mngon sum du rtogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9404: yul can mthong lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mngon sum du 'gyur ba na /
NK124(ngo)001:9405: spang bya'i sgrib pa cir yang mi dmigs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9406: spang bya min pa spang rgyu med de /
NK124(ngo)001:9408: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:9409: bzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK124(ngo)001:9410: yang dag nyid la yang dag lta //
NK124(ngo)001:9411: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK124(ngo)001:9414: 'khor ba spang bar gyur ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9415: myang 'das khyod kyis mi bzhed kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:9416: 'khor ba mi dmigs pa yis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9417: zhi nyid mgon po khyod kyis ni bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:9420: mthong b+hee gnyis spang bya spang tshul gnad gcig yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:9421: bye brag b+hee lam dgu'i chung ngu'i chung sogs skyes pa'i tshe /
NK124(ngo)001:9422: b+hee spang chen po'i chen po sogs ldog pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9424: sa dgu la ni chen po yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9425: chen po la sogs dri ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9426: gnyen po chung ngu'i chung ngu la //
NK124(ngo)001:9427: sogs pa'i lam ni dag pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9429: 'o na gnyen po che rim nas skye bar rigs te /
NK124(ngo)001:9430: spang bya che rim nas spang ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9431: zhe na spang bya rags pa che bar brjod pa yin gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9432: spang dka' bar che bar brjod pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9433: dper na gos kyi dri ma 'khru ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9434: gnyis pa lam la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9437: dang po mthong lam la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9441: dang po ni nges 'byed yan lag bzhi yin cing
NK124(ngo)001:9442: dngos rgyu chos mchog chen po'i ye shes yin te
NK124(ngo)001:9444: de nas de ni 'jig rten las //
NK124(ngo)001:9445: 'das pa'i ye shes bla med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9446: rnam par mi rtog dri ma med //
NK124(ngo)001:9447: 'dzin pa gnyis dang bral bas thob //
NK124(ngo)001:9449: gnyis pa ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9450: byang sems mthong lam gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9454: chos nyid mngon sum gsar du mthong ba'i ye shes
NK124(ngo)001:9455: rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi go skabs dbye' bar gyur
NK124(ngo)001:9456: ba'o // de dag rim pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:9459: theg pa dang po'i ldog pa gsal nas /
NK124(ngo)001:9460: mthong lam du mtshon pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9462: chos nyid mngon sum du mthong zhing sangs rgyas kyis lam gyi thog ma yin pas mthong lam /
NK124(ngo)001:9463: sa bcu'i thog ma yin pas sa dang po /
NK124(ngo)001:9464: don dam sems bskyed kyi don yin pas sems dang po bskyed pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9465: gsum pa dbye' ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9467: skad cig du la spyad la /
NK124(ngo)001:9468: gnas lugs kyi 'thad pa bsam pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9469: gling gsum gyi skyes pa bud med dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9471: lha rigs drug kho na skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9472: skyo shas che zhing shes rab gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9473: ngan song gsum la mi skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9474: rnam par smin pa'i las kyi sgrib pa chen pos sgrib pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9475: gzugs khams dang gzugs med pa'i lha la mi skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9476: sdug bsngal gyi tshogs med pa snyoms par 'jug pa la srid pas skyo shas chung ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9477: sgra mi snyan pa la yang mi skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9478: skyo ba med pas khams gong ma dang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9480: chos mchog chen po'i rjes su chos nyid bden pa
NK124(ngo)001:9481: mngon sum du rtogs pa'i ye shes bya rdzogs kyi
NK124(ngo)001:9482: skad cig ma gcig la skye zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:9483: de yang byang chub sems dpa' mthong lam chen po rdzas skad cig gcig la skye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9484: chos nyid gsar du rtogs pa dang las med pa'i phyir dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9485: mthong spang gcig char spang pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9487: gang gis de ltar mthong ba de'i chos kun mthong /
NK124(ngo)001:9489: rigs pa drug cu ba las /
NK124(ngo)001:9491: 'di la rnam par dbye yod na //
NK124(ngo)001:9492: rnam par mi mkhas de yis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9493: rkyen las byung ba'i don ma mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:9495: mthong ba 'di la sbyar ma thag tu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9496: 'jig tshogs lta dang tshul khrims brtul zhugs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9497: thos bsam dang ni nyon mongs gsum po dag /
NK124(ngo)001:9498: gcig char spang ste 'phags pa'i bden mthong ba //
NK124(ngo)001:9501: bden pa rnams kyis bden par rtogs pa ni gcig yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9502: de bas na sa dang po'i skad cig ma dang po mthong ba'i lam yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9503: gsum pa 'thad pa bsam pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9504: dbu' ma pa'i lugs don dam par mthong ba'i lam skye bar mi 'thad de /
NK124(ngo)001:9506: byang chub sems dpa' mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9508: 'phags pa rnams chos thams cad 'dus ma byas kyis rab tu phye bar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9509: gal te de ltar na mdo' bstan bcos rnams las /
NK124(ngo)001:9510: skad cig gcig dang bcu drug la sogs par skye bar bshad pa dang mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:9512: dngos por smra ba rnams rjes su bzung ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:9514: dgongs gzhi ni rten cing 'brel ba 'byung ba yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:9515: dgongs pa ni dngos po la mngon par zhen pa
NK124(ngo)001:9516: rnams bzhugs pa'i don du yin zhing dngos po la
NK124(ngo)001:9517: gnod byed ni / bdag dang gzhan dang gnyis dang rgyu med pa las mi skye ba'i phyir te /
NK124(ngo)001:9519: bdag las ma yin gzhan las min //
NK124(ngo)001:9520: gnyis las ma yin rgyu med yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9521: dngos po gang dang gang la yang //
NK124(ngo)001:9522: skye ba nam yang yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9524: 'o na brten nas skye ba nyid skye ba ma yin nam /
NK124(ngo)001:9527: rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo' las /
NK124(ngo)001:9528: gang zhig rkyen las skye ba de ma skyes //
NK124(ngo)001:9529: de la skye ba'i rang bzhin yod ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9530: rkyen las rag las gang de stong pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:9534: 'gags pa med pa skye med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9536: mthong lam byang chub lam gyi yan lag bdun ni brjod zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:9537: gsum pa mthong lam thob pa'i rtags sam yon tan ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9538: 'og tu sa lam gyi skabs su ston par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9539: gsum pa b+hee lam la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9541: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i b+hee lam mo //
NK124(ngo)001:9545: dang po ni sa gong ma'i bsam gtan 'grub pa rgyu gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9549: dang po ni yid la byed pa drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9550: mtshan nyid rab tu rigs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:9554: dpyod pa sbyor ba'i thabs yid la byed pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9555: thar pa'i lam la dod sbyar na /
NK124(ngo)001:9556: sbyor matha'i 'bras bu yid la byed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9557: bsam gtan dngos gzhi sems yin pa ma rtogs so //
NK124(ngo)001:9559: nyon mongs pa mang bas lus sems sdug bsngal rags /
NK124(ngo)001:9560: de'i stobs kyi tshe thung ba khams 'og ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:9561: de las zlog pa khams gong ma'i mtsham nyid du
NK124(ngo)001:9562: thos bsam gyis rig pa rtse gcig tu yid la
NK124(ngo)001:9563: byed pa ste / thar pa'i lam dang dod sbyar na tshogs lam gyi dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9565: de ltar yid la byas pa las gong ma'i sa
NK124(ngo)001:9566: dang rjes mthun pa'i rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK124(ngo)001:9567: skye ba ste / sbyor lam gyi dod /
NK124(ngo)001:9568: gsum pa ni de ltar sbyangs pas 'dod khams kyi
NK124(ngo)001:9569: nyon mongs pa che gsum gyis dben pa'i rtse gcig
NK124(ngo)001:9573: gong ma'i nyon mongs pa 'bring gsum spangs pa'i lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:9574: bdag bde' thob pa'i ting nge 'dzin skye ba ste b+hee lam sa drug pa'i dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9576: de ltar b+hee ba las sa 'og ma'i nyon mongs
NK124(ngo)001:9577: pa spangs sam snyams na bde' skye mi skye dpyad
NK124(ngo)001:9578: pas / chung gsum skye bar shes nas rtse gcig gnas pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9580: drug pa ni chung gsum spong byed kyis ting nge 'dzin b+hee pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9581: bar chad med pa'i lam gyi dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9582: bsam gtan dang po yid la byed pa ci lta
NK124(ngo)001:9583: bar gnyis pa nas srid rtse'i bar gyi yid la
NK124(ngo)001:9584: byed pa drug gam bdun gyi 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK124(ngo)001:9586: yid la byed pa de dag la de'i yon tan dran pa'i gus pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9587: rtag tu byed pa'i sbyor ba rgyun du b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9588: de yang che 'bring gis gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9589: gnyis ka dang mi ldan pa chung ngu /
NK124(ngo)001:9590: gang rung gnyis dang ldan na 'bring po //
NK124(ngo)001:9591: gnyis ka dang ldan pa chen por b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9592: bsam gtan gong ma rnams kyis nyer zlog la yang che 'bring b+hee tshul de bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9593: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9594: skyon yon gyi bsam gtan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9596: de dag gi byed las so //
NK124(ngo)001:9597: dang po la yang gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:9598: bsam gtan dang gzugs med kyi ting nge 'dzin la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:9603: the tshom shas che ba'i bsam gtan te /
NK124(ngo)001:9604: rim pa ltar bsam gtan gyi bde' ba'i myong bar byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9605: sngon gyi mthu' la rtogs pa la sogs pa'i drug cu rtsa gnyis kun slong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9606: khyad par thob nas sems khengs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9607: de kho na ma rtogs pa thar pa 'dod pa
NK124(ngo)001:9608: bsam gtan thob pa thar pa yin nam ma yin
NK124(ngo)001:9610: de'i phyir nyon mongs pa'i bsam gtan zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9611: de dag gi sa de dang der skye ba'i mtshan nyid la sogs par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9612: gnyis pa yon tan can la bsam gtan dang gzugs med gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:9613: dang po bsam gtan yan lag bco brgyad las /
NK124(ngo)001:9614: bsam gtan dang po yan lag ldan te /
NK124(ngo)001:9616: yid mi bde ba thag sring bas rtogs dpyod gnyis gnyen po'i yan lag /
NK124(ngo)001:9617: dge' bde' gnyis lus dang sems la phan 'dogs pas phan yon gyi yan lag /
NK124(ngo)001:9618: ting nge 'dzin la rtogs dpyod gnyen po 'jug cing
NK124(ngo)001:9619: dga' bde' yi phan yon 'byung bas tshe gcig pa
NK124(ngo)001:9621: bsam gtan dang po la dngos kyi rtsam po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9623: dang po rtog pa dang bcas /
NK124(ngo)001:9627: rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9629: gnyis pa yan lag bzhi ldan te /
NK124(ngo)001:9630: nad rab tu dang ba rtog dpyod thag sring bar byed pa gnyen po /
NK124(ngo)001:9631: dga' bde' phan yon rtse gcig pa gnas kyi yan lag go //
NK124(ngo)001:9633: dran shes shing btang snyoms gsum dga' ba thag sring bas gnyen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9635: rtse gcig pa gnas kyi yan lag go //
NK124(ngo)001:9637: btang snyoms dran pa gnyis bde' bya thag sring ba'i gnyen po /
NK124(ngo)001:9638: bde sdug gnyis ka ma yin pa yon tan te /
NK124(ngo)001:9639: btang snyoms rdzas gcig la bsring ba'i cha gnyen po /
NK124(ngo)001:9640: mi gnod pa'i cha nas phan yon no //
NK124(ngo)001:9641: rtse gcig pa gnas kyi yan lag sngar bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9642: gnyis pa gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9643: gzhi rag tu dmigs pas 'da' ba yin gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9646: thams cad kyang yan lag rtse gcig pa dang btang snyoms su mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9648: sbyor ba'i dus na gzugs kyi dmigs pa las 'das nas /
NK124(ngo)001:9649: nam mkha' mtha' yas zhes bya ba /
NK124(ngo)001:9650: gzung ba'i dmigs pa las 'das nas nam mkha' la
NK124(ngo)001:9651: dmigs pa'i rnam par shes mtha' yas so zhes bya
NK124(ngo)001:9652: ba / 'jig rten pa'i dmigs pa las 'das nas
NK124(ngo)001:9653: nam mkha' la dmigs pa'i rnam par shes pa ni
NK124(ngo)001:9654: ba / / rags pa med cing phra ba med
NK124(ngo)001:9655: pa yang ma yin mnyam pa'i mos pa sngon du
NK124(ngo)001:9656: ba / / btang nas / dngos gzhi'i dus su dge ba rtse gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9657: gnyis pa 'bras bu skye ba'i tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9658: bsam gtan dang po la che 'bring chung gsum du b+hee pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9659: tshangs ris la sogs gsum du skye la /
NK124(ngo)001:9660: de bzhin du gnyis pa la gsum du b+hee bas 'od chung la sogs pa gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9661: bzhi gsum du b+hee pas sprin med 'od la sogs pa gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9662: de yang bsam gtan bzhi pa'i sems la bsten nas zag med bden pa'i rnam pa can /
NK124(ngo)001:9663: zhes pa mnyam gzhag gnyis kyi bar du zag bcas
NK124(ngo)001:9664: zhi drag kyi rnam pa can zhes pas rjes thob
NK124(ngo)001:9666: zag bcas zag med gsum du 'phel pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9671: bco lnga spel bas rim pa bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:9676: gzugs med la yang gzugs sun byung bas gzhal med
NK124(ngo)001:9677: khang gi gnas gzhan med pas sa tha dad med
NK124(ngo)001:9678: / 'on kyang che 'bring b+hee pas tshe thung dang mthu' che chung du skye'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9679: nyon mongs pa'ang che 'bring gsum du 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9680: de lta bu'i bsam gtan de dag 'jig rten pas
NK124(ngo)001:9681: chung zhing dman pas zag pa dang bcas pa yin
NK124(ngo)001:9682: la / nyan rang gi zag pa med cing 'jig
NK124(ngo)001:9683: rten pa las rgya che zhing byang chub sems dpa'
NK124(ngo)001:9684: rnams nyon mongs pa med pa'i rnam byang gi ting
NK124(ngo)001:9685: nge 'dzin la thabs mkhas pa gnas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:9686: bsam gtan gyi pha rol du phyin pa la dbang ba 'byor ba yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:9687: sangs rgyas rnams kyis ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshul gyis 'jug par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:9689: bsam gtan b+hee pas spang bya mgo' non pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9691: mngon par shes pa la sogs pa'i yon tan dang lam gyi brten byed pa'i las can /
NK124(ngo)001:9692: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i b+hee pa la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9693: gang zag la skye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9695: rang bzhin nges par bya ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9697: theg pa chen po ltar na gling gsum gyi skyes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9706: 'du shes med pa la mi skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9707: las kyi sgrib chen po'i sgrib pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9709: nyan thos pa bsam gtan dngos gzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9710: bsam gtan dang po'i nyer zlog mi lcog pa med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9713: gzhan la mi brten pa ni 'dod pa'i sems las
NK124(ngo)001:9714: su mi rung zhing srid rtse'i sems mi gsal ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:9715: phyir ro // theg pa chen po pa ni bsam
NK124(ngo)001:9716: gtan bzhi pa shin tu dag pa la brten la
NK124(ngo)001:9717: phyir ro // / 'on kyang ting nge 'dzin gyis rtsal sbyang pa na /
NK124(ngo)001:9721: gsum pa rang bzhin nges par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9726: rang bzhin med par mngon sum du mthong zin goms
NK124(ngo)001:9727: par byed pa rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi go skabs
NK124(ngo)001:9729: mthong lam gyis rtogs zin b+hee par byed pa b+hee lam zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9730: gsum pa dbye' ba la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9732: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i b+hee lam tsam yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:9734: bden bzhi chos thams cad la dmigs pa'i mnyam gzhag zag med dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9735: sgyu ma lta bu la dmigs pa'i rjes thob snang
NK124(ngo)001:9736: bcas kyi ye shes che 'bring gis dbye' ba dgu
NK124(ngo)001:9738: de ni rgyu mchog yin pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:9739: chung dang 'bring dang chen po rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:9740: chung ngu'i chung sogs dbye' ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9741: rnam pa rnam pa dgur bzhed do //
NK124(ngo)001:9743: gcig dang tha dad bsam pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9744: dgu po dngos po tha dad yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9745: rigs can du skye ba'i phyir te /
NK124(ngo)001:9746: bzhi pa grangs nges pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9747: sa dgu la brten pa'i spang bya che 'bring chung dgur nges pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9748: gnyen po yang rim pa dgur nges te /
NK124(ngo)001:9750: sa dgu la ni chen po yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9751: chen po la sogs dri ma yis //
NK124(ngo)001:9752: gnyen po chung ngu'i chung ngu la //
NK124(ngo)001:9753: sogs pa'i lam zhi dag pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:9755: de la b+hee spang dang de'i gnyen po ci ltar spong ba'i tshul ni gong du brjod zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:9756: lnga pa mi slob pa'i lam la yang rnam par bzhag pa bshad mod kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:9757: seng ges bzang pos 'grel chen las /
NK124(ngo)001:9758: sa dang po'i skad cig ma dang po ni mthong ba'i lam yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9759: de las gzhan skad cig ma gnyis pa la sogs pa nas /
NK124(ngo)001:9760: rdo rje lta bur brjod pa bar chad med pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:9761: lam gong ma de ma thag tu sangs rgyas kyi
NK124(ngo)001:9762: sa kun du 'od thob pa'i bar 'di dag thams
NK124(ngo)001:9763: cad ni mchog gi don la sogs pa chos dbyings
NK124(ngo)001:9764: so sor rtogs pa'i phyir b+hee pa'i lam yin par
NK124(ngo)001:9766: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis spang bya'i bag chags phra ba spong ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9767: b+hee lam mthar thug pa yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:9768: spang bya dag pa rnams grol gyi lam du tha snyad byed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9769: sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9771: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni lam chad pa
NK124(ngo)001:9772: 'jug pa chad pa spros pa dang srid par 'dren
NK124(ngo)001:9775: gnyis pa sa bcu' ni 'phags pa'i gang zag mthong
NK124(ngo)001:9776: b+hee lam gyis bsdus pa byang chub sems dpa' bcu
NK124(ngo)001:9782: ma thob pa thob pa'i rgyu la sa dang po'i rgyu ni mos pa spyod pa'i sa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:9783: sa bcu rnams kyi rgyu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9784: snga ma snga ma rnams yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9785: gnyis pa thob pa rdzogs pa'i rgyu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9786: sa rang rang gi yongs sbyong thabs shes zung du 'brel ba yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:9787: bye brag sa bcu rdzogs pa'i rgyu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9788: sa 'og ma rnams kyis thabs shes cha pa rang
NK124(ngo)001:9789: ldan du 'dus pa nyid mthar phyin pa yin no
NK124(ngo)001:9790: // gnyis pa rang bzhin la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9799: nam mkha' rang bzhin med par mngon sum du rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:9800: pa thabs dang zung 'jug rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyis
NK124(ngo)001:9801: lam gyis brten du gyur ba ni 'thad de /
NK124(ngo)001:9802: lam ni bdag med pa shes rab kyi cha yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:9803: sa ni zung 'jug gi cha yin pa mi srid pa yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9804: rang lugs ni bdag med mngon sum du rtogs pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:9805: shes rab thabs khyad par can dang zung du 'jug
NK124(ngo)001:9806: pa byang sems 'phags pa'i yon tan byed pa can
NK124(ngo)001:9807: no // 'o na theg pa yangs pa'i cha zer na /
NK124(ngo)001:9808: ma nges te theg pa ni sems bskyed la sogs thabs kyi yin pa'i phyir te /
NK124(ngo)001:9810: nyan thos theg pa de la ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9811: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9812: spyod pa bsngo'a ba ma bstan te //
NK124(ngo)001:9813: theg pa chen po ga la 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9817: sems can dpag tu med pa 'khor ba'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:9818: yon tan dpag tu med pa dang ldan pa'i rab
NK124(ngo)001:9819: dga' la sogs de dag la gong nas gong du
NK124(ngo)001:9822: dper na sa gzhi bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9825: dpag tu med pa de dag la //
NK124(ngo)001:9826: phyir phyir gong du 'grod ldan phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:9827: de dag nyid ni sa 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9829: gnyis pa so so'i sgra don ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9830: bye brag nyan thos las khyad par 'phags pa'i dga' ba thob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9832: byang chub la yang nye ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9833: sems can don bsgrub mthong ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:9834: rab tu dga' ba skyes gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:9835: de phyir rab dga' zhes brjod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9837: tshul khrims 'chal ba dang theg dman yid la byed pa'i dri ma med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9839: dri ma med pa'i sa zhes bya /
NK124(ngo)001:9840: ting nge 'dzin gyis stobs kyi rang gzhan la brjod bya /
NK124(ngo)001:9841: rjod byed kyi don byed pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9842: chos kyi snang ba chen po ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9843: byed pa'i phyir na 'od byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9844: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i bdag med kyi shes rab kyis sgrib gnyis bsreg par byed pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9846: 'di ltar byang chub phyogs mthun chos //
NK124(ngo)001:9847: rab tu gsal byed 'od lta bu //
NK124(ngo)001:9848: de dang ldan phyir sa de bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:9850: sems can smin par byed pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:9851: gzhan gyi log bsgrub kyis rang gi sems nyon mongs par mi 'gyur ba de gnyis sbyangs dka' ba /
NK124(ngo)001:9852: sems can rnams ni smin byed cing /
NK124(ngo)001:9853: rang gi sems kyang bsrungs ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:9854: blo ldan gyis sbyangs dka' bas /
NK124(ngo)001:9855: de phyir sbyangs dka' zhes brjod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9857: gang la yang mi gnas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9858: shes rab pha rol phyin brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:9860: mngon sum 'gyur bas sa zhes brjod /
NK124(ngo)001:9861: mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i sa las ring du song zhing
NK124(ngo)001:9862: sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'grod pa gcig pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:9863: 'brel bas / 'grod gcig lam dang 'brel ba'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:9864: ring du song ba'i sar 'dod do //
NK124(ngo)001:9865: mtshan ma dang mtshan nyid pa las rtsol ba'i 'du shes med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9866: 'du shes gnyis kyis mi g.yo' phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:9867: mi g.yo' ba zhes nges par brjod /
NK124(ngo)001:9868: so so yang dag rig pa bzhi'i blo gros kyis chos ston pa la 'byor bas /
NK124(ngo)001:9869: so so yang dag rig blo bzang /
NK124(ngo)001:9870: sa de legs pa'i blo gros yin /
NK124(ngo)001:9871: dbyings ye shes dbyer med nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK124(ngo)001:9872: gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyis sgo gnyis las //
NK124(ngo)001:9873: thos pas char sprin lta bu khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:9874: sprin bzhin gnyis kyi nam mkha'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:9875: khyab pa'i phyir na chos kyi sprin //
NK124(ngo)001:9877: de la sa bcur nges pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9878: spangs bya nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i ma rig pa bcu yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9879: de'i gnyen por sa bcu nges te /
NK124(ngo)001:9881: chos kyi dbyings la ma rig pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9882: nyon mongs can min sgrib pa bcu' //
NK124(ngo)001:9883: sa bcu mi mthun phyogs rnams kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:9884: gnyen po dag ni bstan pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:9886: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa rnams kyis lam phar
NK124(ngo)001:9887: phyin bcu rdzogs par bya ba la ltos pas kyang
NK124(ngo)001:9889: gsum pa sa thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9890: bzhi pa sa'i khyad par rnams 'dir yi ge mang dogs pas ma smos so //
NK124(ngo)001:9891: spyi don lnga pa theg chen lam gyi nges par 'byung ba'i tshul gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:9892: thabs kyis nges par 'byung tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9893: dus kyis nges par 'byung tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:9895: 'bras bu thams cad mkhyen pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:9896: rgyu nor ba spyod pa las mi 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9897: dper na 'o ma 'dod pa la rwa la mthen pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9898: rgyu ma tshang ba las kyang thams cad mkhyen pa mi 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:9899: dper na sa bon la sogs med na 'bras bu mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:9900: des na gong du bshad pa'i rang bzhin gyis rim dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9901: rgyas 'gyur gyis rigs gnyis la brten nas rgyu tshogs gnyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9902: lta ba bden pa gnyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9903: lam lnga sa bcu mthar phyin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9904: 'bras bu sku gnyis la sogs thob pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9906: gter dang ljon pa'i shing bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:9907: rigs de rnam gnyis shes bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:9908: thog med rang bzhin gnas pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:9909: yang dag blang ba mchog yin nam //
NK124(ngo)001:9912: thabs dang bral ba'i shes rab kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:9914: shes rab bral ba'i thabs dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:9915: mkhas pa de ni zhir mi 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:9918: chos kyi sku de mdor bsdus na //
NK124(ngo)001:9919: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las 'khrungs //
NK124(ngo)001:9920: gzugs kyi sku de mdor bsdus na //
NK124(ngo)001:9921: bsod nams tshogs las yang dag 'khrungs //
NK124(ngo)001:9923: shes pas srid la mi gnas shing //
NK124(ngo)001:9924: snying rjes zhi la mi gnas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9926: don gnyis ldan pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9928: gnyis pa dus kyi nges par 'byung tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:9930: dka' spyad dpag med brgya phrag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9931: dpag med dge ba bsags pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9932: dpag tu med pa'i dus dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9933: dpag med sgrib pa zad pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:9934: sgrib pa kun gyi dri med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:9935: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid thob //
NK124(ngo)001:9936: rin chen snod ni phye ba ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:9937: sangs rgyas nyid ni sangs rgyas bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:9939: byang chub sesama dpa' bya ba dka' ba dpag tu med pa spyad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9940: tshogs gnyis dpag tu med pa bsags pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9941: sgrib gnyis ma lus pa zad pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:9942: thams cad mkhyen nyid thob pa de la dus dpag tu med pa dgos te /
NK124(ngo)001:9943: dbang po rno zhing brtson 'grus myur bskal pa grangs med gsum gyis rdzogs par bshad de /
NK124(ngo)001:9944: mos spyod kyi sa la grangs med gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:9945: ma dag sa bdun la gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:9946: dag pa sa gsum la grangs med gcig go //
NK124(ngo)001:9947: de yang le lo dang mi dge bas bar ma chod na /
NK124(ngo)001:9949: gzhan du na grangs med gsum gyis rdzogs pa'i nges pa med de /
NK124(ngo)001:9951: de ltar ltung ba stobs ldan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9952: byang chub sems stobs ldan pa gnyis //
NK124(ngo)001:9954: sa thob pa la yun ring thogs //
NK124(ngo)001:9957: 'grang du med pa'i grangs med ni ma yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9958: grangs kyi gnas gzhan drug cu gcig pa'i ming yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:9960: gcig bcu brgya stong khri 'bum dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9961: bye ba sa ya dung phyur dgu' //
NK124(ngo)001:9962: gnas gzhan rkyang pa dgu' zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:9963: ther 'bum phrag phrig rab bkram dang //
NK124(ngo)001:9979: thog ma ma rtogs chen por sbyar /
NK124(ngo)001:9980: brgyad ni bar las ma snyed do //
NK124(ngo)001:9981: de ltar gnas gzhan drug cu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:9984: bsod nams stobs rin po che'i mdo' las /
NK124(ngo)001:9985: don mthun ming ni tshad med pa bzhi la gnyis gnyis su byas pas kha bskang du rung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:9989: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:9990: mthar phyin pa yi 'bras bu bzhed //
NK124(ngo)001:9992: de ltar spang rtogs mthar phyin pa'i sangs rgyas la /
NK124(ngo)001:9993: nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal dang /
NK124(ngo)001:9994: mtshan ma la sogs pa'i 'ching ba tha dag dang bral te /
NK124(ngo)001:9995: bdag dang bdag gis stong pas /
NK124(ngo)001:9997: gsal 'grib med par thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mngon du gyur bas med pa'i mtha' las grol /
NK124(ngo)001:10000: 'dus ma byas shing lhun gyis grub //
NK124(ngo)001:10001: gzhan gyi rkyen gyis rtogs med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:10002: mkhyen dang brtse dang nus pa ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:10003: don gnyis ldan pa'i sangs rgyas nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10004: ces pas 'bras bu sku gsum dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10005: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang brtse ba'i thugs rje dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10008: tshogs brgyad sku gsum du gnas gyur pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10010: 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa gnas gyur pas sprul pa'i mngon du 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:10011: kun gzhi la gnas pa'i yid sbyangs pas longs spyod par rdzogs pa'i sku ston no //
NK124(ngo)001:10012: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa sbyangs bas chos kyi sku thob bo //
NK124(ngo)001:10014: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10015: sprul pa'i sku ni sangs rgyas thams cad dang spyod pa mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:10016: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni sangs rgyas thams cad dang dgongs pa mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:10017: chos kyi sku ni sangs rgyas thams cad dang sku mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:10019: de ltar sku gsum dbyer med pas gdul bya rnams la gang 'dul gyis don mdzad /
NK124(ngo)001:10021: sum cu rtsa gsum mtshan dang mthun stobs pha mtha' yas //
NK124(ngo)001:10022: sems can rnams la chos rab ston pa sgrog par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:10025: yum las yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10026: chos thams cad la sgrib pa med pa'i ye shes brten pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10029: sangs rgyas rnams ni mngon sum spyan //
NK124(ngo)001:10030: kun du thog med gzigs par 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:10032: de yang chos can ci snyed pa'i mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10033: chos nyid ci lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10034: dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:10037: rnam pa thams cad du ma mthong pa'am ma thos pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:10039: khong du ma chugs pa gang yang med do //
NK124(ngo)001:10042: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:10043: phyogs bcu 'jig rten gyi khams kyis sems can de dag gi sems bsdus pa dang spros pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10044: chos nyid kyi yan lag ci lta ba bzhin du rab tu mkhyen to //
NK124(ngo)001:10045: sems can de dag gi sems 'dod chags dang bcas pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:10046: 'dod chags dang bcas pa zhes bya bar yang dag par ci lta ba bzhin rab tu mkhyen to //
NK124(ngo)001:10047: de bzhin du 'dod chags dang bral ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10057: btsum pa la sogs pa yang dag par ci lta ba bzhin du rab tu mkhyen to //
NK124(ngo)001:10059: yang 'das pa'i chos la ma chags ma mthong ba'i ye shes gzigs pa 'jug go //
NK124(ngo)001:10063: gnyis pa ci lta ba mkhyen pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10065: gang zag pha rol gyi sems de la 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10069: gnas pa la gzhan du 'gyur ba mi gzigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:10070: ma nor ba de bzhin nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10076: yang dag pa ci lta ba bzhin rab tu mkhyen to //
NK124(ngo)001:10078: gsum pa ci snyed mkhyen pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10079: ci snyed pa nyid ci lta bar mkhyen pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10081: ye shes 'chi med dam pa de la gzhan med thabs bcas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10082: 'di ni nam mkha'i khams dang mtshungs te tha dad med //
NK124(ngo)001:10085: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i ye shes la mkhas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10087: gsum pa brtse ba'i thugs rje ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10088: sangs rgyas nas sems can thams cad la thugs rjes ma bzung ba gcig kyang med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:10089: 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du thugs rje chen pos skyob pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10091: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni spyod lam rnam bzhir ye shes kyis ma bzung ba med do //
NK124(ngo)001:10092: chos thams cad la thugs rje ma gzigs pa med do //
NK124(ngo)001:10093: sems can thams cad la phan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10094: bde bas ma bzung ba med do //
NK124(ngo)001:10097: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis thugs rje chen pos /
NK124(ngo)001:10098: sems can mtha' yas pa yongs su smin par byas pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:10099: gzigs pa rtogs par 'byung ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10100: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rjes 'byung ba zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10102: bzhi pa 'phrin las kyis don mdzad pa la ye shes kyis mdzad pa yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10103: de yang 'bad rtsol med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10104: rgyun mi chad par don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10105: ye shes kyis mdzad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10107: sku'i 'phrin las thams cad ye shes sngon du 'gro zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10109: gsung gi phrin las thams cad ye shes sngon du 'gro zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10111: thugs kyi 'phrin las thams cad ye shes sngon du 'gro zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10113: 'bad rtsol med par don mdzad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10114: rgyun mi chad par don mdzad pa ni khog dbub kyi skabs nas brjod zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:10115: gzhan yang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan gyi bye brag
NK124(ngo)001:10116: mdo' rgyud du ma nas bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK124(ngo)001:10117: gsungs kyang / 'dir bsdus te brjod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10119: nyon mongs med dang smon mkhyen dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10120: mngon shes so so yang dag rig /
NK124(ngo)001:10121: rnam pa thams cad dag bzhi dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10122: dbang bcu dang ni stobs bcu dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10123: mi 'jigs pa ni bzhi dag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10124: bsrung pa med pa rnam gsum dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10125: dran pa nyer bzhag rnam gsum dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10126: snyel ba mi mang'i chos dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10127: bag chags yang dag bcom pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10128: skye ba thugs rje chen po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10129: thub pa kho na'i ma 'dres chos //
NK124(ngo)001:10130: bco brgyad bshad pa gang yin dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10131: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen nyid dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10133: de rnams kyis dbu' ma'i don bshad zin to //
NK124(ngo)001:10134: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:10135: dbu' ma'i theg pa'i rnam par bzhag pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:10136: gnyis pa dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la yang gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10138: gsang sngags kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10139: bye brag so so nas bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10140: dang po ni la la dag gzhi 'bras nas khyad par med de /
NK124(ngo)001:10141: thabs lam gyi khyad par yod zer ba de mi 'thad de /
NK124(ngo)001:10142: shes bya gshis yin tshul nas 'khor 'das lam gsum
NK124(ngo)001:10143: gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la khyad par med
NK124(ngo)001:10144: na / lam la khyad par yod pa 'gal la /
NK124(ngo)001:10145: de rtogs shing mngon du gyur ba'i cha nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10146: gzhi lam 'bras gsum ka la khyad par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:10148: gsang sngags kyi sgra 'jug pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10149: don dam gyi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:10151: don dam pa na rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis su
NK124(ngo)001:10152: med pa la kun rdzob rgyu lam du byed cing
NK124(ngo)001:10153: / mtshan nyid ma 'dres pa gtso bo ru ston pa ni rgyu mtshan nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:10154: 'bras bu lam du byed cing dbyer med gtsor ston pa ni 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10155: po pi ti ka ra las /
NK124(ngo)001:10156: don gcig la yang ma rmongs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:10157: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10158: dbang po rno po dbang byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10159: sngags kyis theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:10161: gnyis pa don dam gyi khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10162: shes bya'i gzhi la gting phyin par rtogs ma rtogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10163: 'bras bu lam du byed mi byed kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10164: 'bras bu 'dus byas ma byas kyi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:10165: de rnams kyi khyad par rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10166: gnyis pa bye brag so so'i bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10170: khrus dang gtsang sbra la gtso bor ston cing lus
NK124(ngo)001:10171: ngag yid gsum dka' spyad la gnas pa'i phyi rgyud
NK124(ngo)001:10173: rang gi ngos la dbye ba med kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:10174: yul gdul bya'i rnam pa gsum du snang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10175: de nas lus kyi bya ba gtsor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud /
NK124(ngo)001:10176: lus ngag gi bya ba ting nge 'dzin mnyam du spyod pa'i rgyud /
NK124(ngo)001:10177: nang gi ting nge 'dzin gtsor ston pa rnal 'byor yo ga'i rgyud /
NK124(ngo)001:10178: de yang brjod bya'i rgyud gzhi lam 'brel chags shing
NK124(ngo)001:10179: rjod byed phun sum tshogs pa lnga 'dzoms pa rgyud
NK124(ngo)001:10180: kyis dngos po rnams ma tshang ba med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10181: des 'dul ba'i gdul bya blo'i bye brag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10182: dbang po 'bring la yang gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10185: 'bring gi mchog /'dul ba'i thabs la yang gsum du snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10187: dka' thub rig byed theg pa yang /
NK124(ngo)001:10188: yul gyis rnam pa gsum nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:10189: bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK124(ngo)001:10190: gdul bya blo'i bye brag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10191: 'bring po nyid la'am rnam gsum te //
NK124(ngo)001:10192: tha ma 'bring dang mchog tu snang //
NK124(ngo)001:10193: 'dul thabs de bzhin gshegs pas bye brag gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:10195: gnyis pa bye brag bya ba'i rgyud la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:10204: spyod dang tshul khrims lam gyi yun //
NK124(ngo)001:10205: 'bras bu dag dang bdun du bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:10211: kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor dang don dam sems nyid
NK124(ngo)001:10212: skye 'gag gnas gsum 'gro 'ong gi mtha' dang bral
NK124(ngo)001:10213: ba'i rang bzhin bden gnyis dbyer med kyis sgor 'jug
NK124(ngo)001:10216: bden gnyis dbyer med sgo nas 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:10218: gnyis pa khyad par bya rgyud rang gi 'jug sgo ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10219: lus dag pa mi dge ba gsum spangs /
NK124(ngo)001:10220: ngag dag pa mi dge ba bzhi spangs /
NK124(ngo)001:10221: yid dag pa mi dge ba gsum spangs pas rnam par dag pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10224: yid thugs kyis rang bzhin du 'jug pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10226: khyad par bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10227: lus ngag yid gsum rnam dag pas //
NK124(ngo)001:10228: sku gsum thugs kyi rang bzhin 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:10230: rdzogs chen nges don 'dus pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:10231: dag pa gsum gyi sgor zhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10232: yo byad phyi la gtsor 'dzin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:10234: spyi don gnyis pa lta ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10238: snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad don dam
NK124(ngo)001:10239: par ngo bo nyid kyis ma grub pas yod med
NK124(ngo)001:10240: la sogs kyi mtha' dang bral zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10241: de nyid ma rtogs pa'i snang ngor sgyu ma rmi
NK124(ngo)001:10242: lam gyi tshul du 'khrul snang ma 'gags pa'i rnam
NK124(ngo)001:10243: par snang dus / don gyis rang bzhin de bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:10244: gshegs pa'i dgongs pa 'bras bu rigs gsum gyi dkyil
NK124(ngo)001:10245: 'khor ye nas chu dang rlan bzhin du gnas so
NK124(ngo)001:10246: par snang dus / // de nyid las /
NK124(ngo)001:10247: lta ba snod bcud chos 'di rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:10248: don dam spros bral mtha' dang bral ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:10249: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:10250: 'khrul pa'i ngo la cir snang yang //
NK124(ngo)001:10251: de bzhin gshegs pa ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10252: 'bras bu ngo bo ye nas gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:10253: chu dang sher ba ci bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:10255: don dam sems nyid dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:10256: de ldogs pa'i yon tan kun rdzob rigs gsum ltar snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10258: dmigs pa phra mo bya ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10259: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10260: rig phyir ye shes gzhan la min //
NK124(ngo)001:10262: gleng glang snang ba'i ye shes kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:10263: mthong ba'i dngos po mtho' mjal rtsub //
NK124(ngo)001:10264: drug phyed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK124(ngo)001:10265: mthong bas rnam par dag par lta //
NK124(ngo)001:10267: gnyis pa spyi'i lta ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10268: mtshan nyid las 'phags pa'i gsang sngags kyi lta ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10269: rnam pa kun dang ldan pa'i rnam kun mchog ldan
NK124(ngo)001:10270: de la gzhan pa'i kun rdzob med par 'dod de
NK124(ngo)001:10272: bden gnyis ye nas dbyer med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:10273: gsang sngags spyi'i lta ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:10276: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK124(ngo)001:10277: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK124(ngo)001:10278: lta ba mtho' dman de tsam mo //
NK124(ngo)001:10282: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10283: yin phyir ngo bo tha dad med //
NK124(ngo)001:10284: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:10285: gnyis pa b+hee pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10289: dmigs pa phra mo bya ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10290: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10292: lta ba gcig char du 'dod pa /
NK124(ngo)001:10293: b+hee pa gcig char du grol bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:10294: mi g.yo' rtogs pa rdo rje chen po'i rgyud las //
NK124(ngo)001:10295: snang srid chos skur sems kyis gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:10297: yul rtogs cir snang ci gyur yang //
NK124(ngo)001:10298: dgag cing spang du ci yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:10300: rtogs pa rags pa'i ngo bo 'di nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10301: rim gyis sbyangs pas mi sbyang ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10302: sems kyis rang bzhin shes pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:10303: skad cig gis ston chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:10304: sems ni ma bcos 'od gsal ba //
NK124(ngo)001:10305: cir snang ci srid ci 'byung yang //
NK124(ngo)001:10306: rang 'byung rang snang ngang gis mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:10308: gnyis pa rim skyes pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10312: rtogs pa'i ngang las bying rgod kyi dbang du ma
NK124(ngo)001:10313: shor bar nyams su blangs pas rim gyis rtogs pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:10314: ye shes 'phel te sangs rgyas gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:10316: de ltar shes na ci la yang //
NK124(ngo)001:10317: mi bsam ma yengs par bzhag ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10318: bying rgod dbang du ma btang na //
NK124(ngo)001:10319: rang dbang med par don rig cing //
NK124(ngo)001:10320: nang nas ye shes 'od shar ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:10321: sems la rig pa'i nyams myong 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:10322: yun ring ba ni gnas pa'i mthus //
NK124(ngo)001:10323: mi g.yo'i ye shes shugs kyis skye //
NK124(ngo)001:10324: ye nas sangs rgyas ngo bo 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:10325: the tshom med par mthong bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10327: gnyis pa lha b+hee pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10328: bdag dam tshig gi sems dpa' b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10329: lha ye shes sems dpa' b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10330: cho ga'i yan lag bcu gcig b+hee zhing sgrub par byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10331: dang po ni rang gi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs su b+hee pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10333: bsod nams kyi mchog nas swa b+ha was stong bar sbyangs pas chos nyid kyi lha'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10334: stong pa'i sgra grags pa sgra snyan gyi lha /
NK124(ngo)001:10335: yig 'bru dngos su byung ba gsung yig 'bru'i lha /
NK124(ngo)001:10336: gdan zla ba las byung gdan gyi lha /
NK124(ngo)001:10337: de'i steng du sa bon phyag mtshan byung ba phyag mtshan gyi lha /
NK124(ngo)001:10338: de la rigs gsum gang mos kyis lhag gis skur bskyed pa sku'i phyag rgya'i lha'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10340: bya ba'i rnal 'byor bsam gtan ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10341: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsum thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:10342: drug gis 'jug pa'i tshul nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10345: gnyis pa ye shes sems dpa' ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10346: mdun gyi nam mkha' la ye shes pa spyan drangs tshul ni bkur 'os jo bo'i tshul drangs na /
NK124(ngo)001:10347: phyag 'tshal la sogs yan lag bdun gyis tshogs bsags
NK124(ngo)001:10348: cing rang gis smin mtshams kyi thad kyi nam mkhar
NK124(ngo)001:10352: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa rgyun mi bcad //
NK124(ngo)001:10353: dngos grub blangs te gtang rags gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:10355: bdag gis thugs ka'i sngags 'phreng gis 'phros pas ye shes sems dpa'i mthar thim par bsam /
NK124(ngo)001:10356: de ltar b+hee zlas byas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:10357: sngags brgya stong la sogs zlas dus /
NK124(ngo)001:10360: mi tshig gis bar ma chod par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10361: rjes su gtang rags gtong zhing dngos grub blangs nas gsol ba gdab /
NK124(ngo)001:10365: mi dmigs pas rgyas gtab rnams ni spyi mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:10367: ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10368: bkur 'os jo bo'i tshul nyid du //
NK124(ngo)001:10369: mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan 'dren te //
NK124(ngo)001:10370: phyag 'tshal la sogs yan lag bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:10371: bsod nams tshul du tshogs bsags shing //
NK124(ngo)001:10372: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa rgyun mi bcad //
NK124(ngo)001:10373: dngos grub blangs te gtang rags gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:10380: phud ma nyams pa la spyod /
NK124(ngo)001:10381: sha chang sgog gsum la sogs pa'i rku ba'i zas spang /
NK124(ngo)001:10382: lha'i dri ma mi 'goms shing nye dang thor 'thung bya ba la sogs pa'i /
NK124(ngo)001:10384: khrus dang gtsang sbra'i spyod pa la 'bad //
NK124(ngo)001:10387: bya ba'i rgyud kyis spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10388: dag pa gsum gyis mtha' bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10389: khrus dang gtsang sbra bder spyod do //
NK124(ngo)001:10390: zhag grangs dus tshod gza' rgyu skar //
NK124(ngo)001:10391: gtsang ma'i yo byad la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:10396: bya ba bsrung ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10397: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK124(ngo)001:10398: spyi'i sdom brtson mi gshig cing //
NK124(ngo)001:10399: lus ngag yid gsum dam tshig dag /'da' bar mi byed yan lag bcas //
NK124(ngo)001:10400: bye brag tshul du gnas pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:10402: bya rgyud kyi dam tshig ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10403: so so thar pa rigs bdun dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10404: byang chub sems dpa' pa smon 'jug gnyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10405: theg pa 'og ma'i sdom pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10406: tshul khrims yar ldan du bsrung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10407: khyad par bya ba rang gi thun mong ma yin
NK124(ngo)001:10408: pa lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs las
NK124(ngo)001:10409: mi 'da' ba'i rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig
NK124(ngo)001:10410: bsrung tshul lo // drug pa lam yun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10414: ring ltar thogs na mi tshe bcu drug gam /
NK124(ngo)001:10415: yun thung na mi tshe bdun gyi bar du /
NK124(ngo)001:10416: rgyal rigs dang bram ze gtsang ma la sogs 'dod
NK124(ngo)001:10417: khams gzugs khams kyi lus rten gtsang ma'i rigs su
NK124(ngo)001:10418: 'gyur nas / theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyis 'jug nas rig 'dzin gyi sa la sbyor ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10421: ring ltar mi tshe bcu drug gis //
NK124(ngo)001:10422: rgyal rigs bram ze gtsang ma dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10423: 'dod pa'i lha dang gzugs kyi khams //
NK124(ngo)001:10424: gtsang ma'i lus 'dzin gsang sngags kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10425: theg pa chen por bsgrub par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10428: de ltar zag bcas kyis lam la mi tshe mthar phyin nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10429: zag pa dang bral nas rang gi lha'i sku nyid brtan pa thob cing /
NK124(ngo)001:10431: lus yi dam lha'i sku snang nas 'og min dga'
NK124(ngo)001:10432: ldan la sogs par rnam par bsags pa'i zhing khams
NK124(ngo)001:10434: de nas mi'i skye ba bcu drug tshun chad kyis rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa non te /
NK124(ngo)001:10441: rdo rje'i sku dang dbyer med lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10443: rigs kyi rdo rje 'dzin gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10445: bcu drug mtha' la zag bral nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10446: rang gi lha'i sku nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10448: rnam dag zhing du rab snang ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10449: brgya' phrag bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10450: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa non te //
NK124(ngo)001:10451: sku lnga lhun gyis grub par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10453: theg pa'i shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:10454: bya ba rgyud kyi rnam par dag pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:10455: gnyis pa spyod rgyud kyi theg pa la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:10459: lus ngag yid kyi spyod pa gtsor ston pa'i theg pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10460: dbang po 'bring gi 'bring du gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10462: spyod pa'i rnal 'byor bye brag bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:10465: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:10467: 'jug sgo spyod dam tshig gsum bya ba'i rnal 'byor dang mthun la /
NK124(ngo)001:10468: lta ba rnal 'byor yo ga mthun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10470: 'jug sgo spyod pa dam tshig gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:10471: bya ba'i rnal 'byor dag dang mtshungs //
NK124(ngo)001:10475: de nyid gzhi'i tshul du b+hee pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10476: bdag gi de kho na nyid dam tshig gis sems dpa' skyed /
NK124(ngo)001:10477: lha'i de kho na nyid ye shes sems dpa' spyan 'dren pa nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10478: smin mtshams kyi thad sor bzhag pas /
NK124(ngo)001:10479: ting nge 'dzin gyi de kho na nyid bdag dang
NK124(ngo)001:10480: thugs ka nas zla ba dang yig 'bru sngags 'khor
NK124(ngo)001:10481: skor bas / sngags kyi de kho na nyid sngags 'phreng las 'od zer 'phros /
NK124(ngo)001:10482: ye shes sems dpa' thams cad bskul /
NK124(ngo)001:10483: tshur 'dus dngos grub brtsol bar bsam /
NK124(ngo)001:10485: bsam gtan rnam snang ting 'dzin las //
NK124(ngo)001:10486: de nyid gzhi'i tshul dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:10487: bsnyen sgrub yan lag rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10494: nye na mi tshe lnga nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10495: zag med la sbyor bar byed de /
NK124(ngo)001:10496: de'i skye ba'i khyad par ni bya rgyud dang mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:10498: zag bcas de nyid mthar phyin nas las dang nyon mongs khams kyi zag pa gsum zad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:10499: sku phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin par 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:10500: de nas mi tshe bcu drug tshun la /
NK124(ngo)001:10501: rigs gsum dbyer med pa'i rang gzhi rnam par snang
NK124(ngo)001:10502: mdzad kyi sku rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa mngon du
NK124(ngo)001:10504: zag bcas sa la mi tshe bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:10505: skye bo gong dang 'dra ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:10506: de mthar zag gsum zad gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10508: bsam gtan lam la rnam gnas te //
NK124(ngo)001:10509: brgya phrag bcu drug tshun chod kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10510: rigs gzhi rdo rje 'chang gi sa //
NK124(ngo)001:10511: 'bras bu thob pa gdon mi za' //
NK124(ngo)001:10513: theg pa'i shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:10514: spyod rgyud kyi rnam par dag pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:10515: gsum pa rnal 'byor yo ga'i theg pa la bdun las /
NK124(ngo)001:10517: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyi sgor 'jug pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10519: dka' thub dka' spyad 'dir mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:10520: khrus dang gtsang sbra 'dir mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:10521: sangs rgyas thams cad sangs rgyas cher //
NK124(ngo)001:10528: don dam dbyings ye shes dbyer med pa'i mtha' bral chen po chos kyi skur ston pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10529: de nyid rtogs pa'i byin rlabs kun rdzob rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10531: rnal 'byor gnyis dbang smra gzhung ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10532: thams cad sems kyi rlab snang phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:10533: de nyid mtha' stong rigs gsal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:10534: rgyu rkyen ma byas mtha' bral ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:10535: rang bzhin chos kyi sku nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:10536: kun gzhi sems 'dun tshun bzhag tu //
NK124(ngo)001:10537: chos kun snang ba'i byin rlabs dril //
NK124(ngo)001:10538: rdo sogs rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK124(ngo)001:10539: sangs ma rgyas pa med pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10540: rang bzhin stug po bkod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10543: pha rol nang dang gnas 'di kun //
NK124(ngo)001:10544: yul dngos ma skye chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:10545: 'dzin pa bdag med ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10546: de nyid ye nas dbyer med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:10547: rnal 'byor zhes bya'i lta ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:10550: rtogs pa'i don la mngon par byang chub pa lngas nyams su len te /
NK124(ngo)001:10551: de yang sems 'gags pa med pa ni so sor rtogs pa'i rigs pa byang chub pas /
NK124(ngo)001:10552: de la yig 'bru' a las zla ba tshes pa
NK124(ngo)001:10553: je cher la gnas sam gang bar bsam pa ni
NK124(ngo)001:10554: sems bskyed pa la byang chub pa /
NK124(ngo)001:10555: de las sems kyi ngo bo h'u du bsam pa
NK124(ngo)001:10556: ni chos nyid rgyud gnas pa la byang chub pa
NK124(ngo)001:10557: / de las 'od 'phros 'dus pa la rdo rje
NK124(ngo)001:10558: rtse lnga pa gyen du 'greng bar gyur pa ni
NK124(ngo)001:10559: / / rten pa la mngon par byang chub pa /
NK124(ngo)001:10560: phyag mtshan gyi 'du 'phro las rnam par snang mdzad kyi skur b+hee pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10561: sku mthar phyin las mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10562: de nyid kyi ngang la rang nyid lha'i sku skyed pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10563: de las cho 'phrul bzhi'i rgyud sbyangs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10567: phyag rgya bzhi'i cho 'phrul gyi sgo nas sems can gyi rgyud sbyangs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10568: dam tshig pa skyed pa de la ye shes sems
NK124(ngo)001:10569: dpa' yul nas gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis brten
NK124(ngo)001:10571: phyag 'tshal la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i dngos po dkar gsum la sogs pa mchod /
NK124(ngo)001:10573: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yi //
NK124(ngo)001:10574: rang gi lha yi sku bskyed de //
NK124(ngo)001:10575: tshul khrims bzhi'i rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10576: dam tshig ye shes dbyer med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10578: de ltar dam tshig pa dang ye shes sems grogs
NK124(ngo)001:10579: pa'i tshul du cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs par nyams
NK124(ngo)001:10580: su len no // gong gi lung de nyid las /
NK124(ngo)001:10581: rkyen lam rnal 'byor rnam gnyis kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10582: mngon byas lhun grub rnal 'byor ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10583: byin rlabs ya mtshan bsam yas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:10587: rang rig dngos stong mtshan ma gnyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10588: dbyer med 'bring dang ye shes las //
NK124(ngo)001:10589: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul lha //
NK124(ngo)001:10590: shar lta grogs po'i tshul du mchod //
NK124(ngo)001:10593: ting nge 'dzin gtso che bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:10595: spyod pa 'jig rten gtsor byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10598: ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i ngang nas ngag gi spyod
NK124(ngo)001:10599: pa ni bzlas pa sngags dang dbyangs la sogs pa'o
NK124(ngo)001:10600: // gar dang phyag rgya la sogs pa ni lus kyi spyod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10601: de dag 'dzoms nas bsgrub pa la 'og ma ltar rdzas dang yo byad dang gtsor ma gsungs kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:10602: 'byor pa mchod na mchog tu gyur par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:10605: thun mong du 'og ma'i so thar dang smon 'jug
NK124(ngo)001:10606: dang bya spyod kyi dam tshig yar ldan du gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:10607: pa ni bde gshegs rigs kyi dam tshig /
NK124(ngo)001:10608: rdo rje slob dpon rtag tu bkur zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10609: rdo rje dril bu thabs kyi brten du 'chang ba ni rdo rje rigs kyi dam tshig /
NK124(ngo)001:10611: mi 'jigs pa'i skyabs kyi sbyin pa ni rin chen /
NK124(ngo)001:10612: nyan thos dang byang chub sems gsang sngags phyi nang
NK124(ngo)001:10613: gsang gsum gyi theg pa'i chos la nyan bsam la
NK124(ngo)001:10615: 'phags pa'i tshogs la bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa ni las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK124(ngo)001:10617: bsrungs ba'i tshul khrims bye brag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10618: 'og ma rnams dang ldan bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:10619: rigs lnga'i dam tshig mchog tu basngagasa //
NK124(ngo)001:10620: sdom gsum mi spangs bder gshegs rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:10621: bla ma rdo rje dril bur ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:10622: rtag tu bkur 'chang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:10623: chos dang zang zing mi 'jigs byams //
NK124(ngo)001:10624: sbyin gsum ldan pa rin chen rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:10625: phyi nang gsang ba theg pa gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:10626: nyan bsam pad ma rigs kyi dam //
NK124(ngo)001:10627: 'phags tshogs rtag tu mchod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10628: las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK124(ngo)001:10630: drug pa lam gyi yun la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10634: rnal 'byor yo ga'i 'grod pa'i yun ring na mi tshe lnga /
NK124(ngo)001:10635: thung na mi tshe gsum gyi nang du sku phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin 'grub cing /
NK124(ngo)001:10636: de nas 'khor ba'i rgyu las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa zad cing dag nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10637: khams gsum du 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa dang bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10639: mi tshe gsum gyi nang rol du //
NK124(ngo)001:10641: las dang nyon mongs kun byang nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10642: khams gsum 'jigs dang zag pa bral //
NK124(ngo)001:10645: de nas zag med mthong lam nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10646: mi tshe bcu drug tshun la phra rags kyi sgrib
NK124(ngo)001:10647: pa rnams b+hee phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin
NK124(ngo)001:10648: gyis sbyangs nas / mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin
NK124(ngo)001:10649: gyi bar du nyams su blang pas stug po bkod
NK124(ngo)001:10650: pa'i sa la sbyor bar byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:10652: de tshe bcu drug tshun chod kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10653: phra rab shes bya'i sgrib sbyangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10656: gong ltar zag bcas zag med mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu stug po bkod pa'i sa non te /
NK124(ngo)001:10657: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su 'gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10659: gtsang ma'i rigs dag spang pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:10660: 'og min zhes bya'i nyams dga' de //
NK124(ngo)001:10661: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:10662: sprul pa po gcig 'dir sangs rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:10664: stug po bkod pa de la yon tan ci lta bu zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:10665: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:10666: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK124(ngo)001:10667: longs spyod zag med rin chen gter //
NK124(ngo)001:10668: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:10669: de dag gis don mdzad tshul ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10670: de tshe 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK124(ngo)001:10671: sdig spong gzugs su rnam par ston //
NK124(ngo)001:10672: dge tshul rnams la dgra bcom gzugs //
NK124(ngo)001:10673: rang rgyal rnams la bse' ru'i tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:10674: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:10675: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK124(ngo)001:10676: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:10677: byang chub sems kyi 'khor rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:10678: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10679: sku'i chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK124(ngo)001:10680: me long stan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:10681: dang po'i mdog ngan thams cad sel //
NK124(ngo)001:10682: 'khor gyis de bzhin kun ltas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10683: byang chub sems dpa'i sgrib dpag med //
NK124(ngo)001:10684: me long bzhin du sku la snang //
NK124(ngo)001:10685: de nas sa bcu rim gyis byang //
NK124(ngo)001:10686: bla med byang chub yang dag thob //
NK124(ngo)001:10688: theg pa thams cad kyis shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:10689: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi rnam par dag pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:10690: gsum pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10691: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nges tshig stan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10692: 'og ma rnams dang shan dbye' ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10693: lam mi mthun pa'i phyogs gol sgrib bsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10694: rtogs nas nyams su len pa'i rim pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10695: dang po ni ngo bo dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10697: dang po gsang sngags kyi ngo bo ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10698: sangs rgyas dang sems can kun gyis don gyi snying
NK124(ngo)001:10699: po gsang ba dam pa yin zhing rgyal ba kun
NK124(ngo)001:10700: gyi dam par basngagasa pas na gsang sngags so //
NK124(ngo)001:10703: blo thun mong rnams kyi spyod yul du ma gyur bas gsang ba /
NK124(ngo)001:10704: yon tan thams cad 'byung bas sngags so //
NK124(ngo)001:10709: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK124(ngo)001:10710: gsang sngags gsang ba'i snying po ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10711: sangs rgyas sems can kun gyis gsang //
NK124(ngo)001:10713: gsang ba zhes bya ni smrar med pa spyod yul du ma gyur ba la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10716: 'di ni gsang ba'i snying po ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10717: rdo rje sems dpa' de kho na nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:10718: nges pa'i ngo bo yin pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:10719: rgyal ba kun gyis dam par basngagasa //
NK124(ngo)001:10722: yon tan gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10724: gnyis pa 'og ma rnams dang shan 'byed pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10725: mdo' sde pha rol du phyin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10726: yo ga man chad nas kyang theg pa thod rgal ba gong ltar 'char bar gsungs pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:10728: theg pa re re'i sgor zhugs kyang gang gis phyogs
NK124(ngo)001:10729: 'dzin med par mnyam pa ris med du rtogs shing
NK124(ngo)001:10731: de tsho la khyad par 'dug pa ni ma dpogs so gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:10732: theg pa rang rang gi lugs la brten nas gzhi
NK124(ngo)001:10733: lam 'bras bu gsum ka la khyad par nyid rgyu
NK124(ngo)001:10734: lam du byas pas 'dus byas su 'gyur la /
NK124(ngo)001:10735: gsang sngags ni chos kun rang byung ye shes su yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:10736: de nyid ci lta ba bzhin du byas pas 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10738: mtshan nyid pas shugs kyis spang bya lhag ma dang
NK124(ngo)001:10739: bcas pa thob bya lhag ma dang bcas pa gong
NK124(ngo)001:10740: ma'i shugs kyis shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10741: gsang sngags sku gsum grangs mthun yang ngo bo khyad par yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:10742: de yang gnas lugs kun rdzob tu yang bden pa
NK124(ngo)001:10743: dbyer med dus gsum 'du bral med par rtogs pas
NK124(ngo)001:10744: 'bras bu rdo rje'i sku mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10745: chos kun shes bya lhag ma med par 'dus ma
NK124(ngo)001:10746: byas kyi ye shes lhun grub bdag nyid chen por
NK124(ngo)001:10747: rtogs pas / ngo bo nyid chos kyi sku thob pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10748: rgyas par rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10749: gnyis pa gsang sngags phyi nang gi khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10750: phyi nang gi rgyu mtshan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10752: don dam dbyings ye shes dbyer med tsam du rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:10753: kyang thams cad bdag nyid chen por ma rtogs pas
NK124(ngo)001:10754: / lha dang ye shes sems dpa' la dngos grub re zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10755: spyod pa blang dor byed pa ni phyi ma /
NK124(ngo)001:10756: chos kun bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas lha dang
NK124(ngo)001:10757: dngos grub kyang rig pa'i cho 'phrul las ma g.yos
NK124(ngo)001:10758: shing / spyod pa blang dor med par dam rdzas
NK124(ngo)001:10759: bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa la longs spyod pa
NK124(ngo)001:10760: shing / ni nang pa'o // gnyis pa khyad par la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10765: shes bya yin tshul la khyad par med la /
NK124(ngo)001:10766: de nyid theg pa'i 'dod lugs la khyad par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:10767: sngags phyi pa don dam dbyings ye shes gnyis su
NK124(ngo)001:10768: med pa'i rnam par snang mdzad la sogs par 'dod
NK124(ngo)001:10769: la / kun rdzob ni de'i byin rlabs dag pa dang ma dag pa gnyis su 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10770: nang pa'i ma h+aa yo ga yang bden pa gnyis dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10771: kun rdzob tu yang 'khor 'das gnyis su med par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10773: thabs kyi theg pa chen po ni //
NK124(ngo)001:10774: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK124(ngo)001:10775: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK124(ngo)001:10776: lta ba mtho' dman de tsam mo //
NK124(ngo)001:10783: gshis 'dod tshul gyi khyad par bzhin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10784: de rtogs pa'i lta ba la yang khyad par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:10785: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:10787: gsang sngags pa mtshan nyid don dam gyi phyogs su lhung la /
NK124(ngo)001:10788: mtshan bcas kun rdzob phyogs su lhung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10789: de yang dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa tha
NK124(ngo)001:10790: dad par 'dod cing dngos grub gzhan nas re ba
NK124(ngo)001:10791: dang bcas pa'o // nang ba'i bden pa dbyer med bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:10792: lha la sogs pa thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul rang snang yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10793: dngos grub gzhan nas re ba'i rtsol ba med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10795: phyi pa dag ma dag gnyis su phye nas blang dor rtsol ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10796: nang pa ni chos sku bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas spyod pa blang dor med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10798: grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10799: ngo bo 'dus byas ma byas kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10800: dgongs pa'i tshul gyi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:10802: yo ga rigs lnga thob kyang sku gsum las med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10803: nang pa ni sku lnga lhun grub mngon du gyur bas thob bya lhag ma med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10805: phyi pa dngos grub gzhan la re zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10806: rtsol bas bsgrub pas 'dus byas yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:10808: bdag nyid chen por ye nas sangs rgyas pa nyid mngon du gyur pas 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10809: gsum pa dgongs pa'i tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10810: phyi bas ngo bo gcig kyang sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres par 'dod la /
NK124(ngo)001:10812: thun mong ma yin pa'i dbyer med chen por ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par bzhugs so //
NK124(ngo)001:10813: spyi don gsum pa lam gyi gol sgrib bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10814: gong ma dang bye brag phyes te bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10816: rdzogs pa chen po theg chen kun gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:10817: gong ma'i don ma mthong bas sgrib pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10818: gong mas 'og ma'i las spyad gol ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10821: chos kun snying po byang chub sems gcig la //
NK124(ngo)001:10822: gcig la rnam par bgrang ba'i gol sgrib byung //
NK124(ngo)001:10823: 'grod du med pa bsgrod pa'i gol sa byung //
NK124(ngo)001:10824: dmigs pa med pa ltas pas ma mthong sgrib pa byung //
NK124(ngo)001:10826: lam yin min 'dra la min pas na gol sa /
NK124(ngo)001:10827: gong ma'i don mthong dus med pas sgrib pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10836: spyir gol sar ltung ba'i sgo dgu la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10837: mu stegs kyi lta bar gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10838: zhor 'byung gi mu stegs su gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10839: theg pa 'og ma 'og ma gong ma gong ma'i gol sa dang lam stegs su bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10840: mu stegs dang zhor 'byung sngar nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:10841: khyad par du gsang sngags kyi 'bras bu lam du byed pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10843: bdag nyid chen por yin pa la sogs pa'i gzhung las /
NK124(ngo)001:10844: phyogs re tsam 'dra ba la don log par go ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10845: mu stegs grangs can pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10847: rigs byed kyi mtha' gsar bar smra ba'i sde pa la sogs pa'i 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10848: mthun par gol ba rnams kyis dmigs shes par byas la gol bar spyad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10849: hril dril na grub mtha' las log cing gol ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10850: chos thams cad dgos byed dgongs gzhi mtha' bzhi rang grol du gsungs pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:10851: zhe 'dod kyis phyogs rer bzung nas gol ba la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:10852: stong nyid thal drag chad par gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10853: chos nyid thal drag dang sa por dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10854: bden gnyis thal drag gzung 'dzin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10855: dbyer med thal drag dmugs rtul mtha' la thug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10859: chos thams cad stong nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10860: rang bzhin med pa la sogs pa gsungs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10862: 'gro drug a mthas zhen par kha ma'i 'dzin pa grol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10863: dgongs gzhi sems nyid rang snang la dngos po dang
NK124(ngo)001:10864: mtshan ma'i sel med pa la dgongs nas gsungs pa'o
NK124(ngo)001:10865: // de ltar ma shes te yang dag pa'i phugs stong pa cang med du 'dod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:10866: mu stegs chad pa'i mthar gol ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10868: stong par rtag pa don la 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:10869: mu stegs chad par lta ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10870: tshig la khyad yod don la med //
NK124(ngo)001:10873: stong pa nyid du mu chad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:10874: chad pa'i lam chen nyid du 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10875: de nas slar yang 'phos pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:10879: thams cad 'dod nas dag pa'i blo yul min //
NK124(ngo)001:10880: de ni chad pa'i mtha' ste grol ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:10881: ces pa la sogs bka' rgyud du ma nas de nyid gol zhing dmyal bar 'gro bar gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:10883: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10884: snang ba 'di chos nyid yin pa lo sogs pa gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:10886: sangs rgyas gzhan nas tshol ba'i gol ba 'gag cing /
NK124(ngo)001:10887: snang sems gnyis med chos sku chen por ngo sprad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10888: dgongs gzhi chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su
NK124(ngo)001:10889: ye nas sangs rgyas shing snang chos nyid rang snang
NK124(ngo)001:10890: ba la dgongs nas gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:10891: de la 'khrul grol gyi shan ma phyed par gnyis
NK124(ngo)001:10892: 'dzin rang kha ma 'di kho na ltar sangs rgyas
NK124(ngo)001:10894: tshig tsam la dam par lta ba mchog tu bzung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:10895: theg pa gzhan dang nyams su myong ba rnams la lta ba dman zhes bskur ba 'debs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10897: chos dang sems nyid so sor mi 'gyur bas //
NK124(ngo)001:10898: de ni rtag pa'i mtha' de grol ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:10901: rang sems rgyun gyi rtag par 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:10902: bdag dang khas len mu stegs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10903: tshig la khyad yod don la med //
NK124(ngo)001:10906: lta spyod log pa'i nga rgyal can //
NK124(ngo)001:10907: ma bcos rang snang rol pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10908: rnam rtog zhen pas rtogs pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:10909: bye brag ma phyed rmongs pa'i blo //
NK124(ngo)001:10910: rdo la gser du 'dzin pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:10911: 'od gsal lhun grub rang snang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10912: rtag pa'i zhen pa bsres nas smra //
NK124(ngo)001:10913: ma bcos rig pa'i gding med par //
NK124(ngo)001:10914: lta ba yang rab mtho' 'dod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:10916: de'i dus kyi gang zag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:10917: sprel la g.yang du lhung ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:10918: rdo rje khams gsum ltung gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10919: byang chub sems dpa'i rigs dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:10922: dgos byed dang dgongs gzhi bden pa gnyis su phye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10924: bdag dang bdag gis 'dzin pa'i mdud pa grol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:10925: bdag med don dam stong nyid kyis rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10927: snang ba 'di la bdag dang bdag gis phyogs su bzung ba cha nas kun rdzob /
NK124(ngo)001:10928: de nyid bdag gam bdag gir stong zhing phyogs med rang snang ba'i cha nas don dam zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10930: de ltar ma ste don dam 'di nyid don dam min /
NK124(ngo)001:10931: 'di'i rang bzhin don dam yin ces pa la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:10932: 'di dang 'di'i rang bzhin du phye nas yin min
NK124(ngo)001:10934: gzung 'dzin gnyis med chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:10935: phra ba tsam ni rtag pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10936: rtag pa'i grub mtha' thams cad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10937: yang dag rtogs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:10940: chos gang sems kyi de nyid las //
