NK124(ngo)001:10941: gnyis dag mtha' ru gang lta ba //
NK124(ngo)001:10942: ma rig 'khrul pas phyin ci la sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:10944: don dam kun rdzob gnyis phye nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10945: dam pa'i rnam grangs skye med dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10946: gnyis med bsam 'das brjod pa tha snyad bral sogs /
NK124(ngo)001:10947: de kun thams cad blo'i yul yin te byang chub gegs //
NK124(ngo)001:10950: chos thams cad dgos byed dang dgos gzhi gnyis med dang dbyer med log pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:10951: dgos byed ni gzung 'dzin dang blang dor la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:10952: pa'i gol ba dgag cing yul sems gnyis su med
NK124(ngo)001:10954: dgongs gzhi ni chos kun sems nyid rang snang la
NK124(ngo)001:10955: gzung 'dzin log pa yin min gyi sel med pas
NK124(ngo)001:10956: na dgongs pa'o // de ltar rtogs te snang stong dang /
NK124(ngo)001:10957: bzang ngan la sogs pa gcig tu 'dres nas med
NK124(ngo)001:10958: par 'dod cing ma 'dres pa'i snang ba 'khrul bar
NK124(ngo)001:10960: bdag gzhan yod med la sogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10961: 'du shes gang du'ang mi skye ste //
NK124(ngo)001:10962: mi skye ba yang 'dod pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:10963: yod min med min mu rtug chad //
NK124(ngo)001:10966: kun du ma 'dres mi shes par //
NK124(ngo)001:10967: bzang po'i tshig la tho gtad nas //
NK124(ngo)001:10968: kun du bzod par khas len par //
NK124(ngo)001:10969: mun pa'i skye mched nyid du ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:10972: gnyis gcig gnyis med byas na de rang gnyis //
NK124(ngo)001:10973: gcig ste gnyis dang gnyis med bya byed 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:10974: byas pa'i gnyis med de yang 'khrul pa'i blo //
NK124(ngo)001:10975: de nas thun mong ma yin gnyis med de //
NK124(ngo)001:10976: gsang sngags zhes su rdo rje sems dpas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:10978: gnyis pa theg pa 'og ma gong ma'i lam rtags gol pa bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:10982: theg pa gong ma lam du 'jug nas 'og ma'i lta ba la ma rtogs par /
NK124(ngo)001:10987: sa dang rnam thar la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:10988: chos kun byang chub dkar ba'i lam mchog phyogs //
NK124(ngo)001:10989: kun kyang bsam du med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:10990: gol sgrib chen po nyid du 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10993: mun pa'i shes dang log sred dang //
NK124(ngo)001:10994: byis pa'i shes dang gso rig shes //
NK124(ngo)001:10995: mtha' dbus 'byed pa'i shes pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:10996: dam pa nyid kyis gol bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:10999: gong mar sems bskyed 'og ma'i snying rje skyed //
NK124(ngo)001:11000: 'og ma la nyams 'og ma'i lam du gol //
NK124(ngo)001:11002: sa la sogs pa theg pa gong ma la ltos
NK124(ngo)001:11003: nas 'og ma rnams gol bar bka' rgyud thams cad
NK124(ngo)001:11004: nas gsungs so // gnyis pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11005: 'og ma 'og ma la sbyor nas rim gyis gong ma la mos shing 'jug pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11006: lam stegs su 'gro bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:11008: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la //
NK124(ngo)001:11009: theg pa gcig gis 'bras bu gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11012: sa gnas khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:11013: gsang ba'i snying po 'gro ba'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:11017: theg pa gcig gis 'bras bu gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11018: lam stegs mngon du rdzogs par sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:11020: gnyis pa b+hee pa'i gol pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11021: lta ba log pa'i rjes su b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11022: lta med lo ka'i b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11023: theg pa 'og ma'i b+hee pa gol sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11024: lam stegs su 'gro ba gong gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11027: zhor 'byung la sogs lta ba log pa'i rjes su b+hee pa rnams yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11028: gong bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11030: lta ba bdag med la sogs pa'i don ma rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:11031: pas bsam gtan mnyam bzhag la gol ba la bzhi
NK124(ngo)001:11032: ste / dran pa rgyun 'gogs 'du shes med pa'i b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11033: snang ba rgyas 'debs yid spyod blo'i b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11034: bde' gsal nyams zhen bsam gtan bzhi'i b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11035: cang med stong b+hee skye mched mu bzhi'i b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11038: bde sdug ma dran btang snyoms ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11039: gzhi gnas ming btags gti mug ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11040: gang gis blo yang ma zhugs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11041: dge sdig gnyis su lung ma bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:11044: gnyis med ma rtogs dran rtogs med par b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:11045: 'du shes med pa'i khrod du de skye nges //
NK124(ngo)001:11049: rang rang snang srid dbyer med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:11050: rtogs nas blo yul ma zad na //
NK124(ngo)001:11051: bdag nyid blo yul byas pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:11052: nyams len thams cad bdag nyid 'ching //
NK124(ngo)001:11055: gong gi don ltar ma rtogs par //
NK124(ngo)001:11056: blo ngan mnyams pa'i khungs phyung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11057: ma rtogs le lo bsnyoms las byed //
NK124(ngo)001:11058: don ma grub par ngan song 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:11060: bsam gyis mi khyab ma shes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11062: blun rmongs mun 'khrul blo can de //
NK124(ngo)001:11063: long ba'i grong khyer chen por 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:11065: gong gi lta ba gol ba'i b+hee pa rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:11067: las dang gol sa bsam gtan gyis skabs su bshad pa bzhin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11069: rang sems ma rtogs rtsol ba de //
NK124(ngo)001:11070: yul gyis 'byung ba sems bsdus nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11071: gsal stong mnyam gzhag don tshol bas //
NK124(ngo)001:11072: dug lnga b+hee pa'i gang zag de //
NK124(ngo)001:11073: bying rgod 'phrang dgo bya ra mkhan //
NK124(ngo)001:11074: lta ba mi shes gti mug ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11075: gsal la mi rtogs 'dod chags b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:11076: bde' la zhen pa'i nga rgyal can //
NK124(ngo)001:11077: nyon mongs spang pa'i zhe sdang gis //
NK124(ngo)001:11078: rtsa dang thig le thabs b+hee nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11079: yul la dmigs pa'i thabs b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11083: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos rnams mtha' bral b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:11084: mtha' bral 'dod pa'i mtha' ste nam mkha' mtha' yas skye //
NK124(ngo)001:11086: 'di b+hee nges med gcig dang du ma bral //
NK124(ngo)001:11087: b+hee med blo yul cir yang med par skye //
NK124(ngo)001:11089: thams cad sems yin cir snang cir med na //
NK124(ngo)001:11090: rnam shes mtha' yas gnas su de skye nges //
NK124(ngo)001:11092: bdag gzhan yod med la sogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:11093: 'du shes gang du yang mi skye ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11094: mi skye ba yang 'dod pa min //
NK124(ngo)001:11095: yod min med min mu rtug chad //
NK124(ngo)001:11096: ces pa la sogs rgyud lung man ngag du ma nas gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:11098: lta ba log pa'i rjes su spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11099: theg pa 'og ma'i spyod par gol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11101: mu stegs kyi spyod pa'i rjes su gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11102: zhor 'byung gi spyod pa log par gol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11105: theg pa 'og ma'i spyod par gol ba la spyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11108: spyi las rgyu 'bras khyad du bsad nas dge sdig 'chol bar spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11109: chos brgyad kyis kun nas slang ste tshul chos kyi rang bzang por 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:11110: brtson 'grus bor 'dod kyang rang 'ching zhing gzhan la gnod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11111: dus tshod dag ma 'brel smyo spyod la sogs pa byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11112: gnyis pa bye brag la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:11113: mdzad pa chos srol las log pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11114: rgyud pa bka' babs las log pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11116: bka' zung ro zung du 'chad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11117: mdos grags rtogs tshugs su dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11118: 'grel thig gtan pa'i skor du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11121: chos nyid kyi rgyud pa med pas phyogs gcig dam par lta zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:11122: rang dang mi mthun pa rnams /
NK124(ngo)001:11123: chos med ces bskur ba 'debs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11124: de ni chos spang ba'i las kyi ngan 'gror ltung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11125: rnal 'byor don yod spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:11126: theg pa la phyogs ris su bzung nas dmod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11127: nyams shing mnar med 'gro gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:11130: rgyal ba'i bka' lung phyogs med la //
NK124(ngo)001:11131: ma rtogs phyogs dang ris bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11132: phyogs re rgyu 'bras sgrub byed kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11133: phyogs med rgyu 'bras ma shes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11135: rgyal ba'i bka' la smod cing spong //
NK124(ngo)001:11136: de'i bskal par dka' spyad kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11139: gnyis pa ni lung man ngag nyams myong gi cho
NK124(ngo)001:11140: med par gang zag gi rtogs spyod kyis yin min
NK124(ngo)001:11141: du 'dzin cing lung gi phyogs la dreg pos bsres
NK124(ngo)001:11143: bstan pa nam mkha' 'dra ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:11144: mos pa tha dad par bzung na //
NK124(ngo)001:11145: yin dang min pa'i cha 'dzin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11148: sems dpa' yod dam med do zhes //
NK124(ngo)001:11149: byis pa rnams kyis rtsod par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:11150: mkhas pa ye nas rtsam dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:11151: yod med rtogs pa'i tshig mi brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:11154: chos la phyogs ris bzung ba yis //
NK124(ngo)001:11155: rtsod pa'i las su gyur ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11158: dam pa'i chos la rtsod phyir slob //
NK124(ngo)001:11159: skyon bcas nyon mongs nga rgyal 'phel //
NK124(ngo)001:11160: log rtog phyir rgyas rtogs ges bsreg /
NK124(ngo)001:11162: gsum pa ni tshig phyir 'brang nas tha snyad la
NK124(ngo)001:11163: sogs zhugs kyis tshig mang po shes kyang rtogs pa
NK124(ngo)001:11164: dang nyams myong gis bcud med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11166: rgyud kyis de nyid mi shes gtams rgyud rlung gis 'khor lo bskor //
NK124(ngo)001:11167: lung gis de nyid mi shes lung rgyal 'dam phur 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:11170: smra brjod tshig la gang dga' ba //
NK124(ngo)001:11171: gang gis dgongs pa dpag mi nus //
NK124(ngo)001:11172: tshig tshogs rgya' mtsho thos pa min //
NK124(ngo)001:11173: tshig gcig don thos thos pa'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:11176: zab mo'i gdams ngag la nyams myong gis dbang po
NK124(ngo)001:11177: med cing tshig the tshom la dam par bzung nas
NK124(ngo)001:11178: / rgyal ba'i bka' rgyud la dmod cing spong ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11181: rnal 'byor dbang phyug tshad ma rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:11182: phal cher mi gnas skabs dag tu //
NK124(ngo)001:11183: mi shes ngan rtogs can rnams kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:11184: log lta don slad gzhung bor nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11185: nor bas bdag gis sun 'byin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11187: bdag stong gzhan la smad pas log /
NK124(ngo)001:11188: de yang ci lta bu zhes na //
NK124(ngo)001:11190: rnal 'byor dpal sbyin bya ba zhig /
NK124(ngo)001:11191: don la blo shed ma byed zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:11192: bgrod kyis thabs la mi mkhas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11193: blo gros ngan pa'i gzhung bor nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11194: chos ma yin pa'i chos brjod cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11195: nges pa'i bgros ldan gzhan dag la //
NK124(ngo)001:11196: de ltar ma nges blo gros ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11197: bdag gis blo gros 'di min zhes //
NK124(ngo)001:11198: mngon pa'i nga rgyal cher spyod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:11199: de ni srid pa log pa'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:11203: man ngag lung la spyad rtogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:11204: snyan ngag bsdebs sbyor glu dbyangs slob //
NK124(ngo)001:11205: de dag spangs pa'i dmyal bar 'tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:11208: man ngag nges dang drod med par //
NK124(ngo)001:11209: nga'i bka' las bzang ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:11210: de skad zer zhing gzhan bslus nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11212: gnyis pa rgyud pa bka' babs las log pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11213: bcos ma sel dang bcas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11214: byin rlabs kyi na bun yal ba'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11215: bar chad bdud kyis khyer ba'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11216: rgyud pa lung gzhan du 'byin pa can no //
NK124(ngo)001:11218: khung nas khungs su rgyud pa'i drod med par /
NK124(ngo)001:11219: yig 'byams la rang bzo' bcos te /
NK124(ngo)001:11220: zab mo yin zhes gzhan bslu' bar byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11221: rnal 'byor don yod pa spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:11222: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' bcos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11224: phri skur byas na chos ci byas kyang 'bras bu med cing nyams so //
NK124(ngo)001:11226: sangs rgyas kyi bka' las thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa lta ci smos /
NK124(ngo)001:11227: sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:11228: tshig gis sgros bskur ma bcug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11231: mi shes log pa'i bshes gnyen ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11232: yang dag don dang mi ldan par //
NK124(ngo)001:11233: bcos mas dam pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11234: 'dra tshul log par ston pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11235: dam pa'i mdzod gnyer mi ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11236: snod mi ldan sems 'dod pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:11237: phrag dog sgog du bu rnams las //
NK124(ngo)001:11238: khyad par khyod min bya'o zhes //
NK124(ngo)001:11239: sgyu ma 'drid nor 'bras bu bslu byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11240: khung gis dbang lung ma thob par //
NK124(ngo)001:11241: tha snyad zung du byed pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11242: khe grags dbang gyur snod med la //
NK124(ngo)001:11243: bya sgron lta zhing bka' la 'jud //
NK124(ngo)001:11246: gsang ba'i man ngag ma go bar //
NK124(ngo)001:11247: slob bu ma byas slob dpon ring //
NK124(ngo)001:11248: khung nas rgyud pa'i man ngag la //
NK124(ngo)001:11249: ma nor yin par mi brtsi'i bar //
NK124(ngo)001:11250: rang bzo' kha tshab che ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:11251: yid ches byed cing dam par 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:11252: lta dman rnams kyis ngo bsrungs byed //
NK124(ngo)001:11255: byin rlabs kyis na bun dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11256: nyams myong gi chu rgyun chad /
NK124(ngo)001:11257: tshig tsam la brten te bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11259: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:11260: bla ma dag la ma brten na //
NK124(ngo)001:11261: gsang sngags gsang ba'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11262: rang dbang ma thob gzhan dbang bskur //
NK124(ngo)001:11263: mkhas pa dmod cing mnyam la 'dren //
NK124(ngo)001:11264: rang la don gyis gdengs med par //
NK124(ngo)001:11265: grags shing nga rgyal mkhas 'dod na //
NK124(ngo)001:11266: tshig tsam lung la khung phyung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11267: rtsal bshad tho zhes gzhung nyams byed //
NK124(ngo)001:11271: byin rlabs nyams myong chu rgyun chad //
NK124(ngo)001:11272: slob dpon ma brten dbang ma gnos //
NK124(ngo)001:11273: chos 'chad byed pa'i rnam smin ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11274: lcags kyi dra bar lus bcug nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11277: bdud kyis khyer zhing chos log ston par byed pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11279: rmongs pa mun par gang spyod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:11280: sngags pa bdud kyi las byed de //
NK124(ngo)001:11281: shi nas dmyal ba chen por 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:11284: bla ma grags pa chung ba la zhus nas /
NK124(ngo)001:11285: grags pa che ba la sogs pa la khung 'byin pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11286: rnal 'byor don yod pa spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:11287: gzhan man ngag can la zhus nas khung gzhan grags che ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11288: rang gang dad pa la 'dod pa rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11289: sangs rgyas kyis kyang rnam par smin pa la bros pa'i thabs med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:11290: 'bras bu mnar med pa'i sems can bskal pa tshad las 'das pa 'gro bar gsungs nas 'dug pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11291: de nyid du lta bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11293: gang gis man ngag khung sub cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11294: sgrang phyir khung 'byin che ngag can //
NK124(ngo)001:11295: bskal pa brgyad khrir sdug bsngal thob //
NK124(ngo)001:11297: spyi don bzhi pa 'bras bu'i gol sa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11299: log pa'i lta b+hee spyod pa rnams kyis ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11301: ngan song du 'gro bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:11303: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes shing //
NK124(ngo)001:11304: rang rig tshad dang mi ldan zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:11305: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma ma grol bas //
NK124(ngo)001:11306: rang gis gar skyes ma shes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11307: 'ol phyir phyogs su gang b+hee kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11308: long ba'i goms par zhen te phyal par gol //
NK124(ngo)001:11311: sbas pa'i don rnams smrar gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11312: spyod khong tsam du byed pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:11313: sku gsung thugs kyi slu byed yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11315: gzhan yang lung dpag tu med pa nas gsungs pas 'di nyid lta bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11316: gol sa ltung ba'i sgo dgu' ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11318: bdud dang srin po ru tra dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11319: bgegs chen can dang sho b+hee nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11320: ldan te gnod sbyin mu stegs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11321: dmyal bar chad pas ltung ba'i sgo //
NK124(ngo)001:11323: gzhan gyi bsam sbyor bzang po la bar du gcod
NK124(ngo)001:11324: cing bsam pa log pas bdud du ltung bar gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:11325: te / rang byung bde ba 'khor lo las /
NK124(ngo)001:11326: gzhan gyi bsam pa bzang po la //
NK124(ngo)001:11327: bar chad byed pa bdud yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:11328: ma rtogs ser sna byed pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11331: khro bo rang rgyud du b+hee pas srin po ltung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11333: bder gshegs rgyal ba b+hee bzlas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11334: cha mthun bcos pa'i cho 'phrul ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11335: gang gis der rtags der gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11336: las kyi srin po'i rig 'dzin yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11338: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:11339: mnyam nyid ma rtogs rang rgyud du //
NK124(ngo)001:11340: chags sdang pho tshod spyod pa'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:11341: dug lnga rang gar spyad nyes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11342: srin po'i sgo ltung rtag tu 'khor //
NK124(ngo)001:11344: lta ba log cing chags sdang rang gar spyod de /
NK124(ngo)001:11345: gzhan gyi slob dpon byas pas ru tra ltung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11347: ji bzhin ma nor ma rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11348: lta log gzhan gyis slob dpon byed //
NK124(ngo)001:11349: rang nyid mi shes gzhan sgrol ba //
NK124(ngo)001:11350: ru tra'i sgo ltung rtag tu 'khor //
NK124(ngo)001:11352: nges don 'dus pa gter gyi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:11353: lta ngan spyod ngan sna tshogs byed //
NK124(ngo)001:11354: rang gis ma shes gzhan sgrol ba //
NK124(ngo)001:11355: ru tra'i sgo ltung dmyal bar skye //
NK124(ngo)001:11357: sha khrag la sogs rang ga mar spyod cing gnod sems gegs su ltung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11359: sha khrag la sogs rdzas chen lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:11360: dngos po kho nar der brtag na //
NK124(ngo)001:11361: 'byung po khrag gis dri bsnams pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:11362: lus len rigs ni 'dzin pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:11364: nges don 'dus pa gter gyi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:11365: ma rtogs 'phrin las ci mkhas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11366: tshogs la mngon par 'dzin pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:11367: rang rgyud dam pas mngon zhen phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:11368: gegs dang bya rog mngon zhen ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:11370: khro mo la sogs dang rang rgyud du b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:11371: 'khor dang sde brgyad rigs su bcad pa sho gam can du ltung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11373: mtshan ma'i mgo' brnyan bla gtags can //
NK124(ngo)001:11374: de 'drar gang gis nges brten nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11375: sho gam gnas kyis gcan chen rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:11378: rang dbang ting 'dzin ma thob pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11379: sde la 'khor dang rigs su bcad //
NK124(ngo)001:11381: gcan chen sho gam dag tu ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:11383: zhi ba rang rgyud du b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11384: chags pa rang dgar spyad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11385: lha chen por ltung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11387: rgyan dang cha lugs thams cad kun //
NK124(ngo)001:11388: gang gis de dang der btag nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11389: bram ze mi sdug lus rig 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:11391: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo las /
NK124(ngo)001:11392: thabs lam dbang la khung byung ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11393: 'dod chags rang dgar gtan spyod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11394: bde ba ma zin bde la zhen //
NK124(ngo)001:11397: ging dang dbang phyug la sogs rang rgyud du b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:11398: 'phrag dog gis gnod sbyin du ltung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11400: las kyi dbang btsan bran mo'i tshogs //
NK124(ngo)001:11401: de 'dra nyid du nges bstan nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11402: gnod sbyin nag po'i tshogs su ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:11403: gzhan gyi tshe la 'tshe ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11406: gzhan gyi chos la 'phrag dog pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11407: yon tan du ma ldan gyur kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11408: rang sems snying po ma rtogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:11409: gnod sbyin sgor ltung rtag tu 'khor //
NK124(ngo)001:11411: lta ba log pa'i mu stegs su ltung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11413: ma rtogs pa dang bdag 'dzin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11414: gsang sngags lta spyod yin zer na //
NK124(ngo)001:11415: sems can srog la brtse' med spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:11416: mu stegs rtag chad sgor ltung 'khyams //
NK124(ngo)001:11418: tshig tsam la khung phyung nas dge sdig khyad par gsod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:11419: chags sdang rang gar spyad pas dmyal bar ltung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11422: spyod khung tsam du byed pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:11423: dmyal chen dmyal ba brgyad kyi yang //
NK124(ngo)001:11424: rdo rje dmyal ba chen por ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:11427: ma rtogs las kyi rtsing spyod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11428: lus ngag yid kyis len pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:11429: mi dge ba la spyod pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:11432: h'u la sogs pa'i yig 'bru rang rgyud du b+hee pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11433: sdug bsngal sdug pa can du skye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11434: chags pas mngal gyi srin bur skye ba la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:11436: de nas gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:11437: gol sa che bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:11439: spyi don gnyis pa sgrib pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11444: thog ma med nas bsags pa'i las kyi rnam pa ra smin pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11445: tshe 'di la myong gyur gyi las dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11446: phyi ma la myong gyur gyi las dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11447: lan grangs gzhan la myong gyur gyi las so //
NK124(ngo)001:11449: ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis nyon mongs pa dug lnga la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11451: shes bya shes su ma ster ba'i sgrib pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11452: shes pa'i don la 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11454: shes bya'i don de kho na nyid la sgrib pas sgrib pa'i /
NK124(ngo)001:11455: lhan cig skye ba'i sgrib pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11456: kun brtags kyi ma rig pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11457: rang gis rang la sgrib pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11458: log pa'i rkyen gyis rtogs su ma ster ba'i sgrib
NK124(ngo)001:11459: pa rnams gong gi gol sa rnams dang mtshungs so
NK124(ngo)001:11460: // gnyis pa shes bya'i don la 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11461: mthong lam mthong ba'i chos la ched du 'dzin pas kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11462: b+hee lam la b+hee pa cher 'dzin yod pas lhan cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11463: mthar lam la shugs las byung ba'i mnyam rjes cha phra mo zhig yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11464: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11465: de rnams rang rang gi skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11467: rtogs nas nyams su blang ba'i lam bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11471: bye brag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11472: lam dang lam gyi khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11474: skabs kyi gtso dang grogs kyi tshul /
NK124(ngo)001:11475: skabs kyi gtsor gyur pa la lam zhes bya la /
NK124(ngo)001:11476: de'i grogs byed pa'i ngos nas cha rkyen yin no gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:11479: de rkyen yan lag rnam gnyis te //
NK124(ngo)001:11480: sgrub byed rkyen dang shes byed rkyen //
NK124(ngo)001:11483: de'i cha rkyen yan lag gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:11484: rtogs par byed dang goms byed thabs //
NK124(ngo)001:11485: ngang las gnas pa'i bar chad bsrung //
NK124(ngo)001:11487: lam shes byed kyi yan lag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11491: spyir rgyud lung man ngag gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11492: de'i rjes su 'jug pa'i rigs pa la sogs pa rgyas par gzhung bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11493: bye brag tu 'og tu rang rang gi skabs su ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:11496: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam rdzas kyi dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11497: 'phrin las bsgrub pa'i las rim gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:11498: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye' ba bya //
NK124(ngo)001:11500: yongs su shes pa'i dngos po bdun la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11502: lam gyi yan lag sum cu gnyis //
NK124(ngo)001:11503: mdo' sde gzhi dang bslab pa'i gzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:11506: dbang dang dam tshig dkyil 'khor dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11507: 'phrin las rtogs tshad goms byed spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:11508: sa dang lam dag 'dir bzhag go //
NK124(ngo)001:11509: zhes klong dgu' nas kyang bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:11510: de tsho yang don 'dus bzhin 'dus te /
NK124(ngo)001:11511: de la gsang sngags kyi bkol mdo' bcu gnyis dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11516: mdo' ni bcu gnyis 'jug sgo dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11517: dam tshig lta ba ting 'dzin dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11518: dmigs pa bzlas brjod 'phrin las dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11519: spyod pa dang ni thob bya dbang //
NK124(ngo)001:11520: rig 'dzin pa dang sangs rgyas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:11521: nges 'byed yan lag dag tu bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:11524: gzhi' ni rnam bcu sgrub pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11525: gsang sngags mi dang spyod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11526: dngos grub gnas dang zlas pa'i smra //
NK124(ngo)001:11527: phyag rgya ting 'dzin lta ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11528: cho 'phrul dag de de ga don //
NK124(ngo)001:11529: dpe' bcus mtshon pas shes rab gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11532: slab pa'i mtha' ni rnam bcu' ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11533: dam tshig bzhi dang rgyud 'grol dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11534: sgo bsrung ba dang phul dbyung dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11535: thag gcad pa dang nyams blangs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11536: la dor spyod dang dbang rim dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11537: man ngag don dang mdor bsdus rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:11538: rnal 'byor slab pa'i mtha' bcur bzhed //
NK124(ngo)001:11540: gang ltar bshad kyang lam thams cad bslab pa'i mtha' bcur 'dus te /
NK124(ngo)001:11541: de yang dang po gzhi dam tshig gi sa gzhi gshin pa lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11543: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig las //
NK124(ngo)001:11546: lha mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11548: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa la sogs tshul bzhin du bsrung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11549: don du mi gyur ba thams cad bsrung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:11550: don 'gyur ci yang nyams su len pa bstan pa /
NK124(ngo)001:11552: dam tshig kun gyi thog ma ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11553: don du mi 'gyur kun spangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11554: don 'gyur ci yang nyams su blang //
NK124(ngo)001:11557: rtsa ba dang yan lag la sogs rang skabs su ston par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:11560: lhag pa'i don la rgyun du gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11563: gzhi 'dzin pa yi dam tshig ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11564: sgo gsum sdom par gnas pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:11565: rtsa ba yan lag la sogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:11566: bsrung dang bsgrub pa de nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:11568: gnyis pa rgyud thos bsam gyis dgrol ba gyi ling gi sgrog sgrol ba lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11569: gong du bshad pa'i bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11570: sgo gsum gyis mnyes par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11571: thos bsam gzhung bzhin du byas pa the tshom bsgro dogs chod /
NK124(ngo)001:11572: mi shes bcing ba kun grol nas /
NK124(ngo)001:11573: shes bya kun la thog med 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11575: dper na gyi ling sgrogs grol ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11576: rnam grol thos bsam b+hee mos kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:11577: shes rgyud kun grol thog med 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:11578: thob bam rgyud dkrol shin tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11580: gsum pa sgo kun nas bsdur ba bung bas rtsi tshol ba lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11581: mu stegs dang zhor 'byung gi mu stegs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11582: theg pa thams cad kyi lta spyod log pa kun shes par byas nas /
NK124(ngo)001:11583: mthar rang gi grub mtha' ma nor ba nyid rtogs par byed pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11585: dper na bung ba rtsi tshol ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11586: lta spyod sgo bstun bsdur byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11587: ma nor don nyid rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:11588: sgo rnams bsdur ba rab tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11590: bzhi pa phul du mkhas pas byung ba mtho' ri rtser phyin pa lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11591: shes rab kyi chos gang la'ang ma rmongs par shes shing /
NK124(ngo)001:11592: khyad par du sems kyi de kho na nyid la mkhas shing phul du byung bya ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11594: dper na mtho' ri rtser phyin pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11595: shes rab mtho' ri rtser phyin te //
NK124(ngo)001:11596: kun la mkhas shing phul du 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:11597: don la mkhas pa rab tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11599: lnga pa rim pa dbang gi bgrod pa rgyal bu dmangs su 'khyams pa rgyal sar ston pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11600: lam dang rtogs pa gong nas gong du 'phel ba /
NK124(ngo)001:11601: dbang la byung ba yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11602: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi dbang la sogs pa skur bas /
NK124(ngo)001:11603: ma smin pa smin par byas /
NK124(ngo)001:11604: ma grol ba grol ba byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:11605: rgyud gong nas gong du 'phar nas /
NK124(ngo)001:11606: chos kyi rgyal srid la dbang thob pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11608: rgyal bu rgyal sar ston pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11609: rim pa dbang gi khyad par te //
NK124(ngo)001:11610: sa lam rtsal gyis bgrod pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:11611: dbang rnams thob par rab tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11613: drug pa thag lta bas gcad pa khyung nam mkha' la lding ba lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11614: chos kun mnyam nyid rang snang du rtogs pas phyogs ris re dogs med par thag chod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11615: gang la'ang nyam nga med par byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:11617: khyung chen mkha' la lding ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:11618: theg pa'i 'jug sgo bsam yas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11619: mnyam nyid re dogs blang dor med //
NK124(ngo)001:11620: the tshom med pa shin tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11622: bdun pa don man ngag gis bsdu gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11623: snyan rgyud zhal gyi man ngag gis mngon du ngo sprod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11624: tshegs med cing bde blag tu gyur pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11626: sgyur ba sman snang gser 'gyur ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11627: sems kyi gsang 'di sus mthong pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:11628: man ngag can gyis 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:11629: man ngag ldan pa rab tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11632: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba rgya mtshor nor ldan gyi mi lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11633: shes kyang nyams su ma blangs na don mi grub cing /
NK124(ngo)001:11634: rtogs pa'i don dka' bas nyams su blangs pas rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:11635: pa mthar phyin te bdag gzhan gyi don rnams 'grub
NK124(ngo)001:11636: pa yin te / de nyid las /
NK124(ngo)001:11637: dper na rgya mtsho'i nor lan mi //
NK124(ngo)001:11638: nyams su ma blang nor med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11639: dka' bas nyams su don rnams 'grub //
NK124(ngo)001:11640: ting 'dzin sgom pa rab tu gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11643: la spyod pas dor ba glang chen chur zhugs pa lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11644: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11645: 'bras bu thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa thob
NK124(ngo)001:11646: par 'dod pa'i spyod pa dus dang 'brel par dka'
NK124(ngo)001:11647: bla gang la'ang nyam nga med par 'jug pa yin
NK124(ngo)001:11649: dper na glang chen chur 'jug ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11650: rtsal sbyangs pa yi bgrod tshul gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:11651: nyam nga bag tsha med pa ru //
NK124(ngo)001:11652: spyod pa dus dang 'brel pa gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11654: mdo' gcig tu 'dus pa mgron po byes logs nas slar rang khyim du 'ong ba lta bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11655: theg pa rnam grangs ci snyed cig gsungs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11656: lam ci ltar bgrod kyang sems nyid rtogs pa'i thabs su gsungs la /
NK124(ngo)001:11657: don sems nyid rtogs pa la thams cad 'dus shing rdzogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11659: dper na kun tu rgyu ba'i mi //
NK124(ngo)001:11661: yul gyi rnam pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11662: bgrod yul lam gnas gcig la med //
NK124(ngo)001:11663: de bzhin bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:11664: rnam grangs chos sgo ci snyed kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11665: bkri' bas grang ba'i tshig yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:11667: don rnams gcig tu bsdus nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11668: slab par bya ba dam pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11669: nges par gcig las med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:11670: kun 'dus dam pa bslab pa gces //
NK124(ngo)001:11672: gsum pa de'i ngang la gnas pa'i lam bar chad bsrung ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11673: bla ma dkon mchog la blo bkal nas gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11674: snying rje dang byams pas bgegs rigs la gtor ma byin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11675: bden pa'i stobs brjod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11676: mkha' 'gro chos skyong la gtor tshogs btang ste las bcol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11678: yi dam lha'i bzlas pa bya ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11679: rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan pa gang la yang nyam nga med par grogs su 'khyer ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11680: de rnams rgyas par rang rang gi gzhung dang bla ma'i zhal nas shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11681: gnyis pa lam gyi ngo bo ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11683: ngo bo shes rab rnams su nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:11686: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11688: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab la bya /
NK124(ngo)001:11690: 'jig ldang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:11691: nges par skye ba ngo bo yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11693: ngo bo sems lnga las bshad /
NK124(ngo)001:11695: rtogs nas 'dris pa gang byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:11696: lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems //
NK124(ngo)001:11698: lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems las bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:11699: de rnams gang la yang mi 'gal bar sems kyi 'phel rim du 'dus pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11703: de la thog mar bstan pa'am //
NK124(ngo)001:11704: skye ba rkyen gyis skye tshul dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11705: skye ba'i ngo bo sems dpa' dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11706: tha mar rang byung nyid kyis rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:11709: skye ba bzhi'i skye ba bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11711: skyes tshul lam rim pa ston pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11713: gzhi nas sems skye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11716: skye ba la nges pa nas skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11718: theg pa mchog phyir skye ba'am //
NK124(ngo)001:11719: mun pa long sres byis pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:11720: phyogs ris mtha' la dam pa phyes //
NK124(ngo)001:11721: drug pa rgyu rkyen dbang gis g.yo' //
NK124(ngo)001:11722: de las byung tshul rnam pa gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:11723: thog ma nyid nas rgyud pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11724: gzhi gnas ma nges gang byung bgrod //
NK124(ngo)001:11725: mtha' nas thog rtsir gcig char 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:11730: de la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK124(ngo)001:11731: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po rang la rang chas su gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11732: lhan cig skyes pa'i rgyu gong ma'i yon tan thob pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11734: gong ma la brod cing dad pa skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11736: rgyu'i rkyen snying po'i don gyis gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11737: rang rang gi sa la skye ba skyes pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11738: bdag po rkyen bla ma dam pa /
NK124(ngo)001:11739: dmigs pa'i rkyen gsang sngags kyi yon tan la sogs pa /
NK124(ngo)001:11740: mtshungs pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni snga ma snga mas go phyes nas /
NK124(ngo)001:11743: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11744: bshes gnyen mgon la chung yang thos //
NK124(ngo)001:11745: yon tan mthong dang skyon mthong dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11746: de'i skyo rmong brod dngas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11747: gnyis pa'i rgyu rgyu gsungs pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11748: de bas gsang sor dmigs pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11749: skad cig 'phel ba de ma theg /
NK124(ngo)001:11752: dpon slob gnyis las dang thugs rje'i 'brel pa yod /
NK124(ngo)001:11753: slob bu dang bstan pa'i chos gnyis snod bcud dam shes bya shes byed kyi 'brel pa yod /
NK124(ngo)001:11754: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum pa bdag nyid gcig pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:11755: ngo bo nyid kyi 'brel pa yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11757: de ltar rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pas gong bzhin sems lnga'i tshul du skye ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11759: de la g.yo' ba byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11760: gsang sngags don spros shing mos pa g.yo' ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11762: rtogs shing khong tu chud na ci ma rung mnyam pa'i 'dun pa dang smon pa byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11764: dngos su gsang sngags don gyi sgor zhugs pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11765: dbang 'gyur nas nyan bsam la sogs byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11766: gnas pa byang chub sems ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11767: rtogs shing dgos par byed pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11769: mthar phyin pa'i byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11770: stobs su gyur lam mthar phyin pas skyed byar med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11771: de yang snga ma snga mas go phye nas /
NK124(ngo)001:11772: phyi ma'i phyi ma'i don gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11774: snga ma snga ma gang dang gang //
NK124(ngo)001:11775: phyi ma phyi ma thabs dang rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:11776: de bzhin phyi ma phyi ma gang //
NK124(ngo)001:11777: snga ma snga ma ma byung 'bras //
NK124(ngo)001:11779: 'o na sems lnga lam gyi ngo bo yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:11780: sems lnga mthar phyin pas lam lnga mthar phyin nam ma phyin /
NK124(ngo)001:11781: mthar ma phyin na sems lam gyi ngo bo yin pas nyams la /
NK124(ngo)001:11782: phyin na tshogs lam lta bu'i sems lnga mthar phyin pas kyang lam lnga mthar phyin par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:11784: lam spyi'i sems lnga mthar phyin la /
NK124(ngo)001:11785: bye brag lam lnga mthar ma phyin no //
NK124(ngo)001:11786: yang sems lnga lam gyi ngo bo yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:11787: gcig char ba sems lnga las skye'am mi skye /
NK124(ngo)001:11788: ma skye na lam gyi ngo bo yin pa nyams la /
NK124(ngo)001:11789: skye na gcig char ba ma yin par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:11791: gcig char ba la sems skye yang don 'khor 'das dbyer med la dus myur bar skye ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11792: se gol gcig la'ang sems lnga skye bas gnyis ka'i skyon mi yong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:11793: gsum pa lam bgrod tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11794: dbang po rno brtul gyis rim skye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11796: theg pa'i rang rang gi skabs su 'og nas ston par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:11797: bzhi pa bye brag so so nas rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:11801: yod pa shes rab yod kyang thabs dang gdams ngag gtso che ba la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11803: yod pa thabs dang gdams ngag yod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:11806: khams ltag shal gyis gtag pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11807: de yang lta ba ni mi mthad de /
NK124(ngo)001:11808: spyir thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel pa dgos par bshad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11809: bye brag tu thabs rkyang pas mi grol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:11810: thabs la shes rab kyis grol dgos pa gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:11811: yang bye brag tu lta ba la sogs shes rab gcig pos grol la /
NK124(ngo)001:11812: thabs ched du mi dgos par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:11814: theg brgyad lam gyis gol sa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11815: khyed cag blo dman ma rig pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11816: thabs dang shes rab 'brel dgos zer //
NK124(ngo)001:11818: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:11820: steng sgo rlung 'khor gyis bde ba la brten nas ye shes skye ba 'bul ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:11822: 'og sgo phyag rgya'i bde ba la brten nas ye shes skye ba myur bas na /
NK124(ngo)001:11824: de ltar thabs lam la brten nas rig pa 'byongs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11825: shes rab kyi ye shes rang snang ngo sprod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:11827: zag bcas kyi bde ba zag med du gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:11828: ye shes rang gnas mngon sum du rtogs nas grol ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11830: bla ma'i dgongs pa rlung gis dus //
NK124(ngo)001:11831: sbyor ba'i thabs dang bsod nams las //
NK124(ngo)001:11832: phyag rgya yon tan ldan gyur pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11833: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa myong //
NK124(ngo)001:11834: de phyir thabs su bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11837: rol pa'i ka ra la sogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:11838: man ngag thabs kyis der 'jug dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11840: rgyas par gzhung man ngag dang bcas pa rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11841: gnyis pa grol lam la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:11849: gzhi gnas tshul rgyas par bshad pa ni gong nas brjod pa ltar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:11851: bden pa gsum du bstan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11857: chos thams cad rig pa byang chub kyi spros bral
NK124(ngo)001:11858: skye ba med cing snang la ngo bo nyid kyis
NK124(ngo)001:11859: rgyur gnas pa'o // rgyu 'bras rgyas pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:11860: phyogs bcu' ma lus thams cad la //
NK124(ngo)001:11861: rang byung chen po kun tu khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:11862: rang byung de nyid dngos med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11863: kun gyis phyag rgya rgyu yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:11866: gzhi 'gyur gzhi la g.yo med ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11867: snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:11870: don mchog lnga 'bras dbyings ye shes //
NK124(ngo)001:11871: bdun ni gsum phyir don dam las //
NK124(ngo)001:11872: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11873: de kun ngo bo nyid rgyur gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11875: de nyid chos kun cir snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:11876: rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul mi 'da' zhing ye nas chos sku chen por gnas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:11878: rang rig nyi ma'i ye shes nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:11879: dngos gnyis la sogs byed pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:11880: cho 'phrul nyid las mi zhen pas //
NK124(ngo)001:11881: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi rgya mtshor 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:11884: 'jig rten rten g.yo' la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:11885: snang ba nyid nas ngo bo med //
NK124(ngo)001:11886: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK124(ngo)001:11887: rang bzhin ngang gis de lta gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11890: kun rdzob rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:11891: rig pa sgyu ma'i cir snang zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:11892: de nyid phung po khams dang skye mched rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11894: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad la //
NK124(ngo)001:11895: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:11898: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11899: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK124(ngo)001:11902: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:11903: gzhi rdzogs phyag rgya ma 'dres bsal //
NK124(ngo)001:11906: cho 'phrul yul sems tshul nyid kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:11907: thabs dang shes rab mtshan nyid de //
NK124(ngo)001:11908: phung sogs yab yum dkyil 'khor du //
NK124(ngo)001:11909: rgyud min rang bzhin snang ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:11912: sems kyi spros bral skye ba nyid kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma'i ngo bor cir snang la /
NK124(ngo)001:11913: cir yang snang ba nyid don dam spros bral skye ba med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11914: de nyid tshig snga phyi ltar snang yang don la tha dad med de /
NK124(ngo)001:11915: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang rang grol du bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11917: gzhi rtsa las ni thams cad byung //
NK124(ngo)001:11918: med pa yod pa gnyis ka min //
NK124(ngo)001:11919: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med de //
NK124(ngo)001:11923: yul dang shes par snang ba yang //
NK124(ngo)001:11924: rang byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK124(ngo)001:11925: rgyu 'bras snang yang gnyis pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:11926: phyi nang snang ba'ang nang nyid dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11929: gnyis med byang sems ngo bo la //
NK124(ngo)001:11930: 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid ngang gis med //
NK124(ngo)001:11932: dbang po rab kyis tha ma ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa la'ang bdun du nges te /
NK124(ngo)001:11934: tha ma skyed pa'i rnal 'byor yang //
NK124(ngo)001:11935: bdun du nges par snang ba ste //
NK124(ngo)001:11947: dbang po mchog gi tha ma ni //
NK124(ngo)001:11948: lta spyod b+hee pa'i ched 'dzin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:11949: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:11950: smin grol thabs kyi bye brag kun //
NK124(ngo)001:11951: kun kyang thabs dang shes rab 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:11954: ma h+aa'i 'jug sgo thabs shes smin grol la sogs gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:11955: mnyam pa rig med kyi tshul du 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11956: gnyis pa lta ba la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:11958: gtan la dbab pa'i grub mtha' lta bas bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11961: gsang sngags mngon sum gyi tshad mas mngon sum du ngo sprad cing rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11962: he dus gtan la phab cing rtogs par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11964: stong thun gyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11965: gnyis pa he dus gtan la phab pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:11966: sngon byung sku lnga dang tshul mthun pa'i he du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11969: ngo bo nyid kyis sku'i gsung /
NK124(ngo)001:11970: ngo bo nyid kyi he dus go ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:11971: chos sku'i gsung gis tshul skye med don gyi go ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11972: longs sku'i gsung gi dgongs pa brda'i go ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11973: rdo rje'i gsung gi tshul grags stong dbyer med du go ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11974: sprul sku'i gsung gi tshul tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi go ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11976: rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:11977: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK124(ngo)001:11978: nges lung yin phyir chos tshur ston //
NK124(ngo)001:11981: chos kyi sku'i gsung lta bus //
NK124(ngo)001:11982: skye med don gyis gtan la dbab //
NK124(ngo)001:11983: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i gsung lta bus //
NK124(ngo)001:11984: dgongs pa brda'i gtan la dbab //
NK124(ngo)001:11985: sprul pa'i sku'i gsung lta bus //
NK124(ngo)001:11986: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gtan la dbab //
NK124(ngo)001:11987: rdo rje sku'i gsung lta bus //
NK124(ngo)001:11988: grags stong dbyer med gtan la dbab //
NK124(ngo)001:11989: la la ngo bo nyid kyi gsung ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:11990: snang srid mthong thos gtan la dbab //
NK124(ngo)001:11991: ces pa la sogs gsungs pas rgyas par der shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:11992: gnyis pa tshig gi he du la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:11993: dpyad du med pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:11994: dpyad du yod pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:11996: rtogs dpyod rtsis pa med par man ngag bstan pa
NK124(ngo)001:11997: tsam gyis rang snang yul med du go ba yin
NK124(ngo)001:11999: rtogs dpyod dmigs 'dzin mi tshor bar //
NK124(ngo)001:12000: de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:12002: dpyad pas go ba 'di la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12003: tshig don mi mthun pa'i he du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12006: don thun mong ma yin pa'i cir yang min pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:12007: he du ci yang min par gtan la phebs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12008: des mtshon ci yang min pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12009: bsam chos ci yang ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:12010: de phyir ma yin kun yin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12011: ci yang yin no lhun gyis grub //
NK124(ngo)001:12013: gnyis pa tshig don mthun pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12015: tshad ma bka' gzhung gtan tshigs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12016: sgra mthun don dpag he du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12019: gsang sngags rang gzhung gi he dus mngon du rtogs par byed pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:12021: go ba dang sgra mthun yang don khyad par 'phags te mngon sum du rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12022: rgyas par gzhung bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12025: ldems dgongs man ngag gtan tshigs gis //
NK124(ngo)001:12026: skabs kyi de nyid mthong bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:12027: dngos po lo rgyus gtan tshigs gis //
NK124(ngo)001:12028: bdag nyid chen po smos ci dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:12030: ldems dgongs man ngag he du'i skabs su ngo sprod cing rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12031: dngos po lo rgyus gtan tshigs yin ches par bya zhing dngos su ngo sprod par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12032: gnyis pa gtan la phebs pa'i grub mtha' lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12033: gong gi bden pa gsum gyi don de nyid khong du chud cing /
NK124(ngo)001:12034: da ltar gyi snang ba 'di nyid rig pa rang snang bas /
NK124(ngo)001:12035: blta bya lta byed med pas yul med rang gsal du rtogs pas gol sgrib kyi dmigs 'byed /
NK124(ngo)001:12036: don ma nor ba nyid khong du tshud cing the tshom yid gnyis med par gdengs dang ldan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12038: yul med rang gsal nyams rnyed la //
NK124(ngo)001:12039: thun mong zhes tha snyad brtags par zad //
NK124(ngo)001:12042: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:12043: dmigs med tshul du der snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:12045: don rang sems can rtogs med gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:12046: rang byung ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:12048: rang rig mngon du dmigs bral bas //
NK124(ngo)001:12049: rang gsal gsum bral mi 'gul ba //
NK124(ngo)001:12050: nges par gdeng du gang byas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12051: thos bsam byas pa lta mthar phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:12053: blta bya lta byed med par chos kun rig pa rang gsal du rtogs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12056: de phyir lta dang lta med par //
NK124(ngo)001:12057: chos kun rang rig rang snang bas //
NK124(ngo)001:12058: me long lta bu'i tshul bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:12059: mi rtogs gsal bas nges tshig 'grub //
NK124(ngo)001:12061: de ltar na chos kun sems nyid rang snang du rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12062: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid khong du chud de /
NK124(ngo)001:12063: gdod nas sangs ma rgyas kyi bar du dmigs phyed cing don khong du chud pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12065: lta ba lta ba gtsor brjod mod //
NK124(ngo)001:12066: don du shes bya kun mnyam nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:12067: ded dpon rin chen ci bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:12068: gdod matha'i bye brag 'dir shes dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:12070: de ltar zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong /
NK124(ngo)001:12071: ma mthong ce na go ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12075: chos nyid spyi'i mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12076: rang gi mtshan nyid yul med /
NK124(ngo)001:12080: spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12081: khyad par spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12082: don byed nus pa rang gi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12083: don byed mi nus pa spyi'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12087: mi 'gag pa spyi'i mtshan nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:12092: zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong na /
NK124(ngo)001:12093: lung rigs pa man ngag gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12095: gzhi gsum pa gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid la 'jug go //
NK124(ngo)001:12098: de dag zag bcas bsam gtan te //
NK124(ngo)001:12099: gnyis med yul bral de mthong min //
NK124(ngo)001:12102: zag bcas kyis skabs su rang gi mtshan nyid mthong na /
NK124(ngo)001:12103: zag med dang khyad par med par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:12105: gnyis pa mthong bar 'dod pa'i lugs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12106: gzhan gyi skyon bsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12109: lung man ngag 'gal ba'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12110: zag med bzhin du ma mthong ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12111: rigs pa'i skyon yang mi 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12112: rgyu dum bu la 'phel 'grib can du yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:12113: zag med dang khyad par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:12114: rgyal ba'i sras dang shing sna'i me //
NK124(ngo)001:12115: rang mtshan mthong yang stobs ma rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:12117: gnyis pa mthong ba'i lugs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12119: mthong ba po zag bcas kyi skabs su rgyun dum bu la 'phel 'grib can du mthong ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12121: spyan 'byed la sogs pa lta ba'i skabs nas mthong bar bshad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12123: sprin bar nyi 'dra gsal yid ches //
NK124(ngo)001:12125: mthong ba gnyis pa zag med mthong lam gyi skabs su 'grib pa med pa 'phel ba yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12127: skabs 'dir bden pa bar ma mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:12129: zag kun zad pa'i rig can de //
NK124(ngo)001:12130: ci ltar bshad kyang log pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:12133: sangs rgyas kyis dus gsum sgrib g.yo' kun dang bral te /
NK124(ngo)001:12134: gsal ba mthar phyin la mthong bas /
NK124(ngo)001:12135: 'phel 'grib med par mngon sum gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12137: tha ma'i tha ma zhes bral ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:12141: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:12142: spang thob gnyis med de bzhin gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:12143: zhen bral kun grol bde chen gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:12146: dang po zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12147: lung man ngag rig pa gsum las /
NK124(ngo)001:12149: rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK124(ngo)001:12150: mthong dang ma mthong rnam gnyis las //
NK124(ngo)001:12151: dman pa'i skabs na de mthong min //
NK124(ngo)001:12152: mthong ba dam pa'i skabs na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12153: mthong ba mngon mthong rnam gnyis las //
NK124(ngo)001:12154: mthar phyin dam pa mngon sum pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12158: da lta chos skur ma shes na //
NK124(ngo)001:12159: gsang sngags kyi man ngag ci la tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:12160: de phyir bstan shes b+hee mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:12163: rgyu 'bras phyir na gcig shos la //
NK124(ngo)001:12164: yul med rang gsal mngon sum pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12166: lam rim le'u gnyis pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:12167: sngags dang dmigs dbya'i med phyir de //
NK124(ngo)001:12168: de bas yul med rang gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12170: gzhan nam khog dbub kyi skabs kyi chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba'i lung rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:12174: ye nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK124(ngo)001:12175: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:12177: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyis zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid ma mthong na /
NK124(ngo)001:12178: gsang sngags 'bras bu lam du byed pa ma yin /
NK124(ngo)001:12179: rgyu lam du byed pa dang khyad par med par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12180: chos nyid mngon sum du ngo sprod pa'i man ngag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12181: rang rig pa'i tshad ma rgyun chad par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12182: mngon sum rtogs par byed pa'i he du rgyun chad pa'i skyon yong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:12184: gsal ba mthar phyin ma phyin gyi bye brag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12185: dper na dbang po'i yul du mthong yang thag nye
NK124(ngo)001:12186: ring gis gsal ba mthar phyin ma phyin yod pa
NK124(ngo)001:12188: dbang po dngas pa'i spyod yul las //
NK124(ngo)001:12189: nye ring drung bzhin stobs 'phebs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12191: gsal ba'i bye brag rim par 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:12193: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid b+hee pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12195: de yang rang bzhin sbyang pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:12196: snod du gyur pa nye ring phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12197: rim dang gcig char bzhi cha yi //
NK124(ngo)001:12200: rim skyes pa'i bye brag bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12201: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12202: rtogs grol dus mnyam pa gong gi sku lnga dang tshul mthun par rtogs shing grol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12205: rtogs pa'i don la myong ba'i rgyun brten tsam las lam gyi rim pa med par grol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12207: srid pa rdzogs par smin tshul du //
NK124(ngo)001:12208: lhag pa'i gdengs ldan skyes bu yi //
NK124(ngo)001:12209: b+hee ba rim bzhi zung ldan pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12210: gdod ma nyid nas goms par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:12212: rim skyes pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12213: rim skyes pa'i gcig char ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12215: rim skyes pa'i rim gyis pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12217: zag bcas zag med kyi thod rgal ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12218: gong gi le'u lnga pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:12219: rnam smin rig pa the tshom med //
NK124(ngo)001:12222: snyoms las med par brtson byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12226: rgya dor gcig char mthar 'gro ba //
NK124(ngo)001:12229: lnga pa rnal 'byor b+ha zhig gis //
NK124(ngo)001:12232: lam nges med bar du long du bgrod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12233: rgyas par lam rim bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12234: gnyis pa rim skyes pa'i rim pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12238: tshogs gnyis sngon du rdzogs pas tshogs lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12239: lta ba ting nge 'dzin gyis zag med mthong lam la sbyor bas sbyor lam mo //
NK124(ngo)001:12246: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis chos thams
NK124(ngo)001:12247: cad sems nyid rang snang la dngos po dang mtshan
NK124(ngo)001:12248: ma med pas / b+hee bya b+hee byed med par ma bcos de bzhin nyid du b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:12249: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel du b+hee pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12250: dngos rnams nyid nang nas dngos med par //
NK124(ngo)001:12251: rtogs pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:12252: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK124(ngo)001:12253: de nyid rang la mi g.yo' ba //
NK124(ngo)001:12254: gzhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK124(ngo)001:12256: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:12257: dmigs med tshul du der snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:12258: dbyings dang dbyings kyi ye shes kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:12259: rang rig kho na tsam du zad //
NK124(ngo)001:12261: gnyis pa kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12262: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can thams cad la /
NK124(ngo)001:12263: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:12264: thams cad ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor gsal ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12266: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12267: srid gsum sgyu ma lta bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12268: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mkhas pas shes //
NK124(ngo)001:12270: 'gro ba de ltar snga nas shes //
NK124(ngo)001:12273: log par rtogs rtag rnam dag cing //
NK124(ngo)001:12274: ye shes nyid las mi zhen phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12275: thugs rje chen por 'brel pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:12276: 'gro ba dus nas ma lus snang //
NK124(ngo)001:12279: gsod chen snying rje'i rang bzhin te //
NK124(ngo)001:12280: mi 'byed phan rdzogs byams chen po //
NK124(ngo)001:12281: mi 'gyod dga' mchog bral med bsnyoms //
NK124(ngo)001:12282: tshangs pa'i rgyud bzhi dus cig rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:12284: gsum pa phyag rgya gcig pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12285: lha yab yum zung cig lhag pa'i lha dgu dang bcu b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:12286: de nyid snang stong zung 'jug rang byung rang snang du b+hee zhing rtsal sbyang pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12287: de yang phyi ma tshang ba srin po'i tshul /
NK124(ngo)001:12288: rdzogs par bya ba zung du 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:12291: sems kyi cho 'phrul rang snang phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12292: lha la dmigs med rig pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:12293: gzhi rdzogs sku de rang snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12296: dkyil 'khor dang cho 'phrul la sogs pa rnams spros pa b+hee zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:12297: snang stong zung 'jug ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rig pa rang gsal du b+hee pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12298: phung sogs dkyil 'khor lhar snang ba //
NK124(ngo)001:12299: rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan ci bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:12300: kun dngos rang rig lhar gsal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:12301: gcig dang du ma yongs kyi med //
NK124(ngo)001:12303: stong 'phyal gnyis kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12304: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor yang //
NK124(ngo)001:12305: ri rab til 'bras bu'i tshul bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:12306: dpe' byad mtshan gyis rgyan spras pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12308: bar chad med pa tshogs bsgrub pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12309: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung //
NK124(ngo)001:12310: bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung srang //
NK124(ngo)001:12311: grogs yo byad lnga la brten nas bsgrub pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12312: phun sum tshogs pa lnga yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:12313: bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i gzhung srang zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:12314: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:12317: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK124(ngo)001:12318: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:12319: sngags kyi yan lag rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12321: dang po phun sum tshogs pa lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12326: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12335: phyag rgya gcig pa la phra ba yig 'bru la slab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12336: yongs su rdzogs pa lha sku la rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12337: phyag rgya spros pa dang lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12338: gsang sngags kyi yan lag lnga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12339: thugs rje ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12340: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum /
NK124(ngo)001:12343: rgyan dang bgo' ba'i yo byad /
NK124(ngo)001:12347: a li ka li yo byad dang lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12348: de ltar gong du lta ba'i skabs su bden gsum dbyer med du rtogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:12349: de nyid nyams su len pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:12350: tshogs lam de bzhin nyid stong nyid b+hee pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12351: kun tu snang stong nyid snying rje dbyer med b+hee pas /
NK124(ngo)001:12352: snang stong dbyer med phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK124(ngo)001:12353: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug phyag rgya spros pa chen po mngon sum du brtan pa mthar phyin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:12354: zag bcas kyi lam de nyid zag med la sbyor
NK124(ngo)001:12355: bar byed pa'i sbyor lam bar chad med par tshogs
NK124(ngo)001:12360: bskyed pa rnam bzhi rim gyis bskyed //
NK124(ngo)001:12361: cho 'phrul rnam bzhi phyag rgya bzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:12362: dus bzhi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12363: rig pa rang snang dkyil 'khor gnyis //
NK124(ngo)001:12364: chu dang chu bzhin dbyer med de //
NK124(ngo)001:12365: ma skyes chos nyid shes rab las //
NK124(ngo)001:12367: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12370: skyed pa bzhi'i ming gi rnam grangs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12371: gong du rnal 'byor yo ga'i skabs dang mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:12373: 'bras bu'i skabs nas bstan par 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:12376: gzhan don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12379: sbyor sgrol la sogs khyad par can gyi spyod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12381: rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12382: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang 'phrin las bzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:12383: sbyor sgrol la sogs spyod pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:12384: bdag gzhan thams cad sgrol bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:12385: thabs kyi zin te nyams su blang //
NK124(ngo)001:12386: des ni bdag gzhan grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:12394: skabs su gang du dgos pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12397: bsrung ba'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12399: rtogs pa 'dul ba'i phyir gsungs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12401: rtogs 'dul gnyen po dam tshig grangs //
NK124(ngo)001:12404: gnyis las bsrung ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12405: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig gi dmigs ma 'dres pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12407: de rnams lus ngag yid gsum gyis bsdom pa'i ngo bo byas nas mi d+ha ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12409: skyon yon gyi cha gnyis la bdag ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12410: sgo gsum bsdom la gnas shing mi gtong na /
NK124(ngo)001:12411: gnas ngan len du mi 'chor ba'i gzung yin pas dam zhes bya /
NK124(ngo)001:12412: des lam la nor bas lta ba ngan pa tshig pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12414: mi gtong phyir na dam zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12415: gzung du gyur bas dam zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12416: rdo rje'i tshig nor lam bston pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12417: de la yang ni tshig zhes bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12418: yang na 'da' ba dka' bas dam zhes bya la /
NK124(ngo)001:12419: 'das na rang rgyud tshig pas tshig zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12421: yang na de bzhin bka' bcag pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12422: mi khoms gnas su tshig par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:12424: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12427: dang po ni byang chub sems dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12432: kun rdzob byang chub sems dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12433: don dam byang chub sems so //
NK124(ngo)001:12435: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK124(ngo)001:12436: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK124(ngo)001:12437: snang stong gnyis med ye shes sku //
NK124(ngo)001:12438: byas mthong zos pa thams cad la //
NK124(ngo)001:12439: sems phyir gang yang byed snang med //
NK124(ngo)001:12441: gnyis pa sku'i dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12445: spyi dang 'dre dang dam tshig dbang //
NK124(ngo)001:12446: chag nyams bskongs dang shes rgyud bkrol //
NK124(ngo)001:12447: man ngag lung gi slob dpon rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12451: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12452: gang yang bdag las gzhan min phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12453: bder gshegs snying po spun yin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12454: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:12455: spyi'i mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:12456: sangs rgyas chos lugs ring ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12457: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:12458: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12459: nang tshang pha spun spun bas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:12460: lhag par gnas te bsrung bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12463: sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12465: rtsa ba skyed dang las sngags kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:12466: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12467: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:12471: lta zab spyod dang barlanga mo dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12472: lha mi gzung dang grub rtags rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12473: spyir gsang rnam pa bzhir bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:12476: bsgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK124(ngo)001:12477: rab tu gsang las bsgrub par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12479: b+han+d+ha phur pa mar med snod //
NK124(ngo)001:12480: rdzas dang lag chad dkyil 'khor rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12481: skye bos mthong bar yongs mi byed //
NK124(ngo)001:12482: dril bu rnge'u chung la sogs sgra //
NK124(ngo)001:12483: skye bos thos par yongs mi brdung //
NK124(ngo)001:12486: gnyer btad pa ni dam pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:12487: sngar bshad dpon mched rnams kyi gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:12489: gnyis pa yan lag la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12490: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12491: thun mong gi dam tshig go //
NK124(ngo)001:12493: spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12495: dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12496: shes par bya ba lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12501: ma byin pa blang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12506: rang bzhin gyi ni sbyor sgrol dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12507: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor sgrol dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12508: dbang po yul gyi sbyor sgrol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:12511: bye brag tu sbyor ba la bcu' ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12513: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12514: dam la log dang 'khus pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12516: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK124(ngo)001:12517: ngan song gsum dang bcu po 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:12518: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blangs //
NK124(ngo)001:12519: grangs ni rtsa ba bzhi bcu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12521: gnyis pa g+ha na'i dam tshig la nyi shu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12522: pad can dung can ri mo can //
NK124(ngo)001:12523: ba glang can dang lcug phrag can //
NK124(ngo)001:12524: sdong gcig me reg phyal ba brgyad //
NK124(ngo)001:12525: gnyen drang rke ring stod smad phyed //
NK124(ngo)001:12527: dpral ba'i dbye' che mig dkyus ring //
NK124(ngo)001:12528: mig dpral dkyil na ud dpal mdog /
NK124(ngo)001:12529: chur zhing gnyis ka 'bring du bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:12530: lus la chu rlung ga bur dri //
NK124(ngo)001:12531: gsang thub shes rab spyod pa dal //
NK124(ngo)001:12532: dad ldan 'grogs shing dad che ba //
NK124(ngo)001:12533: gsang ba'i gnas su spyad par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12535: gsum pa rdzun du smra ba'i dam tshig la bcu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12537: mtshan nyid chad dang rnam grangs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12538: ltos pa'i kun brtags rnam pa gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:12539: dngos po de nyid la rdzun shes //
NK124(ngo)001:12540: thams cad rang rig snang phyir bden //
NK124(ngo)001:12541: shes nas kun smra skyes bu'i yul //
NK124(ngo)001:12542: dkon mchog gsum dang slob dpon mched //
NK124(ngo)001:12543: sems can gnod par 'ong ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:12544: rdzun du smra ba'i dam tshig bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12545: gsang bcu la 'dri rdzun bcu smra //
NK124(ngo)001:12546: bsrung ba bcu bdun nyams su blangs //
NK124(ngo)001:12548: bzhi pa ma byin blang ba'i dam tshig la bcu bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:12550: zhing bcu gyur ba'i nor bcu dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12551: mtshan ldan bzung dang bkra shis rdzas //
NK124(ngo)001:12552: sbas chos phal 'chang byin che rdzas //
NK124(ngo)001:12553: bsrung ba yod dang med pa'i gter //
NK124(ngo)001:12554: phyug po ser snas bcing pa'i nor //
NK124(ngo)001:12555: ming gis blangs la tshogs su 'bul //
NK124(ngo)001:12556: dam tshig bcu bdun spyad par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12558: lnga pa ngag barlanga pa'i dam tshig la bco lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12560: zhing bcur gyur pa'i sems can la //
NK124(ngo)001:12561: barlanga tshig bcu'i zhe gcad cing //
NK124(ngo)001:12562: drag shugs spyod pa'i man ngag dag /
NK124(ngo)001:12563: gzung la barlanga por sbyor ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12564: slob bu'i gnod bcos zhe gcod dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12565: 'byung po zhe gcod rngams pa'i dgra //
NK124(ngo)001:12566: snod ldan bu la barlanga chos bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:12567: ngag gi dam tshig bco lnga bsrungs //
NK124(ngo)001:12569: spyi don gnyis pa mi spang pa la bco lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12571: mi dbang dam tshig bshad bya ba //
NK124(ngo)001:12572: yang dag lnga dang log dug lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:12573: bshad pa'i thabs mkhas 'dod chags chung //
NK124(ngo)001:12574: 'dod spyod sems kyi rgyan shes na //
NK124(ngo)001:12575: shin tu zhen pa'i lam du gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:12576: zhing bcu slag byed zhe sdang mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:12577: lta ngan 'joms pa'i de bzhin te //
NK124(ngo)001:12578: thabs la mkhas pa'i spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:12579: ma nor mtho' ba'i lta ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12580: ting 'dzin nges par sren tshugs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12581: shin tu rgyal ba'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:12582: lta ba phyogs ris mi phyed dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12583: spyod pa blang dor mi byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12584: theg pa chen po'i gti mug go //
NK124(ngo)001:12585: lta spyod dman la 'phrag dog che //
NK124(ngo)001:12586: dam pa ma 'dres spangs byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12587: 'phrag dog dam tshig bsrung ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:12588: log dug sems can kun ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12589: dug lnga rang rig rang snang phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12591: spyi don gsum pa dang du blang ba la sum cu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12592: kun gyis blang ba'i dam tshig lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:12593: dri chen dri chu mang ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12594: zil pa lhag pa'i sems rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:12595: grub pa bzhi'i rgyan pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12596: nad lnga gsal phyir blang ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12597: gtsang sme sdig sbyang phyir blang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12598: thun mong dgongs pa lnga phyir dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12599: rigs lnga grub pa yon tan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12600: sdug bsngal las dgrol bde' ba thob //
NK124(ngo)001:12601: bcud lnga btung dbang lam gyi mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:12602: thabs kyi lung la brten shes na //
NK124(ngo)001:12603: yon tan brjod las 'das par gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:12604: phye ba'i dam tshig sum cu nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:12605: skabs kyis dang du blang bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12606: bzhi pa bsgrub par bya ba la bzhi bcu zhe lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12608: bsgrub par bya ba lnga rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:12609: rigs lnga ye shes yab yum la //
NK124(ngo)001:12610: gcig la'ang lnga lngar shes par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12611: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan las //
NK124(ngo)001:12612: gcig kyang lnga lngar phye bas na //
NK124(ngo)001:12613: bzhi cu lnga'i bye brag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12614: mtshan nyid shes nas bsgrub par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12616: lnga pa shes par bya ba la bdun cu ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12618: shes bya lnga la bye brag tu //
NK124(ngo)001:12619: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:12620: dbang po yul dang yan lag sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:12621: nyon mongs dam sam sha dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12622: phyogs dang kha dog 'gro ba lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:12623: snying ma bag chags lnga lnga po //
NK124(ngo)001:12624: bdun cu la sogs 'khor ba'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:12625: ye shes sku rig yab yum sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:12626: rang bzhin ngang giis ka dag pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:12627: blo la nyams su lon pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12628: spyod yul yang dag rnal 'byor pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12630: spyi don gnyis pa thun mong gi yan lag dam tshig la //
NK124(ngo)001:12632: gzhan don la bzhi bcu zhe bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12634: thun mong dam tshig mdor bsdus na //
NK124(ngo)001:12635: bdag gzhan don du shes par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:12637: chang dang dre spyod khengs sems dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12638: rdo rje gsum po'i phyag byed dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12639: che ngag dge smad sdig stod dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12640: le lo ser sna gnyid g.yengs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12641: khro gtum ye shes sngon mi gtong //
NK124(ngo)001:12642: bka' gcog sdig pa'i grogs rten dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12643: bag med spyod dang dam bca' mdor //
NK124(ngo)001:12644: chog mi shes shing ngoms la dga' //
NK124(ngo)001:12645: spang bya nyi shu gcig bzlog pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12646: bdag don mchog tu gyur ba de //
NK124(ngo)001:12647: kun gyis bdag nyid khur bar 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:12648: pha rol phyin bcu chos spyod bcu //
NK124(ngo)001:12649: rnam bzhi las kyi spyod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12650: mthun 'jug thabs kyi spyod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12651: theg pa dgu' dang mu stegs dgu //
NK124(ngo)001:12652: 'gro ba drug gi spyod pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12653: 'dzin dang nyam nga med par spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:12654: don 'gyur ci yang nyams su blangs //
NK124(ngo)001:12655: bzhi bcu bzhi la sogs pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:12656: gdul bya gang yang 'dor mi bya' //
NK124(ngo)001:12657: bsrung ba de dag grangs btab pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12658: dran dang shes bzhin gyis spyod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12659: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen por gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:12661: de ltar gong gi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams nyams pa'i rgyu bstan pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12663: nyams par gyur ba'i rgyu dag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12664: mi chos blun po'i las byed dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12665: bdag stod gzhan smad zur za mkhas //
NK124(ngo)001:12666: khe grags nyid phyir 'du ba bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:12667: rdzas la chags sems rang phyogs che //
NK124(ngo)001:12668: chang dang rang mthong lta spyod nyams //
NK124(ngo)001:12669: chos la phyogs ris ngom skyes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12670: gsang chung le lo gtsang sme che //
NK124(ngo)001:12671: sgro bskur grogs kyi nyams len dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12673: gcig por mi gnas 'du' la dga' //
NK124(ngo)001:12674: nyi shu nyams pa'i rgyu 'gyur ro //
NK124(ngo)001:12676: lnga pa skabs gang du dgongs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12677: sa lam rang rang gi dus skabs dang bstun nas bsrung /
NK124(ngo)001:12679: pha rol phyin bcu chos spyod bcu' //
NK124(ngo)001:12680: rnam bzhi las kyi spyod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12681: mthun 'jug thabs kyi spyod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12685: bsrung ba'i yon tan rnams 'dir yi ge mang gis dogs pas ma sbyar /
NK124(ngo)001:12686: gsal bkra'i nang bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12687: drug pa lam yun dang 'bras bu thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12696: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK124(ngo)001:12697: dbang phyug rim gyi dam pa 'grub //
NK124(ngo)001:12701: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK124(ngo)001:12702: drug cu dgu cu rtsa drug tu //
NK124(ngo)001:12706: sbyor lam la phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung /
NK124(ngo)001:12708: grogs yo byad lnga la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:12709: tshe gcig lus gcig la zag bcas kyi lus zag med la sbyor ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:12710: lus snang sems gsum la rang dbang 'byor ba'i mthong lam tshe la dbang thob pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12711: dbang ma thob pa'i rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK124(ngo)001:12714: 'di tshe gcig la mngon par grub ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12715: rtsal chen ldan pa'i skyes bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12716: lhag mar bcas pa'i lus nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:12717: las dang nyon mongs nyes 'brel nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12718: tshe dbang la sogs rig 'dzin thob //
NK124(ngo)001:12720: gnyis pa zag med kyi yun ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12721: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12722: blo chung ba'i dbang gis 'bras bu tshe dbang rig 'dzin dngos su ma thob kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:12723: phyi ma len grangs gzhan nas tshe dbang thob par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:12725: rnam par smin pa bya can tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:12728: seng 'phrug gi mngal rgya bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:12729: rnam smin de yang rnal 'byor pa lus rgya lha mi'i rnam pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:12730: sems yi dam lha'i skur smin pas lus rgya' bral
NK124(ngo)001:12731: ma thag phyag rgya'i rig pa 'dzin par 'gyur bar
NK124(ngo)001:12735: lus kyi dra ba sgrib gyur pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12736: ka la ping ka'i mi 'jigs bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:12737: bral nas snang byed de rnam smin //
NK124(ngo)001:12739: yid kyis lha'i gzugs gzung bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:12740: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12741: lha'i sku nyid gsal gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12742: rnam par smin zhes de la gtags //
NK124(ngo)001:12745: zag bcas kyi lus nyid zag med du 'byung rdo
NK124(ngo)001:12746: rje'i lus su gyur cing lus ma bor ba sangs
NK124(ngo)001:12749: phung khams skyes gnas zag pa zad //
NK124(ngo)001:12750: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe'i rig /
NK124(ngo)001:12751: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:12752: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12754: tshe dbang de nyid gong ma la sbyor tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12756: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad du //
NK124(ngo)001:12757: sku lnga lhun gyis grub par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:12760: rig pa 'dzin pa'i tshe nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:12761: skye 'chi med pa'i sa bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12762: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul pa'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:12763: tshul gyis 'gro rnams rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12764: bde bar gshegs shing sbyong byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:12765: sems can sdug bsngal gnas las grol //
NK124(ngo)001:12766: brgya' phrag bcu drug tshud chad du //
NK124(ngo)001:12767: shes bya'i phra sgrib byang gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12768: rnal 'byor rtsal cher rdzogs pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:12769: sku lnga lhun gyi grub par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:12771: zag med mthong lam pa de'i gdul bya'i zhing khams
NK124(ngo)001:12772: dang mdzad pa'i 'phrin las mdor bsdus tsam brjod do
NK124(ngo)001:12774: stong gsum brgya bcu'i 'jig rten rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12775: g.yo dang rab g.yo' shin tu g.yo' //
NK124(ngo)001:12776: mdzad pa snang bas de gnas rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12777: nang g.yos pa yi rim sbyor byed //
NK124(ngo)001:12778: gsang ba sngags kyi sgra sgrags pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12779: kun kyang rmad 'byung sngags kyi sgra //
NK124(ngo)001:12780: grags pas bdud 'dul ngan song sbyangs //
NK124(ngo)001:12781: 'gro ba ma lus don yang byed //
NK124(ngo)001:12782: las rnams thams cad kun byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12783: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung thob //
NK124(ngo)001:12784: ces pa la sogs rgyas par gzhung bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12785: gnyis pa b+hee lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12787: phyag rgya chen por gyur te mtshan dpe' dang ldan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12789: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK124(ngo)001:12790: b+hee pa gang yin mngon gyur sku //
NK124(ngo)001:12791: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dpe' ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:12792: longs spyod gnyis la phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:12795: ye shes sku'i cha lugs can //
NK124(ngo)001:12796: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus la grol //
NK124(ngo)001:12797: de phyir sku tshe'i tshad med do //
NK124(ngo)001:12798: sgyur zhing mngon du bya dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:12801: mnyam gzhag ngang nas ma g.yo' bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:12802: stong gis 'jig rten brgya' stong phrag /
NK124(ngo)001:12804: zhing grangs med pas brgya stong phrag /
NK124(ngo)001:12805: bcu'i rdul rnyed zhing khams su //
NK124(ngo)001:12806: rgyan dang smad tshong la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:12807: sprul pa lus kyi 'dul bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:12808: bzhi dang drug sogs de bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:12810: gsum pa mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12811: sku lnga lhun grub kyis grub cing /
NK124(ngo)001:12812: bag la nyal gyis sgrib pa bcom nas /
NK124(ngo)001:12813: skad cig ma phyi ma la sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12815: de ltar dag pa'i shes pa nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:12816: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:12817: lhun mnyam ngang las mi g.yo' zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:12818: mi rtogs nyid du bzhugs pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:12819: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:12820: skad cig dag las rig 'dzin thob //
NK124(ngo)001:12823: tha ma'i ming grangs mthar phyin lam //
NK124(ngo)001:12824: rang rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12825: de nyid dang ni mthar sbyor lam //
NK124(ngo)001:12826: yang dag rdzogs pa'i rgyal tshab bo //
NK124(ngo)001:12828: de ltar zag med kyi rig 'dzin bzhi'i khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12830: rnam par smin pa bya can tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:12831: dbang sgyur phung po 'jig pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:12832: phyag rgya chen po bdag lus snang //
NK124(ngo)001:12833: nyi shu lnga grub rang snang ba'o //
