NK124(ngo)001:12835: 'o na mthar lam dang sangs rgyas la khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:12836: mnyam gzhag la khyad par med kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:12837: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa phra rags kyi phra
NK124(ngo)001:12838: ba yod pas mnyam gzhag gi rtsol ba yod pas
NK124(ngo)001:12840: de la de'i rtsol ba can //
NK124(ngo)001:12842: 'dra la bag la nyal gyis phyes //
NK124(ngo)001:12844: de bzhin du mthong lam la tshe dbang rnam smin gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:12845: b+hee lam la phyag chen po'i rig 'dzin /
NK124(ngo)001:12846: mthar lam la lhun grub rig 'dzin dang bzhi'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12847: 'o na mtshan nyid kyi mthong b+hee mthar phyin pa'i lam gsum dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12848: rig 'dzin bzhi la khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:12850: rgyu'i theg pa'i mthong lam gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:12851: mthong lam tsam du skal ba mnyam la /
NK124(ngo)001:12852: dgongs pa rgyu'i sa brgyad pa dang mnyam la /
NK124(ngo)001:12853: b+hee lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang rgyu'i sa brgyad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12854: b+hee lam tsam du mnyam yang /
NK124(ngo)001:12855: dgongs pa rgyu'i mthar lam sa dang mnyam /
NK124(ngo)001:12856: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12857: rgyu'i sa bcu'i byang sems gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:12858: mthar lam tsam du skal ba mnyam yang /
NK124(ngo)001:12859: dgongs pa kun du 'od dang mnyam ste /
NK124(ngo)001:12861: de yang dang po'i dang po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12862: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog ste //
NK124(ngo)001:12863: brgyad pa'i sems dpar bskal ba mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:12864: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK124(ngo)001:12865: dgongs spyod rgya mtshor khyad par 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:12867: bdun pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:12870: dang po ni bshad ma thag gi rig 'dzin rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:12871: gnyis pa mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12873: mtshan nyid tha ma'i tha ma ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12874: ngo bo tshul dang khyad par gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:12877: 'bras bu'i chos nyi shu rtsa lngar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:12879: lus gsum snga ma brjod byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12880: sku dang gsung dang thugs nyid dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12882: lnga'am lnga nyid ngo bor gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:12884: tshul ni mar la mar bzhag bzhin rgyun gcig tu sangs rgya' ba ma yin zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:12885: shing gis me dpung ltar sbyang ba'i ye shes ma 'dres pa yang yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12886: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su bzhugs so //
NK124(ngo)001:12888: don dam gcig po ma yin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12889: chu la chu ltar gcig pa'ang yin //
NK124(ngo)001:12891: shing gis me dpung ltar brjod pa'ang //
NK124(ngo)001:12892: grang ba tsam du de nyid min //
NK124(ngo)001:12894: mnyam pa gsum pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:12896: tha snyad bral ba'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:12900: grub mtha' so so'i sangs rgyas la //
NK124(ngo)001:12901: grangs rdzogs ngo bo'i byin rlabs las //
NK124(ngo)001:12902: snang dang don byed che chung gis //
NK124(ngo)001:12903: dpag pa'i ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:12905: grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12906: ngo bo 'dus byas ma byas kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12907: byin rlabs mngon du snang mi snang gi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12908: 'phrin las don byed che chung gi khyad par la
NK124(ngo)001:12909: sogs pa rgyas par bshad pa lam rim ltar shes
NK124(ngo)001:12911: mdo' sngags kyi dgongs don gsal byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:12912: ma h+aa yo ga'i grub mtha' bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:12913: gnyis pa dbang po rab kyi 'bring lung a nu yo ga'i 'dod pa bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12914: ma h+aa dang shan phye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12917: yod pa bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka yod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:12918: bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor bston pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:12919: yod pa bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka yod kyang rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtsor ston pa a nu /
NK124(ngo)001:12920: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i mtha' las grol ba a ti'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12921: yang gzhi' lam 'bras bu gsum gyi khyad par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:12923: ma h+aa don dam la snang ba 'di chos nyid dngos su khas len mi nus te /
NK124(ngo)001:12924: kun rdzob kyang snang ba sems kyi cho 'phrul lha'i dal du 'dod la /
NK124(ngo)001:12925: de gnyis gnyis su med pa ni bden pa dbyer med du 'dod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12926: nges na 'khrul pas rtags pa'i snang ba 'di nyid chos nyid du khas len mi nus pas /
NK124(ngo)001:12927: don dam phyogs 'dzin gyi rgya ma bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12928: kun rdzob kyang sems kyi cho 'phrul du 'dod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:12929: gzhi ngo bo sems dang bcas shing dngos su mi bden pas /
NK124(ngo)001:12930: bden rdzun gyi mtha' dang ma bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12931: dbyer med kyang de nyid kyi ngo bo dbyer med par yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:12932: mnyam pa nyid kyi dgongs pa mngon sum ma gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12934: nang pa ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12935: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12936: bdag nyid chen po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK124(ngo)001:12937: phyi nang gsang bas bsdus pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12938: srid pa sems kyis bsdus pa kun //
NK124(ngo)001:12939: dbang po spyod yul gyur ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12940: dus gsum ma nges rnam bzhi ste //
NK124(ngo)001:12941: spyod pa'i 'phrin las thams cad ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12942: bdag nyid chen po gcig bsdus kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:12943: ye nas yin pa gdod bsgrub rtsol //
NK124(ngo)001:12945: ma nor tshul gyis lam zhugs kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:12946: zhag ni bcu sam phrag drug gam //
NK124(ngo)001:12947: bcu pa gsum phrag bcu drug tu //
NK124(ngo)001:12948: rtsol zhing bsgrub pas ting 'dzin sbyangs //
NK124(ngo)001:12950: phyi ma a nu yo ga rang gzhung la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:12960: rnal grol rig pa'i tan+t+ra te //
NK124(ngo)001:12961: de yang ltos pa'i bye brag bdun //
NK124(ngo)001:12963: rab kyi 'bring po gsung rdzogs rim gtsor ston pa'i tshul du snang ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:12964: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum dbyer med pa'i tan+t+ra brjod byed rtogs pa'i bye brag /
NK124(ngo)001:12965: rjod byed de la'ang 'jug sgo la sogs 'og ma
NK124(ngo)001:12966: rnams la ltos pa'i dbang du byas nas gcig tu
NK124(ngo)001:12967: bstan pa'o // dang po 'jug sgo ni /
NK124(ngo)001:12968: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad dbyings skye ba med cing ye shes 'gag pa med pa gnyis /
NK124(ngo)001:12969: dus la snga phyi med pa'i dbyer med kyi sgo nas 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:12971: dbyings dang ye shes 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK124(ngo)001:12975: chos can gyi ngos nas ma 'gags par snang ba
NK124(ngo)001:12976: thams cad ye shes kun tu bzang po'i rol par
NK124(ngo)001:12979: rnal 'byor rdzogs pa'i lta ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:12980: bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas //
NK124(ngo)001:12981: na rag dmyal khams yan chod du //
NK124(ngo)001:12982: snod bcud phra rag bem rig rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:12983: dge sdig mtho dman bzang ngan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:12984: bye brag rnams la cir snang yang //
NK124(ngo)001:12987: snang tsam nyid nas ngo bo nyid kyis ma skyes pas dbyings kun tu bzang po yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:12989: ngo bo nyid kyis ma skyes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:12990: mi dmigs mi gnas spros dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:12991: bzung du mtshan ma'i dngos po med //
NK124(ngo)001:12992: ma skye ma bcos chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:12995: de gnyis dbyer med pa sras bde ba chen po
NK124(ngo)001:12996: ye shes kyi rol pa chos nyid kyi rgyan du
NK124(ngo)001:12999: de nyid 'gags pa med tshul gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13000: thams cad thams cad mi 'gags pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13001: ye shes rol pa'i rgyan du rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13003: des na dbyings sam don la snang ba rtsal rdzogs su 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:13004: 'khrul pas rtags pa'i snang ba 'di nyid chos nyid
NK124(ngo)001:13005: rang snang mngon sum du snang bar 'dod cing rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:13006: pa phyogs 'dzin gyi rgya dang bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13007: kun rdzob bam ye shes ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13008: don dam dbyings kyi rtsal rol par snang bas bden /
NK124(ngo)001:13011: ma h+aa ngo bo dbyer med las //
NK124(ngo)001:13012: a nu mtshon tshul yang dbyer med mnyam pa nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:13013: sangs rgyas thod pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:13014: khams gsum sems can thams cad kun //
NK124(ngo)001:13015: sangs ma rgyas pa gcig med do //
NK124(ngo)001:13017: yang yul sems rtogs pa lta ba yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:13019: sems la sems kyi rjes su lta zhing mthong bar ma rigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13021: mi nus pa bzhin sems de la sems des dmigs mi nus so //
NK124(ngo)001:13022: zhes ltas nas sems lta ba 'di ltar mthong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:13047: rnam par mi rtogs mi skyod /
NK124(ngo)001:13050: gang byung ba yang gzugs med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:13051: gang la gzugs med pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:13053: ces pa la sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13054: des na gzhi'i lta ba la khyad par yod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13056: ma h+aa yo ga'i yan lag gsum gyis lhar b+hee
NK124(ngo)001:13057: zhing bskyed rdzogs rim par b+hee pa las khyad par
NK124(ngo)001:13059: bzhi po rim gyis mi skyed de //
NK124(ngo)001:13061: dwangs ba'i mtsho la gza' skar bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:13062: rig pa'i rtsal gyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13063: mi skyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:13065: a nu'i b+hee pa phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:13066: cho 'phrul la sogs rim gyis skyed mi dgos par /
NK124(ngo)001:13067: zhi khro'i lha tshogs rgya' mtsho la gzugs brnyan bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:13068: du rig pa'i blo rtsal che bas bskyed basngagasa brjod
NK124(ngo)001:13069: pa tsam gyis dbu'i gtsug tor dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13070: zhabs kyi gdan khri sogs rgyan cha lugs thams cad rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13072: 'bring la rdzogs par snang la gang //
NK124(ngo)001:13073: mnyam pas mnyam pa'i don mthong na //
NK124(ngo)001:13074: mnyam rdzogs ye shes dbyings ye shes //
NK124(ngo)001:13075: kun rig kun rdzogs kun tu snang //
NK124(ngo)001:13076: chos nyid mi gyur gdal ba'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:13078: gsum pa spyod pa la yang spyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13081: 'bad dang rtsol ba la rag ma lus pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:13082: lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin spyod par 'dus par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13084: rnam grol rig pa'i spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13085: rnal 'byor che dang bye brag med //
NK124(ngo)001:13087: dbyings ye shes dbyer med 'ching ba las grol ba'i rang rig pa'i ye shes su spyod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13088: thun mong du rnal 'byor ma h+aa'i skabs dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13090: gnyis pa bye brag gi spyod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13091: rang gzhung gi spyod pa brtul zhugs nyi shu rtsa gsum la spyod do //
NK124(ngo)001:13093: nags tshal dgon pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK124(ngo)001:13094: snyoms pa blang ste za bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13095: sems kyi brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13096: ting 'dzin stobs dang ldan par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13097: lus kyi brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13098: thog med stangs stabs tshul du gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:13099: ngag gi brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13100: sngags kyi yi ge drag tu brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:13101: dben pa'i gnas su gnas bcas la //
NK124(ngo)001:13102: che ba'i nga rgyal rtag tu skyed //
NK124(ngo)001:13103: wa'i brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13104: spang bar bya ba'i thabs su spyad //
NK124(ngo)001:13105: cang shes brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13106: shes bya kun la 'jug par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:13107: lus kyi rtsal gyi bya ba dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13108: gyi ling brtul shugs chen po bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13109: phag pa'i brtul shugs chen po ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13110: gtsang sme med pa kun la spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:13111: glang chen myos pa'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13112: mi 'byed rmongs tshul ston par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13113: stag mchongs rngams pa'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13114: dpa' bsdul gtums pa'i las chen bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13115: khyung chen mkha' lding brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13116: lta ba'i phyi rgya rlabs kyis bcad //
NK124(ngo)001:13117: gtum thung dom gyis brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13118: re ba med pa'i las chen bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13119: rgya mtsho gser gyi brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13120: yid thub mi bzlog rten par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13121: lkugs pa lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13122: gti mug shin tu shes rab ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:13123: ri bo lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13124: mi 'gyur rab tu brtan par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13125: nam mkha' lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13126: yang dag don kun bral bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13127: gnam lcags lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13128: drag shul las la sbyor bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13129: lag na rdo rje'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13130: mthu stobs dag la spyad par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13131: bya rog lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13133: glang chen chur 'jug brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13134: nges pa'i nga rgyal brten par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13135: ri dgas seng ge'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13136: grogs ngan la sogs spang par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13138: 'grogs na chags shing bde bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13139: sgyu ma lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13140: thabs la mkhas pa'i lam chen bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13141: lce spyang lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13142: che ba'i nga rgyal bskyed par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13143: mkha' lding lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13144: kun du mtshams pa'i spyod pa spyad //
NK124(ngo)001:13145: rgyal po 'khor bsrung brtul shugs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13146: so thub 'khor dang ldan par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13147: bcu gnyis dag ni gsum dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:13148: brtul shugs blo dang ldan par bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13151: brtul shugs nyi shu rtsa gsum po //
NK124(ngo)001:13152: lung las bshad pa de dag yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13154: lnga pa dam tshig la thun mong ma yin pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13158: brtul shugs spyod pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13159: dam tshig kun gyi thog mar 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:13160: don du mi 'gyur kun spangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13161: kun dang mthun phyir de ltar spyad //
NK124(ngo)001:13162: mi shigs pa ni seng ge ste //
NK124(ngo)001:13163: gcan zan rgyal po yin pas so //
NK124(ngo)001:13164: za ma rtogs ni rgyal po'i mdzod //
NK124(ngo)001:13165: dug g.yo' ba ni der mi rigs //
NK124(ngo)001:13166: rin chen mug gu'i lcug phran dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13167: bregs te 'byung rgyun bcad ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13168: gang gis zhun chu phal pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:13169: mkhas pas btung ba mi bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13170: pad ma'i ze'u 'bru kha mi dbye' //
NK124(ngo)001:13171: zla zer ma yin dbye mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13172: ma rtags bul rtol can snod du //
NK124(ngo)001:13173: bdud rtsi sman blug zag par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13174: don med bcos ma'i tshul rtags can //
NK124(ngo)001:13175: bsrel zhing spyad par bya ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:13176: shel dkar rin chen sgong nga dag /'dam khung rdzab tu sba mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13177: seng ge dkar mo'i 'o ma dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13178: gser snod ma yin blug mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13179: yid bzhin nor bu rin po che //
NK124(ngo)001:13180: bsreg par bya ba yongs ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13181: khyung chen bshog pa mkhar rgyang ba //
NK124(ngo)001:13182: de dag bcag par bya ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:13183: gnam lcags mi'i ngur mo dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13184: brta' bar bya ba ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:13185: stag seng rol pa las byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13186: las kyi rjes su brdu' mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13187: rdo rje brag chen gtams pa'i gzhi' //
NK124(ngo)001:13188: bshig par bya ba ga la yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13189: rdo rje ra ba'i re ga dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13190: bsdom bya hral bar bya ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:13191: bud shing bsreg pa'i sgron ma de //
NK124(ngo)001:13192: 'thor rlung drag pos bskyod mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13193: rdo rje tshig gis chu rgyun dag /'ol dkar bcag par bya ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:13194: rgyal po'i bka' rtags phyag rgya dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13195: nam zhar dbye ba mi bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13196: rdo rje pha lam gtams pa'i 'khar //
NK124(ngo)001:13197: rmang nas zlog par mi bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13198: gtsug gi yid bzhin nor bu de //
NK124(ngo)001:13199: rgyal mtshan rtse la dpog mi bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13200: rnal 'byor thabs kyi khyad par can //
NK124(ngo)001:13201: rtsal chen rnams kyi dam tshig de //
NK124(ngo)001:13202: skal ldan dag gi nor mchog yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13203: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13204: gnyis pa thun mong gi dam tshig ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13206: sum brgya' drug cu mtha' yas te //
NK124(ngo)001:13207: gong 'og bsrung ba'i bye brag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13210: dam tshig sum brgya' drug cu sogs /
NK124(ngo)001:13211: spyi dang bye brag rnams 'og ma dang mthun pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13217: zla ba lo dang lo bcu gnyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13218: bcu drug rgyun gyi khyad par gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13220: lta ba mthong ba zag bcas te //
NK124(ngo)001:13222: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor gnyis thob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:13223: zag med la sbyor tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13224: lta ba rtogs nas b+hee pa la gcig char ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13227: rtogs grol dus mnyam pa'i gcig char ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13228: rtogs pa'i don la myong ba'i rgyun rten pa tsam gyis lam gyi rim pa med par grol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13230: tshul gyi he du la sogs pa'i lta ba yun
NK124(ngo)001:13231: med rang gsal gcig chod du rtogs nas b+hee pa
NK124(ngo)001:13232: yang gcig chod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13233: rtogs grol dus mnyam pas 'bras bu gcig char du sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13236: kun ni kun gyi sa yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:13237: gang gis sa chen 'di non na //
NK124(ngo)001:13238: sa rnams skad cig tsam 'grod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13241: de bas mnyam pa'i don 'di la //
NK124(ngo)001:13242: btud de gcig char 'jug shes nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13243: b+hee pa'i yun ni ring thung dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13244: las 'phro yod dam med pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13245: nam zhig mnyam pa'i khar lus //
NK124(ngo)001:13248: gang dag blo chen sngon rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13249: mnyam nyid yul bral rang gsal bar //
NK124(ngo)001:13250: mi g.yo' gcig char gang 'jug pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13251: sa dang lam gyi grangs rtsol med //
NK124(ngo)001:13254: rtogs pa'i don la dran pa'i rgyun rten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:13255: b+hee bya b+hee byed med par rang lugs rtsol med du blang pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13256: nyams dang yon tan phyogs med du shar nas grol bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13258: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsam gtan ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13259: ci bzhin pa'i de nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:13260: ma bcos pa'i blo bzhag ste //
NK124(ngo)001:13264: skad cig tsam gyis ting 'dzin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13265: sgrib pa'i phung po phyag par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13266: ci ltar ma shes mun gsal ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:13267: mun nyid snang bar 'gyur ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:13268: skad cig ma nyid don rig pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13269: sngon nas bsags pa'i mun pa sel //
NK124(ngo)001:13272: de nyid las mtha' zhi gnas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13273: lhag pa'i don mthong 'dres pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:13274: stong gsum nges par rdzogs pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:13275: 'bum phrag mtha' yas brjod mi lang //
NK124(ngo)001:13278: rgya mtsho yangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:13279: sems ni chu gsal nam mkha' la //
NK124(ngo)001:13280: dngos grub nyi zla skar tshogs bkrams //
NK124(ngo)001:13281: rang byung rang snang thog med med //
NK124(ngo)001:13282: ltas dang sbyar las bsgrub mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:13283: don gcig yon tan dus gcig 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:13287: gcig chos 'jug pa lnga dang bcu //
NK124(ngo)001:13288: spros pas bzhi bcur gyur pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13290: rim 'jug dbang po rab zla ba lnga phrag dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13292: tha ma sum cu phrag gam /
NK124(ngo)001:13295: dbang po rab kyi zla ba gcig /'bring lo gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:13296: tha ma'i tha mas lo bcu gnyis sam /
NK124(ngo)001:13297: bcu drug la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin b+hee pa'i rgyun gyis khyad par zag med la sbyor ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13298: gnyis pa zag med lam yun la gnyis las /
NK124(ngo)001:13301: mthong lam nas sangs rgyas kyi bar 'grod pa yang gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13305: gnyis pa rim skyes pa ni b+hee lam nas rim pa ltar 'grod par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13307: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13308: mngon sum gyur pa lam gyi yun //
NK124(ngo)001:13309: de nas ring sogs ma thogs par //
NK124(ngo)001:13311: bdun pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:13312: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13313: bsdus pas sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las so //
NK124(ngo)001:13315: shes bya ci lta ba nyid mngon sum du gyur pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13316: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod las 'das par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13318: bya byed mthong goms mthar phyin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13319: sa bcu sa mtha' gang phyin pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13320: dpag bsam shing ltar rin chen ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:13321: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:13323: dwangs pa'i chu dang me long dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13324: nyi zla gza' skar tshul bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:13325: 'du shes zad pa'i rang rigs nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:13326: dpag med yon tan ngo bor shar //
NK124(ngo)001:13329: lang ka'i bdag po de yang min pa zhig bsgrub pa'ang /
NK124(ngo)001:13330: mi 'dra ba zhig 'dra bar bcos pa ni ma yin gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:13335: ye nas rang bzhin gyis de ltar yin par zad do //
NK124(ngo)001:13339: ngo bo ye shes bsdus pa lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:13340: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13341: mdzad pa'i 'phrin las nyid dang lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:13343: ngo bo sku rnam pa lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13350: de bzhin nyid dang gsang ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13351: chos dang longs spyod sprul pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13353: mi mthun gnyen po med par gnas lugs ci bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:13354: pa nyid mngon sum gyur bas ngo bo nyid kyis
NK124(ngo)001:13355: sku dang / chos kyi dbyings skye ba med cing
NK124(ngo)001:13356: rnam par dag pa nyid sgrib g.yog dang bral ba
NK124(ngo)001:13358: sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan cing dgongs pa bde ba chen por longs spyod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13359: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13360: thugs rje'i rnam 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas dag
NK124(ngo)001:13361: pa dang ma dag pa'i sems can gang la gang
NK124(ngo)001:13364: ngo bo dbyer med cing gsang ba dam pa bde ba chen po ni gsang ba'i sku'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13367: gang med pa la rgyud kyis 'byung ba la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13368: longs spyod rdzogs pa ni smin pa phun sum tshogs pa la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13370: yongs su rnam par dag pa la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13371: ngo bo nyid ni ci bzhin pa de nyid la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13374: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13375: ma brjod ngo bo nyid kyis go ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13377: rang gsal byin rlabs kyis mtshon pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13378: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i gsung ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13383: dbyangs kyi sgo nas tshig gis mtshon pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13385: gang ngo bo nyid med pa'i gsung ni nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13386: rnam par dag pa'i gsung ni nyi ma'i snying po lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13387: yongs su smin pa'i gsung ni me long lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13388: gsang ba dam pa'i gsung ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13390: rgyun du 'byung ba'i gsung ni gsung gcig la yan lag bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13392: gsum pa thugs rje ye shes la ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13393: stong nyid dam chos dbyings kyi ye shes ni chos kun mtshan ma med pa rang gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13394: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13395: chos dbyings sgrib pa med cing rtogs pa med par rang gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13396: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13397: bzang ngan che chung med par mnyam pa nyid du rang gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13398: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13399: chos kun bye brag ma 'dres pa rang gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13400: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13401: rtsol bsgrubs med par bya ba byed cing dgongs don 'byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13403: kha cig tu ni chos dbyings ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13404: kha cig tu ni rnam par gsal ba'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13405: kha cig tu ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13406: kha cig tu ni so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13407: kha cig tu ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13410: stong nyid thugs kyi nam mkha' bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:13411: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13412: chen po lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13413: sna tshogs bkod pa'i ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13414: yid bzhin nor bu'i ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:13417: bde' ba chen po la sogs pa'i zhing khams ya na tan can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13418: rin po che sna tshogs las 'grub cing mdzes pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:13419: rgyan dang ldan pas gzhal yas yon tan can dang
NK124(ngo)001:13420: / thugs rje'i 'od zer snang ba'i rtags su 'od zer yon tan can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13421: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13423: nyi zla pad ma la sogs pa'i gdan khri yon tan can dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13424: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan zhing rin po che'i rgyan
NK124(ngo)001:13425: sna tshogs dang ldan pas rgyan cha yon tan can
NK124(ngo)001:13427: zhing khams gzhal yas dkyil 'khor dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13428: gdan khri rgyan rnams zad 'phel med //
NK124(ngo)001:13435: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las kyis gang
NK124(ngo)001:13436: la gang 'dul las su ci ltar mtshams pa ltar
NK124(ngo)001:13437: don mdzad pa'o // de nyid las /
NK124(ngo)001:13438: tshad med 'phrin las zhi rgyas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13439: dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13441: gzhan yang ma h+aa yo ga'i sa bcu 'khor lo tshogs chen las khyad par 'phags pa'i /
NK124(ngo)001:13442: lung a nu yo ga rang gzhung gi sa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13444: gdal ba chos nyid sa zhes pa'am //
NK124(ngo)001:13445: kun bzang dbye' ba med pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:13446: thog med mngon gyur lhun gyis grub //
NK124(ngo)001:13448: dbyings ye shes dbyer med mngon du gyur zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:13449: shes bya kun la khyab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13450: gdal ba chen po'i sa yang thob cing /
NK124(ngo)001:13451: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams rang snang du lhun gyis grub cing bzang ngan dang dbye' bsal med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13452: kun tu bzang po dbye' ba med pa'i sa zhes bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13453: mdo' sngags theg pa'i dgongs don gsal byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:13454: a nu yo ga'i 'dod pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:13455: gsum pa dbang po rab kyi yang rab rdzogs pa
NK124(ngo)001:13456: chen po'i don rtogs shing nyams su len pa la
NK124(ngo)001:13457: bzhi ste / theg pa 'og ma a nu yo ga man chad dang shan dbye' ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13458: bye brag gi gol sa bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13459: rdzogs pa chen po'i yon tan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13460: rtogs shing bral ba'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13467: lung man ngag la sogs pa'i khung dang khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13468: rang rang skabs nas bshad pa bzhin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13470: ma h+aa yo ga' don dam du //
NK124(ngo)001:13471: rang rig gnyis med de bzhin nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:13472: rtogs pa'i cho 'phrul la sogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:13473: lhar snang ngang las 'khor ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:13475: a nu yo ga don dam du //
NK124(ngo)001:13476: bde chen rtogs pa'i rig rtsal las //
NK124(ngo)001:13478: de phyir skye bos rtags pa 'khrul //
NK124(ngo)001:13480: a ti yo gas bden gnyis bral //
NK124(ngo)001:13481: thams cad rang byung rang snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13483: ma h+aa yo ga bas snang ba sems kyis cho 'phrul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13484: a nu sems kyis rtsal snang bar 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:13485: a ti 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK124(ngo)001:13486: cad rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba la
NK124(ngo)001:13488: 'og ma gnyis ni sems las snang ba'i cho 'phrul rtsal du 'dod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13489: gzhi ngo bo sems su lta zhing shugs kyis 'dzin pa'i cha dang ma bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13490: a ti ni chos kun rang byung ye shes la
NK124(ngo)001:13491: rgya chad phyogs lhung med par chos kun mnyam nyid
NK124(ngo)001:13492: du grol ba'o // yang ma h+aa snang ba chos nyid du 'dod la /
NK124(ngo)001:13493: rtag zhes chos nyid du mi 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13494: a nu snang rtag gnyis chos nyid du 'dod la zhen pa mi 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13495: a ti chos kun rang byung gi ye shes mngon
NK124(ngo)001:13496: sum du snang bas bcos slad med par chos nyid
NK124(ngo)001:13498: chos nyid med pa'i chos gcig kyang med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13500: rang bzhin nyid la rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13501: de phyir lta sogs khyad par bas //
NK124(ngo)001:13502: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13503: a ti ni gnyis dang gnyis med kyis phyogs la mi gnas shing rang grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:13505: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13506: 'gyur ba ma yin drang por gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:13507: nam mkha' bzhin du mtha' mnyam las //
NK124(ngo)001:13508: gzhan las ltos gyur chos ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13511: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:13512: bden pa gnyis kyi snyad las 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:13517: mtshan bcas mtshan med dang bsnyen sgrub bzhi la sogs pa rtsol bsgrub kyi mtha' las 'das la /
NK124(ngo)001:13518: a ti b+hee bya b+hee byed med par gcig char nyid kyis rang b+hee yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13520: b+hee dang b+hee byar bya ba gnyis med de //
NK124(ngo)001:13521: b+hee pa'i tshe na ci yang mi b+hee mo //
NK124(ngo)001:13522: chos kyi dbyings na b+hee rgyu brdul tsam med //
NK124(ngo)001:13525: ye 'byams chos nyid rtogs nas ma yengs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13526: ye 'byams chos nyid dgongs pa yin par bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:13529: 'og ma gnyis bya byed rtsol bsgrub can yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:13530: a ti bya byed rtsol bsgrub med pa bya bral bde' ba chen por gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13531: yi ge med pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:13532: ci spyod don las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:13533: thug phrad rang grol rtsis zin na //
NK124(ngo)001:13534: ming tsam gcod ces de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:13537: 'og ma gnyis zhe 'dod rtsol bsgrub kyis bsgrub pas shugs kyis spangs thob can du 'gyur la /
NK124(ngo)001:13539: shes bya ci lta ba nyid che ba lngar sangs rgyas la /
NK124(ngo)001:13540: de nyid ma bcos par mngon du byas pas spangs thob lhag ma med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13541: rgyas par rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13542: gnyis pa gol sa bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:13543: a ti la skur pa 'debs pa'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13544: kha 'byams tshig gis lta bar gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13545: ma rtogs pa'i b+hee par gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13546: a ti la ltos nas a nu man chad gol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13548: rdzogs pa chen po bstan pa nam mkha' dang 'dra zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:13549: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK124(ngo)001:13550: bstan pa thams cad kyi yang snying 'di la /
NK124(ngo)001:13551: blo chung phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyis skur pa btab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13552: nam mkha' gnas kyi bar du dmyal bar 'gro gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13554: gang zhig gsang ba'i gsung mchog la //
NK124(ngo)001:13555: gang zhig spongs shing skur btab pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13556: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog spong ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:13557: thar pa'i sems dang gtan du bral //
NK124(ngo)001:13559: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:13560: nges don rdzogs chen snying po'i don bshad du //
NK124(ngo)001:13561: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' skrag /
NK124(ngo)001:13562: rgyud lung rnal 'byor sgro skur 'debs shing 'phyal //
NK124(ngo)001:13563: tshul chos sde pa zhe sdang dbang gis 'phrag dog byed //
NK124(ngo)001:13564: nges don 'di la 'gal sems sdig can rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13565: dmyal bar nges 'gro gtan du snying re rje //
NK124(ngo)001:13568: don bstan skad cig de nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:13569: rgyud lung sangs rgyas skrag cing sdangs //
NK124(ngo)001:13570: nyan thos mdo sde rgyal zhing 'bog /
NK124(ngo)001:13571: lha dang lha mi srin po' tshogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13572: sgro skur 'debs pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13573: gtan du dmyal ba chen por ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:13576: kun bzang dgongs pa 'di la bshe' 'gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:13577: nam mkha' ji srid gnas kyis bar du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13578: shi ba'i 'og tu rdo rje dmyal bar 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:13581: bstan pa'i snyigs ma tha ma'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:13582: nyon mongs sdug bsngal ngos drag pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13584: bstan pa'i sgor zhugs chos byed kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:13585: bstan gnyis grub mtha' ngan pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:13586: chos la phyogs dang ris bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13587: log rtogs rtsod pa 'phel ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13588: nyon mongs 'phrag dog dbang gis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13589: chos pas chos spongs las byed 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:13590: phyogs bral mnyam nyid ma rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13591: byis pa'i blo can rmongs pa'i mis //
NK124(ngo)001:13593: rang chos bstod cing gzhan la smod //
NK124(ngo)001:13594: bstan pa'i snying po gsang sngags la //
NK124(ngo)001:13596: zhes sogs rgyud lung man ngag du ma nas gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:13597: gnyis pa lta ba las gol ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13598: chos kun rang byung ye shes mngon sum du snang zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:13599: ye nas sangs rgyas pa nyid blo che ba rnams
NK124(ngo)001:13600: la da ltar gyi snang ba 'di nyid ma bcos
NK124(ngo)001:13601: ma slad na / 'khor ba rang grol lam gnyis med rang snang du ngo sprad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13603: snang srid chos skur shar nas /
NK124(ngo)001:13604: sa dang lam grang rtsol ba med par sangs rgyas par gsungs pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:13606: 'khrul grol gyis shan ma phyed par kha 'byams tshig gi lta ba la mngon par zhen nas /
NK124(ngo)001:13607: snang ba 'di ka ltar sangs rgyas yin zhes dngos
NK124(ngo)001:13608: po rang kha ma la smra ba ni gol bar
NK124(ngo)001:13609: gsungs te / nam mkha' mtha' mnyam las /
NK124(ngo)001:13610: skal med sgra bzhin spyod pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13612: rang gi rnam rtog mi mthun pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13613: rang gsal gnyis med ye shes la //
NK124(ngo)001:13614: yin dang ma yin cha 'dzin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:13618: 'dab gshog ma rgyas par 'phur mi nus //
NK124(ngo)001:13619: nyams su ma blangs kha tshig gis //
NK124(ngo)001:13620: chags sdang zil gyis mi non te //
NK124(ngo)001:13621: skye bo tha mal pa ru gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13623: rang byung bde' ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:13624: dpe' na bya sgro rlung khyer 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:13625: nges med gzhi la blo gtad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13626: ma rtog rtsol bsgrub ci spyad kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:13627: mi grol dug lnga rgyas par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13630: snying rje med pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13631: deng sang dus nas 'byung ba dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13632: kun bzang tshig tsam smra byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:13633: gdeng med don dang mi ldan par //
NK124(ngo)001:13634: phata hral rtsing chos na rag snod //
NK124(ngo)001:13635: rgyud 'bras don la yid dbyung zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:13636: tshig tsam lta ba brten pa dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13637: gdeng med spyod rtsing 'cha' ba'i rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:13638: bskal par dge ba ci spyad kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:13642: gdeng med lta ba mtho' 'dod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13643: rang gi nga rgyal bsnyoms byed pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13644: ri bos srog chags mnan pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:13645: nam du thar pa'i khar mi 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:13646: zhes pa la sogs rgyud lung man ngag du ma nas gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13647: gsum pa don ma rtogs pa'i b+hee pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13649: mi grol zhing gol bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13651: dpyid dus so nams ma byas par //
NK124(ngo)001:13652: ston dus r+ts+wa ru 'gro ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:13653: rang sems don nyid ma rtogs par //
NK124(ngo)001:13654: b+hee du 'gro ba snying re rje //
NK124(ngo)001:13655: rkyal ma sbyangs pa chur 'jug ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:13656: de bzhin ma rtogs su b+hee pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13659: yul dang gol sa ma chod par //
NK124(ngo)001:13663: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong par //
NK124(ngo)001:13664: bsam med ngang du gang 'jug pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13665: byis pa de nyid blun po ste //
NK124(ngo)001:13666: mun pa'i skye mched nyid du ltung //
NK124(ngo)001:13669: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong bar //
NK124(ngo)001:13671: blun po mun sprul blo can te //
NK124(ngo)001:13672: long ba'i grong khyer chen por 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:13674: bzhi pa a ti la ltos nas a nu man chad gol bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13675: de yang chos kun rang byung gi ye shes rang snang zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:13676: ye nas 'dus ma byas su sangs rgyas pa la /
NK124(ngo)001:13677: nyan rang gis skyon du bzung nas spangs shing bkag pas gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13678: dbu' ma sems tsam gyis bden pa gnyis su bzung nas sbyangs pas gol ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13680: sngags nang pa gnyis kyis bsgyur zhing dbang du byed
NK124(ngo)001:13681: pas rang byung ye shes la bcos cing gol bar
NK124(ngo)001:13683: 'di man rgyu 'bras mnyam pa'i theg che la //
NK124(ngo)001:13684: spang gegs sbyangs pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13685: rang sems chos nyid don la sgrib cing gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13686: rang la bzhag nas gzhan la rgyang du 'tshol //
NK124(ngo)001:13687: bya med bde bor rtsol ba dang du len //
NK124(ngo)001:13688: tshe chad pa'i nad la de las che ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:13689: ma yengs ting 'dzin b+hee pa'i brten phung yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13690: ye nas yin la yangs med shor ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:13691: ma yengs ting 'dzin re ba'i blu mkhan des //
NK124(ngo)001:13692: rgyu 'bras theg chen drang ba'i lung bstan yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13695: mdo' sde dang ni kri ya dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13696: u pa ya dang yo ga dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13697: ma h+aa yo ga a nu drug /
NK124(ngo)001:13698: rdzogs pa chen po'i gol sa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:13702: mu stegs rang bsam log pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13703: brgyad kyis rang 'dod dbyings la ltas //
NK124(ngo)001:13704: phyi nang med par spro bsdu' byas //
NK124(ngo)001:13705: ngo bo nyid la dmigs 'dzin byas //
NK124(ngo)001:13706: rang byung nyid la rgyu las brtsol //
NK124(ngo)001:13707: ma bcos spyi yang ma yin la //
NK124(ngo)001:13708: ci yang 'dzin pa'i bsam pa brtags //
NK124(ngo)001:13710: lam brgyad bsgrod pas bsgrod med slad //
NK124(ngo)001:13713: log lta mu stegs rnam gnyis dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13714: phyi rol yang dag gsang sngags lam //
NK124(ngo)001:13715: gsang chen 'khrul tshul nges bshad nyon //
NK124(ngo)001:13716: ces sogs rgyud lung man ngag nas rgya cher gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13717: spyi don gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po'i yon tan la drug ste /
NK124(ngo)001:13718: bka' rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13719: lnga rgya tha ma la byang phyogs kha ba can
NK124(ngo)001:13720: gyi rgyal khams su dar zhing sems can gyi sgron
NK124(ngo)001:13721: me byed pa lung bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13722: bstan pa 'dzin cing 'chang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13728: bstan pa'i snying po bka' rdzogs pa chen po lnga
NK124(ngo)001:13729: brgya'i tha ma la kha ba can du 'byung bar
NK124(ngo)001:13730: gsungs te / rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:13731: dus kyi tha ma lnga brgya na //
NK124(ngo)001:13733: mtshon dang mu ge tshe thung dus //
NK124(ngo)001:13734: rdzogs chen snying po dus der bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:13735: de yang rdo rje sems dpa' nyon //
NK124(ngo)001:13736: de yang dus kyi deng sang nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13737: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'dzin daka'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:13738: 'dzam gling bod kyi byang phyogs su //
NK124(ngo)001:13739: lung dang bstan gnyis mang po 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:13740: lus dang sems kyi chos dar te //
NK124(ngo)001:13741: sde snod chos rnams nub 'gyur zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:13742: de tshe skal ldan g+ha g+ha la //
NK124(ngo)001:13743: rang sems rtogs pa tsam gyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13747: de nas thugs rje'i byin rlabs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13748: dad pa las 'phro ldan pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13749: gnyis su med par mthun pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13750: mtha' 'khob yul du snang gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13751: skal ldan rig rgyud 'dzin pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13752: rang gsal rig pa'i don go nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13754: 'di rnams skal ldan rgyal sras te //
NK124(ngo)001:13755: rigs su nges pa nyid du gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13758: rtsod bral gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:13759: lha gnas gsum du grags gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13760: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13761: 'dzam gling dbus su rgyas par byed //
NK124(ngo)001:13762: rgyal sras gsang ba'i snod ldan la //
NK124(ngo)001:13763: sna rgyud rig pa lnga'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:13764: 'phrul tshig rig pa'i sgo nas bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:13765: gsang tshig rig pa'i snod ldan rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13766: ma bcos gsang ba'i snod ldan la //
NK124(ngo)001:13768: de nas gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:13770: der yang gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:13771: skal ldan gdul bya ngos dag dus //
NK124(ngo)001:13772: rig pa'i sgron me byed par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13774: gnyis pa bstan pa 'dzin cing 'chang ba la'ang rgyal ba kun gyis bu bzhin skyob cing /
NK124(ngo)001:13775: rgyal ba'i gsung 'dzin bka' la gnas par bstan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13777: klog dang bri dang 'dzin pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:13778: kun kyang bu bzhin skyong bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:13780: bstan pa'i snying po gang 'chang ba //
NK124(ngo)001:13781: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs 'chang bas //
NK124(ngo)001:13782: de bzhin ma nor rig pa 'dzin //
NK124(ngo)001:13785: rgyud 'di glegs bam la bris te //
NK124(ngo)001:13787: rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin bka' la gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:13789: tha na ming tsam 'dzin cing mos pas kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:13790: ngan song du mi ltung zhing thar lam rnyed par 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:13792: skyes bu dam pa'i spyod yul te //
NK124(ngo)001:13793: yon tan sgra sgrogs sus thos pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13794: ming tsam gyis kyang bde' thob cing //
NK124(ngo)001:13795: dran pas ngan 'gro las skyob yin //
NK124(ngo)001:13799: ngan song sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:13800: thar pa bde ba'i lam rnyed 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13801: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13802: gsum pa 'di la mos pa byas pas sangs rgyas rnams dang skal ba mnyam par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13804: 'di la mos pa'i gang zag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13805: sangs rgyas sa la skal ba mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:13808: nges don 'di la gang mos rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:13809: bka' dang mthun par don go nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13810: rdul tsam du'ang ma b+hee kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:13811: sangs rgyas sa la smos ci dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:13815: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin rlabs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13816: bsod nams mi zad gter dang mjal //
NK124(ngo)001:13818: kun tu bzang pos de skad bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:13819: ces sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:13821: gzhung bzhin du nyan cing spyad na sangs rgyas bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13823: de yang 'dus pa'i snying po nyon //
NK124(ngo)001:13824: dbang po rab kyis don du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13825: bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:13826: thig le nyag gcig chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:13827: shes pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas nges //
NK124(ngo)001:13830: gzhung ni thos shing spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:13831: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa thob //
NK124(ngo)001:13832: rgyal ba nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:13833: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13835: lnga pa gzhung bzhin du spyad pa'i yon tan ni /
NK124(ngo)001:13836: bla ma'i yon tan gyis skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:13838: rtogs nas ma b+hee kyang sangs rgyas pa'i yon tan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13839: rtogs shing goms pa'i yon tan rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13841: chos kun rang byung ye shes su ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13842: de rtogs nas ma b+hee kyang sangs rgyas shing yon tan thams cad rdzogs par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13844: bde' legs ci snyed ma lus kun gyis dngos //
NK124(ngo)001:13845: bder gshegs byang chub rtogs pa nyid la 'dus //
NK124(ngo)001:13848: dper na nor bu rin chen la //
NK124(ngo)001:13850: de bzhin chos sku nges don la //
NK124(ngo)001:13851: rtogs pa tsam gyis yon tan rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13854: skye shi med pa rang gi sems //
NK124(ngo)001:13855: de rtogs b+hee du rdul tsam med //
NK124(ngo)001:13856: de nyid rig pa chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:13857: ma b+hee 'bral med bde' ba'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:13859: 'og nas rtogs grol dus mnyam gyi bskor ltar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:13860: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bcu bzhi ste //
NK124(ngo)001:13861: gol sa thams cad dus gcig la chod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13862: sgrib pa thams cad dus gcig la dag pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13863: tshogs gnyis dus gcig la rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13864: mkha' 'gro chos skyongs bka' gnyan pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13865: mchod pa thams cad kyi mchog yin pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13867: sdom pa gsum rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13868: shes rab gsum rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13869: dge ba bcu rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13870: pha rol du phyin pa drug rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13871: tshad med bzhi rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13872: gsang sngags kyi 'bras bu ma lus pa rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13873: sa dang lam dus gcig la rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13874: 'bras bu sku lnga la sogs sangs rgyas kyi yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13876: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la yul dang
NK124(ngo)001:13877: yul can med par rtogs pas gol du gol sa
NK124(ngo)001:13879: sgrib du sgrib byed med par gol sa thams cad dus gcig la chod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13881: nyi shar mun sgrib med pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:13882: rang byung chos sku'i don rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13883: gol sgrib yul sems gzhi nas dag /
NK124(ngo)001:13884: chos kun sel med byang chub sku //
NK124(ngo)001:13886: byung tshor rjes su ma 'brang bas //
NK124(ngo)001:13887: 'jig rten phal pa'i sar mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13888: sgo lnga'i shes pa mi 'gags pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13889: 'du shes med par de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13890: shes rab zab mo'i don 'dzin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13891: lung ma bstan du de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13892: zhi gnas ro la ma zhen pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13893: sems 'dzin bsam gtan sar mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13894: yul med yul du ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13895: rtag chad mthar ni de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13896: rnam rtog ma spang rang zhi bas //
NK124(ngo)001:13897: nyan thos 'og mar der mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13898: rtogs dka' stong ba ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13899: rang rgyal sems su de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13900: rang rig skad cig ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13901: sems tsam lta bar de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13902: yul 'di kun rdzob blos byas te //
NK124(ngo)001:13903: he du dag gis bzhigs rgyas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13904: mtshan ma stong par ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13905: dbu' ma gnyis su de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13906: dag gzhi ting 'dzin ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13907: kri ya'i theg par de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13908: chos nyid dbyings kyi ye shes kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:13910: byang chub sems lngar ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13911: yo ga'i sems dpa' de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13913: phung po khams dang skye mched kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13914: rtogs tshogs rnam grangs mang po yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13915: rnam rtog ltar ni ma b+hee pas //
NK124(ngo)001:13916: ma h+aa yo gar de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13917: kun gzhi dag pa'i mkha' klong du //
NK124(ngo)001:13918: bde chen gnyis med rig pa'i rtsal //
NK124(ngo)001:13920: a nu yo gar de mi gol //
NK124(ngo)001:13922: lung de rnams kyis nges don blang las mtha' bkrol zhing rgyas par bshad do //
NK124(ngo)001:13924: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13925: rig pa la sgrib pa med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:13927: las dang las kyis gos pa med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:13929: bsags pa'i sgrib pa thams cad dus gcig la 'dag pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13931: bskal par bsags pa'i mun pa 'thug po yang //
NK124(ngo)001:13932: rig pa'i rgyal po ye shes nyi zer gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13933: gnyen po mi mthun spong la mi ltos par //
NK124(ngo)001:13934: skad cig yud tsam nyid la gsal ba'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:13937: snying po don gyi gzhi rtogs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13938: rang bzhin tshogs rdzogs sgrib pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:13941: thog ma nyid nas bsags pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:13942: rnam rtog sprin du dpag med pa //
NK124(ngo)001:13943: stong med chos sku rig pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:13944: rnam rtog stong pa'i ngang du yal //
NK124(ngo)001:13945: 'di shes rang rig b+hee pa'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:13948: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13949: gang la'ang phyogs rig dang zhen 'dzin med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:13950: bla ma dang rgyal ba thams cad mnyam pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13951: bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs la /
NK124(ngo)001:13952: de nyid rang gsal sgrib pa med pas ye shes kyis tshogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13954: rang rig ltar ni bdag b+hee na //
NK124(ngo)001:13955: bsod nams ye shes dus gcig rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13958: 'bras bu ye shes tshogs ni sems nyid de //
NK124(ngo)001:13959: bsod nams ye shes byang chub sems la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13960: spyad pas mi mdzad ma bsags dbri' ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:13961: klong yang nam mkha' rgya mtsho' lta bu yi //
NK124(ngo)001:13962: tshogs chen rnam gnyis thams cad rang la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:13965: rtogs shing nyams su myong ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:13967: lha srin sde brgyad thams cad kyi gnod pas mi tshugs shing bran bzhin byed pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:13969: nges don rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK124(ngo)001:13970: lha srin mkha' 'gro dgrar langs kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:13971: gnod pas mi tshugs bka' bzhin byed //
NK124(ngo)001:13972: de phyir lung bstan shin tu brten //
NK124(ngo)001:13975: don 'di tshigs du ma khyer bar //
NK124(ngo)001:13976: gnad kyis gdeng du chud pa gang //
NK124(ngo)001:13977: dman pa'i lus la dam pa'i sems //
NK124(ngo)001:13978: dus gsum sangs rgyas sras gcig po //
NK124(ngo)001:13979: 'jig rten dregs pas bcing ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:13980: lha srin sde brgyad thams cad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:13981: jo bo'i tshul bzhin 'khur bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:13982: sangs rgyas kun dang bla ma mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:13985: sems nyid rtogs shing nyams su blangs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:13986: rgyal ba thams cad dang dgongs pa gnyis su med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:13987: mchod pa thams cad kyi mchog tu gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:13989: dus gsum sangs rgyas rtag tu sems ltas mchod //
NK124(ngo)001:13990: de'i yon tan mi 'bral de thob nas //
NK124(ngo)001:13991: chos rnams kun byed rgyal por nges par 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:13994: sangs rgyas mi mchod bdag nyid mchod //
NK124(ngo)001:13997: rtogs shing goms pa la skyabs gsum dkon mchog gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:13998: skyabs bsrung ba thams cad kyis mchog yin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:13999: sems b+hee don bcu gnyis pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:14000: bdag med gnyis med bde bar gshegs /
NK124(ngo)001:14001: mi rtogs ye shes chos dbyings sku brnyes pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14002: kun gyis rang bzhin 'di la gsal zhing bla med lam mchog ste /
NK124(ngo)001:14003: mi ldog pa la sogs te dbang phyug rgyal ba kun dang gcig brnyes pa /
NK124(ngo)001:14004: gnas gsum mnyam nyid de la bdag med yid kyis rab tu dad pas mos /
NK124(ngo)001:14006: rang lus na tsha bzod dka' ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14007: rkyen dbang mi gol gang zag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14008: gang la blo'i ma bzung bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14009: bzod dka' rang rig chos skur shes //
NK124(ngo)001:14010: snga phyi ma btang da lta yis //
NK124(ngo)001:14011: bde' sdug dag kyang chos skur gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14012: bde' sdug rang bzhin chos skur shar //
NK124(ngo)001:14013: yid chad 'khang zhi'i rkyen rnams thub //
NK124(ngo)001:14016: sems nyid rang byung ye shes su rtogs shing nyams su myong ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:14017: sdom pa gsum rdzogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14018: nyes pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14019: nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14020: gnyis su med pa'i snying rje 'gro don rdzogs pa byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14021: de nyid las mi d+ha bas gsang sngags kyi dam tshig gis yongs su rdzogs par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:14022: sems b+hee don bcu gnyis pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:14023: tshul khrims la sogs pha rol phyin lam spyod pa rgya mtsho'i gzhir 'gyur ba //
NK124(ngo)001:14025: dkyil 'khor gsang bar zhugs shing theg chen dam tshig gi mchog kyang bsdus pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:14026: tshul khrims las sdom pa kun 'dus shing sbyin gnas dam pa rab tu sngags //
NK124(ngo)001:14029: sdom pa phyi nang dam tshig kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:14030: gdul bya ci ltar gdul bar ston //
NK124(ngo)001:14031: tha snyad tsam du 'dul mos kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:14032: dam du bca' ba sdug bsngal tsam med //
NK124(ngo)001:14035: chos kun sems kyis ming 'dogs su thob cing go bas /
NK124(ngo)001:14036: tshig dang yi ge rigs su rjes su mi 'brang
NK124(ngo)001:14037: ba ni thos pa las 'byung ba'i shes rab dang
NK124(ngo)001:14038: / de'i don la bsam pas rtogs spyod the tshom med par thag chod pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14039: bsam pa las 'byung ba'i shes rab kyis sgro 'dogs chod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14040: de kha tsam tshig tsam ma yin par nyams su
NK124(ngo)001:14041: myong bas spang bya dgag sgrubs med par rang grol
NK124(ngo)001:14042: ba ni / b+hee pa las 'byung ba'i shes rab ste /
NK124(ngo)001:14045: gcig char ba dang rim skyes pa'i dmigs shes par byas te rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14047: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs shing nyams
NK124(ngo)001:14048: su myong bas mi dge ba'i sel med cing ci
NK124(ngo)001:14049: byed dge' bar 'gro bas dge bcu' yongs su rdzogs
NK124(ngo)001:14050: pa yin te / de'i bye brag gzhung bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14052: rtogs shing nyams su myong ba las pha rol du phyin pa drug tshang ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14054: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14055: nyes byas mi 'byung bas tshul khrims las kyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14056: khong khro ba med cing rtogs pa'i klong du kun shong bas bzod pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14057: ma yengs 'du bral med pas brtson 'grus dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14058: rgyun mi 'chad cing snying po'i don mi g.yel bas bsam gtan gyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14059: rang byung ye shes rtogs shing 'khor 'das kyi rtsa
NK124(ngo)001:14060: ba chod pas shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin
NK124(ngo)001:14063: lo ka gol bar don rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14064: ser sna 'dzin pa'i sems med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:14065: re ba med pa'i sbyin pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14066: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14067: ma nor khrims la mi 'da' phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14068: lus ngag yid kyi las rnams kun //
NK124(ngo)001:14069: mi dge' ba'i nyes byas mi 'byung bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14070: tshul khrims pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14071: zab la rgya che lta ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:14072: yin dang min pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK124(ngo)001:14073: chos kyi dbyings su kun shong bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14074: bzod pa'i pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14075: ngo bo nyid las 'bral med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:14076: ched du mi b+hee da lta nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:14077: lta ba'i don la ma yengs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14078: brtson 'grus pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14079: bzhi gsum dus gsum 'bral med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14080: ye shes kun tu rgyun mi chad //
NK124(ngo)001:14081: snying po'i don la ma g.yos pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14082: bsam gtan pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14083: dang po'i 'khor ba rtsad chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14084: ye shes rig pa ngos zin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14085: yid ches gding gis thag chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14086: shes rab pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14089: bdag gzhan gnyis su med par rtogs shing mi gtong 'dzin pas snying rje dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14090: brtse bas kun la khyab cing bsnyoms pas byams pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14091: mi 'bral zhing spro bas dga' ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14092: kun la snyoms shing nye ring med pas btang bsnyoms /
NK124(ngo)001:14093: rgya' mtsho klong dgu'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:14094: snying rjes mi byed yul las bral //
NK124(ngo)001:14095: byams pa nam mkha'i mtha' ltar brdal //
NK124(ngo)001:14096: dga' ba rang byung gsal ba'i nyams //
NK124(ngo)001:14097: gtang snyoms 'dzin bral yengs pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:14100: snying rje chen pos cir mi mdzad //
NK124(ngo)001:14101: byams pa'i don gnyis rnams sbyangs phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14102: dga' ba chen po rtsol med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14103: gtang snyoms snyam med kun tu khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:14105: bcu gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:14106: gsang sngags kyi bsgrubs pa kun rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14109: rtogs shing nyams su len pa la bskyed rim la
NK124(ngo)001:14110: sogs bsgrubs pa thams cad don gyis tshang zhing rdzogs
NK124(ngo)001:14111: pa yin te / 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog grol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:14112: rkyen rnams grogs su shar bas /
NK124(ngo)001:14113: phyi nang gi 'tshams bcad rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14114: rang gis rang ngos shes pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14115: ma rig pa nyon mongs pa dang las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14116: shes bya'i sgrib pa la sogs pas rang sar dag pa don gyis gshegs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14117: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing rang sems sangs rgyas su rtogs pa'i brten pa byin rlabs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14118: 'byung ba lnga rang byung ye shes su gsal bas 'byung ba rim rtsegs rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14119: thams cad sems nyid la gnas shing bzhugs pa'i gzhal yas sam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14120: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing dbyer med pas spyan drangs stim pa la sogs rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14121: phyogs 'dzin log rtogs sgral zhing gnyis med don la sbyor bas sbyor sgrol la sogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14122: yon tan lhun gyis grub cing mthar phyin pas smon pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14123: chos kun sku gsung thugs su 'dus shing /
NK124(ngo)001:14124: de'i rol pa ltar snang bas don gyis bzlas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14125: snod bcud rig par longs spyod pas tshogs kyis mchod pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14126: 'khor 'das thig le nyag gcig tu 'dus shing /
NK124(ngo)001:14127: ci spyod don la mi d+ha bas dal bsdu' ba la sogs rdzogs pa'i yon tan no //
NK124(ngo)001:14129: lta ba med pa'i gdeng zin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14130: mi rtog ye shes gegs sel bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14131: rnam par rtog pa'i bgegs med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:14132: phyi nang 'tshams bcad de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14133: ye nas ngo bo nyid sku la //
NK124(ngo)001:14134: ma rig rnam rtog sgrib pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:14135: bsgrub tu med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:14136: don gyis bshags pa de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14137: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14138: yul dang dbang po mi 'byed pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14139: gnyis med don gyis blo gsal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14140: byin gyis rlabs pas de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14141: dbang po yul gyis rnam pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:14142: dngos po 'byung ba'i rtsa ba ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14143: sa chu me rlung kun khyab pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14144: dbang chen rim pa de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14145: bden dang yig 'bru la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14146: rang gis sems kyi cho 'phrul te //
NK124(ngo)001:14147: phyogs bcu' rang bzhin lhun grub pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14148: gzhal yas khang chen de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14150: rig tshor don gyi lha min pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14151: ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:14152: ye shes lha rnams de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14153: ngo bo nyid kyi snying po la //
NK124(ngo)001:14154: sangs rgyas sems can rgyu gcig phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14155: ye nas gnas pa'i ched du byed med rig pa 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:14156: spyan drengs stims pa de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14157: ye nas snying po byang chub la //
NK124(ngo)001:14158: blo dang dngos po gcig pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14159: sems dang chos su don 'byor bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14160: sbyor sgrol mchod pa de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14161: ye nas gnas pa'i don go bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14162: skye 'chi med par thag chod phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14163: yon tan thams cad lhun grub pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14164: mthar phyin smon lam de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14165: sangs rgyas che ba'i yon tan gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14166: sku gsung thugs kyi don tshang pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14167: da lta nyid du rtogs pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14169: dga' ldan lha dang 'byor ldan tshogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14170: nges pa'i lta bas gding zin pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:14171: snod bcud ye nas tshogs yin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14172: tshogs kyi mchod pa de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14174: thig le gcig tu 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14175: ci spyod rang gi lus ngag la //
NK124(ngo)001:14176: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa de la rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14178: de la sogs pa lung man ngag du ma nas gsungs par 'dug go //
NK124(ngo)001:14180: chos kun rang byung ye shes la /
NK124(ngo)001:14181: bgegs rigs dang nyon mongs pa la sogs ngang gis zhi bas zhi ba'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14182: rang byung ye shes mtha' dbus phyogs mtshams med cing yon tan thams cad rdzogs pas rgyas pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14183: rig pa la dbang thob cing snang ba dbang du 'dus pas dbang dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14184: log rtog phyogs 'dzin la sogs pa gnyis su med par sgral bas drag po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14187: nyon mongs rang sar zhi ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14188: byang chub sems 'di zhi bar grags //
NK124(ngo)001:14189: yon tan mchog tu rgyas pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14190: byang chub sems ni rgyas par grags //
NK124(ngo)001:14191: rig pa rang dbang thob pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14192: byang chub sems ni dbang du grags //
NK124(ngo)001:14193: 'khrul pa rtsad nas bcod pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14194: byang chub sems ni drag por grags //
NK124(ngo)001:14196: rang byung ye shes la 'khor 'das gnyis su med
NK124(ngo)001:14197: pas lam la bgrod du med cing lam lnga dus
NK124(ngo)001:14199: sa la sbyangs du med cing sa rnams dus gcig la non pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14201: rang byung ye shes dngos su rtogs pas tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pas tshogs lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14202: chos nyid rang gis mtshan nyid la dngos su sbyor bas sbyor lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14203: chos nyid 'du 'bral med par mngon sum mthong bas mthong lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14204: de'i ngang la g.yos pa med par gnas pas b+hee lam dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14205: de nyid rtogs pa mthar phyin pas mthar lam ste /
NK124(ngo)001:14206: de rnams rang snang mngon sum rtogs pas dus gcig la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14208: ye nas thig le dbyer med tshogs kyi lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14209: rtogs pa'i ye shes dbyer med sbyor ba'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14210: chos nyid don rtogs bde chen mthong ba'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14211: yid kyi g.yo' ba zad pa b+hee pa'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14212: bya byed med par don rdzogs mthar phyin lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14215: yang dag don gyi chos nyid las //
NK124(ngo)001:14216: lam gyi dbye' ba med mod kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:14218: theg pa'i bye brag tha dad pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:14219: lam gyi dbye' ba dus gcig rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14222: gnas lugs ci bzhin pa nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14223: de nyid rtogs pas sa rnams dus gcig la non pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14225: klong yang 'ub chub gda' khyab pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14226: spyir chib pa bcu' 'dus pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:14227: spyi la bye brag phye ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14228: sa bcu snang ba yon tan yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14231: sa med rdzogs chen chos sku ye shes la //
NK124(ngo)001:14232: gar yang mi 'gro sa mchog spyi chib pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14233: bgrod med sems nyid ye shes mchog gi lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14234: ye shes chos sku mthar phyin chos nyid sa //
NK124(ngo)001:14237: 'khor ba byang chub lam du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14238: cong rong ye shes gnas su spor //
NK124(ngo)001:14239: bgrod med bla ma'i sa la 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:14240: sa gcig gnas pas sa dgu' mnon //
NK124(ngo)001:14242: de yang sems nyid rtogs pa la pha rol du
NK124(ngo)001:14243: phyin pa'i sa bcu dus gcig la rdzogs pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:14244: / 'bras bu'i sa thams cad dus gcig la rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14247: sa lam thams cad lhun grub rang nyid rang //
NK124(ngo)001:14248: mi 'gyur kun gzhi sems kyi sa gzhi la //
NK124(ngo)001:14249: de nyid rang dbang mthong bas rab tu dga' //
NK124(ngo)001:14250: de la gzung 'dzin dag pas dri ma med //
NK124(ngo)001:14251: de nyid rgya ma chad pas 'od byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14252: rtogs pa'i don la ye shes 'od 'phro ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14253: blo'i spyod yul mi 'gyur sbyangs dka' ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14254: rang gis mngon du gyur bas mngon du gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14255: 'dod pa'i blo ma skyes pas ring du song //
NK124(ngo)001:14256: mi skyes mi 'gags dbye' ba med pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:14257: skyon rnams kun gyis ma gos legs pa'i blo //
NK124(ngo)001:14258: thams cad chos nyid dbyings las mi phyed sprin //
NK124(ngo)001:14261: rang byung gi ye shes la sgrib par bsal bas kun du 'od kyi sa zhes bya /
NK124(ngo)001:14262: gang la yang chags pa med cing skyon gyis ma gos pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14263: ma chags pad ma spyan gyi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14264: skye 'jig med pa rdo rje 'dzin gyi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14265: dpag tu med cing thams cad mnyam par bkod pas stug po bkod pa'i sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14266: byang chub sems su thams cad 'dus shing bkod pas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14267: thams cad sku gsung thugs dbyer med cing mnga' mdzad pas rdo rje 'chang gi sa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14268: 'khor 'das dbye ba med cing bzang ngan blang dor
NK124(ngo)001:14269: med par rtogs pas kun bzang dbye' ba med pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:14271: rang byung ye shes ma 'gags pa'i rtags //
NK124(ngo)001:14272: dbang po sgo lnga kun tu gsal ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:14273: kun du 'od kyi sa zhes brtags pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14274: yul la mi rtog chad pa med pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:14275: ma chags pad ma can du brtags pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14276: skye 'jig med pa byang chub sems de la //
NK124(ngo)001:14277: rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes su nga yis brtags //
NK124(ngo)001:14278: rang gis rang bzhin chos dbyings dpag med la //
NK124(ngo)001:14279: rang byung ye shes mi rtog mnyam par bkod //
NK124(ngo)001:14280: stug po bkod pa'i sa zhes btags pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14281: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkyil 'khor te //
NK124(ngo)001:14282: rang la gnas pa'i byang chub chos rnams la //
NK124(ngo)001:14283: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sa rnams te //
NK124(ngo)001:14284: sku gsung thugs la skye dang 'jig med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14285: rdo rje 'chang gi sa zhes bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14286: byang chub sems la rgyu 'bras gnyis med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14287: sems las byung ba'i chos rnams thams cad la //
NK124(ngo)001:14288: bzang ngan blang dor dbye' ba med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14289: dbye' ba med pa'i sa zhes nga yis bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:14290: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:14292: rang sems mngon du rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14293: sku lnga la sogs che ba'i yon tan thams cad dus gcig la rdzogs par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:14294: de'i dbye' ba rgyas par bshad pa ni 'bras bu'i skabs nas ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:14296: stobs dang mi 'jig la sogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14297: thig le chos sku rtogs par 'dus //
NK124(ngo)001:14299: chos sku gzhi nges rtogs pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:14300: ma rig med pas dug lnga grol //
NK124(ngo)001:14301: thams cad rang byung chos sku gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14302: lung ldan rkyen gyis ma rig dag /
NK124(ngo)001:14303: dug lnga byang chub lam yin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14304: sku lnga lhun grub dus gcig rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14306: spyi don bzhi pa rtogs shing grol ba'i thabs la bdun te /
NK124(ngo)001:14316: theg pa'i yang rtser 'jug pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14317: bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas //
NK124(ngo)001:14318: mnar med dmyal ba yan chod du //
NK124(ngo)001:14319: gnyis snang phyi nang chos 'di rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:14320: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14321: phyogs lhung bral ba 'jug sgo yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14323: gzhi ka dag lhun grub kyi dbyer med /
NK124(ngo)001:14324: lam khregs chos thod rgal dbyer med /
NK124(ngo)001:14327: dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi sgo nas 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14328: de rnams rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14329: 'og nas lam dang 'bras bu'i skabs nas ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:14330: gnyis pa stobs kyi lam gsum ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14332: mi rigs rig pa'i chos gsum gyi khyad par 'phags te bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14333: rdzogs chen dgongs pa'i gnas lugs kyi rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14336: de rtogs par bya ba'i thabs so //
NK124(ngo)001:14338: gzhi'i skabs su chos kun rang byung ye shes su
NK124(ngo)001:14339: lhag ma med par rdzogs shing ye nas sangs rgyas
NK124(ngo)001:14342: rtogs thabs dang shes bya dbyer med du gtan la phabs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14343: rtogs thabs rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14345: mngon du phyung ba'i mdo' lugs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14349: gtan la dbab pa'i mdo' lugs dang lnga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14351: chos kun ci ltar snang yang rang byung gi ye
NK124(ngo)001:14352: shes mngon sum du snang bas mngon du phyung ba'o
NK124(ngo)001:14355: rang byung ye shes chos kyi snying po las //
NK124(ngo)001:14356: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK124(ngo)001:14357: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14358: chos kyi snying po yin pas yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14361: ci ltar snang ba'i chos can chos nyid kun //
NK124(ngo)001:14362: rtsol ba ma byas byang chub mi 'gyur zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:14363: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14364: chos kyi snying po yin par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14367: chos kun rang byung ye shes las //
NK124(ngo)001:14368: don dam kun rdzob bden brdzun yin min gnyis med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:14369: snang srid chos skur rtogs shing ma nor nges pa'i mdo' lugs yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14371: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14372: don dam kun rdzob bden brdzun gnyis med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14373: ma nor nges pa'i byang chub sems ston pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14374: the tshom som nyi med par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14377: sems can kun la khyab pa'i snying po ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14378: thams cad rang las byung ba'i ye shes te //
NK124(ngo)001:14379: lung ldan bstan pas shes phyir nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:14380: nges pa'i sangs rgyas yin par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14383: chos kun rang byung ye shes yin pas rgyu 'bras
NK124(ngo)001:14384: gnyis su med cing 'khor 'das gnyis med ye nas
NK124(ngo)001:14387: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14388: rgyu la mi brten rkyen las mi bsgrub pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14389: gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14390: rang byung ye shes yin par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14393: ye nas gnas pa'i rang byung snying po 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:14394: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma skyed pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14395: rgyu 'bras gnyis med ye nas chos sku 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:14396: rang byung ye shes yin par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14399: chos kun rang byung ye shes su ye nas lhun gyis grub pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14400: rgyu rkyen rtsol ba med par bdag gzhan gyi don rnams rtogs pas 'grub pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14402: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK124(ngo)001:14403: rgyu rkyen med par lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14404: 'phrin las rtsol zhing bya byed bya mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:14405: ma btsal lhun gyis grub par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14408: chos kyi dbyings la rtsal dus med //
NK124(ngo)001:14409: rtsal du med pa'i don de la //
NK124(ngo)001:14410: rang bzhin gnas pa'i de bzhin gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:14411: de la sus kyang bcos su med //
NK124(ngo)001:14414: rang byung ye shes la bstan pa thams cad rdzogs shing de nyid ma sgrib par rang gsal /
NK124(ngo)001:14415: chos thams cad gnyis med ngo sprod cing gtan la phebs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14417: rang byung ye shes gcig gis ngo bo de //
NK124(ngo)001:14418: rang byung ye shes ye nas ma sgrib pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14419: chos rnams thams cad gtan la phebs pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14420: bstan pa'i sgron me yin par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14423: sde snod chos rnams man ngag kun gyi ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14424: 'byung gnas gtan la 'bebs pa'i chos yin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14425: bstan pa gong bzhin bstan pa 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14426: bstan pa'i spyi 'brel yin par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14428: de ltar shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med
NK124(ngo)001:14429: par rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba yin
NK124(ngo)001:14430: te / khyad par du phyi nang snod bcud bde
NK124(ngo)001:14431: sdug sna tshogs su snang ba 'di rang byung gi
NK124(ngo)001:14432: ye shes mngon sum du snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14433: gnyis pa rtogs thabs rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14434: lung man ngag rigs pas dngos su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14435: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste dngos su rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14438: rigs pa'i tshad mas mngon sum cer phrad du ngo sprad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14439: gong gi stong thun gyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin rgyas par shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14440: phyi ma ni rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid kyis
NK124(ngo)001:14441: gtan tshigs kyis dngos su rtogs par bya ba dang
NK124(ngo)001:14442: / he du gtan la phab ste rtogs par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14444: rgyud lung man ngag thams cad kyang byang chub sems yin par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14445: des na rang sems nyid ston par snang nas mngon sum du ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14447: byang chub sems la thams cad tshang zhing 'brel pas rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14448: byang chub sems kyis thams cad zin pas lung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14449: de nyid kyis de nyid gnyis su med par ngo sprad pas man ngag yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14450: de rnams kyang byang chub sems la tshang zhing rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14451: de yang mtshon bya don gyi rgyud dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14452: mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14454: lung la ma bstan man ngag rang rig 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:14455: rgyud ni byang chub sems su thams cad 'brel //
NK124(ngo)001:14456: lung ni byang chub sems su thams cad zin //
NK124(ngo)001:14457: man ngag byang chub sems la gzung 'dzin med //
NK124(ngo)001:14458: nyid kyis nyid rtogs nyid du rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14461: theg pa'i khyad par ci snyed du //
NK124(ngo)001:14462: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:14463: klong chen gcig gis yon tan te //
NK124(ngo)001:14464: gdul bya rnams la bstan par zad //
NK124(ngo)001:14467: phyi 'byung ba lnga la sogs pa snang nas ngo sprad nas gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14468: nang nyon mongs pa la sogs par snang nas chos
NK124(ngo)001:14469: nyid mngon sum du ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs
NK124(ngo)001:14471: rang byung gi ye shes de nyid kyi phyir 'byung ba lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14472: 'dod yon lnga la sogs par snang zhing rang byung
NK124(ngo)001:14473: ye shes mngon du phyung nas tshig dang yi ge
NK124(ngo)001:14474: ma yin par don mngon sum ngo sprod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:14475: gnyis su med par gtan la 'bebs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14477: snang ba chos dbyings bla ma ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14479: 'dod yon lnga sogs chos rnams ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14480: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon par //
NK124(ngo)001:14481: ldems dgongs rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14482: snang ba chos kyi dbyings su bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:14485: stong pa bas kyang snang ba gtso' //
NK124(ngo)001:14486: snang ba rang shar nges med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:14488: gnyis med klong du thag chod du //
NK124(ngo)001:14489: rang sar grol ba yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14492: byang chub sems kyi ye shes de //
NK124(ngo)001:14493: ston pa po'i sgor phyung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:14494: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon te //
NK124(ngo)001:14495: rang gis rang bzhin ston byed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14496: bdag tu mi rtogs gzhan mi rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14497: mi rtog mnyams pa'i ngo bos ston //
NK124(ngo)001:14498: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14499: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:14502: nang nyon mongs pa la sogs pa rang byung ye shes mngon du snang nas /
NK124(ngo)001:14503: gnyis su med par ngo sprod cing rang grol du gtan la 'bebs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14504: de yang sems can sangs rgyas su dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14505: sdug bsngal bde chen du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14508: sangs rgyas bas kyang sems can gtso //
NK124(ngo)001:14509: sems can dngos su snang ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:14510: dngos med sangs rgyas gtan la 'bebs //
NK124(ngo)001:14511: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14512: rang sar grol ba yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14514: bde chen bas kyang sdug bsngal gtso //
NK124(ngo)001:14515: sdug bsngal zhen chags mtshan ma yis //
NK124(ngo)001:14516: bde chen chags med gtan la 'bebs //
NK124(ngo)001:14517: gnyis su med par thag chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14518: rang sar grol ba yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14520: ye shes bas kyang nyon mongs gtso //
NK124(ngo)001:14521: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i zhags pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:14522: rang byung ye shes gtan la 'bebs //
NK124(ngo)001:14523: nyon mongs ye shes dbyer med de //
NK124(ngo)001:14524: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14525: rang sar grol ba yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14528: dug lnga spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK124(ngo)001:14529: sangs rgyas bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:14530: de nyid rtogs na sangs rgyas yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14531: nor bu rin chen rnyed pa'i mi //
NK124(ngo)001:14532: 'jig rten so nams mi dgos bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:14533: ma b+hee sems kyis don rtogs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:14534: de las mi d+ha dam tshig yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14536: de rnams ngo sprad pa ni bla ma'i zhal nas shes //
NK124(ngo)001:14537: gnyis pa he du'i gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14538: he du chen po bzhi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14540: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i he du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14541: bdag nyid chen po'i he du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14543: chos kun 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes ma bcos rang snang bas /
NK124(ngo)001:14544: rang bzhin skye med kyi he du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14545: de nyid cir yang snang bas rol pa 'gags med kyi he du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14546: de nyid dbyer med pas mtshan med gnyis med kyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14547: 'ching grol med par blo ngo bo nyid du rang grol ba'i gtan tshigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:14548: de nyid chos kyi sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14551: ngo bo nyid kyi skur ngo sprod //
NK124(ngo)001:14553: rang bzhin skye med gtan tshigs gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14554: lhun gyis grub par yid ches bya //
NK124(ngo)001:14555: rol pa 'gags med gtan tshigs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14556: cir yang 'char bar yid ches bya //
NK124(ngo)001:14557: mtshan nyid gnyis med gtan tshigs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14558: chos rnams cig par yid ches bya //
NK124(ngo)001:14559: ngo bo rang grol gtan tshigs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14560: rtsol ba med par yid kyang ches //
NK124(ngo)001:14563: ma bcos rang gsal bas ngang gi gtan tshigs /
NK124(ngo)001:14564: cir yang snang yang de nyid la mi d+ha bas rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14565: gnyis su med pas bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:14567: rang gi rig pa gsal ba de //
NK124(ngo)001:14568: rang bzhin rig pa cir yang snang //
NK124(ngo)001:14569: bdag nyid stong dang tha dad med //
NK124(ngo)001:14570: 'khrul pa byang chub sems su shes //
NK124(ngo)001:14573: chos nyid mu mtha' med pas dbyings kyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14574: ma sgrib rang gsal bas ye shes kyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14575: de nyid gnyis su med pas gnyis su med pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK124(ngo)001:14577: dbyings dang ye shes gtan tshigs ni //
