NK124(ngo)001:14578: dbyings ni dag pa rgyu yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:14579: ye shes 'bras bu nyid du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14583: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su lhag ma
NK124(ngo)001:14584: med par rdzogs pas bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs
NK124(ngo)001:14586: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14587: thams cad byang chub sems su shes //
NK124(ngo)001:14589: gnyis pa mi rigs rig pa bshad gsum ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14591: mi rigs rig pa bshad gsum ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14592: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14593: mi rigs rig par bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14594: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14595: mi rigs rig par bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14596: lung las ma byung man ngag kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:14597: mi rigs rig par bshad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14599: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14600: rgyu las ma byung ba'i gdams ngag rnams bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14602: sangs rgyas kyi go ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14607: chos kun rang byung ye shes su ye nas sangs rgyas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:14608: dus gsum snga phyi 'pho 'gyur med par ye nas gnas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14609: de yang phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa thams cad rang byung ye shes su snang zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:14610: yul dang yul can med pa snang srid chos skur sangs rgyas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14611: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14613: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14614: rang byung ye shes chos sku ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14615: sangs rgyas kun gyi nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:14616: rnal 'byor kun gyi dam pa'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:14617: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:14619: thog mtha' chod na dus gsum gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:14621: snga phyi med par rang byung sku //
NK124(ngo)001:14622: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14625: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14626: chos nyid mkha' la dbyings nyid klong //
NK124(ngo)001:14627: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14630: tshogs bsags sgrib sbyangs kun rtags pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:14631: sems bral rang byung chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:14632: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14633: theg pa kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:14636: mtha' gang du yang ma lhung bas gsang /
NK124(ngo)001:14637: mtha' thams cad du ma 'gags par snang bas rgyas pa zhes bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:14640: rgyas ni chos sku gsal bar rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:14642: khog dbub kyi skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:14643: gsum pa ngo sprad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14644: spyir rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad du snang ba
NK124(ngo)001:14645: 'di sems can thams cad kyi rang snang ba yin
NK124(ngo)001:14646: la / de ngos 'dzin pa ni rang byung ye shes mngon sum 'dzin pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14647: de ltar rtogs pas mngon sum du snang ba nyid sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14649: snyan rgyud zhal gyis gdams pa las shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14651: ngo bo nyid ni rnam par shes pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14652: ngos 'dzin pa ni ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:14653: mngon sum du ni sangs rgyas so //
NK124(ngo)001:14656: thog ma med pa rang gi rtsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14657: gang mthong chos nyid gcer mthong la //
NK124(ngo)001:14658: sgrib g.yogs med par ngo mtshar che //
NK124(ngo)001:14660: bzhi pa sangs rgyas lugs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14661: che ba lngar sangs rgyas te /
NK124(ngo)001:14662: khog dbub kyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:14663: gnyis pa rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14664: de ltar chos kun rang byung ye shes ye nas sangs rgyas pa de nyid /
NK124(ngo)001:14665: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma skyed pas 'dus
NK124(ngo)001:14666: ma byas kyi ye shes mngon sum du rtogs shing
NK124(ngo)001:14668: rgyu las ma phyung ba'i 'bras bu yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14670: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14671: byang chub sems kyi 'bras bu ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14672: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14675: rang byung ye shes rgyu ma skyed //
NK124(ngo)001:14676: skye med rang gsal rgyun mi chad //
NK124(ngo)001:14677: gnyen po rkyen gyis bcos su med //
NK124(ngo)001:14678: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14680: de nas 'bras bu tshogs gnyis las ma byung bar
NK124(ngo)001:14681: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de nyid rtogs pas yon
NK124(ngo)001:14682: tan thams cad mngon du gyur ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14684: skye med rang byung don rtogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:14685: tshogs gnyis ma bsags khyad par 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:14686: de phyir tshogs bsags rtse mo 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:14688: gsum pa lung las ma byung ba'i gdams ngag ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14689: de ltar chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su sangs rgyas shing /
NK124(ngo)001:14690: cir snang chos thams cad gcer mthong yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14691: tshig dang rtog dpyod ma yin par /
NK124(ngo)001:14692: snang ba gang snang gi rig pa'i rang ngo bstan nas /
NK124(ngo)001:14693: rtogs shing nyams su myong ba ni lung las ma byung ba'i gdams ngag yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14695: lung las ma byung man ngag ni //
NK124(ngo)001:14696: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don //
NK124(ngo)001:14697: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:14698: ci ltar rtogs shing rig pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:14699: lung las ma byung gdams ngag yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14700: de ltar rtogs shing nyams su myong ba ni theg
NK124(ngo)001:14701: pa thams cad kyis sems su 'dus shing 'khor ba
NK124(ngo)001:14702: rang grol chos sku chen por shar te /
NK124(ngo)001:14703: spang blang med par mngon sum du sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14704: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:14705: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas rnyed //
NK124(ngo)001:14706: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14707: lung la ma brten chos rnams shes //
NK124(ngo)001:14708: theg dgu' chos rnams gcig las med //
NK124(ngo)001:14709: dug lnga mya ngan 'das par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:14710: thugs kyi klong rdol chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:14712: gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:14713: rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14714: rdzogs chen gyi dgongs pa'i don bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14715: de mngon sum du rtogs pa'i lta ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14717: shes bya gting mtha' med pas rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14718: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14719: mtha' bzhi rang grol gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14720: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i dgongs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14721: thig le nyag gcig la sogs pa ming grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14724: klong chen gcig po kun yin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14725: thams cad kun gyi dngos bzhir shar //
NK124(ngo)001:14726: phyogs 'dzin gang yang ma spang pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:14727: phyogs med kun tu shar ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14728: zang thal yin pas kun du shar //
NK124(ngo)001:14729: mu mtha' med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:14730: rang byung ye shes rgya chad med //
NK124(ngo)001:14731: rang bzhin gcig la mtha' med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14732: byang chub sems la rgya chad med //
NK124(ngo)001:14734: spyir shes bya la gting mtha' med pas rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14737: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par rang byung ye shes kyi klong du 'dus la /
NK124(ngo)001:14738: de nyid mu mtha' med cing klong yang rgya khyon
NK124(ngo)001:14739: bral bas shes bya la gting mtha' med pa yin
NK124(ngo)001:14740: te / de yang chos kyi dbyings la gting mtha' med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14741: sems can gyi khams la gting mtha' med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14742: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la gting mtha' med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14744: chos kyi dbyings kyis ma khyab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14746: ma gyur pa gcig kyang med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:14747: mu mtha' med cing tshad las 'das pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14749: spyir chos kyi dbyings de sems can gyi khams kyis
NK124(ngo)001:14750: khengs shing bye brag tu yung 'bru' tsam re re'i
NK124(ngo)001:14751: khog pa na'ang sems can tshad med grangs las 'das
NK124(ngo)001:14752: par gsungs / de rnams kyang gcig gis khog pa gcig gis ma bkag par gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14754: khams su gnas pa'i sems can kun //
NK124(ngo)001:14755: skad cig ma yi tshod tsam la //
NK124(ngo)001:14756: dus gcig dag tu sangs rgyas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:14757: de las mang du gyur pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:14758: sems can nyung ngu mi 'gro ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14761: yung 'bru' tsam re re'i khog pa na'ang bskal pa
NK124(ngo)001:14762: nas bskal pa'i bar ston kyang nyung ngu mi 'gro
NK124(ngo)001:14764: spyir sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams mu mtha' med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:14765: bye brag tu rdul phra re re'i steng na sangs
NK124(ngo)001:14766: rgyas kyi zhing khams tshad med cing grangs las 'das
NK124(ngo)001:14767: par gsungs te / mdo' theg chen sgron ma las /
NK124(ngo)001:14769: sangs rgyas bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:14770: de dag 'dres par gyur pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:14773: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te //
NK124(ngo)001:14774: zhing der bsam gyis mi khyab sangs rgyas rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:14777: rdul phran re re'i steng na'ang sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK124(ngo)001:14778: khams yan man 'phred chags la sogs zhing khams dpag
NK124(ngo)001:14780: des na shes bya la gting mtha' med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14781: phyogs rer 'dzin pa ni mun pa'i glo yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14783: shin tu gting ring dpag dka' bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14784: yangs la rgya chen nam mkha'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:14785: nam mkha'i klong la kha gting med //
NK124(ngo)001:14786: rang gsal rig pa phyi nang med //
NK124(ngo)001:14788: rdzogs chen lta ba gting mtha' med //
NK124(ngo)001:14789: ye gdal chen po'i chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:14790: thug pa med cing skyon 'gel ba //
NK124(ngo)001:14791: mtha' med ma go mun pa'i blo //
NK124(ngo)001:14792: mu med gcig chod bstan pa de //
NK124(ngo)001:14793: 'og ma'i klong du mi rigs te //
NK124(ngo)001:14794: rdzogs pa chen por rig pa'i gnad //
NK124(ngo)001:14796: phyi nang sgo phugs med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14797: ye nas kha gting med par gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14799: des na shes bya la gting mtha' med pas rgya
NK124(ngo)001:14800: chad kyi snang ba gang yang ma spang pa'i rgya
NK124(ngo)001:14801: chad phyogs lhung med pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14802: de yang gang du rgya ma chad cing phyogs su
NK124(ngo)001:14803: ma lhung bas phyogs med kun du rang shar ba
NK124(ngo)001:14804: yin la / phyogs med kun tu rang shar zhing
NK124(ngo)001:14805: 'dug pa kas gang gis phyogs su ma lhung ba'o
NK124(ngo)001:14806: yin la / // de yang gshis chos nyid de
NK124(ngo)001:14807: stong pa rgya ma chad cing phyogs su ma lhung
NK124(ngo)001:14808: yin la / // bas / 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa thams cad du rang snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14809: shar ba'i dus nyid nas snang ba rgya ma chad de /
NK124(ngo)001:14810: rang byung gi ye shes la dngos po'i sel med cing stong par grol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14811: de nyid gnyis su rgya ma chad de ngo bo dbyer med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14812: de ltar rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14813: sangs rgyas kyi bde ba lam gyis snang ba thams cad rang rtsal du shar ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14815: rig pa yul med yul du shar //
NK124(ngo)001:14816: kun gyis dngos po yin pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14817: phyogs 'dzin gang yang ma spangs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14818: phyogs med klong nas 'byams pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14819: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14820: nam mkha'i dbyings ltar dngos dang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:14821: mtha' bzhi ma 'gag ma zhen pas //
NK124(ngo)001:14822: yul la dmigs pa med pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:14823: mi 'gyur lhun grub bdal ba che //
NK124(ngo)001:14824: klong yangs rgya khyon med par gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:14826: mtha' gnyis ma grub ma spang bas //
NK124(ngo)001:14827: chos nyid klong la yangs dog med //
NK124(ngo)001:14828: bde' bdal byang chub sems kyi dbyings //
NK124(ngo)001:14829: thams cad 'dus pa'i thig le gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:14832: gang zag gcig gi shes pa'i rgyud la sbyar na /
NK124(ngo)001:14833: rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de
NK124(ngo)001:14834: nyid bkor gling du rgya ma chad cing phyogs su
NK124(ngo)001:14835: ma lhung ste / rig pa la mu mtha' med cing kun la gnyis su med par khyab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14836: klong yangs rgya khyon dang bral ba yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:14837: khyad par de nyid rtogs pa gcig gi steng du ngo sprad cing rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14838: bla ma'i gdams pa las shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14839: de ltar ngo sprad cing rtogs pas phyogs 'dzin las grol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:14841: gnyis pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14842: spyir snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14843: bye brag so so nas ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gtan la phab pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14844: snang tshul la gang yang ma 'dres la /
NK124(ngo)001:14845: yin tshul chos kun rang byung ye shes la lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14846: de'i rgyu mtshan rang byung ye shes su ma gyur ba'i chos gcig kyang med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14847: de nyid 'khrul grol la sogs pa tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma 'dres la /
NK124(ngo)001:14848: de nyid mu mtha' med cing kun la gnyis su med par khyab pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14849: yul med du yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14851: tha dad pa yang med de /
NK124(ngo)001:14852: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14853: de yang ma 'dres pa'i dus na thams cad dbyer med dam yul med du yongs su rdzogs la /
NK124(ngo)001:14854: yongs su rdzogs kyi dus nyid nang ma 'dres par so sor snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14855: de nas ma 'dres pas yongs su rdzogs pa ma bkag /
NK124(ngo)001:14856: yongs rdzogs kyis ma 'dres pa'i khog pa ma bkag par ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14858: mnyam nyid gcig po'i klong dkyil nas //
NK124(ngo)001:14859: mi mnyam klong phran mtha' yas shar //
NK124(ngo)001:14861: cir yang yin no gang yang 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:14862: dbyings la bye brag gang yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:14864: klong chen gcig gis klong dkyil nas //
NK124(ngo)001:14865: klong phran mtha' yas kun shar kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:14867: kun kyang 'byams pa de ru gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:14870: sangs rgyas ye shes thugs dang sems can sems //
NK124(ngo)001:14871: 'brel med so so snang ba ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:14872: rtsal med rang sems chos skur gcig pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14873: blo dngos gcig par yid ches sems nyid yin //
NK124(ngo)001:14876: yongs su rdzogs pa kun mnyam yang //
NK124(ngo)001:14877: ma 'dres par yang kun tu snang //
NK124(ngo)001:14879: thams cad ma 'dres tha dad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14880: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK124(ngo)001:14881: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:14882: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK124(ngo)001:14885: rgyud gcig gis bsdus pa'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14886: rgyud tha dad kyis bsdus pa'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs so //
NK124(ngo)001:14888: rig pa'i rgyud gcig la 'khrul grol mtshon tshul tha dad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14890: rgyud rig pa'i ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14891: de yang gzhi ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14892: lam ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14893: 'bras bu ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14896: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad so sor snang la /
NK124(ngo)001:14897: yongs su rdzogs pa ni de nyid rang byung ye
NK124(ngo)001:14898: shes mu mtha' med pa kun la gnyis su med
NK124(ngo)001:14899: cing yul med du yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14901: dbyings nyid med la mi zad pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14902: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK124(ngo)001:14903: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:14904: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK124(ngo)001:14907: nyon mongs dang ni ye shes dang //
NK124(ngo)001:14908: snang srid skye rgu yod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:14909: mi srid med pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK124(ngo)001:14910: rang byung ye shes klong dkyil du //
NK124(ngo)001:14911: ma rdzogs pa ni med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14912: rdzogs chen lhun grub bla na med //
NK124(ngo)001:14913: mnyam pa nyid du thag chod du //
NK124(ngo)001:14914: kun kyang rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:14916: gzhi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs la ltos nas /
NK124(ngo)001:14919: dug lnga la sogs pa yang de bzhin du shes par byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:14921: chos can phyogs nas ma 'dres pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14922: chos nyid phyogs nas yongs su rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14923: kun rdzob phyogs nas ma 'dres pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14924: don dam phyogs nas yongs su rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14926: gnyis pa lam ma 'dres pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14927: theg pa rim dgu' la sogs pa so sor snang yang rang byung gi ye shes su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14929: theg pa'i khyad par ci snyed pa //
NK124(ngo)001:14930: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsung pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:14931: klong chen gcig gi yon tan de //
NK124(ngo)001:14932: gdul bya rnams la bstan pa zad //
NK124(ngo)001:14934: lta b+hee spyod pa 'bras bu rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:14935: gser dngul phra man rdzas lta bur //
NK124(ngo)001:14936: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gcig gi rgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:14937: khyad par gyur ba a ti'i rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14940: sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyi dgongs pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14941: de yang spyir sku dang ye shes la sogs ma 'dres so sor snang la /
NK124(ngo)001:14942: rang byung gi ye shes su tha dad med par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14944: 'bar ba'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK124(ngo)001:14945: rang gsal rig pa kun mkhyen thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:14946: mnyam la ma 'dres kun tu bzang //
NK124(ngo)001:14947: ma 'dres gsal ba'i ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:14950: mkha' la gza' skar bkrams pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:14951: ma 'dres rang gsal dbyings su rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:14952: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:14953: ma bcos ci bzhin rig pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:14955: gsum pa mtha' bzhi rang grol ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:14956: stong mtha' rang grol rang byung ye shes su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14957: snang mtha' rang grol du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14958: gnyis mtha' rang grol du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14959: gnyis med rang grol rang byung ye shes su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14961: stong par gsung pa rnams kyang drang don phyogs gcig yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14962: de yang shes bya'i gshis stong ma myong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:14963: 'khor 'das la sogs bar rang snang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14964: bye brag tu 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:14966: 'bras bu'i snang ba rnams ma 'gags par rang shar ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14968: ci ltar snang zhing grags pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:14969: rang las byung zhing rang gi rgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:14972: blos brtags chos kyi stong pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:14973: rang snang ngo bo stong ma myong //
NK124(ngo)001:14975: gnyis pa snang bar gsung ba'i lung rnams kyang drangs don phyogs re yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14976: chos kun ci ltar snang yang sems nyid las logs su rdul tsam yang med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:14977: snang ba rang grol chos sku stong pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14979: bdag las gzhan pa mi mnga' zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:14981: snang med stong pa chen por gsung //
NK124(ngo)001:14984: snang stong log par gsung pa yang drangs don phyogs re yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14985: ngo bo snang stong dbyer med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14986: des na ci ltar snang yang rang byung ye shes rang snang /
NK124(ngo)001:14987: ci ltar stong yang rang byung ye shes rang stong pa yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:14988: rang byung ye shes la snang stong bden brdzun med pas ngo bo dbyer med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:14990: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:14991: bden pa gnyis kyi snyad las 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:14994: gnyis med dang dbyer med la sogs pa gsung pa yang /
NK124(ngo)001:14995: drangs don phyogs re yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:14996: ngo bo snang stong la sogs pa snang tshul phyogs
NK124(ngo)001:14997: med du 'char zhing ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK124(ngo)001:14999: cis kyang ma sgribs ye shes mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:15000: thams cad ma 'dres yongs su gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15003: cir yang snang ba'i chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:15004: sna tshogs 'byung ba dbyings kyis brgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:15005: mu mtha' med pa chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:15006: mtha' yas snang bar dbyings kyis brgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:15007: brjod du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:15008: rnam grangs bung ba ngo mtshar che //
NK124(ngo)001:15010: bzhi pa mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i dgongs pa bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15014: chos kun rang byung ye shes su bzang ngan blang dor med par mnyam zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15015: chos kun lhag ma med par bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan nam /
NK124(ngo)001:15016: rol par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15018: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15019: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i brgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:15022: thams cad gcig tu rdzogs pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:15023: theg pa'i yang dog ci'i brgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:15024: bdag nyid chen po'i kun 'dus dpal //
NK124(ngo)001:15025: rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa'i mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:15028: rang byung gi ye shes de nyid rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15031: theg pa'i bye brag rnams rang rang snang ba mthun pa ltar snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:15032: snang dus nyid nas rang byung gi ye shes kyi
NK124(ngo)001:15033: ngang du shar ba las 'gro drug gi 'khrul snang
NK124(ngo)001:15034: dang / mu stegs kyi log shes dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15035: theg pa'i phyogs 'dzin gyi sel med pas bdag nyid chen po'i dgongs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15037: 'gro drug rgyud lnga'i sems can la //
NK124(ngo)001:15038: chos nyid spyi khyab yin pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:15039: yul med rig pa ye nas med //
NK124(ngo)001:15041: a ti yo ga'i lta ba ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15042: chos nyid rgya chad med pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:15043: gnyis ka rang shar rang grol bas //
NK124(ngo)001:15044: mu stegs ma spangs rdzogs chen brgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:15046: lnga pa thig le nyag gcig la sogs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15047: 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa thams cad thig le
NK124(ngo)001:15048: nyag gcig tu dbyer med cing klong yang rgya khyon
NK124(ngo)001:15049: bral bas thams cad 'dus shing rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15051: phyogs mtshams blo 'go mtho' dman kun //
NK124(ngo)001:15052: thig le gcig gis rgyar mnyams pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15053: sangs rgyas gong na med par gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15057: thig le chen po gcig po nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:15058: ther zug rgyun las ye nas sgrol //
NK124(ngo)001:15060: gnyis pa mngon sum rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15061: de ltar gtan tshigs du ma rnams kyis gtan la phebs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15062: chos kun rang byung ye shes mngon sum du rtogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15064: chos spyir rang rang gi mtshan nyid shes /
NK124(ngo)001:15066: rang sems kyi ngo bo mthong bas the tshom thams cad yid gnyis grol /
NK124(ngo)001:15067: 'gyur med gdeng dang ldan zhing log rtogs rtsad nas grol ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15069: rang sems tshad ma'i gdengs ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15070: mi 'gyur don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15071: lung rig don gyi bya ra bas //
NK124(ngo)001:15072: log rtogs rkun po rdul du rlog /
NK124(ngo)001:15075: rig pa mchog ldan bder gshegs bka' //
NK124(ngo)001:15076: rang byung tshad ma mngon sum gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15079: ye nas rang byung ye shes las //
NK124(ngo)001:15080: chos kun dus gsum sgrib med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15081: spong dang len pa mi mnga' ste //
NK124(ngo)001:15082: rang byung ye shes 'gyur med gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:15084: de yang hril gyi dril na /
NK124(ngo)001:15085: cir snang rang byung ye shes mngon sum du mthong bas yul med rang gsal gyi lta ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15086: rig pa mtha' dbus phyi nang med pa'i lta ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15087: thams cad rang byung ye shes su gcig pas bzang
NK124(ngo)001:15088: ngan blang dor med pas mnyam pa nyid kyi lta
NK124(ngo)001:15089: ba dang / rig pa rgyun chad med pas 'pho 'gyur med pa'i lta ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15091: ci snyed pa yi rnam grangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:15092: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:15093: chos nyid cer mthong bla na med //
NK124(ngo)001:15095: snang zhing grags pa'i chos rnams dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15096: mthong thos sgo lngar ci shar yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15097: rang zhal rang gis mthong bas na //
NK124(ngo)001:15098: gnyis su lta ba'i yul gzhan med //
NK124(ngo)001:15099: gnyis su med do mnyam pa che //
NK124(ngo)001:15100: yul sems mnyam nyid klong du grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15102: phyi nang sgo phugs med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15103: kha gting med par ye nas gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15105: gnas pa'i tshe na mnyam par gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:15106: bzang ngan med par rig pa'i rtsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15107: grol ba'i tshe na mnyam par grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15108: bzang ngan med par rig pa'i rtsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15111: lta med ye shes rang gsal ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15112: yul med spros bral de bzhin nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:15113: rang snang rig pa'i 'khor lo la //
NK124(ngo)001:15114: yul med rang gsal rig pa mthong //
NK124(ngo)001:15118: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15119: gong 'og gi dmigs phyes te ston pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:15122: sngags nang pa shan dbye' ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15123: sngags phyi nang gi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:15124: dang po ni khyad par mang du yod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:15125: sa dang rnam thar la spyad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15126: byang chub thob par 'gyur pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:15127: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum las //
NK124(ngo)001:15128: gang dag rim par bkod legs na //
NK124(ngo)001:15129: mnyam par blang dor med spyod cing //
NK124(ngo)001:15130: byang chub gzhan nas mi tshol ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:15131: thabs mchog dpag gis mi lang ba'i //
NK124(ngo)001:15132: nges pa'i theg pa cang ma gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:15135: chos nyid las blang dor byed mi byed kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15136: lam byang chub gzhan nas tshol mi tshol gyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15137: mdzad pa thabs kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15140: mtshan nyid kyi mthar thug gi dus su rang bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:15141: nam don dam du skye ba med cing gnyis su
NK124(ngo)001:15143: 'khrul snang kun rdzob tu nyams su myong ba byang chub tha dad par 'dod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:15145: gsang sngags nang pa spyir 'khor 'das gnyis med rang
NK124(ngo)001:15146: byung ye shes su lhag ma med par rdzogs la
NK124(ngo)001:15147: / khyad par du nyon mongs pa rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum du snang bas /
NK124(ngo)001:15148: spang bya dang gnyen po gnyis su med pa rang snang rang grol du nyams len pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15150: yul dang shes par snang ba yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15151: rang byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK124(ngo)001:15154: nyon mongs ye shes lngar rtogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:15155: gzhan ni de la gnyis su sgrib //
NK124(ngo)001:15156: rtogs dang ma rtogs gnyis med na //
NK124(ngo)001:15157: rtogs pa nyid kyang yang dag lam //
NK124(ngo)001:15160: ye shes bas kyang nyon mongs gtso' //
NK124(ngo)001:15161: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i zhags pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15162: rang byung ye shes gtan la 'bebs //
NK124(ngo)001:15163: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15164: gnyis pa lam la rgyu mtshan nyid pas don dam gong ltar 'dod kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:15165: de ltar snang ba'i kun rdzob 'khrul snang du 'dod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:15166: sems kyang rgyu'i rnam pa tsam du 'dod /
NK124(ngo)001:15167: lam brten pas 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15168: gsang sngags ni da ltar gyi snang ba 'di nyid chos nyid rang snang la bden rdzun gnyis med /
NK124(ngo)001:15169: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'tshol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15170: de nyid rtogs pa mngon du byed pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15172: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:15173: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:15174: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK124(ngo)001:15175: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK124(ngo)001:15176: ces rgyud lung man ngag gsum ka nas gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15177: gsum pa mdzad pa thabs kyi khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15179: thabs mkhas che dang mang yas yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15180: bsgyur dang brlabs chen cir yang ston //
NK124(ngo)001:15183: phyin ci log gi gdul bya thabs sna tshogs kyis brgyud nas yang dag pa'i lam du 'jug pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15185: nyon mongs pa nyid la spang bar lta ba dang
NK124(ngo)001:15186: ting nge 'dzin gyi ldan pas sngon du spyad nas
NK124(ngo)001:15187: / yang dag pa'i lam du gyur ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15188: mang ba ni zhi rgyas dbang drag la sogs gang 'dul du ston pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15190: thabs sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15192: nyon mongs pa spangs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15193: ma spangs pa la sogs gang yang bkag pa med par shod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15194: de ltar shes bya ci lta ba nyid mngon du
NK124(ngo)001:15195: rtogs ma rtogs yod pas lam la khyad yod pas
NK124(ngo)001:15196: / 'bras bu nyid lam du byed cing thabs sgo dpag mi lang ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:15197: bzhi pa 'bras bu la yang khyad par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:15198: ngo bo 'dus byas 'dus ma byas kyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15199: spang thob lhag ma dang bcas ma bcas kyi khyad par ro //
NK124(ngo)001:15200: snga ma ni mtshan rang gi mtshan nyid du /
NK124(ngo)001:15201: rang rig mngon sum gsal dus na /
NK124(ngo)001:15202: rang snang mtha' bral rgyun las grol /
NK124(ngo)001:15204: gsum pa rtogs nas nyams su len pa ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15205: spyir a ti rtogs grol dus mnyam lam gcig chod du gsung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15206: de yang bye brag tu dbye' na bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15208: yang rab rab dang 'bring dang mtha' ma grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15210: yang rab gcig shes bya gcig chod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15211: rtogs grol dus mnyam pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15213: gong ltar 'khor 'das gnyis su med par chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15215: nyams kyi rim pa med par rtogs pa dang grol ba dus mnyam par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15216: snying po don gyi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:15217: dus gsum rnam dag rig pa dbyer med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15218: rig pa dbyer med gcig tu lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:15219: ma bsags ma sbyangs ye sangs rgyas pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:15220: mtha' bral rig pa'i klong la bsam brjod med //
NK124(ngo)001:15221: ye nas lhun rdzogs bdag nyid lhun rdzogs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:15222: sa la mi bgrod lam la mi sbyangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:15223: ma rtogs ting 'dzin sbyong ba sgyu ma'i gnad //
NK124(ngo)001:15224: ma rtsal rang bzhin bzhag pas 'grub pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15226: nya mo 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:15227: ma skyes mi 'gag mnyam nyid klong //
NK124(ngo)001:15228: mkha' la mi skyod dgongs pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:15229: ma sgrod rig pa gcig chod smin //
NK124(ngo)001:15230: 'phur skyes lta bu'i rim pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:15231: lam lnga sa bcu rtogs pa'i gnad //
NK124(ngo)001:15232: bskyed rdzogs ting 'dzin don gyis gnad //
NK124(ngo)001:15233: blang dor rim skyes chad pa'i rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:15234: mtshan 'dzin rnam rtog mdzad pa'i tshul //
NK124(ngo)001:15237: dbang po rab kyis don du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15238: bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:15239: thig le nyag gcig chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:15240: shes pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas nges //
NK124(ngo)001:15245: rdzogs chen nges don a ti yo ga ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15246: grangs dang dus la mi ltos rang byung thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:15247: chos sku ci bzhin ma nor rtogs pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:15248: 'bras bu sangs rgyas sku gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:15251: slob tshul rim pa ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:15252: ma bgrod gcig char 'jug pa'i sa //
NK124(ngo)001:15255: gong ltar rtogs pa'i don la gnas pa tsam gyis rig pa'i ye shes phyogs med du shar zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15257: 'khor 'das spang blang med par chos kun rang byung ye shes su sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15259: dbang po rab kyi b+hee pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:15260: mnyam dang mi mnyam med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15261: 'bral med don la bcos mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:15262: sprin med nam mkha' ci bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:15265: rang byung chos nyid nam mkha' 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:15266: rang bzhin spros bral ting 'dzin gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15267: de la gnyen pos bcos su med //
NK124(ngo)001:15268: de phyir 'bral med dgongs pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15270: sems b+hee don drug pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:15271: b+hee dang b+hee par bya ba gnyis med na //
NK124(ngo)001:15272: don dam ngang la bde' bar gnas pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15273: byang chub sems b+hee zhes kyang de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:15274: rtogs pa'i klong chen ma yeng don ston dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15275: rnam dag byang chub sems kyi dgongs pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15278: blo nyid dngos por gyur pas spang bya len byed med //
NK124(ngo)001:15279: sems de chos nyid ngang du gyur tsam na //
NK124(ngo)001:15280: b+hee mkhan gang yin b+hee dang ci zhig b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:15281: chos nyid ye 'byams rtogs nas ma yengs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:15282: ye 'byams chos nyid dgongs pa yin par bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:15285: a ti b+hee pa dmigs gtad med //
NK124(ngo)001:15286: b+hee kyang skyon gyis ma gos te //
NK124(ngo)001:15287: rang byung rol pa rang la shar //
NK124(ngo)001:15288: ma b+hee mtshan ma rang sar grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15289: rang byung gnyis med b+hee pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15290: phyogs su 'dzin pa'i mdud pa grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15292: gtang bsnyoms res 'jog med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15295: rgyun mi chad pa'i bsam gtan yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15296: nyon mongs zad par zad pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:15297: mthar thug don gyi bsam gtan yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15298: bde chen klong du thim pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:15302: rang sems rtogs pa'i 'bras bu la //
NK124(ngo)001:15303: btud de gcig char 'jug nus na //
NK124(ngo)001:15304: b+hee pa'i thun la ring thung med //
NK124(ngo)001:15305: nams 'grub snyom pa'i khar ma lus //
NK124(ngo)001:15306: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15307: 'bring ni rtogs pa'i don la blo bzhag thabs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15311: rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs rgyun chad med par gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15312: don la ma g.yos bar cir snang b+hee du bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15313: b+hee bya b+hee byed med par nyams su blangs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15314: rtsol med rang lugs su b+hee pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15316: ye shes klong du phyin pa la ma yengs don dang mi 'bral ba'i dgongs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15317: rtogs pa'i ngang la rang lugs rtsol med du nyams su blang ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15320: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK124(ngo)001:15321: ci bzhin pa yi ye shes te //
NK124(ngo)001:15322: brjod med rgyun mi 'chad par lta //
NK124(ngo)001:15324: kun bzang rig pa rtsal shar ba'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:15325: rig pa rtsal shar rnal 'byor pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15326: shes pa chos kun rang gsal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:15327: ma yengs cog bzhag nyid du bzhag /
NK124(ngo)001:15330: rang gsal snang ba gzhan med la //
NK124(ngo)001:15331: rgyun du yod pa'i chos nyid las //
NK124(ngo)001:15332: ma yengs don la gang gnas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:15333: de ni rnal 'byor dam pa'i lam //
NK124(ngo)001:15335: gsal la ma yengs chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:15336: ma b+hee bral med ting 'dzin ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15337: dmigs su med pa nam mkha' 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:15338: 'du bral med pa rgyun du gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:15341: cir snang ci srid ji ltar snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:15342: dgag sgrub spang blang med par rang byung rang snang nyid du nyams su blangs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15344: yul gyi mtshan ma cir yang snang //
NK124(ngo)001:15345: yid kyis dgag bsgrub med pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15346: chos dbyings gdeng ldan nges don la //
NK124(ngo)001:15347: spro dang bsdu ba'i zhan med bde' //
NK124(ngo)001:15350: bdag gzhan 'du shes ngang gis dben pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:15351: snang srid rdo rje sems dpa' dgongs pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15352: ci ltar yin pa'i don de rab rtogs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:15353: ci ltar rung rung skal ldan nyams su long //
NK124(ngo)001:15356: ye nas ma b+hee ci bzhin gsal ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:15357: b+hee pas gzhan nas rgyal ba'i chos mi rnyed //
NK124(ngo)001:15358: rdo rje nyi ma dbyings nas shar ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:15359: thams cad kun kyang de bzhin nyid du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15361: gsum pa ni ci ltar snang yang rang byung gi
NK124(ngo)001:15362: ye shes rang snang bas skye med kyi rang bzhin
NK124(ngo)001:15364: blang du med pa'i nyams blang 'di lta ste //
NK124(ngo)001:15365: gcig tu rtogs nas blo dngos 'phrod tsam na //
NK124(ngo)001:15366: nyams su blang ba su'i len pa gang //
NK124(ngo)001:15367: blo nyid dngos por gyur bas blang bya blang byed med //
NK124(ngo)001:15368: sems de chos nyid ngang du gyur tsam na //
NK124(ngo)001:15369: b+hee mkhan gang yin b+hee du ci zhig b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:15370: ye 'byams chos nyid rtogs nas ma yengs pa //
NK124(ngo)001:15371: ye 'byams chos nyid dgongs pa yin par bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:15374: rang sems don rtogs snying po chos sku la //
NK124(ngo)001:15375: b+hee bya'i ye shes chos sku gud na med //
NK124(ngo)001:15376: snga phyi sems kyi ye shes mtha' bral phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15377: ma nor b+hee pa po yang ga la yod //
NK124(ngo)001:15378: de ltar b+hee chen sems la dngos med na //
NK124(ngo)001:15379: mi gnas mi rtogs 'jog pa rnal 'byor min //
NK124(ngo)001:15382: cir snang rang byung ye shes las g.yos pa med
NK124(ngo)001:15383: pas rang lugs rtsol med du nyams su blang ste
NK124(ngo)001:15385: ma bcos gnas lugs rang lugs la //
NK124(ngo)001:15386: lus sems khong slod gang dgar bzhag /
NK124(ngo)001:15387: shes pa bag yang rtsol med la //
NK124(ngo)001:15388: bya byed skyes bu bzhin du gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:15389: drim lhod med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:15390: lus sems gang dgar bzhag pas bde //
NK124(ngo)001:15393: sgrim ci bzhin ma nor rang sems rtogs pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:15394: lus ngag ma skyes rtogs pa bzhi med phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15395: dkyil krungs srang 'dug smra bcad kha na med //
NK124(ngo)001:15396: de phyir sems kyang dngos med rtag chad med //
NK124(ngo)001:15397: rtogs pa spang bas bya ba'i khar mi yong //
NK124(ngo)001:15398: ye shes lta ba shugs las byung ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15399: rnal 'byor dmigs pa'i shes pas ma b+hee ste //
NK124(ngo)001:15400: rnam rtog rang sems ma bcos ye shes phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15401: de ldan ched du b+hee pa brten mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:15404: ma rtsal ba yi chos nyid ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15405: rtog dpyod med pa b+hee pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:15406: nyams ni shes rig gsal ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:15407: de la ma yengs b+hee pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15410: bya byed lam gyi 'bad rtsol gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:15411: rang byung byang chub gegs yin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15412: shes pa rtsol med ye shes 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:15413: lam gyi ye shes dam pa gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:15414: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15415: gnyis pa skyon bcos thabs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15422: de thams cad sems nyid rang snang bas skyon yon
NK124(ngo)001:15423: dgag sgrub med par rang snang shar grol du nyams
NK124(ngo)001:15424: su blang ngo // sems b+hee don drug pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:15425: rnal 'byor rtogs pa'i mtshan ma ci byung yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15426: rtogs pa de nyid chos nyid yin zhes na //
NK124(ngo)001:15427: chos dbyings nyid las gzhan ni b+hee mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:15428: de la gnyen po'i bcos shing dgag tu med //
NK124(ngo)001:15429: 'di ltar dus gsum rnam pa thams cad du //
NK124(ngo)001:15430: nyid las ma yengs pa ni chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:15431: stobs su gyur na 'jig rten rang bzhin med //
NK124(ngo)001:15434: 'dzin pas rtags cing snang ba'i chos rnams ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15435: rang gi rgyan du snang bas mi dor spang mi byed //
NK124(ngo)001:15436: rnam pa cir yang mi b+hee thabs kyis de la rol //
NK124(ngo)001:15437: kun dang mi mthun yongs kyis spong ba'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:15438: nyon mongs lnga dang mtshams med lnga po //
NK124(ngo)001:15439: rnam dag lam der zhugs na //
NK124(ngo)001:15443: sems kyi spyod yul la shes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15444: de dag chos rnams kyi ni chos nyid yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15445: rnam bral gang la'ang mchog dang tha ma med par lam mchog 'di b+hee mo /
NK124(ngo)001:15448: shan pa smad 'tshong mtshams med lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:15449: kha na ma tho'i 'jig rten spong //
NK124(ngo)001:15450: yongs su rdzogs pas chos kyi rtsi //
NK124(ngo)001:15451: bde' ba che la gzhan med do //
NK124(ngo)001:15453: 'o na skyon de rnams dngos po rang kha mar bzhag gam zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:15455: thams cad rang byung gi ye shes rang snang du rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15456: gang la yang dngos po dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15457: mtshan ma med par me 'bar ba la shing bsnan pa bzhin du /
NK124(ngo)001:15458: ye shes chen po'i ngang du rang byung rang zhir nyams su blang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:15460: gal te byung tshor rtag chad rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:15461: rnam rtog ye shes bskur mar shar //
NK124(ngo)001:15462: me la shing snan ci bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:15463: de tsam nyid na b+hee par gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15464: sgo lnga shes pa smugs gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:15465: nyid gsum sre ba'i don go bas //
NK124(ngo)001:15466: chos nyid chos kyi klong du byings //
NK124(ngo)001:15467: bum nang rin chen gter dang 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:15470: rtog mtshan bzang ngan nyon mongs lnga //
NK124(ngo)001:15471: ci skyes dgag par mi bya zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:15472: de don dran pas 'brang ba min //
NK124(ngo)001:15473: rang byung rang zhir nga smra'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15476: nyams dang gdeng rtags bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15478: mnyam rjes gnyis su med cing rang grol 'phel 'grib med pa'i nyams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15479: nam mkha'i sprin ltar chos kun rang zhir chos skur gsal ba'i nyams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15480: spang la me mched pa bzhin du ci dran ye shes chos skur gsal ba'i nyams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15481: rin po che'i gser gling na sa rdo'i sel med
NK124(ngo)001:15482: pa ltar chos kun rang byung ye shes la gzhan
NK124(ngo)001:15483: gyis sel med par nyams su myong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15484: de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la snying rje phyogs ris med par gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15487: rang sems lta ba rtogs pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:15488: mnyam rjes dug lnga gcig tu shes //
NK124(ngo)001:15489: de tshe nyon mongs ci spyad kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:15493: gtang snyoms res 'jog med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15497: dper na nam mkha'i sprin bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:15498: rang byung rang zhir gnod med ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:15499: rnam rtog rang grol 'jig med phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15500: ye shes ngo bo chos skur gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15503: bde' dang sdug bsngal gtang snyoms kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:15504: rang byung rang zhi nyid du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15505: rang rig klong du rnam par dag /
NK124(ngo)001:15506: de bzhin nyid de bcos su med //
NK124(ngo)001:15510: dper na dgun zla 'bring po la /
NK124(ngo)001:15511: spang la me mched ci bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:15512: ci dran chos sku 'od gsal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:15513: thams cad ye shes nyid du shar //
NK124(ngo)001:15516: dper na rin chen gser gling du //
NK124(ngo)001:15517: sa rdo btsal gyis mi rnyed ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:15518: gang yang chos nyid rang gsal phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15521: thams cad chos nyid gyur pa la //
NK124(ngo)001:15522: b+hee pa'i tha snyad bral ba'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:15523: rang rig ye shes nyid du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15526: skye shi med pa'i mtha' med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15527: mtha' bral klong chen nam mkha'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:15528: dbye' gsal blang dor med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15529: gser gling lta bur yang pa'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:15532: chos kun sems nyid rang snang du rtogs nas /
NK124(ngo)001:15533: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can thams cad la gnyis su med pa'i byams pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15534: snying rje phyogs ris med par skye zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15535: sems can gyi don la shin tu brtson par 'byung bar gsung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15537: de ltar de bzhin chos kyi dbyings rig na //
NK124(ngo)001:15538: ma rig rnams la snying rje phyogs med skye //
NK124(ngo)001:15539: snying rje skye nas sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:15540: 'gro don thabs kyis spyod pa sna tshogs ston //
NK124(ngo)001:15543: khyab pa'i snying rje rgyun mi chad //
NK124(ngo)001:15544: rtsal ba'i 'phrin las rgyun chad med //
NK124(ngo)001:15546: gnyis pa nyams kyi gdeng ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15548: rtags chen gdeng ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15549: ci spyad sangs rgyas ye shes thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:15550: mi lus rin chen 'di nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:15553: bsam gtan mnyams kyi gdeng rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15554: chags sdang rang sar grol ba'i gdeng rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15555: mi mthun gnyen po med pa'i gdeng rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15556: the tshom sgro 'dogs chod pa'i gdeng rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15557: bde sdug rtsa ba chod pa'i gdeng rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15558: pho 'gyur re 'dogs med pa'i gdeng rtags la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15559: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs shing nyams su myong bas /
NK124(ngo)001:15560: yin min gnyis su med cing yul sems gnyis su med du grol bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15562: rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo la //
NK124(ngo)001:15563: ming gis tha snyad 'dzin med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15564: yul la mi zhen rang sar grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15565: bsam gtan rtsal med nyams kyi gdengs //
NK124(ngo)001:15568: tshogs drug rang sar grol ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15569: mtshan ma'i rtog pa zil gyis non //
NK124(ngo)001:15570: snang ba rgya yan yin pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15573: gnyis pa ni byams pa'i gnyen dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15574: gnod skyel gyi dgra dang 'phrad kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:15575: chags sdang gi rtogs pa mi skye ba'am /
NK124(ngo)001:15576: skyes kyang rang byung ye shes su gsal thebs cing grol bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15578: phan gnod med par gang 'phrad kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:15579: byams sdang gnyis ni skyes pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:15580: mnyam nyid rig pa gsal thebs na //
NK124(ngo)001:15581: klong rdol gnyis med nyid kyi gdeng //
NK124(ngo)001:15584: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15585: bde ba chen po'i rgyan yin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15586: zhe sdang rtsad nas bcad du med //
NK124(ngo)001:15589: srog gcod pa'i bshes gnyen la sogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15590: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po la sogs pa'i zhal mthong yang /
NK124(ngo)001:15591: mnyam nyid rang snang du rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15592: spang blang re dogs med pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15593: lta ba gdeng du gyur pa'i rtags yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15595: kun bzang bshes gnyen gang 'ong yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15596: gzhi la med cing 'khrul par rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:15597: gnyis ka spang blang med rtogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:15598: lta ba gdeng ldan nyams kyi gdengs //
NK124(ngo)001:15601: mi mthun gnyen po g.yer med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15602: gcig gi klong du rab tu thims //
NK124(ngo)001:15605: bka' ston pa la sogs pa thams cad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15606: rgyud lung man ngag la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15607: rgyal ba nyid mngon sum du byon nas gsungs kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:15608: the tshom dri rgyu med cing chos bzang ngan mi 'byed 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15610: de bzhin nyid du thag chod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15611: bzang ngan sgro skur med rtogs na //
NK124(ngo)001:15612: chos la bzod pa thob pa'i gdengs //
NK124(ngo)001:15615: rang sems tshad ma'i gdengs ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15616: mi 'gyur don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK124(ngo)001:15618: lnga pa lus kyi na tsha dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15619: sems kyi sdug bsngal la sogs ci ltar byung yang /
NK124(ngo)001:15620: skyon yon blang dor med pa rtogs pa 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15622: lus kyi bde sdug ci byung yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15623: skyon yon med pa'i don dran na //
NK124(ngo)001:15624: snga phyi ma slad don dran pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15625: chos nyid rang gsal mnyams kyi gdengs //
NK124(ngo)001:15629: mkha' rlung bar snang sprin bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:15630: rang byung rang zhi klong du grol //
NK124(ngo)001:15632: drug pa rang byung ye shes la skye 'chi 'pho
NK124(ngo)001:15633: 'gyur med par dus gsum mnyam pa nyid du rtogs
NK124(ngo)001:15634: pas / skye 'chi la nyam nga med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:15635: 'khor 'das la re dogs med par rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15637: sems la skye 'chi med pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15639: skye 'gag med pa'i don la gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:15640: 'bral med dgongs pa nyams kyi gdeng //
NK124(ngo)001:15643: byang chub sems la skye ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:15644: 'chi ba med pa'i lam kyang bcad du med //
NK124(ngo)001:15645: ma spyad byang chub sems kyi klong //
NK124(ngo)001:15646: byang chub sems la 'chi ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:15648: rang la gnas pas rtsal mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:15650: de ltar rtogs shing goms pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15651: nyams kyi rim pa med par sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:15653: mnyam pa'i don la ye gnas pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15654: 'bras bu'i rig pa da lta nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:15655: de nyid ma rjod don ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15656: mya ngan 'das zhes de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:15659: rang byung ye shes sku rnyed pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15660: mtha' rnams kun gyis mi nus phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15661: rgyal mtshan nor bu rin po che //
NK124(ngo)001:15662: khyad par 'phags pa mchog gi lam //
NK124(ngo)001:15663: bla med bder gshegs rnams kyi thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:15666: gdams ngag ngo sprod la rtogs pa'i don la bzhag thabs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15670: snyan rgyud zhal gyis gdams pas ngo sprad cing /
NK124(ngo)001:15671: khrid par bya ba'i zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15672: de nas rig pa sna kha zin cing b+hee kyis dmigs shes na /
NK124(ngo)001:15673: ngo sprad cing rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs rgyun sring nas nyams su blang bar bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15675: tha ma rnal 'byor b+hee pa pos //
NK124(ngo)001:15676: snga phyi med pa'i gnyugs ma la //
NK124(ngo)001:15677: ma 'phros ma bying rang lugs tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:15678: de las rgyun du ma yengs b+hee //
NK124(ngo)001:15681: rang la yod kyis gzhan la lta //
NK124(ngo)001:15682: chos nyid ngang la thun ma gcod //
NK124(ngo)001:15683: lta ba'i rgyun la b+hee ma ngas //
NK124(ngo)001:15684: b+hee pa'i ngang la dran ma gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:15685: spyod pa'i chos la bcos ma slad //
NK124(ngo)001:15686: dam tshig gzhung la gtsur ma skyon //
NK124(ngo)001:15687: 'bras bu'i chos la rtags ma rings //
NK124(ngo)001:15689: de rnams kyi don ngo sprad la nyams su blang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:15690: gnyis pa skyon bcos thabs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15694: spyir blo chung ba'i rigs la tho yor glang snying la sogs pa'i b+hee chen pa'i rigs drug dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15695: byung tshor g.yeng ba la sogs pa'i skyon drug dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15696: rtogs pa phra rags la sogs pa'i skyon bcu' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15697: bying rgod la sogs pa'i skyon drug go //
NK124(ngo)001:15702: rgod pa la yang gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15706: de yang bsdus na bying rgod lding gsum la 'dus so //
NK124(ngo)001:15707: de rnams rgyas par ma h+aa'i skabs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15708: a nu'i skabs nas bshad pa dang mthun la /
NK124(ngo)001:15710: gnyis pa de rnams kyi bcos thabs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15711: rgyas par ma h+aa dang a nu'i skabs bzhin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15713: rang rang gi khrid gzhung dang bla ma'i zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15715: nyams rim bzhi ltar shes par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15717: dang po gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15718: gnyis pa la ni mi g.yo' ba //
NK124(ngo)001:15719: gsum pa nyams pa nyid du sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:15720: bzhi pa ye shes lhun grub kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:15727: nyams gong ma la sbyor tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:15729: rtogs pa'i ngang las rig pa phyi nang med par
NK124(ngo)001:15730: gsal ba'i ngang du shes pa rtse gcig tu gnas
NK124(ngo)001:15731: pa'o // de yang ngo bo nyid kyi bde ba /
NK124(ngo)001:15733: gnyis su med par thag chod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15734: rjes la dran pas ma zin tsam na a 'thas gtang snyoms su ltas la /
NK124(ngo)001:15735: dran pas zin tsam na rnam rtog rjes snyegs shing thugs phrad choms par gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:15737: chu bo dal drag dang 'dra ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15738: dang po rnam rtog mang zhing cung zad gnas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15739: de la thun phyed tsam du dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15740: de nas thun re tsam gnas par gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:15741: rtogs pa ye shes dum bur 'char zhing yid ches pa'i dpe' ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15742: sprin bar gyi nyi ma 'dra ba skabs su rig
NK124(ngo)001:15743: pa phyi nang med pa ye shes rang gsal du
NK124(ngo)001:15744: rtogs te / nges shes lhang lhang skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15746: sprin bar nyi 'dra gsal yid ches //
NK124(ngo)001:15749: bzhi pa rmi lam ni 'di'i skabs su g.yo' thob tsam du 'byung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15751: lnga pa gong ma la sbyor tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15752: nyi ma gcig la cha bcur dbyi' ba'i dgu' tha mal du 'chor zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15753: nyams nyi ma'i bcu cha tsam rig pa'i ye shes rang gsal ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15754: de nas 'khrul pa je nyung je sang /
NK124(ngo)001:15755: ye shes je gsal je sten du 'gro bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15756: mjug tu mi g.yo' ba'i nyams mthar phyin tsam na /
NK124(ngo)001:15757: 'khrul pa'i sel med par rtogs pa'i ye shes hril der 'gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:15758: de nyid du sangs rgyas pa yang 'byung bar gsung /
NK124(ngo)001:15759: ma rgyas nang nyams nyid kyis nyams 'char bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15761: dang po rtogs pa'i rang byung ye shes de //
NK124(ngo)001:15762: nyi ma gcig la cha bcur gnas pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:15763: cha gcig ye shes tha mal cha dgu' ste //
NK124(ngo)001:15764: rim gyis ma spang ma bsgrub bcu' 'gag pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15765: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i thob tshul de ltar thob //
NK124(ngo)001:15767: de ltar gnas pa'i cha las /
NK124(ngo)001:15770: kun rtags kyis bsgrib pa 'bring grol nas /
NK124(ngo)001:15771: mi g.yo' ba'i nyams thob par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15773: nyon mongs kun rtags 'bring bcoms nas //
NK124(ngo)001:15774: brten pa'i cha las mi g.yo' thob //
NK124(ngo)001:15777: de dag g.yo dang goms brtan nas //
NK124(ngo)001:15778: rim 'byung gsang ba'i dngos grub myur //
NK124(ngo)001:15780: gnyis pa mi g.yo' ba'i nyams gong bzhin la lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15782: cir snang rig pa'i ye shes su gsal ba'i ngang las /
NK124(ngo)001:15783: yid la 'byung 'jug med par nyams len zhig tsam du gnas par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15785: ji srid mnyam par gzhag pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:15786: skyon gyis rnam pa gang 'gog nas //
NK124(ngo)001:15787: rang byung ye shes drod dang ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:15788: nyin mtshan 'das pa'i bar du gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:15791: dran pas ma zin tsam la /
NK124(ngo)001:15792: a 'thas zhig cing shes pa gtang snyoms su gnas la /
NK124(ngo)001:15793: dran pas zin tshad rnam rtog thug phrad rang grol du 'gro bar gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15795: g.yo' 'gul med pa rgya mtsho' lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15796: mi g.yo' ba rang gsal ba mar me lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15797: ma gos rnam dag pad ma lta bu la sogs rnams 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15799: mi rtogs thig le ngang la gnas pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:15800: mi skyod dang ba'i rgya mtsho' chen po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15801: mi g.yo' gsal ba'i gtil gyi mar me 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:15806: drod ni shing bal ltar yang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15807: lus kyi bzod pa che thob dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15808: mkhas snyoms rang lus bde ba brgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:15809: 'byung ba cha dang mthun mtshams bral //
NK124(ngo)001:15810: de'i don rgyas par bkrol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:15812: mthun pa lam gyi rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15813: lung ma bstan thun mong gi rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15814: bar chad bdud kyi rtags so //
NK124(ngo)001:15816: sems skye 'chi med par nyams su myong bas /
NK124(ngo)001:15818: 'gro ba'i khams la skyo ba med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15819: nyon mongs pa zhen chags shin du chung zhing snyoms pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15821: snying rje skye ba la sogs pa yon tan du ma 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15823: rtags ni dus gsum gcig rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15824: phyogs bcur mthong la nyam mi nga //
NK124(ngo)001:15825: 'khrul pa'i khams la skyo ba med //
NK124(ngo)001:15828: lus kyi bzod pa thob pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15829: 'chod pa spong len med pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15830: gang la'ang nyon mongs mi skye na //
NK124(ngo)001:15833: gzhan yang rtogs pa'i don dang ldan pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15834: gang la'ang nyam nga re dogs med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15835: spyod lam rnam bzhir don dang mi 'bral zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:15837: gang ltar bsam pa ltar 'byung zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:15838: cir snang rig pa'i ye shes las mi 'da' zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:15839: goms pa las su rung ba'i rtags yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:15841: ci spyod don la mi nyams na //
NK124(ngo)001:15842: goms pa las su rung ba'i rtags //
NK124(ngo)001:15844: gzhan yang mngon shes drug 'byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15845: tshul khrims bzhi yang g.yo thob tsam du 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15846: mngon par shes pa drug snang ba'ang /
NK124(ngo)001:15847: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15848: rdzu 'phrul chos ston kun rjob dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15849: rjes rten la sogs g.yo' thob 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:15851: lung ma bstan thun mong gi rtags ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15852: rig pa dngas shing rtsa gnas su rlung song ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15854: mtho' srid pa'i rtse mo man chad nas /
NK124(ngo)001:15855: dma' na rag dmyal ba yan chad snang tshul la mi 'char ba gang yang med de /
NK124(ngo)001:15857: gzhan nam rlung zin bag chags dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15858: sems nyid rang snang phyogs med phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15859: ngan song gnas gsum sdug bsngal dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15860: 'dod khams lha mi'i snang tshul dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15861: gzugs khams skye mched bsam gtan dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15862: skye mos 'tshal dang gzhal yas zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:15863: nyams ni snang ba cir yang 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:15865: gzhan nam smig sgyu lta bu la sogs rlung rtags lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15866: me long dkar 'das brgyan pa la sogs pa shugs snang brgyad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15867: sprul pa grangs med 'gyed pa la sogs pa bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15868: yi dam lha'i zhal mjal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15869: lung bstan pa la sogs pa mthong snang bsam gyis mi khyab par 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15870: mthong snang de rnams rang snang gi 'char lugs yin pa la bdud du 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15871: lung ma bstan du 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15872: lam du 'gro ba'i bye brag shes par bya ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15874: rang snang du ma shes pas bden par bzung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15875: skyon yon gnyis su lta ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15876: nyams tshad ma zin par sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams mthong ba la sogs pa bden par bzung nas /
NK124(ngo)001:15877: bzang por barlomasa pa ni bdud du song ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15878: gnyis pa skyon yon gang du yang ma shes par gtang snyoms su 'dug pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15880: gsum pa ni mthong snang de rnams rang byung rang
NK124(ngo)001:15881: snang du shes pas skyon yon re dogs med pa
NK124(ngo)001:15882: dang / rang gis nyams tshod zin pas de dag
NK124(ngo)001:15883: gi bye brag shes shing bden 'dzin rloms sems med
NK124(ngo)001:15884: dang / pa'o // nyams tshod zin pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15885: zag pa gsum dang ma bral ba'i skabs su /
NK124(ngo)001:15886: nyams ci ltar mthong yang mi g.yo' ba'i nyams las ma 'das pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15887: gong gi mthong snang de rnams kyang nyams snang tsam
NK124(ngo)001:15888: las dngos su mthong ba med par shes par bya'o
NK124(ngo)001:15889: // dngos su yi dam lha skabs dang nyams dang
NK124(ngo)001:15890: rmi lam du zhal mthong zhing sgra snyan du gsung
NK124(ngo)001:15891: thos pa la sogs pa las mi 'ong bar gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:15892: // pa las / de rnams kyang bdud dang nyan
NK124(ngo)001:15893: dbye' ba ni shin tu gces par gsung bas bye
NK124(ngo)001:15896: sgren mor phung nas khrus byed pa la sogs pa sgrib pa dag pa'i ltas brgyad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15897: mun khung mdams nas thon pa la sogs pa ngan song nas thon pa'i ltas brgyad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15898: rang la 'od byung nas snang srid gsal ba la sogs bden pa mthong ba'i ltas dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15899: gzhan nam yi dam lha'i zhal mthong lung bstan pa
NK124(ngo)001:15900: la sogs pa'i rmi ltas bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK124(ngo)001:15902: de yang bdud du 'gro ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15903: lam du 'gro ba'i bye brag ni gong bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15905: dus ma yin par zhal mthong gsung thos pa la sogs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15906: 'khor slob dang zang zing gis g.yeng ba skyed nas /
NK124(ngo)001:15908: chags sdang la sogs pa'i chos brgyad 'phel te /
NK124(ngo)001:15911: de rnams nyams kyang gong bzhin du tshod zin par
NK124(ngo)001:15912: byas shing 'khor ba'i chos la blo log pa dang
NK124(ngo)001:15914: brtson 'grus drag pos nyams su blangs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15915: hril gyi dril nas gong gi rtags de rnams rang rang gis nyams tshod zin pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15916: rang byung rang snang du shes par byas la 'grub
NK124(ngo)001:15917: mi 'grub re dogs med par nyams su blang ngo
NK124(ngo)001:15919: 'phrang gsal rtags mtshan la sogs kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:15920: sgo drug mtshan ma ci snang yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15921: ma skyes rig pa rang snang bas //
NK124(ngo)001:15922: rang byung rang zhi rang dgar bzhag /
NK124(ngo)001:15925: phyi nang rtags kyi rim pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:15926: skyes kyang dga' brod sems mi 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:15927: med kyang de la mi dga' med //
NK124(ngo)001:15929: nyams gong ma la sbyor tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:15930: mi g.yo' ba'i nyams la yang g.yo' thob goms rtan la sogs la brtan pa thob pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15931: kun brtags kyi zhen pa dang nyon mongs pa'i 'ching
NK124(ngo)001:15932: ba la sogs 'khor ba'i skyon rnams rtsad nas grol
NK124(ngo)001:15933: nas mnyam pa nyid kyi nyams thob pa yin te
NK124(ngo)001:15935: mi g.yo'i ngang gnas rnal 'byor pas //
NK124(ngo)001:15936: mi rtogs thig le'i klong gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15937: dgongs pa'i nyon mongs kun rtags sgrib //
NK124(ngo)001:15938: phra ba bcoms nas mnyam nyid thob //
NK124(ngo)001:15940: gal te mnyam pa ma thob par 'pho na rab gcig phung po dor ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15941: dbyings su grol ba dus mnyam ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15942: ye shes kyi bar do dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15943: chos nyid kyi bar do dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15944: tha ma srid pa'i bar do lha mi'i rigs ni thob ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15945: de nas grol bar gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15946: mnyam nyid kyi mnyams la bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:15948: chos kun rang byung ye shes mngon du rtogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15949: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing dgongs pa mnyam nyid phyogs ris med par bzhugs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15950: de yang sgrib pa med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:15951: 'phel ba yod de rgyun chad med par gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:15952: der yang mnyam rjes phra mo yod cing tshul bzang po'i rtsol ba tsam la gnas par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15954: mnyam nyid ngang nas mnyam rjes thob //
NK124(ngo)001:15955: cung mnga' tshul bzang rtsol ba can //
NK124(ngo)001:15957: dpe ni rgyun chad med pa chu bo dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15958: ye shes rang gsal nyi ma dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15959: nyam nga re dogs med pa khyung chen la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15960: rtags ni 'khor ba las grol ba'i rtags dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15964: skye rgas na 'chi dang chos spyod la sogs nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba rtsad nas grol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:15965: zag pa gsum dang bral ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15966: 'jigs pa lnga dang bral zhing bdud bzhi gtan nas bcoms pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15967: chos nyid brjod pa med par rtogs pa yi dam gyis lha dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15968: sprul pa'i sku zhal mthong ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15971: lung bstan pa la sogs pa dngos su 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15973: bdud dang cha dbye'i bye brag med //
NK124(ngo)001:15974: mnyam nyid kun bral kun dngos phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15975: zag med zas gos zhen pa bral //
NK124(ngo)001:15976: kun brtags nyon mongs chags sdang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15977: chos brgyad nyon mongs rtsad nas gcad //
NK124(ngo)001:15978: 'jigs pa lnga bral bdud bzhi bcoms //
NK124(ngo)001:15979: rgyal bas lung bstan dbang 'gyur rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:15980: khyad par mnyams rtags cir snang yang //
NK124(ngo)001:15981: nyon mongs rtsad grol mnyam nyid phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:15982: rtag pa'i bye brag 'di las med //
NK124(ngo)001:15985: stong gsum yung 'brur tshud pa la sogs pa rdzu 'phrul gyi dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15986: 'gro ba kun gyi skad du gsung ba la sogs pa'i chos snang ba'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15987: stong gsum brgya phrag la sogs pa g.yo zhing rgyud gong 'phel ba rjes su bstan pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:15988: gsang sngags kyi sgra sgrags pas bdud btul ba ngan song sbyor bas kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:15989: de ltar yon tan du ma dang ldan pas /
NK124(ngo)001:15990: mnyam nyid ngang las ma g.yo' bar zhing khams brgya stong la sogs thugs rjes 'dul bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:15992: mnyam nyid ngang las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:15993: zhing khams stong gsum brgya' stong phrag /
NK124(ngo)001:15994: ma nges cho 'phrul sna tshogs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:15995: sprul pa'i lus kyis 'dul bar byed //
NK124(ngo)001:15998: zag pa med pa'i mngon shes drug gis de snyed mkhyen par gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:15999: nyams gong ma la sbyor tshul 'di /
NK124(ngo)001:16000: mnyam pa nyid kyi dgongs spyod kyis /
NK124(ngo)001:16001: shes sgrib che 'bring gnyis bcoms nas lhun gyi grub pa thob pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16003: mnyam nyid rnal 'byor dgongs spyod dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16004: dgongs pa'i ngang du shes rab kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16005: shes sgrib rab dang 'bring bcom dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16006: rtsol ba med par lhun grub thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16008: lhun gyis grub pa'i mnyam nyid bzhi ste /
NK124(ngo)001:16009: ngo bo sku lnga lhun grub kyi rigs 'dzin cing /
NK124(ngo)001:16010: dgongs pa rab gsal mtha' dbus 'gro 'ong med pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:16011: ngang la che bcas kyis mnyam bzhag rjes thob med
NK124(ngo)001:16012: par bzhugs so // de'i ngang la ma g.yos par
NK124(ngo)001:16013: zhing khams mthar thug med par sprul pa bsam gyis
NK124(ngo)001:16014: mi khyab pa gang la gang 'dul du don mdzad
NK124(ngo)001:16015: par bzhugs so // par gsungs / dpe' ni phyogs ris med pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16016: ye shes rang gsal nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16017: dgos 'dod 'byung ba nor bu rin po che lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16019: sangs rgyas nyid dang mtshungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16023: mngon shes nyid kyang 'dra bar gsung la /
NK124(ngo)001:16024: bag la nyal gyi dri ma cha phra mo gcig
NK124(ngo)001:16025: dang bral ma bral gyi khyad par yod par gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:16027: rtags ni sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16028: yon tan sna tshogs rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16029: ma sgrib kun gsal mngon shes drug /
NK124(ngo)001:16030: yul dang mkhyen tshad rgyal ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16031: 'dra la bag la nyal le che //
NK124(ngo)001:16034: lhun gyi grub pa rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi
NK124(ngo)001:16035: bag la nyal gyi dri ma cha phra mo ste
NK124(ngo)001:16036: gnyis su med par grol nas /
NK124(ngo)001:16037: spang thob med par sangs rgyas par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16040: dmigs med rang rig ye shes kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16041: skad cig gcig la tha ma yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16042: bag la nyal bcoms de bzhin gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:16044: de ltar chos kun mtha' bral 'od gsal ba'i 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes mngon du gyur te /
NK124(ngo)001:16045: rtsol bral lhun grub chen po'i ngang la shugs la 'byung /
NK124(ngo)001:16046: mnyam rjes cha phra mo bag la nyal du gnas pa de /
NK124(ngo)001:16047: rang rig pa'i ye shes des gnyis su med par mngon du gyur nas /
NK124(ngo)001:16048: dgongs pa 'gro 'ong gsal 'grib med par sangs rgyas te /
NK124(ngo)001:16049: yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16051: kun du bzang po'i spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16052: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16053: rgyan cha lugs dang ldan pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16054: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16056: spyod pa'i rgyal po byar med du bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16059: bya bral rdzogs pa'i spyod pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16060: spyod yul rgyan gyis 'khor lo las //
NK124(ngo)001:16061: bya spyod bral ba'i rig pa 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:16062: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16064: sems nyid rang byung ye shes kyi don rtogs pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:16065: ngang nas ci spyod pa thams cad bya rtsol med
NK124(ngo)001:16066: pa'i dgongs pa lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod yul
NK124(ngo)001:16067: rnams sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK124(ngo)001:16069: ched du bya spyod dang bral ba'i rigs ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16070: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16072: spyod pa blang dor med par spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:16073: gang yang mi rgyu rgyun du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16074: ched du bya med spang blang bral //
NK124(ngo)001:16075: de phyir spyod pa ma spyod zhog /
NK124(ngo)001:16078: nyon mongs dug lnga dug gsum la sogs pa'i rtog pa phra rags gang shar yang /
NK124(ngo)001:16079: chos nyid blo 'dod chen po'i rang bzhin nyid du
NK124(ngo)001:16080: 'gag med rang grol blang dor med par spyod pa
NK124(ngo)001:16082: dug lnga dug gsum la sogs rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:16083: 'gag med rang byung nyid du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:16084: spang blang med pa'i spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16087: ha la nag po'i dug dag kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16088: thabs mkhas zas legs sman gyi mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:16089: de bzhin 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16090: nyon mongs rang sar grol tsam na //
NK124(ngo)001:16091: de nyid rang byung ye shes yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16094: sems nyid rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16095: gzugs sdug mi sdug la sogs 'dod yon snang yul
NK124(ngo)001:16096: du gang shar kyang ched 'dzin dgag bsgrub med par
NK124(ngo)001:16097: spyod pa ni / chos kun byang chub sems su rtogs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:16098: chos dbyings dag pa'i ngo bor shar bas /
NK124(ngo)001:16099: rgyan dang cha lugs dang ldan pa'i spyod pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16103: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16104: chos dbyings dag pa'i ngo bor shar //
NK124(ngo)001:16105: rgyan dang cha lugs ldan spyod yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16108: skyes bu goms pa gar rgyug ltung med ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:16109: skye med rtogs shing 'bres pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16110: gang ltar spyad kyang mnyam nyid thig le'i ngang //
NK124(ngo)001:16111: ched du mi spang ngang du bzhag pas grol //
NK124(ngo)001:16112: ma spangs lhun grub byang chub chen por spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:16113: kun gzhi ma bcos ngang nas des spyod pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16114: chos rnams kun la spyod pa gang yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:16115: gang la yang mi gnas mi rtogs mi skyod na //
NK124(ngo)001:16116: skye med gnas lugs rtogs pa'i spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16119: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa man chad nas lo ka'i bya spyod gang ltar shar yang /
NK124(ngo)001:16120: dgag sgrub re dogs med par gnyis med rang byung
NK124(ngo)001:16121: ye shes kyi ngang du lam du khyer nas rang
NK124(ngo)001:16123: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i spyod pa yin par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16125: bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16126: 'jig rten bya spyod thams cad kun //
NK124(ngo)001:16127: ched kyis dgag sgrub gang yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:16128: rang byung ye shes nyid du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:16129: bsam gyis mi khyab spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16132: nam mkha'i ngang du mdung skor 'dra //
NK124(ngo)001:16133: gang la yang ni thogs pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:16134: ral gri'i so dang 'dra ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:16135: gdong du ci byung thams cad spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:16139: thog mtha' dus dang snod bcud rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:16140: lhun grub rang byung ye shes kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16141: rtsal du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:16142: bdag nyid chen po'i spyod pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16144: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i snod bcud thams cad /
NK124(ngo)001:16145: yin lugs snang lugs rang byung gi ye shes rtsal las byung zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:16146: de'i ngang las ma g.yos par lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:16147: rang bzhin du rtogs pas de dang ma bral bar
NK124(ngo)001:16148: nyams su blang ba ni bdag nyid chen po'i spyod
NK124(ngo)001:16149: pa yin te / nges don 'dus pa las /
NK124(ngo)001:16150: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du //
NK124(ngo)001:16151: rang gsal rig pa 'di nyid la //
NK124(ngo)001:16152: de bas gzhan du bogs mi 'don //
NK124(ngo)001:16153: da lta lus ngag yid kyis kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16154: gzhan nas ma tshol dus 'di la //
NK124(ngo)001:16155: ma yengs rig spyod don dran na //
NK124(ngo)001:16156: 'khor ba med pa'i mdzad spyod yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16157: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16159: de lta spyod pa ci ltar spyad kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:16160: spyad bya spyod byed gnyis su med cing /
NK124(ngo)001:16161: yul sems dbyer med snang bas /
NK124(ngo)001:16162: rang grol rig pa gdod ma nas gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma med pas rang shar rang grol bas /
NK124(ngo)001:16163: theg pa 'og ma'i ched 'dzin mi mnga' zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:16164: 'og ma rnams kyi spyod pa yar ldan tshul du rdzogs par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16166: spyod pa'i khyad par ci byung yang //
NK124(ngo)001:16167: dgag sgrub ched 'dzin bral bas na //
NK124(ngo)001:16168: spyod pa'i rgyal po byar med yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16172: ci spyod don la ma g.yos bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16173: don dam bde ba'i rtsis zin na //
NK124(ngo)001:16174: spyod pa zhes ni de la bya //
NK124(ngo)001:16177: rtogs par bya ba'i dam tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16178: ched du bya ba'i dam tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16179: bsrung bar bya'i dam tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16180: spang bar bya ba'i dam tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16181: spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16182: thun mong gi dam tshig go //
NK124(ngo)001:16183: dang po la yang lnga ste /
NK124(ngo)001:16184: kun gzhi ma spangs par chos skur rtogs pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16185: dug lnga ma spang par ye shes su rtogs pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16186: dug lnga rang grol ba'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16187: chos nyid 'gyur med kyi don rtogs tsam gyis grol ba'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16191: kun gzhi nang gis chos sku las //
NK124(ngo)001:16192: sangs rgyas mi rtsal dam tshig ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16193: de nyid ngos zin rtogs pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:16196: dug lnga spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK124(ngo)001:16197: sangs rgyas gzhan na med pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16198: dug lnga mi spang dam tshig mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:16200: dug lnga chos nyid don shes na //
NK124(ngo)001:16201: spang blang med pa'i chos sku gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:16205: dug lnga rang grol don shes na //
NK124(ngo)001:16206: ched du mi b+hee dam tshig ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16207: yid kyis bsam pas b+hee mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:16211: rin chen rnyed pa las mi dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:16212: de bzhin don rtogs dam tshig ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16213: b+hee mi dgos pa'i chos yin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:16214: ma b+hee stong bral gol pa med //
NK124(ngo)001:16218: de dag rtogs thabs dam tshig kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16219: rtsa ba rang sems 'di nyid las //
NK124(ngo)001:16220: gzhan nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:16221: rang rig rtogs na dam tshig mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:16224: bya bral rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16225: chos nyid ngang las d+ha nyams med //
NK124(ngo)001:16226: rig pa ye shes d+ha nyams med //
NK124(ngo)001:16227: ma bcos ting 'dzin d+ha nyams med //
NK124(ngo)001:16229: de dag gis don rgyas par bkrol nas ston par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16230: gnyis pa ched du bya ba'i dam tshig ni gnyis te /
NK124(ngo)001:16236: dper na mig gi 'bras bu bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16237: lung ldan rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK124(ngo)001:16238: brtse gdung dam tshig rgyun du bkur //
NK124(ngo)001:16239: nges don mchog gi dngos grub thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16240: dper na rang gi lus bsrungs bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16241: nges don gcig pa'i grogs dag la //
NK124(ngo)001:16242: gdung sems mi 'bral gus byed na //
NK124(ngo)001:16243: dngos grub tshe ring longs spyod 'phel //
NK124(ngo)001:16247: dper na rang gi snying bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:16248: dam tshig gdag pa ma nor bar //
NK124(ngo)001:16249: snod med gzhan la mi spel bar //
NK124(ngo)001:16250: ched du sus byas bsam pa 'grub //
NK124(ngo)001:16254: ka la ping ka dbyangs snyan zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:16255: rang gis lta b+hee nges pa'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:16256: rgyun du mi 'bral ched du ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16257: rig pa so thub dam tshig bsrungs //
NK124(ngo)001:16259: bden mthong rkyen khar mi stong zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:16260: lung bstan ngan pa'i dam tshig la //
NK124(ngo)001:16261: bdud kyi cho 'phrul gang byung yang //
NK124(ngo)001:16262: zil mnon dgag pa dran pa gces //
NK124(ngo)001:16264: bu la mi chags ni ti bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16265: don ldan dam tshig gdeng ldan na //
NK124(ngo)001:16266: chos brgyad spang blong med shes phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:16267: ched du ma zhen gnyen po dgos //
NK124(ngo)001:16268: de dag ched bya'i dam tshig kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16269: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs su 'dus //
NK124(ngo)001:16270: de phyir brtse gdungs dam tshig ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16271: chos rnams kun gyi gzhi ma yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16273: de dag gi dgongs don ma 'khrul bar bya ba gces so //
NK124(ngo)001:16274: gsum pa bsrungs bar bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16276: rdo rje slob dpon sku dgra dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16277: bshes 'dris mi bya bsrung gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:16278: rin chen sku'i dngos grub thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16279: nag mo 'jing dang dam nyams kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16280: 'thab sdum shugs ma spong gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:16281: bgegs kyis mi tshugs byin rlabs 'jug /
NK124(ngo)001:16282: mig zlum sha ni ma zos na //
NK124(ngo)001:16283: bram ze gtsang mas rig 'dzin skyob //
NK124(ngo)001:16284: mkha' 'gros thun mong dngos grub gter //
NK124(ngo)001:16285: gser dang bye ma mi barje bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16286: nges don rgyud drug chod dang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16287: bka' kun chos bzhan ma rjes na //
NK124(ngo)001:16288: thugs kyi dngos grub sangs rgyas thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16292: rnal 'byor nges lung ldan pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16293: bems zug mi shigs bsrung dgos na //
NK124(ngo)001:16294: sems can tha mal 'gro ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16295: dam tshig can gyis srog gcod spang //
NK124(ngo)001:16296: til gyis 'bru ma tsams yang ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16297: ma byin blang bar mi bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16298: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i rdzas //
NK124(ngo)001:16300: reg pa dug chen dpe' bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:16301: bsrung ma lnga ldan gzhan gyi la //
NK124(ngo)001:16302: chags sems tsam yang mi bya ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16303: rnal 'byor dam tshig ldan pas spang //
NK124(ngo)001:16304: kha blang dug gis dpe' bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:16305: mi chos bla ma'i rdzun la sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16307: de dag rtsa ba bzhi po dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16309: de ma spang bar grol mi srid //
NK124(ngo)001:16310: de phyir rnal 'byor kun gyis spangs //
NK124(ngo)001:16311: de rnams shin tu bsrung bar bya //
NK124(ngo)001:16313: lnga pa blang bar bya ba'i dam tshig ste /
NK124(ngo)001:16314: don dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16315: thabs mkhas pas gdul bya 'dul bar gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16317: dug sbrul nyes byed gsod pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16318: sku dgra nyes byed zhing bcu la //
NK124(ngo)001:16319: sngags dang bskul ba la sogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16320: sdig can bsgral na dngos grub thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16321: dper na sbrang bu bcud len bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16322: rnal 'byor thabs rnams sna tshogs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16323: ser sna can gyis zas nor ni //
