NK124(ngo)001:16324: ma byin blang la tshogs su 'bul //
NK124(ngo)001:16325: shing thog smin pa'i bcud 'jib bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16326: snga phyi ma song gdeng ldan pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16327: mtshan ldan bcud ni len gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:16328: don la ma 'das bde ba'i grogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16329: byis pa lag stong brid pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16330: nges don bka' la bzhug byed du //
NK124(ngo)001:16331: drang don chos kun rdzun du smra //
NK124(ngo)001:16332: gol sgrib gsal phyir nyes med dge' //
NK124(ngo)001:16333: gnang ba'i dam tshig de dag kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16334: lta ba'i gdeng ldan bya ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:16335: tha mal kun gyis byar mi rung //
NK124(ngo)001:16336: de phyir gdeng ldan blo yis bya //
NK124(ngo)001:16337: zhes pa la sogs gsungs pa rnams skabs dang bstun nas sbyar bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16340: bla med theg pa'i dam tshig dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16341: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16342: bsdom pa'i bye brag mtha' yas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16343: thun mong bya spyod thams cad kun //
NK124(ngo)001:16344: ched du dgag pa gcig kyang med //
NK124(ngo)001:16345: ched du 'dzin pa spong bral bas //
NK124(ngo)001:16346: bla med theg pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16348: 'dir dam tshig mdor bsdus tsam du smos pa yin gyis /
NK124(ngo)001:16349: bye brag tu theg pa rang rang gi skabs su bstan pa bzhin rgyas par shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16350: lam gyi yun la gsum ste /
NK124(ngo)001:16356: rang las thob pa'ang gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16357: de yang rgyu rkyen las byung ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16358: rtogs pa mthar phyin pas don mngon du gyur te 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16360: rgyu mtshan nyid kyis lugs kyi /
NK124(ngo)001:16361: rgyu la rkyen gyis 'bras bu 'byung bar 'dod de /
NK124(ngo)001:16363: sems ni ye shes skye ba'i rgyu //
NK124(ngo)001:16364: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma mtshol cig /
NK124(ngo)001:16367: de bzhin dang po'i sems kyang byang chub mchog tu ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16368: rim gyis dkar po'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:16369: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16370: rgyas par rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16372: gsang sngags chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su
NK124(ngo)001:16373: ye nas sangs rgyas de nyid rtogs shing mngon du
NK124(ngo)001:16374: gyur bas 'bras bu thob ces gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16376: de las gzhan pa'i thob bya med //
NK124(ngo)001:16379: lang ka'i bdag po de yang min pa zhig yin par bsgrub pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:16380: mi 'dra ba zhig 'dra bar bcos pa ni ma yin gyi /
NK124(ngo)001:16381: ma bcos ma slad ma byas ma rtsal bar ye
NK124(ngo)001:16382: nas rang bzhin gyis de ltar yin pa nyid du
NK124(ngo)001:16385: 'bras bu sangs rgyas 'dus ma byas yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:16386: chos nyid sems nyid ye nas 'dus ma byas //
NK124(ngo)001:16387: bsgrub nas 'grub cing thob pa ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:16388: ye nas yin pa'i don de rab rtogs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16389: rtogs pas rten pa de la 'bras bur gtags //
NK124(ngo)001:16391: rgyas par bka' rgyud tha dag na gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16393: mtshan nyid pa skal pa grangs med gsum la sogs pa na sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16394: kri yog mi tshe bdun dang gsum nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16395: gsang sngags nang pa ni tshe gcig la rtogs grol dus mnyam pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16397: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa chen po'i gzhung lugs kyis
NK124(ngo)001:16398: skal pa grangs med gsum la sangs rgyas par gsungs
NK124(ngo)001:16400: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK124(ngo)001:16401: bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16402: bar du gcod pa'i bdud bzhi bcom mdzad pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:16403: bcom ldan seng+ge de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:16405: byams chos gzhung 'brel la sogs pa nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16406: bzang dang smon pa'i stobs can dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16407: sems can khyab par 'gro ba las //
NK124(ngo)001:16408: byang chub sems dpa' grangs med gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:16409: kun tu 'od la brtson par mdzad //
NK124(ngo)001:16412: gsung gi sprul pa sh+aaka thub kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16413: sems can skye bo las dag la //
NK124(ngo)001:16414: sde snod rnam pa gsum gyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16415: bskal pa grangs med rnam gsum la //
NK124(ngo)001:16418: gnyis pa kri yog pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16419: kri ya'i mi tshe bdun dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16420: yo ga ba mi tshe gsum nas thob par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16422: kri ya bya ba'i rgyud kyis theg pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16423: rang gzhung chos kyi yan lag tshang pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16424: mi tshe bdun gyis rigs kyi sa la sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:16426: byang chub rnam lnga lhar rdzogs tshul khrims kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16427: rnal 'byor yo ga'i rgyud kyi theg pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16428: mi tshe gsum gyis rig 'dzin sa la sbyor //
NK124(ngo)001:16431: mi tshe gsum gyis bar du gol zhing sgrib //
NK124(ngo)001:16433: gnyis su med pa mi tshe gsum gyis gol dang zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:16434: gsum pa gsang sngags nang pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16435: ma h+aa dang a nu'i tshe gcig dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16436: a ti rdzogs grol dus mnyam pa la sogs gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:16439: rgyu 'bras dus gcig rdzogs pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16440: rang rig nyid la dbang thob ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16441: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16442: brgya' brgya' dag tu snur zhing gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:16443: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:16445: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhus len las /
NK124(ngo)001:16446: gsang sngags tshe gcig gis 'bras bu ci lta bu lags zhes zhus pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16447: lhag mar bcas pa'i lus nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16448: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16449: rig pa 'dzin pa'i lus nyid kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16450: bla med byang chub thob par bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:16453: rnal 'byor zhag ni sum cu phrag drug na //
NK124(ngo)001:16454: tshe la dbang ba'i dngos grub thob par nges //
NK124(ngo)001:16455: lo ni nyis stong lnga brgya rang gnas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16456: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i tshul du lus bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16457: dus der sangs rgyas sa la 'gro bar nges //
NK124(ngo)001:16459: gnyis pa a ti ni yid skyob las /
NK124(ngo)001:16460: yang rab rab dang 'bring dang tha ma bzhi //
NK124(ngo)001:16464: tshe 'di nyid du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16465: rab phung po dor ba dang dbyings su grol ba dus mnyam du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16466: 'bring srid pa bar dor rtogs pa'i rgyun 'thud nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16467: tha ma skye ba phyi ma la mos pa'i mthus 'di dang 'phrad de sangs rgyas par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:16469: yang rab phung po lhag ma mi lus te /
NK124(ngo)001:16470: gzung 'dzin dbyen pa'i rtogs pa brten pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16471: bdag gzhan mnyam pa'i ngang gis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16472: chos kun mnyam pa'i ngang du ban bun la //
NK124(ngo)001:16473: bdag gzhan snang srid thams cad chos skur ban gyis bun //
NK124(ngo)001:16474: 'byung ba lnga'i dgongs pa lhag gis shar //
NK124(ngo)001:16475: yang rab 'bras bu de ltar de'i thob //
NK124(ngo)001:16478: rdzogs chen nges don a ti yo ga ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16479: grangs dang dus la mi ltos rang byung thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:16480: chos kun ci bzhin ma nor rtogs pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16481: 'bras bu sangs rgyas sku gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16483: gzhan nam gcig char ba'i lugs rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:16486: rab ni thun mong ma yin gnyis med de //
NK124(ngo)001:16487: rtogs pa gcig gis gzung 'dzin ngang du gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:16488: le lo phra mo snang ba ma gyur kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16489: 'chi ba'i srid pa rang gis grogs byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16490: sa chu me rlung rnam shes rang gsal dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16491: gnyis med ngang du rim gyis 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:16492: lhun grub nam mkha'i dgongs pa lhag gis shar //
NK124(ngo)001:16493: rang gis ngo bo 'gyur ba med na yang //
NK124(ngo)001:16494: rab kyis 'bras bu tha snyad de la 'dags //
NK124(ngo)001:16497: bag chags ltas pa'i bdag lus la //
NK124(ngo)001:16498: snying po mchog gi stobs rdzogs te //
NK124(ngo)001:16499: skye shi'i 'phrang las brgal ba'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:16500: bar do med pa lus bor nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16501: rig pa gcig po rten med de //
NK124(ngo)001:16503: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa ru //
NK124(ngo)001:16504: sprul pa grangs med 'byung ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16505: ces pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16508: 'bring gis zla bral dus gcig rtogs nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16509: tha dad 'khrul pa yin par nges shes skyes nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16510: 'khrul pa 'khrul par nges pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16511: bar ma do la bar do'i shes pa 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:16512: bar dor bar do'i shes pa byung tsam na //
NK124(ngo)001:16513: gong gi dgongs pa nam mkha' lta bur dran //
NK124(ngo)001:16514: dran pa de'i ngang la gnas tsam nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16515: gzung 'dzin dbyen pas skye ba len par ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16516: rdo rje sems dpas gsungs pa ma yin no //
NK124(ngo)001:16520: 'dod khrid rig pa der shes nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16521: ngang du gnas pas de grol ba //
NK124(ngo)001:16522: gnad kyis rang grol nye dus yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16526: tha ma 'di'i don la zhugs nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16527: rtogs kyang bden pa bya ba'i skabs med de //
NK124(ngo)001:16529: slu byed rmi lam yin par ma brten te //
NK124(ngo)001:16530: 'dod pa yod pas skye ba phyi ma len //
NK124(ngo)001:16531: mos pa'i dbang gis mi lus blang nas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:16532: bla med theg chen 'di dang 'phrad gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16533: de la phung po mi lus sangs rgyas par //
NK124(ngo)001:16536: tha ma phyi rol brtag pa rjed //
NK124(ngo)001:16537: dus tshe rkyen dang 'phrad pa'i tshe //
NK124(ngo)001:16538: skad cig gzung bstan 'dra yis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16539: the tshom med par don go nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16540: skye ba gcig gis sangs rgyas 'grub //
NK124(ngo)001:16542: spyi don gsum pa dpe' ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16544: rgyal bu 'bangs su 'khyams pa rgyal por ngos bzung nas rgyal sar ston te /
NK124(ngo)001:16545: rgyal srid la mnga' byed pa bzhin dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16546: nyi ma shar bas mun pa rang sar grol ba bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don de /
NK124(ngo)001:16547: lam gyi rkyen gyis rtogs pa mngon du gyur pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16548: ma rig pa la sogs pa skyon mtha' dag las grol te /
NK124(ngo)001:16549: yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16551: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK124(ngo)001:16552: rgyal bu rgyal sar bston tshul du //
NK124(ngo)001:16553: rim dang gcig char lam rkyen gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16554: rang gnas ye shes mngon du rtogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16557: 'bras bu'i ngo bo ye nas yin pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:16558: rtogs pas brten pa thob ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:16559: de yang gzhan nas thob pa ci yang med //
NK124(ngo)001:16560: dper na ma h+aa ra tsa' dpe' bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:16562: snang ba shar bas mun pa rlag pa ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:16563: lhun grub rtogs pa bya rtsal log pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16564: gnyis med rtogs pas gzung 'dzin log pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16565: gcig pur rtogs pas re dogs log pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16566: mnyam nyid rtogs pas dgag bsgrub log pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16567: 'bras bu thob ces rdo rje sems dpas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:16568: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:16569: a ti yo ga'i sa lam gyi rnam par bzhag pa'i le'u ste bco lnga'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:16570: spyi don bdun pa mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa la don brgyad de /
NK124(ngo)001:16574: theg pa rim dgu'i 'bras bu gcig gam tha dad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16575: sangs rgyas la ma rig pa yod med kyi brtag pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16576: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya gzigs tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16577: gzigs nas thugs rje skyes tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16578: 'phrin las kyis don mdzad tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:16580: ngo bo dang nges tshig go //
NK124(ngo)001:16582: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes gsal ba mthar phyin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16583: gzhi dang lam gyi nyes pa dag pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:16584: dgongs pa bde chen 'gro 'ong gsal grib med par mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16586: rang byung chos sku spros dang bral bas sangs //
NK124(ngo)001:16587: spros bral rtogs pa gdeng du gyur pas rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:16589: gzung 'dzin bag chags ma lus kun sangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16590: ye shes mkha' la nyi shar bzhin du rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:16593: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16594: spang thob med par der bzhin gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:16595: gzhan mtha' grol te bde chen gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16599: ngo bo sems nyid gsal mthar phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:16600: gzhi lam zhor snang skyon bral yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16604: sangs rgyas kyi nges tshig go //
NK124(ngo)001:16606: 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes mngon sum rtogs pas smin cing bgrod du med la /
NK124(ngo)001:16607: yon tan thams cad rdzogs pas 'bras bu zhes tha snyad du btags pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16609: rgyu la rkyen gyis skyed med de //
NK124(ngo)001:16610: 'dus ma byas kyi chos nyid de //
NK124(ngo)001:16611: rang gsal mthar phyin bsgrod med cing //
NK124(ngo)001:16612: yon tan kun rdzogs 'bras bur bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:16615: rgyu la rkyen gyis skyed men la //
NK124(ngo)001:16616: mthar phyin skyes bu byar med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16617: smin pa'i 'bras bu brdar rtags pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16618: mthun pa'i ming du nges pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16621: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa la sogs pa skyon thams cad sangs shing /
NK124(ngo)001:16622: ye shes yon tan thams cad phyogs med du rgyas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16624: nyon mongs zhen pa'i rtsol ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16625: ma rig shes sgrib gtan nas sangs //
NK124(ngo)001:16626: ye shes yon tan phyogs med rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:16627: ngo bo'i cha nas ming du brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:16630: sangs ni nyon mongs bag chags sangs //
NK124(ngo)001:16631: rgyas ni rang gi bde chen rgyas //
NK124(ngo)001:16634: gzung 'dzin bag chags zhes gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16637: dang po sku gsung thugs rnams dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16638: yon tan las lngar bsdus pa'i yin //
NK124(ngo)001:16639: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16640: bskyed rdzogs gsum dang 'bras bu yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16641: rnam grangs phyogs gcig nas mthun la //
NK124(ngo)001:16642: don gyis khyad par lta ba'i rim pa bzhin yod de 'og nas ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:16644: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16646: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las //
NK124(ngo)001:16647: bsam gyis mi khyab ma 'dres rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16650: rnam par brjod pa'i sku nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:16651: smra brjod bral bas gsung nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:16652: thams cad mkhyen pas thugs nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:16653: 'dod dgu 'byung bas yon tan nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:16654: bya ba byed pas 'phrin las nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:16662: gzhan gyi log rtog bsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16663: don lnga pa rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16665: med pa la skur 'debs kyi log rtog gsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16668: sa bcu rgyun gyi tha ma rdo rje lta bu'i
NK124(ngo)001:16669: ting nge 'dzin shes bya'i sgrib pa cha phra mo
NK124(ngo)001:16670: de bcom nas / shes byed kyang med de /
NK124(ngo)001:16671: shes bya shes byed bye brag gnyis ka 'gags nas stong par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16672: de yang shing la gnyen po me byung bas shing zad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16673: me shi ba bzhin du 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16674: des na sangs rgyas la ye shes med la /
NK124(ngo)001:16675: ye shes yod na shes pa yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16676: shes pa thams cad rnam rtog 'khrul pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:16677: sangs rgyas 'khrul bcas su thal ba'i skyon 'ong /
NK124(ngo)001:16678: des sems can gyi don 'ong ngam /
NK124(ngo)001:16680: ye shes med kyang smon lam gyi dbang gis gdul
NK124(ngo)001:16681: bya'i ngo la sku gnyis dang ye shes la sogs
NK124(ngo)001:16682: pa yod par ltar snang nas don byed pa yin
NK124(ngo)001:16683: te / dper na sngags pa tsug li zhes bya ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:16685: khyung sgrub ste klu gtul bas /
NK124(ngo)001:16686: gzhan thams cad yang klu 'ong ba bsrungs /
NK124(ngo)001:16687: 'chi khar mchod rten gcig la byin rlabs byas nas bzhag pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16689: gzhan gyis klu thub pa lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16690: rtogs pa med kyang don byed pa nor bu rin po che lta bu yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16692: dper na nam mkha' lding gis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16693: mchod rten bsgrub nas 'das gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:16694: de 'das yun ring lon kyang de //
NK124(ngo)001:16695: dug nad la sogs zhi ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16696: de bzhin byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK124(ngo)001:16697: rgyal ba'i mchod sdong bsgrub pa yang //
NK124(ngo)001:16698: byang chub sems dpa' mya ngan 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:16699: 'das kyang don rnams thams cad mdzad //
NK124(ngo)001:16702: yid bzhin nor bu dpag bsam shing //
NK124(ngo)001:16703: ci ltar re ba yongs bskongs ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:16704: de bzhin gdul bya'i smon lam gyi //
NK124(ngo)001:16705: dbang gis rgyal ba'i skur snang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:16707: rgyas par lung dang bcas pa dbu ma'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:16708: de yang lung rig man ngag gsum dang 'gal te /
NK124(ngo)001:16709: dbu' ma'i skabs su ye shes med pa skyon brjod pa'i lung rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16710: sku dang ye shes yod pa'i lung rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16712: thub pa chos kyi sku can phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:16713: tshogs kyang de'i mthar thug go //
NK124(ngo)001:16716: ngo bo nyid lung rdzogs bcas dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16717: de bzhin gzhan pa sprul pa'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16718: chos sku mdzad pa dang bcas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:16719: rnam pa bzhir ni yang dag brjod //
NK124(ngo)001:16721: sangs rgyas mngon gnas mkhyen pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16722: lhun gyis grub dang chags spang dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16723: thog ma med dang brtag gnas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16724: 'dri ba kun len thebs par bzhed //
NK124(ngo)001:16728: me shi mi zad dpe' bzhin 'dod pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:16729: ye shes rnam rtog rgyun chad spong bya med //
NK124(ngo)001:16730: de phyir gnyen po med pas bsgrub bya bral //
NK124(ngo)001:16731: ye shes med par 'dod phyir don la gol //
NK124(ngo)001:16734: la las shes bya zag zad de //
NK124(ngo)001:16735: de shes zad gyur shing zad pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:16736: me ltar stong zhing mya ngan 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:16737: smon lam las grub 'byung ba'i skus //
NK124(ngo)001:16738: don byed 'dod na dngos byed stong //
NK124(ngo)001:16741: rig snang mthar thug sa bcu'i ye shes rig /'gegs pa'i gnyen po ye shes nyid len gang //
NK124(ngo)001:16742: me'i shing zad 'thun dogs gcig mthong ba //
NK124(ngo)001:16743: yang dag rig par 'gyur med ci ltar shing //
NK124(ngo)001:16744: ting ting ting ka mtshan mo lo ma 'khums //
NK124(ngo)001:16745: shing dang srog dang bcas bsgrub de rig 'gyur //
NK124(ngo)001:16746: 'dod na stong chad sdig can de nyid mod //
NK124(ngo)001:16747: rang bzhin rnam pa'i mchog ldan byang chub sems //
NK124(ngo)001:16749: stong par ma shes na ni ci ste lto //
NK124(ngo)001:16750: stong par shes pa'i rig pa mi 'gags pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16751: stong par sgros btags ngo bo snang ba nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:16754: ye shes med na sangs rgyas kyi nges tshig med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16755: mu stegs chad pa bden pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16756: shes byed med pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:16758: yangs pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16759: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa la sogs nyes pa thams cad sangs pa yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16760: rgyas pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16761: ye shes dag yon tan phyogs med du rgyas pa yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16762: ye shes med na sangs rgyas kyis nges tshig med cing sangs rgyas rang ma yin par thal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:16763: nges tshig med kyang yin na mi 'thad de /
NK124(ngo)001:16764: ri bong gi rwa la sogs pa mi srid pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:16765: chos rnams kyang sangs rgyas su thal ba'i skyon 'ong
NK124(ngo)001:16766: ngo // gnyis pa ni mu stegs 'chad pa'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16767: 'dir yang ye shes med na rgyun chad de med par thal te /
NK124(ngo)001:16770: ye shes med par lung gis shes sam /
NK124(ngo)001:16772: lung gis shes na ye shes med pa'i lung rnams sus gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:16773: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs na ye shes med pa nyams la /
NK124(ngo)001:16774: ma gsung zhing gdul bya'i ngor snang ba yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:16776: 'khrul na gdul bya 'khrul pa'i log shes yin pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16777: bka' rgyud rnams kyang gdul bya 'khrul pa'i log shes su thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:16778: ma 'khrul pa'i ngo la snang na sangs rgyas kyi gsung zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:16779: de ka sangs rgyas yin pas ye shes med pa nyams so //
NK124(ngo)001:16780: 'on te sangs rgyas med na mkhyen no zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:16781: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa shes shing kun mkhyen 'dug pas kyang lhag par thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:16783: sangs rgyas med par shes pa'i rig shes de 'khrul lam ma 'khrul /
NK124(ngo)001:16784: 'khrul na ye shes yod par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:16786: med par shes pa 'khrul pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:16787: ma 'khrul na de'ang sangs rgyas su thal /
NK124(ngo)001:16789: 'khrul pa sangs shing dgongs pa shes pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:16790: de skad du byas la rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i ye shes las /
NK124(ngo)001:16791: gdul bya gzhan snang du yod pas skyon med dam ce na /
NK124(ngo)001:16792: skye bo rang rgyud pa ltar bdag dang bcas pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:16793: rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i ye shes med pa yin nam
NK124(ngo)001:16794: / sangs rgyas kyi thugs rig pa'i ye shes rgyun chad nas med pa yin /
NK124(ngo)001:16796: nga bdag dang bcas pa med kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:16797: thugs rig pa ye shes yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16798: ye shes med pa nyan thos phyi ma ltar na ye shes rgyun chad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16799: sngar gyi skyon las ma 'das so //
NK124(ngo)001:16801: gdul bya 'khrul lam ma 'khrul te gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:16802: yang sku dang ngo bo la med kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:16803: smon lam gyi dbang gis mkhyen cing don byed do //
NK124(ngo)001:16805: smon lam gyi rten sangs rgyas kyis byas nas mkhyen cing snang ba yin nam /
NK124(ngo)001:16806: gdul bya'i sems kyis byas nas snang ba yin nam /
NK124(ngo)001:16807: bems po'i dngos po gcig gis byas nas snang ba yin nam /
NK124(ngo)001:16808: stong pa cang med gcig gis byas nas mkhyen cing snang ba yin nam rtags /
NK124(ngo)001:16810: sangs rgyas la sku dang ye shes yod par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:16812: sangs rgyas thugs kyis byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:16813: 'dod na ye shes med pa nyams so //
NK124(ngo)001:16815: gdul bya 'khrul lam ma 'khrul gyis brtag pa gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:16817: bems po rang ma yin par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:16819: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK124(ngo)001:16820: 'dod na bems po mkhyen pa'i dam bca' bud /
NK124(ngo)001:16822: stong pa cang med rang ma yin par thal /
NK124(ngo)001:16826: stong pa cang med yin pa nyan thos /
NK124(ngo)001:16827: de ltar ma yin brten spyi mthun gyis byas nas mkhyen to zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:16829: mkhyen pa'i dngos po gnyis yod dam med /
NK124(ngo)001:16830: yod na ye shes yod par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16832: med na gcig grol bas kun grol ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:16833: gnyis pa dngos por sgro 'dogs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16834: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba dngos po rang rgyud pa bzang po gcig 'og min na yod la /
NK124(ngo)001:16836: dbu' ma'i skabs nas bstan cing mtha' grol ba bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:16839: rig pa'i dngos po gcig brtag bde' //
NK124(ngo)001:16840: ye shes mu mtha' yas par 'dod //
NK124(ngo)001:16841: chos dbyings rgya bral rtogs dngos mtha' //
NK124(ngo)001:16843: gong gis dngos po yod par 'dod pa'i gol sa bkag pa shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16846: rang byung rtag pa chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16847: spros bral brjod de rig pa'i gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:16848: mtshan nyid dran rtogs med pa'i thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:16850: bya rtsol med pa'i las chen po //
NK124(ngo)001:16851: kun la khyab cing cir yang bdal //
NK124(ngo)001:16853: kun gyi gzhi rten du gyur pas sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16854: don gyis brda' sprod mtshon pas gsung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16855: gsal 'grib med par thams cad mkhyen pas thugs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16856: zad mi shes pa 'dod dgu 'byung bas yon tan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16857: mdzad pa lhun gyis grub cing bya ba byed pas 'phrin las so //
NK124(ngo)001:16858: de re re la'ang lnga lngar phye bas nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16859: bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsung ste /
NK124(ngo)001:16861: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las //
NK124(ngo)001:16862: gcig la lnga lngar rtsa lnga dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16863: shin tu bsam yas lhun grub pa //
NK124(ngo)001:16867: de yang 'bras bu sku lnga dang //
NK124(ngo)001:16868: ye shes rnam lnga yod tshul ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16869: 'dus ma byas kyi nam mkha' bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:16871: sku dang ye shes yang dag yod //
NK124(ngo)001:16874: lhun nas bde chen dag pa'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16875: chos sku 'khrul pa kun las grol //
NK124(ngo)001:16876: rang rig bde chen longs spyod rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:16877: 'od zer thugs rje'i rnam par sprul //
NK124(ngo)001:16878: dbyer med ngang du rdzogs pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:16881: ngo bo nyid kyi sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16888: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la mi mthun gnyen po med
NK124(ngo)001:16889: par gnas lugs ci bzhin pa mngon du gyur pa
NK124(ngo)001:16890: ni / ngo bo nyid kyi sku yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16892: ma bcos ye nas kun gyi gzhi' //
NK124(ngo)001:16893: rang byung ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16894: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba'i gzhir //
NK124(ngo)001:16895: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyis gsung //
NK124(ngo)001:16898: ngo bo nyid kyi sku ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16899: gnyen po med pa rnam par rtog pa thams cad dang ldan te /
NK124(ngo)001:16901: ngo bo nyid ni ci bzhin de nyid la bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16904: chos dbyings skye 'gag gsal 'grib med pa mngon du gyur pas chos sku yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:16906: chos sku rang byung rig pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:16907: dus gsum dag tu skye 'gag med //
NK124(ngo)001:16909: de phyir kun bzang chos kyi sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16913: skye med chos kyi dbyings su gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:16915: de yang chos dbyings skye 'gag gsal 'grib med pa mngon du byas pa nyid chos kyi sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16916: de nyid longs sku'i ngo la chos dbyings rang gsal
NK124(ngo)001:16917: byin rlabs kyis ston pa kun du snang ba ni
NK124(ngo)001:16920: chos sku lhag ma med par dgongs pa bde ba
NK124(ngo)001:16921: chen por rdzogs shing longs spyod pas longs sku yin
NK124(ngo)001:16922: te / nam mkha' mtha' nyams las /
NK124(ngo)001:16923: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:16924: rang byung mtshan dpe' rang la chas //
NK124(ngo)001:16925: bde ba kun la mnga' mdzad cing //
NK124(ngo)001:16926: ye shes dmigs pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK124(ngo)001:16929: nyid kyis rol pa nyid longs spyod //
NK124(ngo)001:16930: longs spyod rdzogs sku nyid kyis bstan //
NK124(ngo)001:16932: de yang chos sku dgongs pa bde ba chen por longs spyod pa ni nyid longs sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16933: de nyid la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16934: smin pa rgya mtsho' 'khor rnams la sku mtshan dang dpe' byad kyis ba rgyan pa /
NK124(ngo)001:16935: rgyal ba rigs lnga la sogs snang nas don mdzad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:16938: de nyid phyogs med cir yang 'char zhing sprul pa
NK124(ngo)001:16939: bsam gyis mi khyab par snang nas don mdzad pa
NK124(ngo)001:16940: sprul sku'o // nam mkha' mtha' nyams las /
NK124(ngo)001:16941: thub pa'i dbang po grangs las 'das //
NK124(ngo)001:16942: mdor bsdus drug snang ye shes drug /'dul dbang ye shes snang tshul gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16946: lhag med thugs rje'i sprul pa ni //
NK124(ngo)001:16947: nges med sku de cir yang snang //
NK124(ngo)001:16949: de yang mdzad pa phyogs med cir yang 'char ba nyid sprul sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16950: dag pa dang ma dag pa'i gdul bya gang la
NK124(ngo)001:16951: gang 'dul du bstan nas don mdzad pas gzhan snang
NK124(ngo)001:16953: gsang mdzad pa'i the tshom gcod pa ni gsang ba'i sku dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16954: de rnams dbyer med cing 'du 'bral med pa ni rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16956: zhing khams la sogs pa'i skabs nas ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:16959: rdo rje'i sku ni 'jigs bral med //
NK124(ngo)001:16961: yang dag rtsa ba bsdus pa'i rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:16962: dus gsum rtag tu mi 'gyur bas //
NK124(ngo)001:16963: rdo rje'i sku'i sku zhes gdag /
NK124(ngo)001:16965: zhing khams la sogs pa rgyas ni mdzad pa'i skabs nas ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:16967: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la ma sgribs rang gsal ba
NK124(ngo)001:16968: mtshon pas rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi gsung dang
NK124(ngo)001:16969: / dbyer med byin rlabs kyis chos sku skye med
NK124(ngo)001:16970: rang snang du mtshon pas chos sku byin rlabs kyi
NK124(ngo)001:16971: / gsung dang / sku mdun dang rgyab med par
NK124(ngo)001:16972: zhal phyogs kun tu thal ler dgongs brda'i mtshon pas
NK124(ngo)001:16973: longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16974: tshangs dbyangs kyi sgo nas gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu la sogs mtshon pas /
NK124(ngo)001:16975: sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16976: mdzad pa thabs kyi sgo nas gsang ba dam pa'i the tshom gcod pas gsang ba'i sku'i gsung dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16977: grags stong dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:16979: gang ngo bo nyid med pa'i gsung ni nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:16980: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:16982: ngo bo mthong tshul gnyis kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:16983: rang rig ye shes cha yin pas //
NK124(ngo)001:16984: rnam par spyad pa'i chos mi gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:16987: zhing khams chos nyid bde ba'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:16988: rang bzhin 'og min byang chub thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:16989: chos sku ston pa kun bzang gis //
NK124(ngo)001:16990: dgongs pa nges thob byin rlabs so //
NK124(ngo)001:16991: phun tshogs nyid las ma gzhan 'khor //
NK124(ngo)001:16992: dus gsum sangs rgyas nyid las bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:16994: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i sgo nas //
NK124(ngo)001:16995: ldems dgongs phyi nang gsang ba'i don //
NK124(ngo)001:16996: sa bcu'i rig 'dzin sems dpa' la //
NK124(ngo)001:16997: gsang sngags rang gis ngo bo bston //
NK124(ngo)001:16999: sprul skus gsung pa'i sgo nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:17000: gang la gang mos drang don du //
NK124(ngo)001:17001: dge' sdig rgyu 'bras gnyis kyi chos //
NK124(ngo)001:17002: sdeb sbyor legs pa'i tshig tu ston //
NK124(ngo)001:17005: ston pa chos skus byin rlabs bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:17006: longs spyod rdzogs pa rang gis ngo bo bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:17007: sprul pa'i skus ni tshig dang don bsdeb bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:17010: zhing khams la sogs skabs nas ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:17011: de yang ngo bo nyid kyi gsung ni shes bya'i
NK124(ngo)001:17012: dkyil 'khor la gsal 'grib med par mngon sum du
NK124(ngo)001:17014: sku gsum gyi gsung gis go tshul ni khog dbub
NK124(ngo)001:17015: kyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin du shes par bya'o
NK124(ngo)001:17016: // gsang ba'i sku'i go tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17017: gsang ba dam pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK124(ngo)001:17018: the tshom chod cing rtogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17019: de ltar lung dang rim par sbyar te go bar bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17024: ci ltar yod pa'i tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17027: chos kun sgrib med rang gsal du mkhyen nas ye shes byas te /
NK124(ngo)001:17029: rang gsal ye shes ma bcos pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17030: don de shes pa ye shes yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17033: cis kyang ma sgrib ye shes mchog /
NK124(ngo)001:17034: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:17036: kun nas rang rig shes gsal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:17037: cis kyang ma sgribs nges pa'i tshig /
NK124(ngo)001:17041: stong nyid ye shes mtshan mas brgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:17042: me long ye shes mi rtag gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:17043: mnyam nyid rig pa'i sems su gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:17044: so sor rtogs pa ma 'dres gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:17045: bya ba nan tan mthar phyin pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17047: chos kun mtshan ma dang dngos po med par chos
NK124(ngo)001:17048: dbyings rang gsal du mkhyen pas stong pa nyid kyi
NK124(ngo)001:17049: ye shes dang / chos kun ma sgrib pa rang gsal bar mkhyen pas me long lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17050: chos kun dbyer med cing mnyam nyid du mkhyen pas mnyam nyid ye shes dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17051: de nyid bye brag ma 'dres par mkhyen pas so sor rtogs pa'i dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17052: rtsol ba med par ye shes kyis bya ba byed bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:17054: stong pa kun ldan ye shes thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:17055: dngos med kun ldan stong chen po //
NK124(ngo)001:17056: 'jigs med rig pa rang gsal ba //
NK124(ngo)001:17057: stong nyid ye shes rtag tu bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:17059: phyogs mtshams kun tu gsal bar 'phro //
NK124(ngo)001:17060: ye shes me long thams cad gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:17061: ma bcos gzugs brnyan snang bas na //
NK124(ngo)001:17062: me long ye shes dag tu bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:17064: dbyer med nam mkha' lta bur khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:17065: snang srid byang chub sems su mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:17066: mnyam pa'i rang gsal phung por brdal //
NK124(ngo)001:17067: 'od gsal rig pa mnyam par bshad //
NK124(ngo)001:17069: 'bar ba'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK124(ngo)001:17070: rang gsal rig pa kun bzang thugs //
NK124(ngo)001:17071: mnyam la ma 'dres kun tu bzang //
NK124(ngo)001:17072: ma 'dres gsal ba'i ye shes so //
NK124(ngo)001:17074: kun gyi gnyen po rang byung la //
NK124(ngo)001:17075: thugs rjes lhun grub shar gyur na //
NK124(ngo)001:17076: gdul bya'i bya ba kun mdzad gsal //
NK124(ngo)001:17077: des na bya ba nan tan to //
NK124(ngo)001:17079: yod dang tshul dang mkhyen tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17080: thams cad mkhyen pa'i gdul bya gzigs tshul gyi skabs nas don ston to //
NK124(ngo)001:17082: spyir yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17083: zhing khams la sogs pa'i yon tan lnga bstan pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17086: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:17089: sangs rgyas che ba'i yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:17091: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod las 'das par gsung kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:17093: bde ba chen po'i ngang nas 'gro 'ong gsal 'grib med par bzhugs pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17094: sangs rgyas pa'i don de rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:17095: gzhan don sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17096: gang la gang 'dul gdul bya'i bsam pa dang bstun nas don mdzad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17097: de yang skus 'dul ba la sprul pa sna tshogs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17099: thugs kyis mkhyen pa la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17100: yon tan nor bu rin po che lta bu dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17101: 'phrin las ci ltar mtshams pa ltar byung ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17103: gzhi'i yon tan phyogs su ma chad pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17104: yon tan mchog tu gyur pa rgyal bas gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:17106: man ngag rgya mtsho'i klong las /
NK124(ngo)001:17107: yon tan nam mkha' mtha' dang mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:17108: kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK124(ngo)001:17109: chos nyid rig pa'i rgyan zhes gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:17112: chos sku 'bras bu rang gsal las //
NK124(ngo)001:17113: rin chen 'bar ba lhun grub ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:17115: skal ldan rang rkyen nyi ma bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:17119: dag pa'i zhing khams gzhal yas bsam /
NK124(ngo)001:17121: ye shes gsal ba'i 'khor lo snang /
NK124(ngo)001:17129: a nu'i skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:17131: rtsol med lhun grub 'phrin las dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17132: zhi rgyas dbang drag 'phrin las so //
NK124(ngo)001:17134: rtsol ba med par lhun grub bde ba chen po'i ngang las /
NK124(ngo)001:17135: gang la gang 'dul thabs mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab par don 'byung ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17137: bya bral 'od gsal chos dbyings las //
NK124(ngo)001:17138: 'phrin las rtsol med lhun grub pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17139: 'od gsal ye shes phyogs ris med //
NK124(ngo)001:17140: rtsol med 'phrin las mchog gi klong //
NK124(ngo)001:17142: gdul bya'i bsam pa ji bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:17143: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:17144: thabs mkhas spyod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK124(ngo)001:17145: dus gcig nyid la gsal bar 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:17148: phyogs ris med par ye bdal bas //
NK124(ngo)001:17149: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17150: rnam dag dbyings la gzhung bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:17151: yongs la khyab pa'i thugs rje 'byung //
NK124(ngo)001:17153: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17154: man ngag rgya mtsho'i klong las /
NK124(ngo)001:17155: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17156: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NK124(ngo)001:17158: zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi ba /
NK124(ngo)001:17161: drag pos 'dul ba la drag pos don mdzad de /
NK124(ngo)001:17162: gang la gang 'dul du don mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17165: gzhan gyis mtha' gsal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17166: dgongs pa ci ltar bzhugs tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:17169: sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres par rgyud tha dad par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17170: chu la chu thim pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:17171: sangs rgyas thams cad rgyu gcig tu 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17173: shing tha dad kyis me'i rang bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:17174: mtshan nyid me ru gcig kyang ngo bo tha dad pa ltar dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17175: 'bras bu'i phung po ltar mtshan nyid gcig pa nyid kyang ngo bo tha dad pa ltar /
NK124(ngo)001:17176: sangs rgyas thams cad kyang sangs rgyas par mtshan nyid gcig kyang /
NK124(ngo)001:17177: sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres te /
NK124(ngo)001:17179: de yang dgongs pa dkor ling mu mtha' can gyis skyon 'ong ste /
NK124(ngo)001:17180: dbu' ma'i skabs su bshad pa'i skyon de rnams kyang 'ong la /
NK124(ngo)001:17182: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17183: drang ba rtsam ste de nyid med //
NK124(ngo)001:17186: phyi ba shing gi me dpung ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:17187: rang bzhin dbyer med ngo bo nyid //
NK124(ngo)001:17188: kun mkhyen tha dad bzhugs pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:17189: phan tshun mi mkhyen kun mkhyen bral //
NK124(ngo)001:17190: mkhyen pas gzung 'dzin don rtogs te //
NK124(ngo)001:17191: rang bzhin spros bral rnam dag las //
NK124(ngo)001:17192: zhes pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:17194: mar la mar thim pa ltar rgyud gcig tu thim ste /
NK124(ngo)001:17195: stong nas med par 'dod pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17196: rig pa rgyud gcig tu thim nas mkhyen pa la sogs pa gsungs yod par 'dod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17198: gong du bskur 'debs kyi mtha' gsal ba'i skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:17200: mu stegs kyi skabs su bshad kyis mtha' gsang bar
NK124(ngo)001:17201: smra ba'i sde pa dang 'dra ba'i skyon 'ong ste
NK124(ngo)001:17202: / mu stegs kyi skabs su bshad pa dang mthun no //
NK124(ngo)001:17204: don dam gcig pur ma yin phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:17205: chu la chu bzhag ltar gcig pa'ang min //
NK124(ngo)001:17208: kun du ma 'dres ma shes par //
NK124(ngo)001:17212: dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ji ltar yin na /
NK124(ngo)001:17213: thun mong ma yin pa'i gcig dang tha dad las grol zhing /
NK124(ngo)001:17214: dgongs pa'i rgyud ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:17216: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK124(ngo)001:17217: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin gshegs //
NK124(ngo)001:17220: mnyam pa gsum po yin pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:17221: nges par rgyud gcig ma 'dres pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:17222: tha dad bral ba'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK124(ngo)001:17224: gong gi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17225: bzhi pa theg pa rim dgu'i 'bras bu gcig gam tha dad pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17226: shes bya ji lta ba nyid mthar phyin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17227: mthar thug rdzogs pa chen po ltar spang thob med par sangs rgyas tsam na khyad par med la /
NK124(ngo)001:17228: rang sa rang sa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17229: theg pa dgu ka la khyad yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:17230: 'og ma 'og ma gong ma gong ma'i lam stegs /
NK124(ngo)001:17231: gong ma gong mar sems bskyed dgos pa bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17232: des na a nu man chad kyi khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17233: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa ltar yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:17234: 'dir a nu man chad dang a ti'i khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17235: khyad par 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17238: lta ba khyad yod pa bzhin /
NK124(ngo)001:17239: 'bras bu la yang khyad yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:17240: lta ba'i don de nyid mngon du byas nas 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK124(ngo)001:17242: mi mthun gzhung gis sangs rgyas pa'ang //
NK124(ngo)001:17243: lta spyod ting 'dzin rim pa bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:17244: grub pa'i mtha' la khyad par pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17245: lta ba'i sgrib pa phye ba yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17248: byang chub sems dpa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17249: yang tig rdzogs chen yas ltas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17250: nges don snying po ma mthong phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:17251: gzhi nas ma rig yod pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:17252: rtsol ba byas pas chos sku sgrib //
NK124(ngo)001:17253: de phyir yang dag sangs rgyas min //
NK124(ngo)001:17255: de bzhin rgyud lung sangs rgyas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17256: yang dag rdzogs chen yas ltas na //
NK124(ngo)001:17257: rang byung nges don ma shes pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17258: ched du bya ba'i rtsol bas bsgrubs //
NK124(ngo)001:17259: re dogs phra mo yod pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:17260: nges lung ma yin snang ba 'chal //
NK124(ngo)001:17261: gzugs can sangs rgyas 'dod pa'i phyir //
NK124(ngo)001:17262: chos sku'i sangs rgyas don la sgrib //
NK124(ngo)001:17265: gnyis med don la gnyis bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17266: bskal pa grangs med gsum nyid du //
NK124(ngo)001:17267: sa bcu lam lnga pha rol phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:17268: sbyong zhing gnyis rtog spong len can //
NK124(ngo)001:17269: rang sa thob kyang mthar ma phyin //
NK124(ngo)001:17272: dbyings dang ye shes rang bzhin gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:17273: rgyu 'bras dag pa'i tshul du lta //
NK124(ngo)001:17274: bzod kyi ting 'dzin stobs kyis ni //
NK124(ngo)001:17275: rdo rje sems dpa' sa la 'gro //
NK124(ngo)001:17276: rang sa'i 'bras bu mngon thob kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17277: mthar thug 'bras bu de la med //
NK124(ngo)001:17280: sbyangs bsgrod rtsol ba 'jug nas rten //
NK124(ngo)001:17281: ti gnas tsam du bstan pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17283: yang kun tu 'od kyi sa ru bzhag pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17284: don la nges par brtag na rnam grangs tsam //
NK124(ngo)001:17285: ces pa la sogs pa a ti'i rgyud lung man ngag thams cad nas gsungs /
NK124(ngo)001:17287: ngo bo la spang thob yod med kyi khyad par ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17288: shes bya la phyogs tsam 'dzin mi 'dzin gyi khyad par dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17289: don che ba lnga'i khyad par du 'phags pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17291: a nu man chad 'khor ba las grol 'dod kyi blos /
NK124(ngo)001:17292: sangs rgyas bzang po gcig thob pa 'dod pas mtshan
NK124(ngo)001:17293: nyid pa dngos su spang thob can du 'dod pas
NK124(ngo)001:17294: / ma h+aa a nu la yang shugs kyis spang thob byung bas /
NK124(ngo)001:17295: shes bya ci lta ba nyid lhag ma med par mngon sum ma gyur ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17297: chos kun rang byung gis ye shes la 'khor 'das gnyis su med pas spang bya 'khor ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17298: thob bya sangs rgyas gnyis su med de /
NK124(ngo)001:17299: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par mngon du gyur pas khyad par du 'phags pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17301: nyan thos a nu man chad du //
NK124(ngo)001:17302: theg pa bye brag bas yas kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17304: bsgrub bya bsgrub byed yod pas na //
NK124(ngo)001:17305: de yang yul dang yul can no //
NK124(ngo)001:17308: bskal pa grangs dang tshe rabs su //
NK124(ngo)001:17309: dman pas sba dor ci byas dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17310: 'bring gis dmigs pas grol thob kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17311: don 'di nyams su ma myong na //
NK124(ngo)001:17312: rtag pa nyid las ma rtogs pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17313: spang thob ngo bo gdod nas med //
NK124(ngo)001:17316: nang pa snang stong zug 'jug mkhyen //
NK124(ngo)001:17317: de grol yul sems 'du bral med //
NK124(ngo)001:17318: byang sems bde chen chos nyid gdal //
NK124(ngo)001:17319: snang dang stong dang bden gnyis las //
NK124(ngo)001:17320: grol nas dbyer med mu thag pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17321: phyogs med bde chen dmar thag chad //
NK124(ngo)001:17323: spang thob med pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17325: len med spong dang yongs bral bas //
NK124(ngo)001:17326: dus gsum mnyam nyid rdo rje'i sku //
NK124(ngo)001:17329: rang byung ye shes mngon du byas pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17330: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od gdal yang //
NK124(ngo)001:17331: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du //
NK124(ngo)001:17332: sangs ma rgyas par byed pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:17333: chos ni rdul tsam yod med pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17334: sangs rgyas med pa'i che bar gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:17337: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:17339: nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud las /
NK124(ngo)001:17340: ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK124(ngo)001:17341: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK124(ngo)001:17342: gzhan nam chos kyi dbyings kyi klong //
NK124(ngo)001:17343: rdzogs ni lhag ma med par rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:17346: ma h+aa dang a nu sku lnga la sogs pa
NK124(ngo)001:17347: thob kyang a nu dbyings ye shes gnyis su med
NK124(ngo)001:17348: pa'i sras bde ba chen po la mchog tu bzung
NK124(ngo)001:17349: bas / shes bya'i dkyil 'khor brgya' theg pa mnyam pa nyid du ma rtogs te /
NK124(ngo)001:17350: phyogs 'dzin gyi rgya dang ma bral ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17352: a ti ni shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par mngon du bya bas /
NK124(ngo)001:17353: gang la yang phyogs 'dzin med par chos kun mnyam
NK124(ngo)001:17354: pa nyid du rtogs pas khyad par 'phags pa yin
NK124(ngo)001:17356: mnyam pa nyid kyis 'phags pa'i theg mchog 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:17357: theg pa kun gyi yang rtser mnyam pas 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:17358: mi spang mi len mnyam pa'i rgyal pos 'phags //
NK124(ngo)001:17361: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams ril //
NK124(ngo)001:17362: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan //
NK124(ngo)001:17364: gzhan yang mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i lung rnams so //
NK124(ngo)001:17367: che ba lnga'i 'phags pa'i 'bras bu de //
NK124(ngo)001:17368: mnyam pa nyid kyis 'phags pas ma go'am //
NK124(ngo)001:17370: che ba lnga'i 'og ma rnams las khyad par du 'phags pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17371: khog dbub kyi skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17373: sangs rgyas la ma rig pa yod med kyi brtag pa ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17374: ma rig pa spang bar rang grol nas /
NK124(ngo)001:17375: de nyid sangs rgyas la che ba'i yon tan du shar ba yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17376: de yang ma rig pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17377: nyon mongs ye nas rang byung gi ye shes su sangs rgyas pa yin la /
NK124(ngo)001:17378: de nyid rtogs pa mngon du gyur pas ma rig pa dang nyon mongs pa rang sar grol te /
NK124(ngo)001:17379: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la spang thob med par sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17380: des na sangs rgyas la ma rig pa spang ba
NK124(ngo)001:17381: med par rang grol nas mkhyen pa'i ye shes phyogs
NK124(ngo)001:17382: su rgyas pas / ma rig pa med ces bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17383: ma rig pa spang pa med par che ba'i yon tan du rgyas pas zhes kyang bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17384: de yang rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17385: ma rig pa dang bcas pa'i sems can rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17386: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par yod de /
NK124(ngo)001:17387: de rnams kyi yod lugs dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17389: rgyud gcig gam tha dad dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17390: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17391: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17393: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi gzigs tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17394: ye shes ci ltar yod pa'i tshul dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17395: des ci ltar gzigs pa'i tshul lo //
NK124(ngo)001:17397: ye shes bya ba ni 'dus ma byas shing rang
NK124(ngo)001:17398: byung gi ye shes yin pas skye 'gag med pa'i
NK124(ngo)001:17400: dus gsum 'phel 'grib med par gnas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17402: rang byung ye shes rgyus ma skyed //
NK124(ngo)001:17403: skye med rang gsal rgyun mi chad //
NK124(ngo)001:17406: kyee lang ka'i bdag po byang chub sems kyi de kho na nyid gsang ba dam pa de ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17407: skye 'gag med par rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17409: gsang ba'i bdag po gang gis rgyun dang bcas lags /
NK124(ngo)001:17411: lang ka'i bdag po ye shes rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17413: byin rlabs rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17414: smon lam rgyun dang bcas pa'i phyir rgyun mi chad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17417: dus gsum rgyun bcas mkhyen pa'i skad cig gis //
NK124(ngo)001:17418: ri rab til 'bru skad cig brgal len dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17419: zhing khams phyag mthil 'khor lo'i nang gnas te //
NK124(ngo)001:17421: khog dbub bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17422: bdun pa gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17424: phyogs ris med pa'i thugs rje ni //
NK124(ngo)001:17425: mthar thug med pa'i 'gro ba la //
NK124(ngo)001:17426: gdung med nyi ma'i 'od bzhin du //
NK124(ngo)001:17427: 'gro ba kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK124(ngo)001:17428: 'gro don med pa'i rgyal ba bzhin //
NK124(ngo)001:17429: ma byung 'byung bar mi srid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17431: thugs rje chen pos phyogs ris med par 'gro ba'i dpal du shar nas don byed par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:17432: de yang rtag par rgyun gyi thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17434: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17435: yul dang 'phrad nas thugs rje skye ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17437: gdod ma nas tha ma ris su ma chad pas /
NK124(ngo)001:17438: thugs rje bzung ba'i gdul bya smin pas 'brel /
NK124(ngo)001:17439: ma rtsal 'gro don rgyun chad med par sel med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:17440: rang shugs bskul bas 'phrad pa'i 'brel don mdzad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17442: gzhan rnams khog dbub kyi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17443: brgyad pa don mdzad tshul ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17444: 'dir yul dang mthun pa'i skabs su sku lngas 'gro ba la don mdzad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17445: dang po ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i zhing khams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17446: chos dbyings spyad du med pa /
NK124(ngo)001:17447: gnas ni spros bral rig pa'i gzhal yas sam /
NK124(ngo)001:17448: 'khor ni sangs rgyas sems can gyi tha snyad med cing thams cad sangs rgyas pa nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17449: bstan pa ni rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi gsungs so //
NK124(ngo)001:17450: dus ni tshad las 'das pa ste /
NK124(ngo)001:17451: dus bzhi dang mnyam pa nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17452: sdud pa po ni kun 'dus rig pa'i skyes bu'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17454: ngo bo mthong tshul gnyis kyis so //
NK124(ngo)001:17455: rang rig ye shes ma yin pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17456: rnam par spyad pa'i chos mi gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:17457: sku gsum rig pa'i klong du rdzogs //
NK124(ngo)001:17458: gnas ni spros bral rig pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:17459: bstan pa rang gsal me long yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17461: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17462: sdud pa kun 'dus rig pa yi //
NK124(ngo)001:17463: rang gsal rang las ma yin pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17464: phun sum tshogs pa mi gnas te //
NK124(ngo)001:17466: bsam gyis mi khyab dus na shes //
NK124(ngo)001:17469: gang ngo bo nyid med pa'i zhing khams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17473: mdzad pa ni cir yang mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17476: ngo bo nyid sku chos sku la //
NK124(ngo)001:17477: dus bzhi mnyam pa'i dus nyid na //
NK124(ngo)001:17478: tha dad mi gnas pa yi gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:17479: kun 'dus rang grol bstan pa ste //
NK124(ngo)001:17480: ma sgribs mthong chos rang shar bas //
NK124(ngo)001:17482: ston pa chos sku'i zhing khams ni //
NK124(ngo)001:17483: bde chen gdal khyab chen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17484: gnas ni ya ga don gyi 'og min /
NK124(ngo)001:17485: 'khor ni longs sku ye shes rgya matsho'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17486: bstan pa ni byin rlabs kyi gsungs te skyed rdzogs su bsam mo //
NK124(ngo)001:17487: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa de thams cad du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17488: sdud pa po ni rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17490: zhing khams chos dbyings bde ba'i klong //
NK124(ngo)001:17491: ces pa la sogs gong gis lung dang sbyar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:17494: gang rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams bde ba chen po'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17495: 'khor ni ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs /
NK124(ngo)001:17496: bstan pa ni bya ba byed pa'i chos so //
NK124(ngo)001:17497: dus ni thams cad nas thams cad du'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17498: mdzad pa ni chos thams cad rnam par mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17502: yid la rkyen gyis shar ba'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17503: yang dag don gyis 'jig rten du //
NK124(ngo)001:17504: bsam gyis mi khyab dus dag tu //
NK124(ngo)001:17505: mi nub don du gtad pa yin //
NK124(ngo)001:17506: bstan pa skyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:17508: ston pa longs sku'i zhing khams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17510: gnas ni 'og min stug po bkod pa'am /
NK124(ngo)001:17512: 'khor ni rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' ste /
NK124(ngo)001:17514: dus ni mnyam gzhag rig pa'i dus /
NK124(ngo)001:17515: bstan pa ni dgongs pa brda'i sgo nas phyi'i theg pa gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:17516: bsdud pa po gsang bdag rdo rje 'chang ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:17518: gang smin pa'i zhing khams de ni bde ba can no //
NK124(ngo)001:17519: 'khor ni yongs su smin pa rgya mtsho' chos so //
NK124(ngo)001:17520: bstan pa ni brjod du med pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17521: dus ni gnas gtsang ma na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17522: mdzad pa ni rnal 'byor dam pa nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17525: ston pa longs sku rig pa'i gnas //
NK124(ngo)001:17527: rang rig bde chen shar ba'i dus //
NK124(ngo)001:17528: bstan pa phyi'i theg pa gsum //
NK124(ngo)001:17529: mtshan dang dpe' byad lha'i skus //
NK124(ngo)001:17530: cha mthun longs sku'i bstan par gsungs //
NK124(ngo)001:17532: ston pa sprul sku'i zhing khams mi 'ched 'jig rten la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17533: gnas ni nges pa med pa rdo rje gdan la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17534: 'khor ni mos pa tha dad pa'i tshogs te 'gro ba drug dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17535: tshogs sbyor dang mthong lam pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17536: dus ni sgron ma bkod pa la sogs pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17537: bstan pa ni tshig gsungs te sde snod gsum mo //
NK124(ngo)001:17538: sdud pa po ni nges pa med de rang rang gi 'khor gyis dam pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17540: gang rgyun gyi zhing khams ni mos pa can no //
NK124(ngo)001:17541: 'khor ni mos pa tha dad pa'i tshogs /
NK124(ngo)001:17544: dus ni sgron ma yongs su bkod pa na'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17545: mdzad pa ni gang gis mun pa sel bar mdzad pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17549: gnas gcig nges med dgongs pas sprul //
NK124(ngo)001:17550: mos pa spyod pa'i 'khor rnams dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17551: sdul tshul rtsol bsgrubs 'khor rnams dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17552: sdul tshul rtsol bsgrubs bcad dus su //
NK124(ngo)001:17553: bstan pa mtshan nyid sde gsum ste //
NK124(ngo)001:17554: skus 'dul ming rtags la sogs mthun //
NK124(ngo)001:17556: rgyas pa khog dbub skabs su bshad pa ltar ro //
NK124(ngo)001:17558: zhing khams ni bde ba can no //
NK124(ngo)001:17559: gnas gsang ba yum gyi ba ga'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17560: 'khor ni dngos kyi rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang go phye ba ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17561: skyes bu blo ldan chags pa can no //
NK124(ngo)001:17562: dus ni gtsug tor 'khor lo bsgyur ba ste /
NK124(ngo)001:17565: stong nyid bde ba chen po'i don de gsang ba rgya mtsho' nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17567: gang gsang ba dam pa de'i zhing khams ni pad mo can no //
NK124(ngo)001:17568: 'khor ni rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs so //
NK124(ngo)001:17569: bstan pa ni gsang sngags gsang ba rgyal tshab nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17570: dus ni gtsug tor chen po 'khor lo bsgyur bas 'dod pas na /
NK124(ngo)001:17571: rgyal ba kun sku skrun par 'byor ba'i dus nyid do //
NK124(ngo)001:17573: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis dgongs pas dam pa'i the tshom gcod par mdzad do //
NK124(ngo)001:17576: stong nyid bde chen bstan pa'i gtso' //
NK124(ngo)001:17579: nam mkha' mtha' mnyam la sogs rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud sde rnams nas gsal lo //
NK124(ngo)001:17580: de ltar na sku lnga la mtho' dman dang bzang ngan yod dam med /
NK124(ngo)001:17581: yod na sku gzhan mthar thug gi sangs rgyas ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17582: rgyud gcig sangs rgyas pa'i dus kyi sku lnga la yang bzang ngan yod pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK124(ngo)001:17583: med na gcig gi 'khor gcig yin par 'gal lo zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:17584: mthar thug gi sku lnga la bzang ngan mtho' dman med la /
NK124(ngo)001:17585: 'og ma 'og ma'i sku gsum la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17586: mtho' dman yod par gsungs te /
NK124(ngo)001:17587: des na mthar thug gi sku la mtho' dman med pas /
NK124(ngo)001:17588: sku gzhan mthar thug gi sangs rgyas pas skyon med do //
NK124(ngo)001:17589: 'og ma sku gsum la sogs pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17591: 'khor du yod pa bshad pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17593: yang mthar thug gi sku lnga la khyad par med na /
NK124(ngo)001:17594: rang rang gi rgyal tshab kyis ston pa sku lnga dang khyad par yod pas /
NK124(ngo)001:17595: gong gi skyon gnyis las grol lo //
NK124(ngo)001:17596: de bzhin du 'og ma'i sku lnga dang gsum la
NK124(ngo)001:17597: sogs pa'ang rang rang gi sku la sogs la khyad
NK124(ngo)001:17598: par med la / 'og ma 'og ma dang khyad par yod cing /
NK124(ngo)001:17599: rang rang gis rgyal tshab byed pa'i ston pa dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17600: khyad par yod pa ni gong bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:17601: yang sku lnga'i ngo bo gcig gam mi gcig /
NK124(ngo)001:17602: gcig na gong gi skyon dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17603: sku lnga'i 'dul zhing la sogs pa tha dad pa'i skyon 'ong la /
NK124(ngo)001:17604: mi gcig na'ang gong gi skyon gnyis po de 'ong zhe na /
NK124(ngo)001:17605: spyir thugs rgyud tha dad sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17606: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK124(ngo)001:17607: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi skabs bzhin no //
NK124(ngo)001:17608: bye brag tu rgyud gcig sangs rgyas pa'i sku ni /
NK124(ngo)001:17609: ngo bo gcig la mtshon tshul tha dad pa yin te /
NK124(ngo)001:17610: de yang gdul bya'i snang ba dang mthun par sku rnam pa lnga snang yang /
NK124(ngo)001:17611: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed cing rgyud gcig pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17612: de'i skyon sel dang theg pa gong 'og gi bye
NK124(ngo)001:17613: brag la sogs pa ni gong bzhin du shes par
NK124(ngo)001:17614: bya'o // theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:17615: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:17616: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa gcig bsdus pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17617: sems nyid gnas lugs snying po'i mthar thug gis //
NK124(ngo)001:17618: don gyis khog dbub snang ba bzhi yi don //
NK124(ngo)001:17619: gol sgrib dmigs bsal theg pa'i shan 'byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:17620: la zlos rang grol mngon sum ston gyur pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:17621: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs nges don mthar thug 'dis //
NK124(ngo)001:17622: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsod nams mchog grub sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:17623: 'gro ba'i don phyir thugs bskyed ldan rnams kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:17624: yang yang bskul phyir bdag gis 'di sbyar te //
NK124(ngo)001:17625: de yang rang 'dod spang nas lhag bsam rnam dag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:17626: gzhan la phan phyin sems bskyed go cha yis //
NK124(ngo)001:17627: ma nor nges pa'i lam mchog bstan phyir du //
NK124(ngo)001:17628: theg pa'i shan 'byed man ngag 'di bsdus pas //
NK124(ngo)001:17629: 'gro mang srid mtsho'i gnas las bsgral phyir bkod //
NK124(ngo)001:17630: rgyal ba'i bka' dang bstan bcos man ngag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17631: mkhas pa'i kri ka gzhung mang rgya che yang //
NK124(ngo)001:17632: zab mo'i dgongs don bla ma'i zhal gdams la //
NK124(ngo)001:17633: legs par rtogs pa'i shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:17634: shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal zhes kyang bya //
NK124(ngo)001:17636: de bzhin bden gnyis drang nges dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17637: theg pa che chung mdo' sngags dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17638: gsang sngags phyi nang rgyud lung dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17639: man ngag la sogs bye brag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17640: de bzhin yin lugs snang lugs dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17641: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs la sogs pa'i //
NK124(ngo)001:17642: rnam grangs dbye' ba mang gsungs kyang //
NK124(ngo)001:17643: mdor bsdus cung zad bkod pa'o //
NK124(ngo)001:17644: bshes gnyen rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17645: nges don snying po'i phyogs su mos pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17646: ngag la nges 'dzin mched grogs dam pa rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:17647: sngon sbyangs rigs sad bstan pa'i sgor zhugs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:17648: ma nor lam gnas thos bsam don la brtson //
NK124(ngo)001:17649: 'di don rtogs shing bsgrub pa lhur len cing //
NK124(ngo)001:17650: shes bzhin bag yod chos la gzhol ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17651: dam tshig khrims ldan sdom gsum tshul bzhin bsrungs //
NK124(ngo)001:17652: legs spyod 'di don dgongs pa'i bcu da len mdzod //
NK124(ngo)001:17653: 'di nyid tshul bzhin spyod pa'i skyes bu rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:17654: skye ba 'di dang tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK124(ngo)001:17655: 'khor ba'i chos la yid 'byung skye gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:17656: skyabs gnas dkon mchog rtag tu bkur byas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17657: rgyu 'bras chos la blang dor byas nas ni //
NK124(ngo)001:17658: lha mi theg pa'i chos la spyod par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17659: der yang nges 'byung slab pa'i tshul bzung nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17660: dge snyen dge tshul dge slong byang chub sems //
NK124(ngo)001:17661: so so thar pa'i lam la gnas bcas nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17662: sa lam mthar phyin dgra bcom 'bras thob shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17663: smon 'jug lhag bsam theg chen sgor zhugs cing //
NK124(ngo)001:17664: las dang nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib byang nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17665: sa dang lam gyi yon tan kun rdzogs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17666: kun du 'od kyi sa la phyin par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17667: dag pa gsum gyis bstan pa'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17668: bskyed rdzogs bden gnyis dbyer med don rtogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:17669: zag bcas zag med dgongs pa mthar phyin cing //
NK124(ngo)001:17670: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la phyin par shog /'khor 'das dbyer med thabs shes sgor bzhugs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17671: bden gsum dbyer med snang srid chos skur 'char //
NK124(ngo)001:17672: bskyed rdzogs mthar phyin sku lnga mngon gyur te //
NK124(ngo)001:17673: 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la phyin par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17674: ka dag lhun grub dbyer med sgor zhugs te //
NK124(ngo)001:17675: sems nyid rang 'byung ye shes mngon 'gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17676: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ci bzhin rtsal rdzogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:17677: gdod ma'i sangs rgyas sa la phyin par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17678: de ltar smon pa'i dge ba ci mchis pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17679: mtha' yas sems can sgrib gnyis rab sbyangs nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17680: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yongs rdzogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:17681: mtha' yas sems can bde la 'god par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17682: dpal ldan bla ma rtag tu bkur byed cing //
NK124(ngo)001:17683: bla ma'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:17684: gnas lugs rang byung ye shes don rtogs shing //
NK124(ngo)001:17685: rang gzhan smin grol lam la 'god par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17686: sgo gsum khrims dang g.yo' zog skyon spang nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17687: slob dpon mchod la mos gus dag snang ldan //
NK124(ngo)001:17688: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i bsrungs mtshams rnams //
NK124(ngo)001:17689: gzhung bzhin ma nor tshul bzhin bsrungs bar shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17690: gnas skabs mthar thug dus rnams thams cad du //
NK124(ngo)001:17691: pha rol mi dang mi min thams cad kyi //
NK124(ngo)001:17692: bsam sbyor 'tshe ba'i gnod pa rab zhi zhing //
NK124(ngo)001:17693: bdag la rtag tu mthun rkyen byed par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17694: bdag la dad cing mos pa'i 'gro ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17695: dkar nag las dang chos dang 'brel gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17696: bdag gi gzugs kyis mthong tsam grol gyur nas //
NK124(ngo)001:17697: gnas ngan spang nas rtag tu bde thob shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17698: dus gsum sangs rgyas bstan pa dam pa'i chos //
NK124(ngo)001:17699: rang bzhin byang chub sems bka' brgyud bla ma dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17700: yi dam lha tshogs mkha' 'gro chos skyong sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:17701: bla ma dkon mchog rnams kyis bkra shis shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17702: phyogs dang dus dang gnas skabs kun du yang //
NK124(ngo)001:17703: sangs rgyas bstan pa yun du gnas pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17704: bla med theg chen yun du gnas pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17705: 'khor slob yon bdag bde zhing skyid pa yis //
NK124(ngo)001:17707: deng nas bzung ste dus rnams thams cad du //
NK124(ngo)001:17708: mi mthun gnod pa'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17709: dgongs spyod thams cad 'bad med lhun grub cing //
NK124(ngo)001:17710: bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17711: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed nyi 'od rab gsal las /
NK124(ngo)001:17712: mjug smon lam dang bcas pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:17713: bka' thams cad gsal bar ston par byed pa /
NK124(ngo)001:17714: bstan pa thams cad kyi spyi 'brel /
NK124(ngo)001:17715: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed /
NK124(ngo)001:17716: man ngag thams cad kyi dgongs don /
NK124(ngo)001:17717: sems kyis chos nyid mngon du rtogs pa'i me long /
NK124(ngo)001:17718: nyi 'od rab gsal zhes bya ba 'di /
NK124(ngo)001:17719: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis yang yang bskul ba'i ngor /
NK124(ngo)001:17720: sh+aakya'i btsun pa sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa /
NK124(ngo)001:17721: o rgyan pad ma'i rjes 'jug bla ma dge ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:17722: bshes gnyen mkhas grub du ma rnams kyi zhabs kyi
NK124(ngo)001:17724: pun+ya'i ming can bdag gis lcags pho stag gi lor /
NK124(ngo)001:17725: o rgyan rin po che'i bsgrub gnas /
NK124(ngo)001:17726: o rgyan rtse mor sbyar ba la /
NK124(ngo)001:17727: bka' gzhung 'gal dang tshig gi sdeb sbyor sogs //
NK124(ngo)001:17728: nongs pa mchis na 'phags pa rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK124(ngo)001:17729: rgyal ba'i bka' dang bla ma'i man ngag dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17730: mkhas grub rnams kyi bstan bcos dang /
NK124(ngo)001:17731: rang gi myong ba rnams la brten nas /
NK124(ngo)001:17732: theg pa dang mdo' sngags thams cad kyi shan 'byed /
NK124(ngo)001:17733: nyi 'od rab gsal zhes bya bar sbyar ba rdzogs so ////
NK124(ngo)001:17734: phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas par gyur cig /
NK124(ngo)001:17737: bkra shis dpal 'bar 'dzam gling brgyan du shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17739: 'jig rten mig gcig pu n+ya'i thugs bcud las //
NK124(ngo)001:17740: 'ong ba'i theg shan nyi 'od rab gsal 'di //
NK124(ngo)001:17741: mun pa'i gling du 'od stong 'phro na'ang //
NK124(ngo)001:17742: bdag dang bdag 'dra'i las ngan can rnams kyis //
NK124(ngo)001:17743: gdams ngag shog steng lus pa ma tshor bas //
NK124(ngo)001:17744: yin kyang gdul byas bskul ba'i sems can la //
NK124(ngo)001:17745: sangs rgyas dus las yol ba med gsung ltar //
NK124(ngo)001:17746: bshes gnyen dam pa slob dpon gnag mdog gi //
NK124(ngo)001:17747: de bzhin ma dpe g.yar po rtsol 'byung ba //
NK124(ngo)001:17748: bka' drin blo'i yul du ga la shong //
NK124(ngo)001:17749: mkhas mchog de la gus pas snying nas btud //
NK124(ngo)001:17750: sgyu ma'i nor la snying po len mkhas pa //
NK124(ngo)001:17751: gtong 'phod lhag bsam bzang po'i sbyin bdag gis //
NK124(ngo)001:17752: bka' yi gnang ba spyi bo'i gtsug blangs te //
NK124(ngo)001:17753: mon pa'i tha chung kun bzang stobs rgyal gyis //
NK124(ngo)001:17754: bzhengs nas dpar du bskrun pa'i dge ba 'dis //
NK124(ngo)001:17755: dpal ldan 'brug pa'i chab srid brtan pa dang //
NK124(ngo)001:17756: mnga' 'bangs bde skyid longs spyod ldan par shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17757: de'i 'thu las bdag sogs 'gro ba kun //
NK124(ngo)001:17758: snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i sa thob shog /
NK124(ngo)001:17759: ces pa'ang spyi lo chig stong dgu brgya bdun cu
NK124(ngo)001:17760: don dgu lo dang rab 'byung bcu drug pa'i nang
NK124(ngo)001:17761: 'phags yul rgyal sa ldi lir dpar du bskrun skabs
NK124(ngo)001:17762: las rogs o rgyan bstan 'dzin dang bsod nams stobs
NK124(ngo)001:17763: rgyal kun khyab bcas chos grogs gsum nas bskul ba'i
NK124(ngo)001:17764: ngor / yig bris pa rang nyid kyis smon mdun du bris pa'o ////
NK124(ngo)001:17765: ma dpe 'di a ri shes rab grags pas dge
NK124(ngo)001:17766: dpal rdor brgyud bskur ba bdag gi lag tu 'phrod
NK124(ngo)001:17767: byung / dpe rnying zhig yin la kahthoga pa bsod
NK124(ngo)001:17768: nams rgyal mtshan gyis 'brug spa gro stag tshang du
NK124(ngo)001:17769: mdzad pa zhu dag byed pa po slob dpon gnag
NK124(ngo)001:17770: mdog dpal ldan 'brug gzhung thim phu 1979zhes mchan zhig
NK124(ngo)001:17771: 'dug pa de las zhal bshus te thengs gnyis zhus
